# <a name="required-diagnostic-data-for-office"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-103">Obavezni dijagnostički podaci za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-103">Required diagnostic data for Office</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-104">Popis proizvoda sustava Office obuhvaćenih ovim informacijama o zaštiti privatnosti potražite u članku [kontrole zaštite privatnosti dostupne za proizvode sustava Office](products-versions-privacy-controls.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-104">For a list of Office products covered by this privacy information, see [Privacy controls available for Office products](products-versions-privacy-controls.md).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-105">Dijagnostički podaci koriste se da bi Office uvijek bio siguran i ažuran, kao i radi otkrivanja, dijagnosticiranja i rješavanja problema te poboljšavanja proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-105">Diagnostic data is used to keep Office secure and up-to-date, detect, diagnose and fix problems, and also make product improvements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-106">Ti podaci ne obuhvaćaju korisnikovo ime i prezime ni adresu e-pošte, sadržaj korisnikovih datoteka ni informacije o aplikacijama koje nisu povezane sa sustavom Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-106">This data does not include a user's name or email address, the content of the user's files, or information about apps unrelated to Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-107">Ovi dijagnostički podaci o klijentskom softveru sustava Office koji se pokreće na uređaju korisnika prikupljaju se i šalju Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-107">This diagnostic data is collected and sent to Microsoft about Office client software running on the user's device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-108">Neki su dijagnostički podaci obavezni, a neki nisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-108">Some diagnostic data is required, while some diagnostic data is optional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-109">Omogućujemo vam da odaberete hoćete li nam slati obavezne ili dijagnostičke podatke putem kontrola zaštite privatnosti, kao što su postavke pravila za tvrtke ili ustanove.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-109">We give you the ability to choose whether to send us required or optional diagnostic data through the use of privacy controls, such as policy settings for organizations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-110">Dijagnostičke podatke koji nam se šalju možete pogledati pomoću preglednika dijagnostičkih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-110">You can see the diagnostic data being sent to us by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-111">***Obavezni dijagnostički podaci*** minimalni su podaci potrebni da bi Office bio siguran i ažuran te da bi na uređaju na kojem je instaliran funkcionirao na očekivan način.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-111">***Required diagnostic data*** is the minimum data necessary to help keep Office secure, up-to-date, and performing as expected on the device it's installed on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-112">Obavezni dijagnostički podaci omogućuju da otkrijete probleme sa sustavom Office koji mogu biti povezani s konfiguracijom uređaja ili softvera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-112">Required diagnostic data helps to identify problems with Office that may be related to a device or software configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-113">Na primjer, pomoću njih možete utvrditi ruši li se značajka sustava Office češće u određenoj verziji operacijskog sustava, zbog tek uvedenih značajki ili kada se onemoguće određene značajke sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-113">For example, it can help determine if an Office feature crashes more frequently on a particular operating system version, with newly introduced features, or when certain Office features are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-114">Obavezni dijagnostički podaci omogućuju nam da otkrijemo, dijagnosticiramo i brže riješimo te probleme kako bi se smanjio utjecaj na korisnike ili tvrtke i ustanove.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-114">Required diagnostic data helps us detect, diagnose, and fix these problems more quickly so the impact to users or organizations is reduced.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-115">Dodatne informacije o dijagnostičkim podacima potražite u ovim člancima:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-115">For more information about diagnostic data, see the following articles:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-116">Neobavezni dijagnostički podaci za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-116">Optional diagnostic data for Office</span></span>](optional-diagnostic-data.md)

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-118">Ako ste administrator svoje organizacije,tvrtke ili ustanove možda će vas zanimati i sljedeći članci:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-118">If you're the admin for your organization, you might also be interested in the following articles:</span></span>

## <a name="categories-and-data-fields-that-are-common-for-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-167">Kategorije i podatkovna polja koja su zajednička svim događajima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-167">Categories and data fields that are common for all events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-168">Ovdje su i neke informacije koje se odnose na sve događaje, bez obzira na kategoriju ili podvrstu podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-168">There is some information about events that is common to all events, regardless of category or data subtype.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-169">Te opće informacije, koje se ponekad nazivaju *podatkovni ugovori*, organizirane su po kategorijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-169">This common information, which is sometimes referred to as *data contracts*, is organized into categories.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-170">Svaka kategorija sadrži polja, a ta su polja metapodaci i svojstva pojedinog događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-170">Each category contains fields, and these fields are the metadata and properties of an individual event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-171">Te podatke možete pogledati pomoću preglednika dijagnostičkih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-171">You can view this information by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-172">Kategorije podataka koji se prikupljaju o događajima mogu se podijeliti u dvije grupe:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-172">The categories of information that is collected about events can be divided into two groups:</span></span>

  - [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-173">Informacije zajedničke svim događajima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-173">Information common to all events</span></span>](#information-common-to-all-events)
  - [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-174">Informacije koje izričito podržavaju prikupljanje dijagnostičkih podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-174">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection</span></span>](#information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection)

### <a name="information-common-to-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-175">*Informacije zajedničke svim događajima*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-175">*Information common to all events*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-176">U sljedeće kategorije prikupljaju se informacije zajedničke svim događajima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-176">Information common to all events is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="app"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-177">Aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-177">App</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-178">Informacije o aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-178">Information about the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-179">Sva su polja konstante za sve sesije određene verzije navedene aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-179">All fields are constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-180">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-180">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-181">**Grana** ― grana iz koje dolazi navedena međuverzija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-181">**Branch** - The branch that the given build came from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-182">Omogućuje da utvrdimo iz koje vrste grane dolazi navedena međuverzija kako bismo ispravno usmjerili rješenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-182">Allows us to determine what type of branch a given build came from so that we can correctly target fixes.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-183">**InstallType** ― identifikator koji određuje način na koji je korisnik instalirao aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-183">**InstallType** - An enumerator that identifies how the user installed the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-184">Omogućuje da utvrdimo stvaraju li mehanizmi određene instalacije probleme kojih nema u mehanizmima drugih instalacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-184">Allows us to determine if specific install mechanisms are creating issues that are not seen in other installation mechanisms.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-185">**Naziv** ― naziv aplikacije koja daje podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-185">**Name** - The name of the application that is providing the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-186">Omogućuje prepoznavanje aplikacije s kojom se pojavljuje problem kako bismo ga znali riješiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-186">Allows us to identify which application is showing an issue so we know how to address it.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-187">**Platforma** ― općenita klasifikacija platforme na kojoj je pokrenuta aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-187">**Platform** - The broad classification of the platform on which the app is running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-188">Omogućuje da odredimo na kojim se platformama problem pojavljuje kako bismo mogli ispravno odrediti njegov prioritet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-188">Allows us to identify on which platforms an issue may be occurring so that we can correctly prioritize the issue.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-189">**Verzija** ― verzija aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-189">**Version** - The version of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-190">Omogućuje prepoznavanje verzija proizvoda s kojima se pojavljuje problem kako bismo mogli ispravno odrediti njegov prioritet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-190">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-212">**ServiceConnectionState** – označava je li korisnik odlučio koristiti ili ne koristiti sva povezana iskustva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-212">**ServiceConnectionState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to use or not use all connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-215">**ServiceConnectionStateSourceLocation** – označava način na koji je korisnik odlučio želi li koristiti sva povezana iskustva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-215">**ServiceConnectionStateSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user provided the choice whether to use all connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-216">**UserCategoryValue ―** određuje vrstu korisnika koji daje pristanak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-216">**UserCategoryValue –** Identified the type of user who made the consent.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-217">Jedan MSAUser, AADUser ili LocalDeviceUser</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-217">One of MSAUser, AADUser or LocalDeviceUser</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-218">**UserContentDependentSourceLocation** – označava kako je napravljen korisnikov odabir omogućivanja ili onemogućivanja povezanih iskustava koja analiziraju sadržaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-218">**UserContentDependentSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user's choice to enable or disable was made for connected experiences that analyze content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-232">**AppId** – vrijednost identifikatora koji označava aplikaciju koja šalje podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-232">**AppId** - An enumerator value representing which application is sending the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-233">Omogućuje prepoznavanje aplikacije s kojom se pojavljuje problem kako bismo ga znali riješiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-233">Allows us to identify which application is showing an issue so we know how to address it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-240">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-240">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-241">**Ciljna skupina** – označava segment određene grupe ciljnih skupina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-241">**Audience** - Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-242">Omogućuje da pratimo podskupove grupa ciljnih skupina za procjenu rasprostranjenosti i određivanja prioriteta problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-242">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-249">Sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-249">Session</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-250">Informacije o sesiji postupka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-250">Information about the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-251">Sva su polja konstante za ovu sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-251">All fields are constant for this session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-252">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-252">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-253">**ABConfigs** – označava skup međuverzija koje se izvode u određenoj sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-253">**ABConfigs** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-254">Omogućuje prepoznavanje pojedinačnih međuverzija koje se izvode u sesiji kako bismo utvrdili je li međuverzija izvor problema koji utječe na korisnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-254">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-255">**EcsETag** – pokazatelj iz sustava međuverzija koji predstavlja međuverzije poslane na računalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-255">**EcsETag** - An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-256">Omogućuje prepoznavanje međuverzija koje utječu na određenu sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-256">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-257">**Zastavice** – zastavice za praćenje bit-maske koje se odnose na cijelu sesiju, trenutno se uglavnom odnosi na uzorkovanje i mogućnosti dijagnostičkih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-257">**Flags** - Bitmask tracking flags applicable to an entire session, currently primarily focused on sampling and diagnostic data options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-258">Omogućuje kontrolu ponašanja određene sesije u odnosu prema dijagnostičkim podacima koje sesija generira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-258">Allows us to control how a given session behaves in relation to the diagnostic data that the session generates.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-259">**HostAppName** – označava naziv host aplikacije koja pokreće podaplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-259">**HostAppName** - Identifies the host app name that launches a sub-app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-260">Aplikacije kao što je Office Mobile (Android) mogu pokrenuti podaplikacije Word, Excel i PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-260">Apps like Office Mobile (Android) can launch Word, Excel, and PowerPoint sub-apps.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-261">Za takve pod-aplikacije glavna aplikacija je OfficeMobile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-261">For such sub-apps, the host app is OfficeMobile</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-262">**Hostsessioid** – jedinstveno prepoznaje sesiju host aplikacije za podaplikaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-262">**HostSessionId** - Uniquely identifies the host app session for a sub-app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-263">**ID** – jedinstveno označava određenu sesiju podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-263">**Id** - Uniquely identifies a given session of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-264">Omogućuje utvrđivanje utjecaja problema procjenom broja zahvaćenih sesija te postoje li zajedničke značajke tih sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-264">Allows us to identify the impact of issues by evaluating the number of sessions that are impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-265">**ImpressionId** – označava skup međuverzija koje se izvode u određenoj sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-265">**ImpressionId** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-266">Omogućuje prepoznavanje pojedinačnih međuverzija koje se izvode u sesiji kako bismo utvrdili je li međuverzija izvor problema koji utječe na korisnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-266">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-267">**MeasuresEnabled** – zastavica koja označava jesu li podaci trenutne sesije uzorkovani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-267">**MeasuresEnabled** - Flag indicating if the current sessions data is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-268">Omogućuje da utvrdimo kako statistički procijeniti podatke prikupljene iz određene sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-268">Allows us to determine how to statistically evaluate the data that is gathered from the given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-269">**SamplingClientIdValue** – ID klijenta kojim se utvrđuje je li dio uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-269">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The ID of the client used to determine if it is part of sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-270">Omogućuje da utvrdimo zašto je pojedinačna sesija uključena ili isključena iz uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-270">Allows us to determine why an individual session was included or excluded from sampling.</span></span>
  
 - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-271">**SubAppName** – za aplikaciju Office za mobilne uređaje ovo polje predstavlja temeljnu aplikaciju koja se koristi za otvaranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-271">**SubAppName** - For Office Mobile app, this field represents the underlying application being used to open a document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-272">Na primjer, ako otvorite dokument programa Word u aplikaciji Office, to polje će prijaviti vrijednost „Word“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-272">For example, if you open a Word document in Office app, this field will report the value of “Word”.</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-273">**VirtualizationType** – vrsta vizualizacije ako se Office izvodi u jednoj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-273">**VirtualizationType** - Type of virtualization if Office is running in one.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-274">Moguće vrijednosti su:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-274">The possible values are:</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-275">0 = Ništa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-275">0 = None</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-276">1 = Windows Virtual Desktop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-276">1 = Windows Virtual Desktop</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-277">2 = Microsoft Defender Application Guard</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-277">2 = Windows Defender Application Guard</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-278">3 = Windows Core OS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-278">3 = Windows Core OS</span></span>

#### <a name="user"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-279">Korisnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-279">User</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-280">Pruža informacije o klijentu za SKU-ove komercijalnog softvera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-280">Provides tenant information for commercial software SKUs.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-281">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-281">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-282">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – identifikator u obliku pseudonima koji predstavlja trenutnog korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-282">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-283">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – vrsta identiteta sadržana u identifikatoru PrimaryIdentityHash.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-283">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – The type of identity contained in the PrimaryIdentityHash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-284">MASCID, OrgIdCID ili UserObjectId.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-284">One of MASCID, OrgIdCID or UserObjectId.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-285">**TenantGroup** – vrsta klijenta kojem pripada pretplata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-285">**TenantGroup** - The type of the tenant that the subscription belongs to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-286">Omogućuje klasifikaciju problema i utvrđivanje je li problem rasprostranjen ili ograničen na skup korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-286">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-287">**TenantId** – klijent s kojim je povezana pretplata korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-287">**TenantId** - The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-288">Omogućuje klasifikaciju problema i utvrđivanje je li problem rasprostranjen ili ograničen na skup korisnika ili određenog klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-288">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

### <a name="information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-289">*Informacije koje izričito podržavaju prikupljanje dijagnostičkih podataka*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-289">*Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-290">Informacije koje izričito podržavaju prikupljanje dijagnostičkih podataka prikupljaju se u sljedećim kategorijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-290">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="activity"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-291">Aktivnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-291">Activity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-292">Informacije za shvaćanje uspješnosti samog događaja prikupljanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-292">Information to understand the success of the collection event itself.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-293">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-293">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-294">**AggMode** – govori sustavu kako prikupiti rezultate aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-294">**AggMode** - Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-295">Omogućuje nam smanjenje količine podataka prenesenih s korisnikova računala prikupljanjem rezultata aktivnosti u jedan događaj koji se šalje povremeno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-295">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user's machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-296">**Count** – broj izvršavanja aktivnosti ako je broj iz skupnog događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-296">**Count** - The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-297">Omogućuje da odredimo koliko je često aktivnost uspjela na temelju načina prikupljanja aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-297">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-298">**CV** – vrijednost koja određuje odnos između aktivnosti i segmenata aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-298">**CV** - A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-299">Omogućuje ponovno stvaranje odnosa između ugniježđenih aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-299">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-300">**Trajanje** – vrijeme potrebno za izvršavanje aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-300">**Duration** - The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-301">Omogućuje prepoznavanje problema s performansama koji negativno utječu na korisničko okruženje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-301">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the user's experience.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-302">**Rezultat** – kôd koji je definirala aplikacija za prepoznavanje određenog rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-302">**Result.Code** - An application defined code to identify a given result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-303">Omogućuje da utvrdimo specifične pojedinosti o određenoj pogrešci, primjerice kod pogreške koji može se koristiti za klasifikaciju i rješavanje problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-303">Allows us to determine more specific details of a given failure such as a failure code that can be used to classify and fix issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-304">**Result.Tag** – oznaka cijelog broja koja označava mjesto u kodu u kojem je generiran rezultat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-304">**Result.Tag** - An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the result was generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-305">Omogućuje jasno utvrđivanje mjesta u kodu na kojem je rezultat generiran što omogućuje klasifikaciju pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-305">Allows us to distinctly identify the location in code where a result was generated which enables classification of failures.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-306">**Result.Type** – vrsta koda rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-306">**Result.Type** - The type of the result code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-307">Određuje vrstu poslanog koda rezultata kako bi se vrijednost ispravno tumačila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-307">Identifies what type of result code was sent so that the value can be correctly interpreted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-308">**Uspjeh** – zastavica koja označava je li aktivnost uspjela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-308">**Success** - A flag indicating if the activity succeeded or failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-309">Omogućuje da utvrdimo uspijevaju li radnje koje korisnik izvršava u proizvodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-309">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-310">Time se omogućuje prepoznavanje problema koji utječu na korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-310">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

#### <a name="application"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-311">Aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-311">Application</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-312">Informacije o instalaciji aplikacije iz koje se prikupljaju događaji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-312">Information about the installation of the application from which the events are being gathered.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-313">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-313">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-314">**Arhitektura** – arhitektura aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-314">**Architecture** - The architecture of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-315">Omogućuje nam da klasificiramo pogreške koje mogu biti specifične za arhitekturu aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-315">Let's us classify errors that might be specific to an architecture of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-316">**Click2RunPackageVersion** – broj verzije paketa Klikom do cilja koji je instalirao aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-316">**Click2RunPackageVersion** - The version number of the Click-To-Run package that installed the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-317">Omogućuje nam da identificiramo verziju programa za instalaciju koja je korištena za instalaciju sustava Office kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme povezane s postavljanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-317">Allows us to identify which version of the installer was used to install Office so we can identify setup-related issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-318">**DistributionChannel** – kanal u kojem je aplikacija implementirana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-318">**DistributionChannel** - The channel where the app was deployed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-319">Omogućuje da podijelimo dolazne podatke kako bismo utvrdili utječu li problemi na ciljne skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-319">Allows us to partition incoming data so we can determine if issues are impacting audiences.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-320">**InstallMethod** – određuje je li sustav nadograđen na trenutnu međuverziju sustava Office sa starije međuverzije, vraćen na nju ili je u pitanju nova instalacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-320">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from an older build, rolled back to an older build, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-321">**IsClickToRunInstall** – zastavica koja označava radi li se o instalaciji „klikom do cilja“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-321">**IsClickToRunInstall** - Flag indicating if install was a click to run install.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-322">Omogućuje da prepoznamo probleme koji mogu biti specifični za mehanizam instalacije Klikom do cilja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-322">Allows us to identify issues that might be specific to the Click-To-Run install mechanism.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-323">**IsDebug** – zastavica koja označava radi li se o međuverziji sustava Office za ispravljanje pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-323">**IsDebug** - Flag indicating if the Office build is a Debug build.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-324">Omogućuje nam da utvrdimo dolaze li problemi iz verzija za uklanjanje pogrešaka, koje se mogu ponašati drugačije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-324">Allows us to identify if issues are coming from Debug builds, which may behave differently.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-325">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** – zastavica koja označava je li Office instaliran na vanjskom uređaju za pohranu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-325">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** - Flag indicating if Office was installed on an external storage device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-326">Omogućuje nam da odredimo mogu li se problemi povezati s mjestom za vanjsku pohranu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-326">Let's us determine if issues can be traced to an external storage location.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-327">**IsOEMInstalled** – zastavica koja označava je li Office instalirao proizvođač originalne opreme (OEM).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-327">**IsOEMInstalled** - Flag indicating if Office was installed by an original equipment manufacturer (OEM).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-328">Omogućuje nam da odredimo je li aplikaciju instalirao OEM, što nam može pomoći u klasificiranju i identificiranju problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-328">Let's us determine if the application was installed by an OEM, which can help us classify and identify issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-329">**PreviousVersion** – verzija sustava Office koja je već instalirana na računalu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-329">**PreviousVersion** - The version of Office that was previously installed on the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-330">Omogućuje da se vratimo na prethodnu verziju ako postoji problem s trenutnom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-330">Allows us to roll back to a previous version if the current one has an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-331">**ProcessFileName** – naziv datoteke aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-331">**ProcessFileName** - The name of the application filename.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-332">Omogućuje prepoznavanje naziva izvršne datoteke koja generira podatke jer može postojati nekoliko različitih naziva datoteka procesa koji izvještavaju s istim nazivom aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-332">Allows us to identify the name of the executable that is generating the data as there may be several different process filenames reporting as the same app name.</span></span>

#### <a name="client"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-333">Klijent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-333">Client</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-334">Informacije o klijentu sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-334">Information about the Office client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-335">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-335">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-336">**FirstRunTime** – prvo pokretanje klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-336">**FirstRunTime** - The first time the client was run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-337">Omogućuje da utvrdimo koliko je dugo sustav Office instaliran na klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-337">Allows us to understand how long the client has had Office installed.</span></span>

#### <a name="device"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-338">Uređaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-338">Device</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-339">Informacije o konfiguraciji i mogućnostima uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-339">Information about device configuration and capabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-340">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-340">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-341">**DigitizerInfo** – informacije o digitalizatoru koji računalo koristi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-341">**DigitizerInfo** - Information on the digitizer used by the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-342">Omogućuje da klasificiramo podatke na temelju središnjeg mehanizma uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-342">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-343">**FormFactor** – utvrđuje format hardvera uređaja koji šalje podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-343">**FormFactor** - Identifies what form factor the device sending the info is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-344">Omogućuje da klasificiramo podatke na temelju središnjeg mehanizma uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-344">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-345">**FormFactorFamily** – utvrđuje format hardvera uređaja koji šalje podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-345">**FormFactorFamily** - Identifies what form factor the device sending the info is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-346">Omogućuje da klasificiramo podatke na temelju središnjeg mehanizma uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-346">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

#### <a name="event"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-391">Događaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-391">Event</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-392">Informacije specifične za događaj, uključujući njegov jedinstveni identifikator u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-392">Event-specific information, including its unique identifier in the session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-393">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-393">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-394">**Ugovor** – popis svih ugovora koje događaj implementira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-394">**Contract** - A list of any contracts that the event is implementing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-395">Omogućuje da procijenimo koji su podaci dio pojedinačnog događaja kako bismo ih mogli učinkovito obraditi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-395">Allows us to evaluate what data is part of the individual event so that we can process it effectively.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-396">**CV** – vrijednost koja omogućuje prepoznavanje povezanih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-396">**CV** - A value that allows us to identify events that are related to one another.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-397">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kako bismo prepoznali uzorke povezanog ponašanja ili povezanih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-397">Used for diagnostics to allow us to identify patterns of related behavior or related events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-398">**Zastavice** – informacije koje se koriste za promjenu načina na koji događaj odgovara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-398">**Flags** - Information used to alter how a given event responds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-399">Koristi se za upravljanje načinom na koji se događaj tretira radi prijenosa podataka Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-399">Used to manage how a given event is treated for the purposes of uploading the data to Microsoft.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-400">**Id** – jedinstveni identifikator za događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-400">**Id** - A unique identifier for the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-401">Omogućuje jedinstveno identificiranje primljenih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-401">Allows us to uniquely identify the events that are being received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-402">**Level** – označava vrstu događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-402">**Level** - denotes the type of event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-403">**Naziv** – naziv događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-403">**Name** - The name of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-404">Omogućuje nam prepoznavanje događaja koji šalje klijent.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-404">Allows us to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-405">**Pravilo** – identifikator pravila koje je generiralo podatke ako ih je generiralo pravilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-405">**Rule** - An identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-406">Omogućuje prepoznavanje izvora dijela podataka tako da možemo provjeriti parametre tog događaja i njima upravljati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-406">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-407">**RuleId** – identifikator pravila koje je generiralo podatke ako ih je generiralo pravilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-407">**RuleId** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-408">Omogućuje prepoznavanje izvora dijela podataka tako da možemo provjeriti parametre tog događaja i njima upravljati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-408">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-409">**RuleInterfaces** – sučelja koja određeno pravilo implementira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-409">**RuleInterfaces** - Any interfaces that are implemented by the specific rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-410">Omogućuje nam klasificiranje i uvoz podataka na temelju njihove strukture, što pojednostavljuje obradu podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-410">Allows us to classify and import the data based on its structure, which simplifies data processing.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-411">**RuleVersion** – identifikator pravila koje je generiralo podatke ako ih je generiralo pravilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-411">**RuleVersion** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-412">Omogućuje prepoznavanje izvora dijela podataka tako da možemo provjeriti parametre tog događaja i njima upravljati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-412">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-413">**SampleRate** – oznaka koliki postotak korisnika šalje ovaj dio podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-413">**SampleRate** - An indication of what percentage of users are sending this piece of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-414">Time se omogućuje statistička analiza podataka i veoma česte točke podataka ne zahtijevaju da to šalju svi korisnici.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-414">This allows us to do statistical analysis of the data and for very common data points not require that to be sent by all users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-415">**SchemaVersion** – verzija sheme koja se koristi za generiranje dijagnostičkih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-415">**SchemaVersion** - The version of the schema used to generate diagnostic data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-416">Obavezno za upravljanje podacima koje šalje klijent.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-416">Required to manage data being sent from the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-417">Time se omogućuju promjene podataka koje šalje svaki klijent tijekom vremena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-417">This allows changes over time in what data is being sent from each client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-418">**Slijed** – brojač koji navodi redoslijed kojim je događaj generiran na klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-418">**Sequence** - A counter that identifies the order that an event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-419">Omogućuje numeriranje primljenih podataka kako bismo prepoznali korake koji su doveli do problema koji utječe na klijente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-419">Allows the data being received to be ordered so that we can identify what steps may have led to an issue that is impacting clients.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-420">**Izvor** – izvorni kanal upotrijebljen za prijenos podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-420">**Source** - The source pipeline that was used to upload the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-421">Obavezno za praćenje svih kanala za prijenos radi ukupnog stanja i prepoznavanja problema s kanalom za prijenos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-421">Required to monitor each of our upload pipelines for overall health and to help identify issues with the upload pipeline.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-422">Time se omogućuje praćenje pojedinačnih kanala za prijenos kako bi bili usklađeni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-422">This allows us to monitor individual upload pipelines to make sure they remain compliant.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-423">**Vrijeme** – vrijeme generiranja događaja na klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-423">**Time** - The time that the event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-424">Omogućuje sinkroniziranje i provjeru valjanosti redoslijeda događaja generiranih na klijentu i uspostavu parametara za mjerenje performansi za korisničke upute.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-424">Allows us to synchronize and validate the order of events generated on the client and establish performance metrics for user instructions.</span></span>

#### <a name="legacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-431">Starije verzije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-431">Legacy</span></span>
