<span data-ttu-id="8046f-433">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-433">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-434">**OsBuild** – broj određene međuverzije operacijskog sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-434">**OsBuild** - The specific build number of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-435">Omogućuje da utvrdimo iz koje verzije operacijskog sustava potječu dijagnostički podaci kako bismo odredili prioritete problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-435">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-436">**OsBuildRevision** – broj revizije međuverzije operacijskog sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-436">**OsBuildRevision** - The revision number of the build of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-437">Omogućuje da utvrdimo iz koje verzije operacijskog sustava potječu dijagnostički podaci kako bismo odredili prioritete problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-437">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-438">**OsMinorVersion** – sporedna verzija operacijskog sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-438">**OsMinorVersion** - The minor version of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-439">Omogućuje da utvrdimo iz koje verzije operacijskog sustava potječu dijagnostički podaci kako bismo odredili prioritete problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-439">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-440">**OsVersionString** – sjedinjeni niz koji predstavlja broj međuverzije operacijskog sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-440">**OsVersionString** - A unified string representing the operating system build number.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-441">Omogućuje da utvrdimo iz koje verzije operacijskog sustava potječu dijagnostički podaci kako bismo odredili prioritete problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-441">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-442">Sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-442">Session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-443">Informacije o sesiji postupka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-443">Information about the process session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-444">Ova kategorija sadrži sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-444">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-445">**ABConfigsDelta** – prati razliku između aktualnih podataka ABConfigs i prethodne vrijednosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-445">**ABConfigsDelta** - Tracks the difference between the current ABConfigs data and the previous value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-446">Omogućuje praćenje novih međuverzija na računalu da bismo lakše otkrili je li nova međuverzija odgovorna za problem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-446">Allows us to track what new flights are on the machine to help identify if a new flight is responsible for an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-447">**CollectibleClassification** – klase informacija koje sesija može prikupiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-447">**CollectibleClassification** - The classes of information the session can collect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-448">Omogućuje filtriranje sesija na temelju podataka koje imaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-448">Allows filtering of sessions based on the data they would have.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-449">**DisableTelemetry** – zastavica koja označava je li ključ DisableTelemetry postavljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-449">**DisableTelemetry** - Flag indicating if the DisableTelemetry key is set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-450">Omogućuje da utvrdimo je li sesija izvješćivala dijagnostičke podatke koji nisu EssentialServiceMetadata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-450">Allows us to know if a session was not reporting diagnostic data other than EssentialServiceMetadata.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-451">**SamplingClientIdValue** – vrijednost ključa za određivanje uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-451">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-452">Omogućuje da utvrdimo zašto je sesija uzorkovana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-452">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-453">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** – vrijednost ključa za određivanje uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-453">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-454">Omogućuje da utvrdimo zašto je sesija uzorkovana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-454">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-455">**SamplingKey** – ključ koji određuje je li sesija uzorkovana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-455">**SamplingKey** - The key used to determine whether the session is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-456">Omogućuje da utvrdimo kako pojedine sesije odlučuju hoće li biti uzorkovane.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-456">Allows us to understand how individual sessions are making their choice of whether they are sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-457">**SamplingMethod** – metoda koja se koristi za utvrđivanje pravila uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-457">**SamplingMethod** - The method used to determine sampling policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-458">Omogućuje da utvrdimo koji podaci dolaze iz sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-458">Allows us to understand what data is coming from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-459">**SamplingSessionKValue** – napredni metapodaci uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-459">**SamplingSessionKValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-460">Koristi se za procjenu statističkog značenja primljenih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-460">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-461">**SamplingSessionNValue** – napredni metapodaci uzorkovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-461">**SamplingSessionNValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-462">Koristi se za procjenu statističkog značenja primljenih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-462">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-463">**Slijed** – jedinstveni numerički identifikator za sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-463">**Sequence** - A unique numeric identifier for the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-464">Omogućuje određivanje redoslijeda sesija za analizu problema koji su se pojavili.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-464">Allows the ordering of sessions for analysis of the issues might have occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-465">**Pokretanje** – vrijeme pokretanja sesije postupka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-465">**Start** - The boot time of the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-466">Omogućuje da utvrdimo kada je sesija pokrenuta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-466">Allows us to establish when the session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-467">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** – vrijednost koja označava razinu dijagnostičkih podataka koje je korisnik odabrao.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-467">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** - Value indicating what level of diagnostic data the user has opted into.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-468">Omogućuje da utvrdimo razinu dijagnostičkih podataka koja se može očekivati od sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-468">Allows us to understand what level of diagnostic data to expect from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-469">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** – razlika u minutama između UTC-a i lokalnog vremena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-469">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** - The difference in minutes between UTC and the local time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-470">Omogućuje normalizaciju UTC-a na lokalno vrijeme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-470">Allows normalization of UTC times back to the local time.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-onenote-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-471">Polja podataka koja su uobičajena za događaje aplikacije OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-471">Data fields that are common for OneNote events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-472">Sljedeća polja podataka uobičajena su za sve događaje za aplikaciju OneNote na sustavima Mac, iOS i Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-472">The following data fields are common for all events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-473">Kada koristite preglednik dijagnostičkih podataka, događaji za aplikaciju OneNote na sustavima Mac, iOS i Android prikazivat će se kao da imaju naziv Aktivnost, Podaci o izvješću ili Neočekivano.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-473">When using the Diagnostic Data Viewer, events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android will appear to have a name of Activity, ReportData, or Unexpected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-474">Da biste pronašli stvarni naziv događaja, odaberite događaj, a zatim pogledajte polje EventName.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-474">To find the actual event name, select the event, and then look at the EventName field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-475">**Activity_ActivityType** – označava vrstu događaja u ovoj aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-475">**Activity_ActivityType** -  Indicates the type of this activity event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-476">Aktivnost može biti normalna aktivnost ili aktivnost visoke vrijednosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-476">An activity can be a normal activity or a high value activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-477">**Activity_AggMode** – govori sustavu kako prikupiti rezultate aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-477">**Activity_AggMode** -  Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-478">Omogućuje nam smanjenje količine podataka prenesenih s korisnikova računala prikupljanjem rezultata aktivnosti u jedan događaj koji se šalje povremeno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-478">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user's machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-479">**Activity_Count** – broj izvršavanja aktivnosti ako je broj iz skupnog događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-479">**Activity_Count** -  The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-480">Omogućuje da odredimo koliko je često aktivnost uspjela na temelju načina prikupljanja aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-480">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-481">**Activity_CV** – vrijednost koja određuje iznos između aktivnosti i segmenata aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-481">**Activity_CV** -  A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-482">Omogućuje ponovno stvaranje odnosa između ugniježđenih aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-482">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-483">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** – vrijeme tijekom kojeg je aktivnost neaktivna te ne obavlja nikakav stvaran rad, no to se vrijeme i dalje uračunava u ukupno vrijeme aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-483">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time an activity is idle and not doing any real work, but the time is still count towards the total activity's time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-484">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** – vrijeme potrebno za izvršavanje aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-484">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-485">Omogućuje prepoznavanje problema s performansama koji negativno utječu na korisničko okruženje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-485">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the user's experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-486">**Activity_Expiration** – datum u brojčanom obliku označava kada će se ovaj događaj prestati slati putem korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-486">**Activity_Expiration** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-487">**Activity_FailCount** – koliko je puta ova aktivnost bila neuspješna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-487">**Activity_FailCount** -  The number of times this activity has failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-488">**Activity_Name** – kratki naziv događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-488">**Activity_Name** -  A short name of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-489">Omogućuje nam prepoznavanje događaja koji šalje klijent.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-489">Allows us to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-490">**Activity_Namespace** – prostor naziva događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-490">**Activity_Namespace** -  A namespace of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-491">Omogućuje nam grupiranje događaja u grupe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-491">Allows us to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-492">**Activity_Reason** – niz koji označava razlog koji uzrokuje završavanje aktivnosti s određenim rezultatom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-492">**Activity_Reason** -  A string indicating the reason causing an activity to ends with a particular result.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-493">**Activity_Result** – zastavica koja označava je li aktivnost uspjela, nije uspjela ili neočekivano nije uspjela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-493">**Activity_Result** -  A flag indicating if the activity succeeded, failed, or unexpectedly failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-494">Omogućuje da utvrdimo uspijevaju li radnje koje korisnik izvršava u proizvodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-494">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-495">Time se omogućuje prepoznavanje problema koji utječu na korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-495">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-496">**Activity_State** – zastavica označava je li događaj početak aktivnosti korisnika ili završetak aktivnosti korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-496">**Activity_State** -  A flag indicates whether an event is a start of a user activity or an end of a user activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-497">**Activity_SucceedCount** – koliko je puta ova aktivnost bila uspješna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-497">**Activity_SucceedCount** -  The number of times this activity succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-498">**ErrorCode** – označava šifru pogreške ako je dostupna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-498">**ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-499">**ErrorCode2** – označava drugu šifru pogreške ako je dostupna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-499">**ErrorCode2** -  Indicates a second error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-500">**ErrorCode3** – označava treću šifru pogreške ako je dostupna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-500">**ErrorCode3** -  Indicates a third error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-501">**ErrorTag** – označava oznaku povezanu s kodom pogreške ako je dostupna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-501">**ErrorTag** -  Indicates the tag associated in code of an error if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-502">**ErrorType** – označava vrstu pogreške ako je dostupna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-502">**ErrorType** -  Indicates the type of an error if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-503">**EventName** – jedinstven naziv događaja aplikacije OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-503">**EventName** -  A unique name of a OneNote's event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-504">Događaji u aplikaciji OneNote koriste ovo prilagođeno polje kako bi odredili jedinstven naziv zbog inženjerskog ograničenja u prošlosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-504">OneNote events use this custom field to specify a unique name due to an engineering limitation in the past.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-505">**ExpFeatures** – označava je li korisnik uključio prekidač za pokusnu značajku u aplikaciji OneNote ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-505">**ExpFeatures** -  Indicates whether a user has turn-on an experimental-feature switch in OneNote app or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-506">**ExpirationDate** – datum u brojčanom obliku označava kada će se ovaj događaj prestati slati putem korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-506">**ExpirationDate** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-507">**IsConsumer** – označava je li korisnik potrošač ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-507">**IsConsumer** -  Indicates whether a user is consumer or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-508">**IsEdu** – označava je li korisnik ujedno korisnik u obrazovnoj ustanovi ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-508">**IsEdu** -  Indicates whether a user is a user in education tenant or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-509">**IsIW** – označava je li korisnik ujedno korisnik iz velike tvrtke ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-509">**IsIW** -  Indicates whether a user is an enterprise user or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-510">**IsMsftInternal** – označava je li korisnik Microsoftov zaposlenik ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-510">**IsMsftInternal** -  Indicates whether a user is a Microsoft employee or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-511">**IsPremiumUser** – označava ima li korisnik licencu za Premium ili nema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-511">**IsPremiumUser** -  Indicates whether a user has premium license or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-512">**Namespace** – prostor naziva događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-512">**Namespace** -  A namespace of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-513">Omogućuje nam grupiranje događaja u grupe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-513">Allows us to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-514">**Release_AppStore** – zastavica označava dolazi li međuverzija iz trgovine aplikacija ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-514">**Release_AppStore** -  A flag indicates whether a build is coming from an app store or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-515">**Release_Audience** – označava segment određene grupe ciljnih skupina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-515">**Release_Audience** -  Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-516">Omogućuje da pratimo podskupove grupa ciljnih skupina za procjenu rasprostranjenosti i određivanja prioriteta problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-516">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-517">**Release_AudienceGroup** – označava krug iz kojeg potječu podaci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-517">**Release_AudienceGroup** -  Identifies the ring where data is coming from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-518">Omogućuje postupno uvođenje značajki i prepoznavanje potencijalnih problema prije nego što dođu do većine korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-518">Allows us to roll out features in a staged fashion and identify potential issues before they reach most users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-519">**Release_Channel** – kanal putem kojeg se izdaje proizvod.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-519">**Release_Channel** -  The channel that the product is being released through.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-520">Omogućuje da odredimo utječe li problem na jedan od naših kanala za uvođenje drugačije od drugih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-520">Allows us to identify if an issue is impacting one of our rollout channels differently than others.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-521">**RunningMode** – označava kako je aplikacija pokrenuta bilo putem korisnika ili procesa sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-521">**RunningMode** -  Indicates how the app is launched either by user or by system process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-522">**SchemaVersion** – označava trenutnu verziju telemetrijske sheme u telemetrijskom cjevovodu aplikacije OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-522">**SchemaVersion** -  Indicates a current telemetry schema version in OneNote's telemetry pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-523">**Session_EcsETag** – pokazatelj iz sustava međuverzija koji predstavlja međuverzije poslane na računalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-523">**Session_EcsETag** -  An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-524">Omogućuje prepoznavanje međuverzija koje utječu na određenu sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-524">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-525">**Session_ImpressionId** – označava skup međuverzija koje se izvode u određenoj sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-525">**Session_ImpressionId** -  Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-526">Omogućuje prepoznavanje pojedinačnih međuverzija koje se izvode u sesiji kako bismo utvrdili je li međuverzija izvor problema koji utječe na korisnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-526">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-527">**SessionCorrelationId** – globalno jedinstveni identifikator za sesiju glavnog računala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-527">**SessionCorrelationId** -  The globally unique identifier for the host's session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-528">**SH_ErrorCode** – označava šifru pogreške ako je dostupna tijekom neuspješne aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-528">**SH_ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available when an activity fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-529">**Tag** – oznaka cijelog broja koja označava mjesto u kodu u kojem je generiran telemetrijski događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-529">**Tag** -  An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the telemetry event is generated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-530">**UserInfo_IdType** – niz označava vrstu korisnikova računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-530">**UserInfo_IdType** -  A string indicates the type of a user's account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-531">**UserInfo_OMSTenantId** – klijent s kojim je povezana pretplata korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-531">**UserInfo_OMSTenantId** -  The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-532">Omogućuje klasifikaciju problema i utvrđivanje je li problem rasprostranjen ili ograničen na skup korisnika ili određenog klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-532">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-533">**UserInfo_OtherId** – popis identifikatora u obliku pseudonima koji nisu primarni predstavlja korisnikove račune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-533">**UserInfo_OtherId** -  A list of non-primary pseudonymous identifiers representing user's accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-534">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** – popis vrsta računa koji nisu primarni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-534">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** -  A list of non-primary account types.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-outlook-mobile-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-535">Polja podataka koja su uobičajena za događaje aplikacije Outlook</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-535">Data fields that are common for Outlook mobile events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-536">Outlook Mobile prikuplja uobičajena polja za svaki naš događaj da bismo mogli osigurati da je aplikacija ažurna, sigurna i funkcionalna kao što se očekuje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-536">Outlook mobile collects common fields for each of our events so that we can ensure the app is up-to-date, secure, and functioning as expected.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-537">Sljedeća polja podataka uobičajena su za sve događaje za aplikaciju Outlook na sustavima iOS i Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-537">The following data fields are common for all events for Outlook for iOS and Android.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-538">**aad_tenant_id** – ID klijenta korisnika ako je dostupan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-538">**aad_tenant_id** - The tenant ID of the customer if available</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-539">**account_cid** – identifikator u obliku pseudonima koji predstavlja trenutačnog korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-539">**account_cid** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-540">**account_domain** – naziv domene računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-540">**account_domain** - Domain name of the account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-541">**account_puid** – globalno jedinstveni identifikator korisnika za Microsoftov potrošački račun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-541">**account_puid** - The globally unique user identifier for a consumer Microsoft account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-542">**account_type** – prati vrstu računa kao što je Office 365, Google Cloud Cache, Outlook.com itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-542">**account_type** - Tracks the account type such as Office 365, Google Cloud Cache, Outlook.com, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-543">**action** – naziv radnje događaja (kao što je arhiva, brisanje itd.) tako da možemo otkriti poteškoće sa specifičnim radnjama koje su poduzete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-543">**action** - The event action name (such as archive, delete, etc.) so we can detect issues with specific actions taken</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-544">**ad_id** – jedinstveni identifikator oglašavanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-544">**ad_id** - The unique advertising identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-545">**app_version** – trenutačna instalirana verzija aplikacije koja nam pomaže otkriti probleme koji utječu na određenu verziju aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-545">**app_version** - Current version of the app installed to help us detect issues affecting certain app version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-546">**AppInfo.ETag** – jedinstven identifikator za upravljanje izdanjima naših značajki kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme koji utječu na određene značajke koje se objavljuju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-546">**AppInfo.ETag** - A unique identifier for managing release of our features to help us detect issues affecting certain features being released</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-547">**AppInfo.Language** – trenutačna jezična postavka uređaja koja nam omogućuje otkrivanje problema koji utječu na određene jezike</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-547">**AppInfo.Language** - Currently language setting of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain languages</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-548">**AppInfo.Version** – trenutačna verzija instalirane verzije s pomoću koje otkrivamo probleme koji utječu na određene verzije aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-548">**AppInfo.Version** - Current version of the app installed to help us detect issues affecting certain app versions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-549">**ci** – identifikator u obliku pseudonima koji predstavlja identifikatora specifičnog za uređaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-549">**ci** - a pseudonymous app-specific device unique identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-550">**cid_type** – označava koja je vrsta računa, npr. poslovni račun ili račun za Outlook.com.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-550">**cid_type** - indicates what type of account it is, such as a commercial account or Outlook.com account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-551">**cloud** – mjesto gdje se poštanski sandučić nalazi za račun na ovom uređaju kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za oblak specifičnog poštanskog sandučića, poput sustava Office 365 ili GCC.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-551">**cloud** - Where the mailbox resides for the account on this device to help detect issues specific to a specific mailbox cloud, like Office 365 or GCC.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-552">**customer_type** – označava vrstu korisnika (potrošač, komercijalni korisnik, treća strane itd.) kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme koji utječu na određene vrste korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-552">**customer_type** - Indicates the type of customer (consumer, commercial, third party, etc.) to help us detect issues affecting certain customer types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-553">**device_category** – označava vrstu uređaja (telefon, tablet itd.) kako bismo lakše prepoznali specifične probleme kategorije uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-553">**device_category** - Indicates what type of device it is (phone, tablet, etc.) to help us detect device category-specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-554">**DeviceInfo.Id** – jedinstven identifikator uređaja s pomoću kojeg lakše otkrivamo specifične probleme uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-554">**DeviceInfo.Id** - A unique device identifier to help us detect device-specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-555">**DeviceInfo.Make** – marka uređaja (tj. Apple, Samsung itd.) kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme specifične za marku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-555">**DeviceInfo.Make** - The make of the device (for example, Apple, Samsung, etc.) to help us detect device make specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-556">**DeviceInfo.Model** – model uređaja (npr. iPhone 6s) kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme specifične za model</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-556">**DeviceInfo.Model** - The device model (for example, iPhone 6s) to help us detect device model specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-557">**DeviceInfo.NetworkType** – trenutačna mreža uređaja koja se upotrebljava (Wi-Fi, mobilna itd.) kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme specifične za mrežu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-557">**DeviceInfo.NetworkType** - The current device network being used (WiFi, cellular, etc.) to help us detect device network specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-558">**DeviceInfo.OsBuild** – trenutačna međuverzija OS-a uređaja kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme koji utječu na određene međuverzije OS-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-558">**DeviceInfo.OsBuild** - The current OS build of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain OS builds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-559">**DeviceInfo.OsName** – naziv OS-a (npr. iOS) kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme koji utječu na određene platforme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-559">**DeviceInfo.OsName** - The name of the OS (for example, iOS) to help us detect issues affecting certain platforms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-560">**DeviceInfo.OsVersion** – trenutačna verzija OS-a uređaja kako bismo lakše prepoznali probleme koji utječu na određene verzije OS-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-560">**DeviceInfo.OsVersion** - The current OS version of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain OS versions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-561">**DeviceInfo.SDKUid** – jedinstveni identifikator uređaja (sličan identifikatoru DeviceInfo.Id)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-561">**DeviceInfo.SDKUid** - The device unique identifier (similar to DeviceInfo.Id)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-562">**EventInfo.InitId** – ID koji se upotrebljava u okviru postavljanja rasporeda događaja preko našeg kanala za telemetriju kako bismo lakše prepoznali uzrok problema u kanalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-562">**EventInfo.InitId** - ID used as part of sequencing for event ordering through our telemetry pipeline to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-563">**EventInfo.SdkVersion** – SDK verzija koju upotrebljavamo za slanje naše telemetrije kako bismo lakše prepoznali uzrok problema u kanalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-563">**EventInfo.SdkVersion** - The SDK version we are using to send our telemetry to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-564">**EventInfo.Sequence** – slijed je za raspored događaja kroz naš kanal za telemetriju kako bismo lakše prepoznali uzrok problema u kanalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-564">**EventInfo.Sequence** - The sequence is for event ordering through our telemetry pipeline to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-565">**EventInfo.Source** – govori nam koji je dio kôda poslao događaj kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati uzrok problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-565">**EventInfo.Source** - Tells us what part of the code sent the event to help us detect the root cause of an issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-566">**EventInfo.Time** – vrijeme i datum emitiranja događaja s uređaja tako da naši sustavi mogu uspješno upravljati događajima koji stižu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-566">**EventInfo.Time** - The time and date the event was emitted from the device so our systems can successfully manage events coming in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-567">**eventpriority** – prioritet telemetrijskog događaja koji se odnosi na druge događaje tako da naši sustavi mogu uspješno upravljati događajima koji stižu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-567">**eventpriority** - The priority of the telemetry event relative to other events so our systems can successfully manage events coming in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-568">**first_launch_date** – prvi put kada je aplikacija pokrenuta da bismo lakše shvatili kada je problem nastao</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-568">**first_launch_date** - The first time the app was launched so helps us understand when an issue first began</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-569">**hashed_email** – identifikator u obliku pseudonima koji predstavlja poruku e-pošte trenutačnog korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-569">**hashed_email** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user email</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-570">**is_first_session** – prati ako je ovo prva sesija aplikacija radi rješavanja pogrešaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-570">**is_first_session** - Tracks if this is the first session of the app for debugging purposes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-571">**origin** – izvor radnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-571">**origin** - The origination of an action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-572">Na primjer, označavanje poruke pročitanom može doći s popisa poruka ili iz obavijesti o novoj pošti, a to nam pomaže otkriti probleme na temelju izvora radnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-572">For example marking a message read can originate from message list or a new mail notification, this helps us detect issues based on action origination</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-573">**PipelineInfo.AccountId** – identifikator u obliku pseudonima koji predstavlja trenutačnog korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-573">**PipelineInfo.AccountId** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-574">**PipelineInfo.ClientCountry** – trenutačna zemlja uređaja kako bi se prepoznali specifični problemi i nedostupnost u vezi zemlje ili regije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-574">**PipelineInfo.ClientCountry** - The current country of the device to detect country or region-specific issues and outages</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-575">**PipelineInfo.ClientIp** – IP adresa na kojoj je uređaj spojen radi rješavanja problema s povezivanjem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-575">**PipelineInfo.ClientIp** - The IP address the device is connected to debug connection issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-576">**PipelineInfo.IngestionTime** – vremenska oznaka telemetrijskog prihvaćanja za ovaj događaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-576">**PipelineInfo.IngestionTime** - Timestamp of when our telemetry ingestion happens for this event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-577">**Session.Id** – jedinstven identifikator za sesiju aplikacije za lakše otkrivanje problema u vezi sa sesijom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-577">**Session.Id** - A unique identifier for the app session to help identify session-related issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-578">**Session.ImpressionId** – jedinstven identifikator za upravljanje izdanjima naših značajki da bi se značajke uspješno objavile svim korisnicima i u svim uređajima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-578">**Session.ImpressionId** - A unique identifier for managing release of our features to ensure features are successfully released to all users and devices</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-579">**ui_mode** – je korisnik u svijetlom ili tamnom načinu rada, pomaže nam razvrstati pogreške u korisničkom sučelju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-579">**ui_mode** - Is the user in light or dark mode, helps us triage UX bugs with dark mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-580">**UserInfo.Language** – korisnikov jezik koji pomaže rješavati pogreške u vezi s tekstom prijevoda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-580">**UserInfo.Language** - The user's language to help debug translation text issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-581">**UserInfo.TimeZone** – vremenska zona korisnika koja pomaže rješavati pogreške u vezi s kalendarom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-581">**UserInfo.TimeZone** - The user's time zone to help debug calendar issues</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="8046f-582">Osim toga, sljedeća su polja podataka uobičajena za sve događaje za aplikaciju Outlook za iOS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-582">In addition, the following fields are common for all events for Outlook for iOS.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-583">**DeviceInfo.NetworkProvider** – davatelj mreže uređaja (npr. Verizon)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-583">**DeviceInfo.NetworkProvider** - The network provider of the device (for example, Verizon)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-584">**gcc_restrictions_enabled** – upućuje na to jesu li na aplikaciju primijenjena ograničenja GCC-a tako da možemo osigurati da korisnici GCC-a sigurno upotrebljavaju našu aplikaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-584">**gcc_restrictions_enabled** - Tells us if GCC restrictions have been applied to the app so we can ensure our GCC customers are using our app securely</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-585">**multi_window_mode** – govori nam upotrebljava li korisnik na iPadu više prozora da bi nam pomogao otkriti probleme u vezi s upotrebom više prozora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-585">**multi_window_mode** – Tells us if the user on the iPad is using multiple windows to help us detect issues related to multi-window usage.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-586">**office_session_id** – jedinstveni identifikator koji prati sesiju za spojene usluge sustava Office kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za integraciju usluge sustava Office u aplikaciju Outlook, poput aplikacije Word</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-586">**office_session_id** - A unique ID tracking the session for connected Office services to help detect issues specific an Office service integration in Outlook like Word</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-587">**state** – je li aplikacija bila aktivna kada je ovaj događaj poslan kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za aktivna i neaktivna stanja aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-587">**state** - Whether the app was active when this event was sent to help detect issues specific to active or inactive app states</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="8046f-588">Osim toga, sljedeća su polja podataka uobičajena za sve događaje za aplikaciju Outlook za Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-588">In addition, the following fields are common for all events for Outlook for Android.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-589">**aad_id** – identifikator u obliku pseudonima za Azure Active Directory</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-589">**aad_id** - a pseudonymous Azure Active Directory identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-590">**DeviceInfo.NetworkCost** – pokazatelj trenutačnog mrežnog troška uređaja koji odražava status mreže Wi-Fi/mobilne mreže/roaminga kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za mrežu uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-590">**DeviceInfo.NetworkCost** - Indication of devices current network cost, which reflects the status of WiFi/Cellular/Roaming to help detect issues specific to device network</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-591">**is_app_in_duo_split_view_mode** – javit će nam da je aplikacija bila u načinu dijeljenja zaslona na uređaju Duo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-591">**is_app_in_duo_split_view_mode** - This will let us know that the app was in Duo split-screen mode.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-592">To je svojstvo podešeno samo za uređaje Duo (samo Android).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-592">This property is set only for Duo (Android only) devices.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-593">**is_dex_mode_enabled** – je li omogućen Samsungov način rada DeX kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za način rada DeX kod Samsungovih uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-593">**is_dex_mode_enabled** - Whether Samsung DeX mode is enabled to help detect issues specific to DeX mode with Samsung devices</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-594">**is_sliding_drawer_enabled** – je li sučelje klizne ladice omogućeno kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi koje uzroku naše sučelje klizne ladice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-594">**is_sliding_drawer_enabled** - Whether Sliding Drawer interface is enabled to help detect issues caused by our sliding drawer interface</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-595">**orientation** – fizičko usmjerenje zaslona (okomito/vodoravno) kako bi se lakše prepoznali specifični problemi u vezi s usmjerenjem zaslona</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-595">**orientation** - Physical orientation of the screen (portrait/landscape) to help detect issues specific to device orientation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-596">**os_arch** – arhitektura operacijskog sustava za uređaj kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za operacijske sustave uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-596">**os_arch** - Operating System architecture for the device to help detect issues specific to device operation systems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-597">**process_bitness** – broj bitova postupka (32 ili 64 bitova) za aplikaciju kako bi se lakše prepoznali problemi specifični za broj bitova uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-597">**process_bitness** - Process bitness (32 or 64 bit) for the application to help detect issues specific to device bitness</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-598">**webview_kernel_version**: verzija jezgre sustava Chromium web-prikaza na uređaju koja nam pomaže prepoznati probleme s kompatibilnošću povezane s verzijom web-prikaza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-598">**webview_kernel_version**: The Chromium kernel version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-599">**webview_package_name**: naziv paketa web-prikaza na uređaju koji nam pomaže prepoznati probleme s kompatibilnošću povezane s verzijom web-prikaza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-599">**webview_package_name**: The package name of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-600">**webview_package_version**: verzija paketa web-prikaza na uređaju koji nam pomaže prepoznati probleme s kompatibilnošću povezane s verzijom web-prikaza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-600">**webview_package_version**: The package version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

#### <a name="officecorrelationmetadatautccorrelationmetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-642">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-642">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-643">Prikuplja metapodatke sustava Office putem UTC-a radi usporedbe s odgovarajućim podacima prikupljenim kroz kanal za telemetriju radi provjere ispravnosti i potpunosti podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-643">Collects Office metadata through UTC to compare with equivalent data collected through the Office telemetry pipeline to check correctness and completeness of data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-648">**AppSessionGuid** – identifikator određene sesije aplikacije koja počinje od vremena postupka stvaranja i traje do završetka postupka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-648">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-649">Oblikovan je kao standardni 128-bitni GUID, ali se sastoji od četiri dijela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-649">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of four parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-650">Ta su četiri dijela redom: (1) 32-bitni ID procesa (2) 16-bitni ID sesije (3) 16-bitni ID pokretanja (4) 64-bitno UTC vrijeme stvaranja procesa, izraženo u koracima od 100 ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-650">Those four parts in order are (1) 32-bit Process ID (2) 16-bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64-bit Process creation time in UTC 100 ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-651">**appVersionBuild** – broj međuverzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-651">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-652">**appVersionMajor** – broj glavne verzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-652">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-653">**appVersionMinor** – broj sporedne verzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-653">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-654">**appVersionRevision** – broj verzije revizije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-654">**appVersionRevision** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-655">**audienceGroup** – naziv grupe ciljne skupine za izdanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-655">**audienceGroup** - The release audience group name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-656">**audienceId** – naziv ciljne skupine za izdanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-656">**audienceId** - The release audience name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-657">**kanal** – kanal putem kojeg je Office distribuiran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-657">**channel** - The channel by which Office was distributed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-658">**deviceClass** – format hardvera uređaja iz operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-658">**deviceClass** - Device form factor from the OS</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-659">**ecsETag** – identifikator eksperimenta za postupak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-659">**ecsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-660">**impressionId** – guid koji označava trenutni skup značajki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-660">**impressionId** - A guid indicating the current set of features.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-661">**languageTag** – oznaka jezika IETF-a trenutnog korisničkog sučelja sustava Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-661">**languageTag** - The current Office UI IETF language tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-662">**officeUserID** – nasumično generirani guid za ovu instalaciju sustava Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-662">**officeUserID** - Randomly generated guid for this Office install</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-663">**osArchitecture** – arhitektura operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-663">**osArchitecture** - Operating system architecture</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-664">**osEnvironment** – cijeli broj koji označava operacijski sustav (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac itd).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-664">**osEnvironment** - An integer indicating the operating system (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac, etc.).</span></span>

determine whether add-in assignments have changed for a user.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-823"> Ako je tako, osf.DLL će se učitati pa možemo pozvati ExchangeGetEntitlements radi dobivanja je toga da se ne učita veliki DLL ako nije potreban.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-825">The idea is to not load the large DLL if we don't need to.</span></span>  <span #### <a name="officeappguardcreatecontainer"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-974">Office.AppGuard.CreateContainer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-974">Office.AppGuard.CreateContainer</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-975">Prikupljamo kodove pogrešaka te informacije o tome je li spremnik već postojao ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-975">We collect error codes and whether the container already existed or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-976">Prikupljamo i kodove pogrešaka za ponovno postavljanje u slučaju da ne uspijemo stvoriti spremnik pri prvom pokušaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-976">We also collect error codes for a reset event in case we fail to create the container on our first attempt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-977">Podaci će se upotrebljavati za identifikaciju postotka sesija za koje uspješno stvorimo spremnik za pokretanje aplikacija Office Application Guard.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-977">Data will be used identify the percentage of sessions we successfully create the container for launching Office Application Guard apps.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-978">Također, podaci će Microsoftu omogućiti identifikaciju i rješavanje kodova pogrešaka u vezi sa stvaranjem spremnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-978">Data will also allow Microsoft to identify and address error codes from the container creation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-980">**ErrorCode1** – vrsta koda pogreške za postavljanje spremnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-980">**ErrorCode1** - Type of container setup error code.</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-981">**ErrorCode2** – kôd pogreške iz provedbe stvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-981">**ErrorCode2** - Error code from executing the creation.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-982">**ErrorCode3** – dodatni kôd pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-982">**ErrorCode3** - Additional error code.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-983">**Id** – jedinstveni identifikator (GUID) za stvaranje spremnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-983">**Id** - A unique identifier (GUID) for the container creation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-984">**ResetError** – kôd pogreške iz pokušaja ponovnog postavljanja spremnika nakon neuspješna pokušaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-984">**ResetError** - Error code from trying to reset the container after a failed attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-985">**ResetErrorCode1** – vrsta koda pogreške postavljanja spremnika nakon naredbe za ponovno postavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-985">**ResetErrorCode1** - Type of Container Setup Error code after reset command.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-986">**ResetErrorCode2** – kôd pogreške iz provedbe stvaranja nakon naredbe za ponovno postavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-986">**ResetErrorCode2** - Error code from executing the creation after reset command.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-987">**ResetErrorCode3** – dodatni kôd pogreške nakon naredbe za ponovno postavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-987">**ResetErrorCode3** - Additional error code after reset command.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-988">**ResetErrorType** – vrsta pogreške tijekom ponovnog postavljanja: Stvaranje, Priprema datoteke ili Pokretanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-988">**ResetErrorType** - Type of error during reset: Creation, Preparing File or Launch.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-989">**WarmBoot** – prepoznaje je li spremnik već bio stvoren ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-989">**WarmBoot** - Identifies whether the container was already created or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1105">Ovo su podvrste podataka u toj kategoriji:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1105">The following are the data subtypes in this category:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1107">Status i pokretanje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1107">Application status and boot</span></span>](#application-status-and-boot-subtype)
- [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1108">Konfiguracija pristupačnosti za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1108">Office accessibility configuration</span></span>](#office-accessibility-configuration-subtype)
- [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1109">Zaštita privatnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1109">Privacy</span></span>](#privacy-subtype)


### <a name="application-feature-success-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1110">*Podvrsta uspjeha značajke aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1110">*Application feature success subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1111">Uspješno funkcioniranje aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1111">Success of application functionality.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1112">Ograničeno na otvaranje i zatvaranje aplikacije i dokumenata, uređivanje datoteka i zajedničko korištenje dokumenata (suradnju).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1112">Limited to opening and closing of the application and documents, file editing, and file sharing (collaboration).</span></span>

#### <a name="accountaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1113">account.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1113">account.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1114">Potrebno za osiguranje da konfiguracija računa uspješno radi i koristi za nadzor stanja kreiranja računa, mogućnost dodavanja novih računa e-pošte i nadzor softverskog vraćanja izvornih postavki računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1114">Needed to ensure account configuration is operating successfully and is used to monitor health of account creation, ability to add new email accounts, and monitor soft account resets</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1115">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1115">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1116">**account_calendar_count** – broj kalendara koji račun ima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1116">**account_calendar_count** - how many calendars the account has</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1117">**action** – vrsta provedene radnje, npr. create_account, delete_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1117">**action** - type of action performed, for example, create_account, delete_account.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1118">**duration_seconds** – trajanje radnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1118">**duration_seconds** - duration of the action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1119">**entry_point** – ulazna točka radnje, kako je korisnik pokrenuo radnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1119">**entry_point** - entry point of the action, how the user started the action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1120">**has_hx** – ima li uređaj račun koji koristi našu novu uslugu sinkronizacije e-pošte, ne nužno račun na kojem je radnja provedena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1120">**has_hx** - whether the device has an account that is using our new mail syncing service, not necessarily the account that the action was performed upon</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1121">**is_hx** – koristi li račun našu novu uslugu sinkronizacije e-pošte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1121">**is_hx** - is the account using our new mail syncing service</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1122">**is_shared_mailbox** – odnosi li se radnja na zajednički poštanski sandučić</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1122">**is_shared_mailbox** - whether the action pertains to a shared mailbox</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1123">**number_of_accounts** – ukupan broj računa na kojima se radnja provodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1123">**number_of_accounts** - total number of accounts that the action is performed on</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1124">**result** – rezultat radnje, npr. uspjeh, neuspjeh.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1124">**result** - result for the action, for example, success, failure.</span></span>
   
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1125">**server_type** – vrsta poslužitelja za račun, slično kao account_type</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1125">**server_type** - the server type for the account, similar to account_type</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1126">**shared_type** – vrsta zajedničkog računa (ako se račun zajednički koristi)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1126">**shared_type** - type of shared account (if the account is shared)</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1127">**scope** – opseg radnje; za brisanje računa, this_device ili all_devices</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1127">**scope** - the scope of the action; for delete account, this_device or all_devices</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1128">**total_calendar_accounts** – broj računa za kalendar u aplikaciji u trenutku radnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1128">**total_calendar_accounts** - count of calendar accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1129">**total_email_accounts** – broj računa e-pošte u aplikaciji u trenutku radnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1129">**total_email_accounts** - count of email accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1130">**total_file_accounts** – broj računa datoteka u aplikaciji u trenutku radnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1130">**total_file_accounts** - count of file accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>

#### <a name="accountlifecycle"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1131">account.lifecycle</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1131">account.lifecycle</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1132">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za osiguranje da konfiguracija računa uspješno radi i koristi za nadzor stanja kreiranja računa, mogućnost dodavanja novih računa e-pošte i nadzor softverskog vraćanja izvornih postavki računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1132">This event is collected to ensure account configuration is operating successfully and is used to monitor health of account creation, ability to add new email accounts, and monitor soft account resets.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1133">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1133">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1134">**account_creation_source** – neobavezno svojstvo koje se upotrebljava za pronalazak i dijagnozu svih problema koji se pojavljuju tijekom stvaranja računa kada se doda vrsta radnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1134">**account_creation_source** – optional property that is used to find and diagnose any issues that happen during account creation when the action type is add.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1135">Ono može imati vrijednosti kao što su jedinstvena prijava (SS0), create_new_account, manual, itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1135">It can have values like single sign-on (SSO), create_new_account, manual, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1136">**action** – vrsta radnje provedene na računu, npr. dodavanje, brisanje ili ponovno postavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1136">**action** - The type of action performed on the account, such as add, remove, or reset</span></span>

#### <a name="addnewaccountstep"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1137">add.new.account.step</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1137">add.new.account.step</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1138">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje prepoznati koji je napredak korisnika u stvaranju obrasca za novi račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1138">This event lets us detect how far the user has gotten in the create new account form.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1139">To označava kada je korisnik prešao na drugi korisnik ili je odustao od rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1139">It indicates when the user has moved to another step or if they have dropped off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1140">Te su nam informacije potrebne da bismo prepoznali postoje li neispravni koraci te da bismo osigurali da je stvaranje korisničkog računa bilo uspješno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1140">We need this information to detect if any steps are failing and to ensure user account creation was successful.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1141">Prikuplja se sljedeće polje:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1141">The following field is collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1142">**OTAddAccountCurrentStep** – to može imati sljedeće vrijednosti: profile_form, redirect_mobile_check, mobile_check_success</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1142">**OTAddAccountCurrentStep** - That can have the following values: profile_form, redirect_mobile_check, mobile_check_success</span></span>

#### <a name="apperror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1143">app.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1143">app.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1144">Prati kritične pogreške korištene aplikacije da bismo mogli spriječiti probleme koji mogu prouzročiti rušenje aplikacije ili vam onemogućiti čitanje e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1144">Tracks critical app errors used so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app to crash or prevent you from reading email.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1145">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1145">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1146">**clientName** – naziv klijenta za datoteku u oblaku u kojoj je pogreška nastupila, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1146">**clientName** - The name of the client for the cloud file where the error occurred, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1147">**cloudfile_error_type** – vrsta pogreške koja je nastupila za datoteku u oblaku, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1147">**cloudfile_error_type** - The type of error that occurred for the cloud file, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1148">**cloudfile_response_name** – naziv odgovora za pogrešku koja je nastupila za datoteku u oblaku, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1148">**cloudfile_response_name** - The response name for the error that occurred for the cloud file, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1149">**component_name** – naziv komponente aplikacije u kojoj je pogreška nastupila, primjerice pošta ili kalendar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1149">**component_name** - The name of the component of the app where the error occurred, such as mail or calendar.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1150">**debug_info** – informacije o pogrešci koja je nastupila za datoteku u oblaku kako bi se moglo utvrditi zašto je pogreška nastupila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1150">**debug_info** - Information on the error that occurred for the cloud file in order to be able to determine why the error happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1151">**error_origin_identifier** – porijeklo pogreške koja je nastupila na skici na kojoj je pogreška nastupila, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1151">**error_origin_identifier** - Origin of the error that occurred on the draft that the error occurred, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1152">**error_type** – vrsta pogreške koja je nastupila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1152">**error_type** - The type of error that occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1153">Neki primjeri obuhvaćaju spremanje skice, slanje skice i pogrešku datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1153">Some examples include save draft, send draft, and cloud file error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1154">**exdate** – datum proširenog pravila (odnosi se samo na pogreške ponavljanja obveze) *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1154">**exdate** - the extended rule date (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1155">**exrule** – vrijednost proširenog pravila (odnosi se samo na pogreške ponavljanja obveze) *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1155">**exrule** - the extended rule value (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1156">**has_attachments** – označava ima li skica na kojoj je pogreška nastupila privitke, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1156">**has_attachments** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on has attachments, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1157">**is_IRM_protected** – označava je li skica na kojoj je pogreška nastupila zaštićena upravljanjem pravima na informacije, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1157">**is_IRM_protected** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on is protected by information rights management, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1158">**is_legitimate** – označava potječe li pogreška iz pogreške u programiranju ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1158">**is_legitimate** - Reflects if the error comes from a programming error or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1159">Pogreške u programiranju ne smatraju se valjanima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1159">Programming errors are considered non-legitimate.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1160">**is_local** – označava je li se skica na kojoj je pogreška nastupila sinkronizirala s poslužiteljem, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1160">**is_local** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on has synced to the server, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1161">**is_recoverable** – označava je li kod pogreške riječ o pogrešci koja se može otkloniti ili o fatalnoj pogrešci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1161">**is_recoverable** - Reflects if the error can be recovered from or if it is a fatal error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1162">**rdate** – datum pravila ponavljanja (odnosi se samo na pogreške ponavljanja obveza) *[To je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, no i dalje se može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1162">**rdate** - the date of the recurrence rule (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1163">**rrule** – samo pravilo ponavljanja (odnosi se samo na pogreške ponavljanja obveza) *[To je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, no i dalje se može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1163">**rrule** - the recurrence rule itself (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1164">**rrule_error_message** – poruka o pogrešci s raščlanjivanjem pravila ponavljanja (odnosi se samo na pogreške ponavljanja obveze) *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1164">**rrule_error_message** - recurrence rule parsing error message (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1165">**rrule_error_type** – vrsta pogreške s raščlanjivanjem pravila ponavljanja (odnosi se samo na pogreške ponavljanja obveze) *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1165">**rrule_error_type** - recurrence rule parsing error type (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1166">**status_code** – kod stanja pogreške koja je nastupila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1166">**status_code** - The status code of the error that occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1167">To nam pomaže razumjeti uzrok pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1167">This helps us understand the cause of the error.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1168">Svi su znakovi također moguća svojstva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1168">All characters are also possible properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1169">To nam pomaže razumjeti znakove u tijelu skice poruke kada je pogreška nastupila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1169">This helps us understand the characters in the body of the draft message when the error occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1170">Primjerice, „a”, „b” i „c” su moguća svojstva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1170">For example, "a", "b", "c" are possible properties.</span></span>

#### <a name="applaunchreport"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1171">app.launch.report</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1171">app.launch.report</span></span>
