<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1172">Ovaj nam događaj omogućava prepoznavanje i popravljanje problema kada se Outlook pokreće sporo ili nepotpuno, zbog čega korisnici imaju probleme s korištenjem naše aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1172">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook is starting slowly or incompletely, making it difficult for users to use our app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1173">To uključuje informacije o konkretnim značajkama koje su bile omogućene i koliko su dugo dijelovi pokretanja trajali.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1173">This includes information on the specific features that were enabled and how long parts of the startup took.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1174">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1174">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1175">**is_agenda_widget_active** – govori nam je li widget za dnevni red aktivan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1175">**is_agenda_widget_active** - Tells us if the agenda widget is active.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1176">**is_alert_available** – govori nam je li aplikacija bila konfigurirana za dopuštanje upozorenja u obavijestima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1176">**is_alert_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow alerts in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1177">**is_background_refresh_available** – govori nam je li aplikacija bila konfigurirana za osvježavanje u pozadini.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1177">**is_background_refresh_available** - Tells if the app has been configured to be able to refresh in the background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1178">**is_badge_available** – govori nam je li aplikacija bila konfigurirana za dopuštanje znački u obavijestima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1178">**is_badge_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow badges in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1179">**is_intune_managed** – govori nam upravlja li Intune aplikacijom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1179">**is_intune_managed** - Tell us if the app is managed by Intune.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1180">**is_registered_for_remote_notifications** – govori nam je li aplikacija bila registrirana za udaljene obavijesti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1180">**is_registered_for_remote_notifications** - Tell us if the app has been registered for remote notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1181">**is_sound_available** – govori nam je li aplikacija bila konfigurirana za dopuštanje zvukova u obavijestima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1181">**is_sound_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow sounds in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1182">**is_watch_app_installed** – govori nam je li aplikacija sata za Outlook bila instalirana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1182">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the watch Outlook app has been installed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1183">**is_watch_paired** – govori nam je li aplikacija sata za Outlook uparena s glavnom aplikacijom Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1183">**is_watch_paired** - Tell us if the watch Outlook app is paired with the main Outlook app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1184">**launch_to_db_ready_ms** – govori nam o količini vremena koje je aplikaciji Outlook bilo potrebno od pokretanja do spremnosti baze podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1184">**launch_to_db_ready_ms** - Tell us the amount of time the Outlook app spent from launch to the database being ready.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1185">**num_calendar_accounts** – govori nam broj računa za kalendar u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1185">**num_calendar_accounts** - Tells us the number of calendar accounts in the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1186">**num_cloud_file_accounts** – govori nam broj računa za pohranu u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1186">**num_cloud_file_accounts** - Tells us the number of storage accounts in the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1187">**num_hx_calendar_accounts** – govori nam broj računa za kalendar u aplikaciji koji se povezuju s našom novom uslugom sinkronizacije pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1187">**num_hx_calendar_accounts** - Tells us the number of calendar accounts in the app that connect to our new mail syncing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1188">**num_hx_mail_accounts** – govori nam broj računa pošte u aplikaciji koji se povezuju s našom novom uslugom sinkronizacije pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1188">**num_hx_mail_accounts** - Tells us the number of mail accounts in the app that connect to our new mail syncing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1189">**num_mail_accounts** – govori nam broj računa pošte u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1189">**num_mail_accounts** - Tells us the number of mail accounts in the app.</span></span>

#### <a name="calendaraction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1190">calendar.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1190">calendar.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1191">Koristi se za nadzor svih mogućih negativnih utjecaja na vašu mogućnost provedbe osnovnih radnji kalendara kao što su kreiranje ili uređivanje događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1191">Used for monitoring any possible negative impact on your ability to perform core calendar actions like creating or editing events.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1192">Događaj također može uključivati niz naziva svojstava te jesu li se ona promijenila ili nisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1192">The event could also include a series of property names and if they have changed or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1193">Primjerice, „title_changed”, „online_meeting_changed” i „description_changed” nazivi su svojstava koja su uključena kako bi nam pomogla razumjeti postoje li problemi s uređivanjem određenih svojstava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1193">For example, "title_changed", "online_meeting_changed", and "description_changed" are property names that are included to help us understand if there are any issues with editing certain properties.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1194">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1194">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1195">**account_sfb_enabled** – pomaže nam osigurati da je Skype za tvrtke ispravno konfiguriran.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1195">**account_sfb_enabled** - Helps us make sure that Skype for Business is configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1196">**action** – vrsta radnje koja je provedena na kalendaru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1196">**action** - The type of action that was performed on the calendar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1197">Ovo uključuje stavke kao što su otvaranje, uređivanje, dodavanje prečaca, odgađanje itd. Pomaže nam osigurati da naš kalendar funkcionira u skladu s očekivanjima i da ne postoje oštećenja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1197">This includes things like open, editing, adding shortcut, snooze, etc. Helps us ensure our calendar experience is functioning as expected and nothing has broken</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1198">**action_result** – rezultat radnje provedene na komponentama kalendara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1198">**action_result** - Result of the action taken on calendar components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1199">To može uključivati vrijednosti kao što su uspjeh, neuspjeh, nepoznato i vremensko ograničenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1199">This can include values such as success, failure, unknown, and timeout.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1200">Koristi se za praćenje stope uspješnosti radnji i utvrđivanje postoji li rasprostranjen problem s radnjama kalendara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1200">Used to track the success rate of actions and determine if there is a widespread issue with calendar actions.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1201">**attendee_busy_status** – status slobodno/zauzeto sudionika s kojim je radnja povezana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1201">**attendee_busy_status** - The free/busy status of the attendee that the action is related to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1202">Ova vrijednost može biti slobodno, zauzeto ili uvjetno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1202">This value can be free, busy, or tentative.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1203">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoji li problem s radnjama povezanim s određenim statusom zauzetosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1203">Helps us understand if there is an issue with actions related to a certain busy status.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1204">**availability** – vrijednost dostupnosti ako se vrijednost slobodno/zauzeto promijenila tijekom sastanka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1204">**availability** - The availability value if the free/busy value has changed on the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1205">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s postavljanjem određene vrijednosti dostupnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1205">Helps us understand if there are issues with setting a certain availability value.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1206">**calendar_onlinemeeting_default_provider** – sadrži zadanog davatelja usluge za mrežni sastanak za upotrebu sa stvaranjem mrežnih sastanaka s podrškom poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1206">**calendar_onlinemeeting_default_provider** - Contains the default online meeting provider for use with server-supported online meeting creation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1207">To uključuje vrste programa Skype, Skype za tvrtke, Hangout i Teams za tvrtke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1207">This includes types of Skype, Skype for Business, Hangout, and Teams for Business.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1208">Pomaže nam dijagnosticirati potencijalne probleme s kreiranjem mrežnih sastanaka na određenim davateljima usluga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1208">Helps us diagnose potential issues with creating online meetings on certain providers.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1209">**calendar_onlinemeeting_enabled** – vrijednost true ako kalendar podržava stvaranje mrežnih sastanaka s podrškom poslužitelja na temelju zadanog davatelja usluga mrežnih sastanaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1209">**calendar_onlinemeeting_enabled** - True if the calendar supports server-supported online meeting creation based on a default online meeting provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1210">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s kalendarima s omogućenim mrežnim sastancima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1210">Helps us understand if there are any issues with online meeting enabled calendars.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1211">**calendar_type** – vrsta kalendara na kojem se događaj nalazi nakon što je korisnik uredio sastanak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1211">**calendar_type** - The type of calendar an event is on after the user has edited the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1212">Moguće vrijednosti uključuju primarno, sekundarno, dijeljeno i grupno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1212">Possible values include primary, secondary, shared, and group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1213">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s određenom vrstom kalendara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1213">Helps us understand if there are issues with a certain calendar type.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1214">**delete_action_origin** – porijeklo provedene radnje brisanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1214">**delete_action_origin** - The origin of the delete action performed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1215">Ovo uključuje vrijednosti kao što su alatna traka navigacijske trake i alatna traka kapsule.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1215">This includes values such as navigation bar toolbar and capsule toolbar.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1216">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s brisanjem sastanka iz određene lokacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1216">Helps us understand if there are any issues with deleting a meeting from a certain location.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1217">**distribution_list_count** – broj sudionika koji se nalaze na popisima za raspodjelu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1217">**distribution_list_count** - Number of attendees that are on distribution lists.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1218">Pomaže nam pratiti postoje li problemi sa sudionicima koji se nalaze na popisima za raspodjelu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1218">Helps us track if there are issues with attendees that are on distribution lists.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1219">**guest_count** – broj gostiju u sastanku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1219">**guest_count** - The number of guests on the meeting.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1220">Pomaže nam osigurati da se gosti ispravno dodaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1220">Helps us make sure that the guests are being added correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1221">**is_all_day** – koristi se zajedno s „meeting_duration” za određivanje je li riječ o cjelodnevnom sastanku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1221">**is_all_day** - Used along with "meeting_duration" to specify if this is an all-day meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1222">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s radnjama provedenim u okviru cjelodnevnih sastanaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1222">Helps us understand if there are any issues with actions performed on all-day meetings.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1223">**is_location_permission_granted** – je li korisnik dodijelio dozvolu mjesta sustava aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1223">**is_location_permission_granted** – Whether user has granted system location permission to the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1224">Ako je dodijeljena dozvola mjesta, aplikacija može prikazati dodatne korisne informacije u korisničkom sučelju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1224">If location permission is granted, the app can show extra utility information in the user interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1225">Ako znamo da je dozvola lokacije dodijeljena, moći ćemo znati koliko se često dodatne korisne informacije prikazuju korisnicima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1225">Knowing if location permission is granted will allow us to know how often the extra utility information is being shown to users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1226">**is_organizer** – pomaže nam razumjeti može li organizator pravilno uređivati i kreirati sastanke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1226">**is_organizer** - Helps us understand if meetings are able to be edited and created by the organizer correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1227">**is_recurring** – pomaže nam razumjeti postoji li problem koji specifično utječe na ponavljajuće sastanke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1227">**is_recurring** - Helps us understand if there is an issue that specifically impacts recurring meetings.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1228">**launch_point** – točka pokretanja radnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1228">**launch_point** - The launch point of the action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1229">Može biti vrijednosti kao što su zaglavlje widgeta, podnožje widgeta, cjelodnevni widget i prečac kalendara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1229">Can be values such as widget header, widget footer, widget all day, and calendar shortcut.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1230">Pomaže nam razumjeti kontekst iz koje je radnja pokrenuta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1230">Helps us understand the context that the action was started from.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1231">**location_count** – broj lokacija koje se postavljaju tijekom kreiranja i uređivanja događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1231">**location_count** - Number of locations that are set on event create and edit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1232">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s kreiranjem ili uređivanjem događaja s određenim brojem lokacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1232">Helps us understand if there are any issues with creating or editing events with a certain number of locations.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1233">**location_selection_source_type** – vrsta izvora za odabir lokacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1233">**location_selection_source_type** - Type of the location selection source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1234">Ovo može uključivati vrijednosti kao što su prijedlog lokacije, prilagođeno i postojeće.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1234">This can include values such as location suggestion, custom, and existing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1235">Pomaže nam dijagnosticirati sve probleme s odabirom lokacije iz određenog izvora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1235">Helps us diagnose any issues with selecting a location from a certain source.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1236">**location_session_id** – ID sesije za odabir lokacije sastanka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1236">**location_session_id** - ID of the meeting location chooser session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1237">Pomaže nam dijagnosticirati sve probleme s odabirom lokacije koja se treba dodati sastanku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1237">Helps us diagnose any issues with choosing a location to add to the meeting.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1238">**location_type** – vrsta odabrane lokacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1238">**location_type** - The type of location selected.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1239">Sadrži vrste kao što su prilagođena lokacija, konferencijska prostorija i Bing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1239">Contains types such as custom location, conference room, and Bing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1240">Pomaže nam razumjeti probleme s dodavanjem određenih vrsta lokacija u sastanak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1240">Helps us understand issues with adding certain location types to the meeting.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1241">**meeting_duration** – trajanje sastanka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1241">**meeting_duration** - The length of the meeting.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1242">Pomaže nam osigurati da se sastanci konfiguriraju s točnim vremenima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1242">Helps us make sure that the meetings are being configured with the correct times.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1243">**meeting_insights_type** – vrsta uvida u sastanak u pojedinostima o događaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1243">**meeting_insights_type** - The type of meeting insights in the event details.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1244">Ovo uključuje datoteku i poruku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1244">This includes file and message.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1245">Pomaže nam razumjeti broj uvida u sastanak koji se prikazuju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1245">Helps us understand the number of meeting insights that are being shown.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1246">**meeting_type** – vrsta mrežnog sastanka povezanog s radnjom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1246">**meeting_type** - The type of online meeting associated with the action.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1247">To uključuje vrste programa Skype, Skype za tvrtke, Hangout i Teams za tvrtke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1247">This includes types of Skype, Skype for Business, Hangout, and Teams for Business.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1248">Pomaže nam razumjeti jesu li mrežni sastanci pravilno konfigurirani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1248">Helps us understand if the online meetings are configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1249">**origin** – porijeklo radnje kalendara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1249">**origin** - The origin of the calendar action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1250">Ovo uključuje vrste kao što su dnevni red, kalendar, dnevni red widgeta itd. Pomaže nam u boljem osiguravanju da interakcija s komponentama kalendara pravilno funkcionira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1250">This includes types like agenda, calendar, widget agenda, etc. Helps us better ensure the interaction within the calendar components are working correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1251">**recurrence_scope** – vrsta ponavljanja sastanka, bilo pojava ili niz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1251">**recurrence_scope** - The type of recurrence of the meeting, either occurrence or series.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1252">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s uređivanjem različitih vrsta ponavljanja sastanka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1252">Helps us understand if there are any issues with editing different meeting recurrence types.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1253">**reminder_time** – vrijeme podsjetnika sastanka ako se ono promijenilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1253">**reminder_time** - The reminder time of the meeting if it has changed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1254">Koristi se za osiguravanje da je vrijeme sastanka pravilno spremljeno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1254">Used to make sure the reminder time of the meeting is saved correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1255">**reminders_count** – broj podsjetnika za događaj ako su se podsjetnici promijenili.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1255">**reminders_count** - Number of reminders on the event if the reminders have changed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1256">Pomaže nam dijagnosticirati sve probleme s višestrukim podsjetnicima za događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1256">Helps us diagnose any issues with multiple reminders on an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1257">**sensitivity** – osjetljivost sastanka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1257">**sensitivity** - The sensitivity of the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1258">To uključuje vrste normalno, osobno, privatno i povjerljivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1258">This includes types of normal, personal, private, and confidential.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1259">Pomaže nam razumjeti je li osjetljivost sastanka pravilno konfigurirana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1259">Helps us understand if the sensitivity of the meeting is being configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1260">**session_duration** – trajanje sesije u milisekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1260">**session_duration** - The length that the session lasted in milliseconds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1261">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi koji povećavaju količinu vremena potrebnog za provedbu radnje kalendara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1261">Helps us understand if there are issues that are increasing the amount of time needed to perform the calendar action.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1262">**shared_calendar_result** – rezultat radnje provedene na dijeljenom kalendaru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1262">**shared_calendar_result** - The result of an action performed on a shared calendar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1263">Moguće vrijednosti obuhvaćaju u redu, nema dozvole, nepoznato, lokalni vlasnik i vlasnik je grupa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1263">Possible values include ok, no permission, unknown, owner on-prem, and owner is group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1264">Pomaže nam razumjeti pouzdanost radnji provedenih na dijeljenim kalendarima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1264">Helps us understand the reliability of actions performed on shared calendars.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1265">**time_picker_origin** – podrijetlo birača vremena za radnju spremanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1265">**time_picker_origin** - Origin of the time picker for a save action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1266">Uključuje vrijednosti kao što su više mogućnosti i manje mogućnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1266">Includes values such as more options and fewer options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1267">Pomaže nam razumjeti kako je korisnik usmjeravao tijek za spremanje sastanka i osigurati da ispravno funkcionira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1267">Helps us understand how the user navigated the flow to save the meeting and ensure that is functioning correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1268">**title** – automatski predloženi naslov iz vrijednosti koje je definirala aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1268">**title** - The auto-suggested title from app-defined values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1269">To uključuje vrijednosti kao što su „Poziv”, „Ručak” i „Skype”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1269">This includes values such as "Call", "Lunch", and "Skype".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1270">Pomaže nam razumjeti je li automatsko predlaganje naslova pravilno konfigurirano.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1270">Helps us understand if the title auto-suggestion is configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1271">**txp** – vrsta rezervacije na događaju, ako postoji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1271">**txp** - The type of booking or reservation on the event, if any.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1272">Ovo uključuje vrste kao što su rezervacija događaja, rezervacija leta, rezervacija najma automobila itd. Pomaže nam razumjeti funkcioniraju li kartice za rezervaciju pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1272">This includes types like event reservation, flight reservation, car rental reservation, etc. Helps us understand if the booking/reservation cards are performing correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1273">**upcoming_event_count** – broj predstojećih događaja prikazan u prikazu predstojećih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1273">**upcoming_event_count** - The number of upcoming events displayed in the upcoming events view.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1274">Pomaže nam razumjeti postoje li problemi s prikazom predstojećih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1274">Helps us understand if there are issues with the upcoming events view.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1275">**upcoming_event_seconds_until_event** – broj sekundi do početka sljedećeg predstojećeg događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1275">**upcoming_event_seconds_until_event** - The number of seconds until the next upcoming event starts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1276">Pomaže nam razumjeti tipične događaje koji se prikazuju u prikazu predstojećih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1276">Helps us understand the typical events that are shown in the upcoming events view.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1277">**value** – pojedinost specifična za radnju kao što je trajanje odgađanja upozorenja ili kategorija ponavljanja do.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1277">**value** - Action-specific detail such as alert delay length or repeat-until category.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1278">Pomaže nam razumjeti kontekst u kojem je radnja provedena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1278">Helps us understand the context that the action was performed.</span></span> 

#### <a name="combinedsearchuse"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1279">combined.search.use</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1279">combined.search.use</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1280">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu sposobnost provedbe ključnih funkcija pretraživanja kao što su traženje pošte, kontakata ili događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1280">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform key search functionality such as searching for mail, contacts, or events.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1281">Sljedeća se polja prikupljaju na svim uređajima iOS i Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1281">The following fields are collected across iOS and Android:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1282">**account_switcher_action_type** – ova vrsta radnje prati je li korisnik koristio preglednik računa bilo u jednostavnom otkrivanju ili se odlučio za promjenu računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1282">**account_switcher_action_type** - This action type tracks if the user used the account switcher either in simply discovery or if they decided to switch the account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1283">**action_type** – vrsta radnje koja je provedena za pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1283">**action_type** - The type of action that was performed for search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1284">Ovo prepoznaje je li pretraživanje pokrenuto, provodi li se ili je dovršeno te koje su se radnje provodile tijekom pretraživanja, na primjer, je li korišten mikrofon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1284">This identifies if a search has been started, in occurring, or ended and what actions were happening during the search, for example, was the mic used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1285">Ovo je ključno za osiguravanje točnih i korisnih pretraživanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1285">This is instrumental in ensuring accurate and helpful searches.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1286">**conversation_id** – jedinstveni ID za svaku sesiju pretraživanja (tj. svaki put kada korisnik otvori okvir za pretraživanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1286">**conversation_id** - Unique ID for every search session (for example, every time the user enters the search box)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1287">**entrance_type** – ovo određuje kako je korisnik pokrenuo upit za pretraživanje, iz kartice Pretraživanje, nulto pretraživanje, zaglavlje pretraživanja ili rezultat pretraživanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1287">**entrance_type** - This determines how the user started the search query, from the search tab, zero query, search heading, or search result.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1288">**has_contact_results** – jednostavna informacija o tome prikazuju li se rezultati kontakata u upitu za pretraživanje ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1288">**has_contact_results** - Simple whether contact results are shown or not in the search query</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1289">**include_deleted** – prikazuje li pretraživanje izbrisane mogućnosti među rezultatima pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1289">**include_deleted** - whether the search is showing deleted options in the search results</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1290">**is_ics_external_data** – bilježi je li dodani događaj interni (tj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1290">**is_ics_external_data** - Captures if an added event is internal (i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1291">dodan u program Outlook u kalendar programa Outlook) ili vanjski (tj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1291">added in Outlook to Outlook calendar) or external (i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1292">dodan iz druge aplikacije za e-poštu kao što je Gmail u kalendar programa Outlook).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1292">added from another email app such as Gmail to Outlook calendar).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1293">**is_network_fully_connected** – ovo služi tome da dobijete naznaku razloga za izvanmrežno pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1293">**is_network_fully_connected** - This is to get a hint of the reason behind the offline search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1294">Ako je mreža povezana, a pretraživanje je izvan mreže, razlog je vjerojatno vremensko ograničenje poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1294">If the network is connected and the search is offline, then the reason is likely to be the server timeout</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1295">**is_offline_search** – je li sesija pretraživanja ujedno pretraživanje izvan mreže na temelju rezultata pretraživanja koje vrati hx</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1295">**is_offline_search** - whether the search session is offline search based on search results returned by hx</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1296">**re_enter_search_tab** – Booleova vrijednost za označavanje je li korisnik promijenio kartice prije odabira rezultata pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1296">**re_enter_search_tab** - Boolean to indicate whether a user has switched tabs before selecting a search result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1297">**result_selected_type** – s kojom vrstom podataka koji su bili prikazani korisnik komunicira, na primjer, prikaži sve kontakte, razgovore, događaje itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1297">**result_selected_type** - What type of data that was displayed is the user interacting with, for example, see all contact, conversations, event, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1298">**search_conversation_result_data** – ovo sadrži podatke o označenom razgovoru iz rezultata pretraživanja uključujući vrstu računa (hx, ac itd.), drži li poruku servis u oblaku te je li prikazani pomak stranice jednaka stranica kao u prvoj poruci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1298">**search_conversation_result_data** - This contains data about the conversation selected from a search result including account type (hx, ac, etc.), whether the message is held by a cloud service, and whether the page offset shown is the same page as the first message.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1299">**search_origin** – podrijetlo pretraživanja, npr. glasovni pomoćnik, Cortana, unos tipkovnicom itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1299">**search_origin** - Where did the search originate from, for example, voice assistant, Cortana, keyboard input, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1300">**search_scope** – niz koji označava u kojoj je vrsti računa korisnik provodio pretraživanje (na primjer, Exchange, Gmail itd.) ili je bila riječ o stavci Svi računi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1300">**search_scope** - A string indicating what type of account the user was searching in (for example, Exchange, Gmail, etc.) or if it was in All Accounts.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1301">**search_suggestion_type** – označava što se nalazi iza prijedloga za pretraživanje, na primjer, je li riječ o ispravku pravopisa?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1301">**search_suggestion_type** - indicates what is behind the search suggestion, for example, is a spell correction?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1302">Temelji li se na povijesti?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1302">Based on history?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1303">Je li došlo do samodovršetka?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1303">Autocomplete?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1304">**search_request_reason** – označava razlog zašto je zahtjev za pretraživanje poslan iz aplikacije, čime označava komponentu ili radnju korisnika koja je pokrenula pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1304">**search_request_reason** - Indicates the reason a search request was sent from the app, in effect indicating the component or user action that invoked a search.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1305">**search_result_filter_type** – označava koja je vrsta fltra primijenjena na pretraživanje, prikaži sve ili samo privitke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1305">**search_result_filter_type** - Indicates what type of filter was applied to search, show all or attachments only</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1306">Sljedeća se polja prikupljaju na svim aplikacijama za iOS programa Outlook Mobile:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1306">The following fields are collected across iOS applications of Outlook Mobile:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1307">**action** – vrsta radnje koja je provedena za pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1307">**action** - the type of action that was performed for search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1308">Ovo prepoznaje je li pretraživanje pokrenuto, provodi li se ili je dovršeno te koje su se radnje provodile tijekom pretraživanja, na primjer, je li korišten mikrofon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1308">This identifies if a search has been started, in occurring, or ended and what actions were happening during the search, for example, was the mic used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1309">Ovo je ključno za osiguravanje točnih i korisnih pretraživanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1309">This is instrumental in ensuring accurate and helpful searches.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1310">**answer_result_selected_count** – prati koliko je puta pretraživanje bilo „uspješno”, na primjer, je li korisnik pronašao ono što je želio?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1310">**answer_result_selected_count** - tracks how many times the search was "successful", for example, did the user find the person they wanted?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1311">Je li sastavljena e-pošta?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1311">Composed an email?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1312">Je li poruka označena knjižnom oznakom?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1312">Bookmarked the message?</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1313">**contact_result_in_full_list_selected_count** – prati koliko je puta korisnik odabrao da se „prikažu svi kontakti” u punom popisu tijekom kombinirane sesije pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1313">**contact_result_in_full_list_selected_count** - tracks how many times the user asked to "see all contacts" in full list was selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1314">**contact_result_selected_count** – prati koliko je rezultata kontakata odabrano tijekom kombinirane sesije pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1314">**contact_result_selected_count** - tracks how many contact results were selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1315">**conversation_result_selected_count** – prati koliko je razgovora označeno tijekom kombinirane sesije pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1315">**conversation_result_selected_count** - tracks how many conversations were selecting during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1316">**mail_paging_gesture_count** – prati koliko je gesti listanja stranica za pretraživanje pošte izvršeno unutar kombinirane sesije pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1316">**mail_paging_gesture_count** - tracks how many mail search paging gestures were performed within the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1317">**mail_requests_count** – prati koliko je zahtjeva za pretraživanje pošte poslano unutar kombinirane sesije pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1317">**mail_requests_count** - tracks how many mail search requests were sent within the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1318">**people_filter_selected_contacts_count** – prati koliko je kontakata odabrano u filtru za osobe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1318">**people_filter_selected_contacts_count** - tracks how many contacts were selected in the people filter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1319">**search_session_ended_type** – označava gdje je upit za pretraživanje završio jer je bio otkazan ili je upit bio ažuriran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1319">**search_session_ended_type** - Indicates where a search ended because it was canceled or the updated was the query</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1320">**search_suggestion_type** – označava što se nalazi iza prijedloga za pretraživanje, na primjer, je li riječ o ispravku pravopisa?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1320">**search_suggestion_type** - indicates what is behind the search suggestion, for example, is a spell correction?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1321">Temelji li se na povijesti?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1321">Based on history?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1322">Je li došlo do samodovršetka?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1322">Autocomplete?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1323">**see_all_contacts_selected_count** – prati koliko je puta „prikaži sve kontakte” bilo odabrano tijekom kombinirane sesije pretraživanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1323">**see_all_contacts_selected_count** - tracks how many times "see all contacts" was selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1324">**subtab_type** – prati gdje je korisnik odabrao rezultat i iz koje kartice rezultata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1324">**subtab_type** -  tracks where the user has selected the result from which result tab</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1325">**top_mail_result_selected_count** – prati koliko puta korisnik odabire glavne rezultate koji mu se pruže.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1325">**top_mail_result_selected_count** - tracks how many times a user selects the top results provided to them.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1326">**ui_reload_result_count** – bilježi vremena ponovnog učitavanja korisničkog sučelja zbog ažuriranja skupa rezultata (tijekom određenog upita)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1326">**ui_reload_result_count** - records the times of reloading UI because of result set update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1327">**ui_reload_result_time** – bilježi ukupno vrijeme utrošeno na ponovno učitavanje korisničkog sučelja zbog ažuriranja skupa rezultata (tijekom određenog upita)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1327">**ui_reload_result_time** - records the total time spent on reloading UI because of result set update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1328">**ui_reload_status_count** – bilježi vremena ponovnog učitavanja korisničkog sučelja zbog ažuriranja statusa (tijekom određenog upita)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1328">**ui_reload_status_count** - records the times of reloading UI because of status update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1329">**ui_reload_status_time** – bilježi ukupno vrijeme utrošeno na ponovno učitavanje korisničkog sučelja zbog ažuriranja statusa (tijekom određenog upita)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1329">**ui_reload_status_time** - records the total time spent on reloading UI because of status update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

#### <a name="composemailaccessory"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1330">compose.mail.accessory</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1330">compose.mail.accessory</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1331">Ovaj događaj omogućava nam prepoznavanje i popravljanje problema s ključnim radnjama sastavljanja poruka kako ne biste imali problema s prilaganjem datoteke, snimanjem fotografije kao privitka ili slanjem svoje raspoloživosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1331">This event lets us detect and fix issues with key mail compose actions to prevent you from running into issues with attaching a file, taking a photo as an attachment, or sending your availability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1332">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1332">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1333">**action** – govori nam radnju koja se pokušala provesti tijekom evidencije radnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1333">**action** - Tells us the action that was attempted when the action is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1334">Neki primjeri uključuju prilaganje datoteke i prikaz većeg broja mogućnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1334">Some examples include attaching a file and presenting more options.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1335">**icon_name** – govori nam naziv ikone koja se prikazuje tijekom evidencije radnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1335">**icon_name** - Tells us the name of the icon that is being shown when the action is logged.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1336">**origin** – otkriva nam porijeklo akcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1336">**origin** – Tells us the origin of the action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1337">Moguće su vrijednosti quick_reply i full_screen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1337">Possible values are quick_reply and full_screen.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1338">**toolbar_type** – Obavijestite nas o vrsti alatne trake koja se prikazuje na stranici za sastavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1338">**toolbar_type** – Tell us the toolbar type that is presenting on compose page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1339">Moguće su vrijednosti compose_actions i formatting.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1339">Possible values are compose_actions and formatting.</span></span>


#### <a name="conversationviewaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1340">conversation.view.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1340">conversation.view.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1341">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost prikaza i odgovaranja na poruke e-pošte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1341">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to view and reply to email messages</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1342">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1342">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1343">**contains_mention** – govori nam je li razgovor imao primijenjeno spominjanje @ kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme sa spominjanjem u e-pošti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1343">**contains_mention** - Tells us if the conversation had an @ mention applied to help us detect issues with email mentions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1344">**conversation_type** – govori nam koja je vrsta prikaza poruke e-pošte renderirana, primjerice prikaz jedne poruke ili prikazi većeg broja poruka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1344">**conversation_type** - Tells us what type of email message view was rendered, such as a single message view or multiple message views.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1345">Pomaže nam prepoznati probleme povezane s određenim tipom poruke u našem prikazu razgovora e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1345">Helps us detect issues related to a specific message type in our email conversation view.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1346">**hx_error_type** – govori nam koja je pogreška dogodila uslugu koja je zabranila dovršavanje uklanjanja, ažuriranja ili dodavanja reakcije na poruku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1346">**hx_error_type** - tells us what error occurred that prohibited the service from completing a remove, update, or add reaction on a message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1347">**hx_string_tag** – govori nam oznaku pogreške u kodnoj bazi servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1347">**hx_string_tag** - tells us the tag of the error in the service's codebase</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1348">**reaction_origin** – govori nam izvor iz kojeg je korisnik reagirao</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1348">**reaction_origin** – Tells us origin from where the user reacted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1349">**reaction_type** – govori nam vrstu reakcije korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1349">**reaction_type** – Tells us the reaction type of the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1350">**suggested_reply_char_count** – govori nam koliko znakova predloženi odgovori koje nudimo (ako postoje) imaju kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati neobičnosti i probleme u vezi s našim prijedlozima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1350">**suggested_reply_char_count** - Tells us how many characters the suggested replies we offer (if available) to help us detect anomalies and issues related to our suggestions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1351">**suggested_reply_click_pos** – govori nam na koji je položaj predloženi odgovor (ako postoji) prikazan kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme s određenim prijedlogom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1351">**suggested_reply_click_pos** - Tells us which position the suggested reply (if available) is rendered so we can detect issues with a specific suggestion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1352">**suggested_reply_type** – označava vrstu predloženog odgovora za tu akciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1352">**suggested_reply_type** - indicates type of suggested reply for this action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1353">Moguće su vrijednosti text, send_avail i create_meeting.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1353">Possible values are text, send_avail, and create_meeting.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1354">**use_default_quick_reply_mode** – govori nam koji je zadani način za brzi odgovor korišten kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s doživljajem brzih odgovora za e-poštu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1354">**use_default_quick_reply_mode** - Tells us if the default quick reply mode was used to help us detect issues related to the quick reply experience for email</span></span>

#### <a name="draftaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1355">draft.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1355">draft.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1356">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost kreiranja i spremanja skica pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1356">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to create and save mail drafts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1357">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1357">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1358">**action** – vrsta radnje, npr. spremi, odbaci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1358">**action** - the type of action, for example, save, discard.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1359">**draft_message_id** – ID poruke za skicu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1359">**draft_message_id** - message ID of the draft</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1360">**is_groups** – šalje li se skica u/iz grupne mape</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1360">**is_groups** - whether the draft is being sent to/from a group folder</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1361">**origin** – gdje je skica pokrenuta, npr. pojedinosti o poruci, sastavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1361">**origin** - where draft was initiated, for example, message detail, compose.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1362">**smart_compose_model_version** – prati koja se verzija modela pametnog sastavljanja upotrebljava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1362">**smart_compose_model_version** - tracks which version of smart compose model is being used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1363">**suggestions_requested** – označava koliko ste modela pametnog sastavljanja tražili</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1363">**suggestions_requested** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions requested</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1364">**suggestions_results** – rezultat prijedloga pametnog sastavljanja, tj. prihvaćeno, odbijeno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1364">**suggestions_results** - smart compose suggestions’ result, that is, accepted, rejected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1365">**suggestions_returned** – označava koliko je prijedloga pametnog sastavljanja vraćeno s poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1365">**suggestions_returned** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions returned from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1366">**suggestions_shown** – označava koliko je prijedloga pametnog sastavljanja prikazano korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1366">**suggestions_shown** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions shown to the user</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1367">**thread_id** – ID niti razgovora s kojim je skica povezana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1367">**thread_id** - thread ID of the conversation draft is associated with</span></span>

#### <a name="draganddrop"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1368">drag.and.drop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1368">drag.and.drop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1369">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje prepoznavanje je li radnja povlačenja i ispuštanja bila uspješna ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1369">This event lets us detect if the drag and drop action was successful or not.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1370">To se koristi za osiguravanje da iskustva povlačenja i ispuštanja pravilno funkcioniraju u svim aplikacijama, kako kao događaj povlačenja u Outlook tako i kao događaj povlačenja koji izlazi izvan okvira programa Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1370">It is used to ensure that drag-and-drop experiences are working correctly across applications both as a drop event into Outlook and a drag event that leaves Outlook.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1371">Pomoću ovih podataka možemo osigurati da cjelovito iskustvo s drugim aplikacijama radi kako se očekivalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1371">With this data, we are able to ensure that the end-to-end experience with other applications is working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1372">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1372">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1373">**action** – radnja će biti povlačenje ili ispuštanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1373">**action** - Action will be either drag or drop</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1374">**location** – u slučaju radnje povlačenja, to će nam javiti s koje je lokacije korisnik započeo povlačenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1374">**location** - In case of a drag action, this will let us know from which location the user started the drag.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1375">U slučaju radnje ispuštanja, to će nam javiti gdje je korisnik ispustio datoteku koja se povlačila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1375">In case of a drop action, this will let us know where the user dropped the file that was being dragged.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1376">**source** – u slučaju radnje ispuštanja, to će nam javiti s koje je lokacije korisnik započeo povlačenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1376">**source** – In the case of a drop action, this will let us know from which location the user started the drag.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1377">To nam pomaže da bolje otkrijemo poteškoće s određenim izvorom kao što su OneDrive ili Datoteke u određeno mjesto za ispuštanje, kao što je nova poruka e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1377">This helps us better discover issues with a specific source like OneDrive or Files into a specific drop location, such as a new email.</span></span>

#### <a name="drawerevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1378">drawer.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1378">drawer.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1379">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost pristupanja mapama u vašoj ulaznoj pošti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1379">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to access folders in your inbox</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1380">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1380">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1381">**add_calendar_option** – označava vrstu kalendara koji se dodaje iz ladice, odnosno, zanimljivi kalendar, kalendar pošte, dijeljeni kalendar, kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim vrstama kalendara</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1381">**add_calendar_option** - Indicates the type of calendar being added from the drawer that is, interesting calendar, mail calendar, shared calendar, to help us detect issues related to specific calendar types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1382">**calendar_accounts_count** – označava broj računa kalendara kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s brojem računa koji imate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1382">**calendar_accounts_count** - Indicates the number of calendar accounts to help us detect issues related to number of accounts you have</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1383">**calendar_apps_count** – označava broj aplikacija kalendara predstavljenih na uređaju korisnika kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s aplikacijama kalendara</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1383">**calendar_apps_count** - Indicates the number of calendar apps present on the user's device to help us detect issues related to calendar apps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1384">**drawer_type** – označava vrstu ladice: kalendar, pošta ili nulto pretraživanje kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s vrstom ladice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1384">**drawer_type** - Indicates the drawer type: calendar, mail or zero query to help us detect issues related to the drawer type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1385">**from_favorites** – označava je li radnja preuzeta iz favorita kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s favoritima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1385">**from_favorites** - Indicates if the action was taken from favorites to help us detect issues related to favorites</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1386">**group_calendar_count** – Označava broj kalendara za račun koji će nam pomoći u otkrivanju problema povezanih s grupnim kalendarima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1386">**group_calendar_count** - Indicates the number of calendars for the account to help us detect issues related to group calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1387">**inbox_unread_count** – označava broj nepročitanih poruka u ulaznoj pošti kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme s prikazivanjem količine nepročitanih poruka u ulaznoj pošti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1387">**inbox_unread_count** - Indicates the number of unread messages in the inbox to help us detect issues with displaying inbox unread counts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1388">**interesting_calendar_accounts_count** – označava broj računa koji ispunjavaju uvjete za zanimljive kalendare na uređaju kao bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi sa zanimljivim kalendarima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1388">**interesting_calendar_accounts_count** - Indicates the number of accounts that are eligible for interesting calendars on the device to help us detect issues related to interesting calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1389">**is_group_calendar** – označava je li kalendar grupni kalendar kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s grupnim kalendarima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1389">**is_group_calendar** - Indicates if the calendar is a group calendar to help us detect issues related to group calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1390">**mail_folder_type** – označava vrstu mape pošte, npr. ulazna pošta, skice itd., kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s vrstama mapa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1390">**mail_folder_type** - Indicates the mail folder type that is, inbox, drafts, etc. to help us detect issues related to folder types.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1391">**mail_accounts_count** – označava broj računa pošte kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s računima pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1391">**mail_accounts_count** - indicates the number of mail accounts to help us detect issues related to mail accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1392">**selected_group_calendar_count** – označava broj grupnih kalendara koji su odabrani i aktivni u korisničkom sučelju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1392">**selected_group_calendar_count** - Indicates the number of group calendars that are selected and active in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1393">**visibility_toggle** – označava uključuje li korisnik ili isključuje određeni kalendar kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s prikazivanjem ili skrivanjem kalendara</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1393">**visibility_toggle** - indicates if the user is turning on or off a given calendar to help us detect issues related to showing or hiding calendars</span></span>

#### <a name="ipccreaterepublishinglicense"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1394">IpcCreateRepublishingLicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1394">IpcCreateRepublishingLicense</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1395">Prikuplja se kada korisnik pokuša otvoriti dokument zaštićen IRM-om ili primijeniti zaštite IRM-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1395">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1396">Sadrži informacije potrebne za pravilno istraživanje i dijagnosticiranje problema do kojih dolazi kada se stvori IpcCreateRepublishingLicense poziv API-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1396">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when the IpcCreateRepublishingLicense API call is made.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1397">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1397">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1398">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hijerarhija klijenata koja označava da aplikacija radi u proizvodnom okruženju ili okruženju za razvojne inženjere</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1398">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy, which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1399">**AppInfo.Name** – naziv aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1399">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name</span></span>
