- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1641">**RMS.LicensePropertyType** – vrsta svojstva licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1641">**RMS.LicensePropertyType** - license property type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1642">**RMS.Result** – uspjeh ili neuspjeh poziva API-ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1642">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1643">**RMS.ScenarioId** – identifikacijski broj scenarija definiran API-jem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1643">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario ID defined by the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1644">**RMS.SDKVersion** – verzija klijenta usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1644">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1645">**RMS.StatusCode** – ID scenarija koji je definirao API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1645">**RMS.StatusCode** - Scenario ID defined by the API</span></span>


#### <a name="linkclickedaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1646">link.clicked.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1646">link.clicked.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1647">Taj se događaj upotrebljava za praćenje uspjeha korisnika prilikom pregledavanja URL-a u web-prikazu preglednika Edge i dovršavanja standardnih web scenarija u tom web-prikazu, bez suočavanja s pogreškama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1647">The event is used to track users' success in viewing a URL in the Edge web view and completing standard web scenarios in that web view without facing errors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1648">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1648">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1649">**account_type** – ako je web-prikaz pokrenut iz poruke e-pošte ili događaja u programu Outlook, vrsta računa odakle je URL došao</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1649">**account_type** – if the Edge web view was launched from an email or event in Outlook, type of the account where the URL came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1650">**action** – radnja koju provodi korisnik u programu Outlook od trenutka kada dodirnu URL do trenutka kada izađu iz tog tijeka (otvorili su vezu u web-prikazu preglednika Edge, neuspjelo učitavanje stranice u web-prikazu, provedeno pretraživanje u web-prikazu, izlaz iz web-prikaza preglednika Edge radi otvaranja veze u aplikaciji web-preglednika itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1650">**action** – action performed by the user inside Outlook from the moment they tap on a URL to when they exit that flow (opened the link in the Edge web view, page failed to load in the web view, performed a search in the web view, exit the Edge web view to open the link in a web browser application, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1651">**duration** – trajanje sesije korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1651">**duration** – duration of the user session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1652">**launch_type** – ako je web-prikaz pokrenut u pregledniku Edge, je li pokrenut iz programa Outlook, iz widgeta ili iz komponente OS-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1652">**launch_type** – if the Edge web view was launched, was it from Outlook, from a widget, or from an OS component</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1653">**origin** – ako je korisnik izveo radnju u web-prikazu preglednika Edge, izvor te radnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1653">**origin** – if the user performed an action in the Edge web view, origin of that action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1654">**referrer** – mjesto URL-a koje je korisnik dodirnuo (e-pošta, događaj u kalendaru, TXP kartica itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1654">**referrer** – the location of the URL the user tapped on (email, calendar event, TXP card, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1655">**search_scope** – ako je korisnik pretraživao u web-prikazu preglednika Edge, opseg tog pretraživanja (Sve, Slike, Videozapisi itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1655">**search_scope** – if the user performed a search in the Edge web view, scope of that search (All, Images, Videos, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1656">**search_subtype** – ako je korisnik pretražio u web-prikazu preglednika Edge, je li to bili izvorno pretraživanje ili suženo pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1656">**search_subtype** – if the user performed a search in the Edge web view, was it an initial search or a refined search</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1657">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** – broj stranica koje je korisnik učitao tijekom sesije u web-prikazu preglednika Edge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1657">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** – number of pages loaded by the user during their session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1658">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** – broj Bing pretraživanja koje je korisnik proveo tijekom sesije u web-prikazu preglednika Edge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1658">**session_summary_search_count** - number of Bing searches performed by the user during their session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1659">**session_summary_session_id** – identifikator trenutačne sesije korisnika u web-prikazu preglednika Edge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1659">**session_summary_session_id** – identifier for the present user session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1660">**txp** – ako je web-prikaz preglednika Edge pokrenut iz TXP kartice, vrste događaja za tu karticu (blagovanje, let itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1660">**txp** – if the Edge web view was launched from a TXP card, event type for that card (dining, flight, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1661">**txp_component** – ako je web-prikaz preglednika Edge pokrenut s TXP kartice, vrsta komponente korisničkog sučelja za tu karticu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1661">**txp_component** - if the Edge web view was launched from a TXP card, UI component type for that card</span></span>


#### <a name="mailaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1662">mail.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1662">mail.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1663">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost provedbe ključnih radnji za poštu (poput pokretanja načina poruka u obliku niti, osiguravanja funkcije razvrstavanja pošte) kako bi se osiguralo da naša propisno funkcionira za poštu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1663">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform critical mail actions (like running mail threaded mode, ensuring mail triage actions work) to ensure our app is functioning properly for mail.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1664">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1664">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1665">**account** – račun u okviru kojeg se provela radnja *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1665">**account** - the account that performed the action *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1666">**action** – prati vrstu radnje koja se provela, tj. arhiviranje, brisanje, označavanje kao pročitano itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1666">**action** - tracks what type of action was taking, that is, archive, delete, mark as read, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1667">**attachment_content_type** – vrsta sadržaja preuzetog privitka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1667">**attachment_content_type** - the content type of the downloaded attachment</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1668">**attachment_content_type_with_count** – prati broj privitaka u poruci e-pošte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1668">**attachment_content_type_with_count** - tracks the number of attachments in email</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1669">**attachment_download_result** – rezultat (tj. uspjeh/neuspjeh) za radnju preuzimanja privitka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1669">**attachment_download_result** - the result (that is, success/failure) for an attachment download action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1670">**attachment_download_time** – trajanje radnje preuzimanja privitka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1670">**attachment_download_time** - the time for an attachment download action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1671">**attachment_extn** – datotečni nastavak preuzetog privitka *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1671">**attachment_extn** - the file extension of the downloaded attachment *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1672">**attachment_id** – identifikator sustava za preuzeti privitak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1672">**attachment_id** - the system identifier for the downloaded attachment</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1673">**attachment_size** – veličina preuzetog privitka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1673">**attachment_size** - the size of downloaded attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1674">**domain** – domena dokumenta koji se otvara</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1674">**domain** - domain of the document being opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1675">**duration** – prati koliko je radnja trajala kao čovjeku razumljivi niz na engleskom jeziku (npr. 1s, 4h)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1675">**duration** - tracks how long the action took as human-readable English string (for example, 1s, 4h)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1676">**error** – poruka o pogrešci povezanoj s radnjom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1676">**error** - error message associated with the action</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1677">**event_mode** – u kojem je načinu događaja radnja bila, grupama ili ostalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1677">**event_mode** - what type of event mode it was in, groups or others.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1678">**Extension** – četiri znaka proširenja datoteke veze ili privitka povezanih s tom akcijom  *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz aktualnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali i dalje će se prikazivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1678">**Extension** - four characters of file extension of link or attachment associated with this action  *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1679">**internet_message_id** – ID poruke o praćenju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1679">**internet_message_id** - tracking message ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1680">**is_group_escalation** – označava je li poruka ili radnja provedena u ili je poslana na korisnikov poštanski sandučić zbog eskalacije (pretplata na grupu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1680">**is_group_escalation** - indicates whether the message the action was taken on was sent to the user's mailbox because of an escalation (subscribed to group)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1681">**is_rule** – označava vraća li provedena radnja za poštu fokusiranu/drugu klasifikaciju na izvorne postavke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1681">**is_rule** - indicates if the mail action done is resetting a focused/other classification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1682">**is_threaded_mode** – označava je li poruka bila u obliku niti ili nije, tj. kako su poruke grupirane</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1682">**is_threaded_mode** - indicates whether the message was in threaded mode or not, that is, how are the messages grouped</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1683">**is_unread** – označava je li poruka o tome da je radnja provedena nepročitana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1683">**is_unread** - indicates whether message is unread that the action was taken on</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1684">**left_swipe_setting** – označava koja je radnja postavljena kao radnja pokrenuta prelaskom prstom ulijevo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1684">**left_swipe_setting** - indicates what action was a set to be the left swipe</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1685">**message_id** – ID poruke poslužitelja s ciljem za radnju ili popis odvojen zarezom ako je radnja provedena s više stavki od jedne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1685">**message_id** - server message ID targeted for action, or comma-separated list if more than one item was in action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1686">**message_type** – označava na kojoj je vrsti poruke radnja provedena\*\* – grupne ili druge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1686">**message_type** - indicates what type of message type the action was taken on - group or other</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1687">**number_selected** – broj stavki koje je korisnik odabrao na popisu poruka i poduzeo radnju tijekom višestrukog odabira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1687">**number_selected** - the number of items the user selected on the message list and took action on during multiple selection mode.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1688">**origin** – izvor radnje, tj. prelazak prstom na mobilnom telefonu, nulti upit, dubinska veza, prikaz e-pošte, popis e-pošte itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1688">**origin** - source of action, that is, cell swipe, zero-query, deep link, email view, email list, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1689">**origin_view** – izvorišni prikaz akcija, na primjer, razgovor, poruka itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1689">**origin_view** - source view of action, for example, conversation, message, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1690">**reported_to_msft** – nakon slanja e-pošte u bezvrijednu poštu (neželjenu poštu) ili smeće (krađa identiteta) može se odabrati prijavljivanje radnje Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1690">**reported_to_msft** - after sending an email to junk (spam) or trash (phishing) they can choose to report their action to Microsoft.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1691">**retry** – je li se radnja pokušala ponovno provesti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1691">**retry** - whether the action was retried</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1692">**right_swipe_setting** – označava koja je radnja postavljena kao radnja pokrenuta prelaskom prstom udesno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1692">**right_swipe_setting** - indicates what action was a set to be the right swipe</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1693">**shortcut** – označava je li korišten prečac te koji je prečac korišten za zakazivanje poruke, odnosno, kasnije, sutra, odabir vremena itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1693">**shortcut** - indicates if a shortcut was used and what shortcut was used for scheduling a message that is, later, tomorrow, choose time, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1694">**size** – veličina veze ili privitka povezanog s ovom radnjom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1694">**size** - size of link or attachment associated with this action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1695">**source_folder** – prati vrstu izvorišne mape kada radnja upućuje na premještanje iz jedne mape u drugu, tj. u ulaznu poštu, smeće itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1695">**source_folder** - tracks source folder type when action is indicating to move from one folder to other, that is, to inbox, trash etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1696">**source_inbox** – označava u kojoj se ulaznoj pošti radnja za poštu provodi (odnosno fokusirana, drugo itd.) state – stanje radnje, odnosno, točka uspjeha ili neuspjeha</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1696">**source_inbox** - indicates which inbox the mail action is taking place (that is, focused, other, etc.) state - state of the action, that is, success or point of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1697">**state** – stanje radnje, tj. točka uspjeha ili točka neuspjeha</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1697">**state** - state of the action, that is, success or point of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1698">**target_folder** – označava vrstu odredišne mape tijekom premještanja poruka e-pošte iz jedne mape u drugu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1698">**target_folder** - indicates target folder type when moving emails from one folder to other</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1699">**thread_id** – ID niti razgovora ciljanog za akciju ili popisa odvojenog zarezom ako je ciljano više od jedne stavke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1699">**thread_id** - thread ID of the conversation targeted for action, or comma-separated list if more than one item was targeted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1700">**time_taken_to_fetch_access_token** – vrijeme potrebno za dohvaćanje tokena za pristup sustavu koji se koristi za otvaranje veze</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1700">**time_taken_to_fetch_access_token** - time taken to fetch a system access token to use for opening a link</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1701">**time_taken_to_fetch_drive_item** – vrijeme potrebno za dohvaćanje resursa servisa OneDrive kada se klikne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1701">**time_taken_to_fetch_drive_item** - time taken to fetch a OneDrive resource when clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1702">**time_taken_to_fetch_embed_viewer_resource** – vrijeme potrebno za pokretanje ugrađenog preglednika tijekom otvaranja veza</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1702">**time_taken_to_fetch_embed_viewer_resource** - time taken to initialize the embedded viewer when opening links</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1703">**time_taken_to_load_embed_viewer** – vrijeme potrebno za pokretanje ugrađenog preglednika tijekom otvaranja veza</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1703">**time_taken_to_load_embed_viewer** - time taken to initialize the embedded viewer when opening links</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1704">**time_taken_to_load_link** – vrijeme potrebno za dovršavanje radnje učitavanja veze</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1704">**time_taken_to_load_link** - time a load link action takes to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1705">**time_taken_to_tap_attachment** – vrijeme između otvaranja poruke i klika na privitak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1705">**time_taken_to_tap_attachment** - the time between opening the message and clicking on the attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1706">**time_taken_to_tap_link** – vrijeme koje je korisniku bilo potrebno između pregleda poruke i klika na vezu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1706">**time_taken_to_tap_link** - time the user took between viewing message and clicking a link</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1707">**txp** – označava postoji li stavka vrste txp povezana s poštom na kojoj je ta radnja provedena, odnosno, rezervacija događaja, rezervacija leta itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1707">**txp** - indicates if there is a txp type of item associated with the mail that action was taken on, that is, event reservation, flight reservation, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1708">**type** – vrsta dokumenta koji se otvara putem veze</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1708">**type** - document type being opened via link</span></span>

#### <a name="mailcompose"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1709">mail.compose</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1709">mail.compose</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1710">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost sastavljanja i odgovaranja na poruke e-pošte, na primjer nailaženje na probleme s odgovaranjem svima, formatiranjem vaših poruka e-pošte ili slanjem vaših poruka e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1710">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to compose and reply to emails such as running into issues with reply-all, formatting your email, or sending your emails.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1711">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1711">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1712">**draft_message_id** – ID skice razgovora koji se stvara kao skica kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi sa skicama poruka e-pošte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1712">**draft_message_id** - The draft ID of the conversation being created as a draft to help us detect issues related to draft emails</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1713">**message_id** – ID poruke razgovora na koji se odgovara ili iz kojeg se prosljeđuje kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenom porukom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1713">**message_id** - The message ID of the conversation being replied to or forwarded from to help us detect issues related to a specific message</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1714">**origin** – govori nam o podrijetlu poruke, primjerice kao odgovaranje svima, kreiranje nove poruke ili brzi odgovor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1714">**origin** - Tells us where the compose originated from, such as from a reply all, a new compose, or quick reply.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1715">Pomaže nam prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenom vrstom podrijetla odgovora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1715">Helps us detect issues associated with a specific reply origin type.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1716">**is_group_escalation** – govori nam je li poruka eskalirana grupna poruka kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme sa sastavljanjem povezane s grupama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1716">**is_group_escalation** - Whether the message is an escalated group message so we can detect compose issues related to groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1717">**is_link** – govori nam je li se stvaranje nove skice provelo iz veze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1717">**is_link** - Tells us if the new draft that was created was done from a link.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1718">Pomaže nam prepoznati probleme u vezi sa skicama stvorenim iz veza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1718">Helps us detect issues associated with drafts created from links.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1719">**is_force_touch** – govori nam je li se stvaranje nove skice provelo iz radnje prisilnog dodira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1719">**is_force_touch** - Tells us if the new draft that was created was done from a force touch action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1720">Pomaže nam prepoznati probleme u vezi sa skicama stvorenim iz ove specifične radnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1720">Helps us detect issues associated with drafts created from this specific action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1721">**is_groups** – je li događaj pokrenut iz prostora grupe kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme sa sastavljanjem u vezi s grupama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1721">**is_groups** - Whether the event was started from the groups' space so we can detect compose issues related to groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1722">**source_inbox** – govori nam koja je izvorna ulazna pošta, primjerice je li to bila fokusirana ili druga ulazna pošta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1722">**source_inbox** - Tells us the source inbox, such as whether it was a focused or other inbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1723">**thread_id** – ID niti razgovora na koji se odgovara ili iz kojeg se prosljeđuje kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim nizom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1723">**thread_id** - The thread ID of the conversation being replied to or forwarded from to help us detect issues related to a specific thread</span></span>

#### <a name="meetingcalltoaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1724">meeting.call.to.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1724">meeting.call.to.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1725">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost provedbe ključnih radnji sastanka kao što su kreiranje, uređivanje i odgovaranje na sastanke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1725">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform critical meeting actions like creating, editing, and responding to meetings.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1726">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1726">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1727">**event_mode** – označava potječe li ovaj događaj iz grupe ili ne kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s grupnim događajima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1727">**event_mode** - Indicates whether this event was from a group or not to help us detect issues with group events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1728">**meeting_id** – ID sastanka koji nam pomaže pratiti probleme tijekom cijelog trajanja sastanka kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim sastancima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1728">**meeting_id** - A meeting ID that helps us track issues throughout the lifetime of a meeting to help us detect issues with specific meetings</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1729">**meeting_provider** – označava davatelja usluga za mrežni sastanak, na primjer, Teams, Skype za tvrtke, kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim davateljima usluga mrežnih sastanaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1729">**meeting_provider** - Indicates the provider for an online meeting, for example, Teams, Skype for Business to help us detect issues with specific online meeting providers</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1730">**notify_type** – označava vrstu odgovora za druge vrste računa kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s različitim vrstama računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1730">**notify_type** - Indicates the response type for other account types to help us detect issues with different account types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1731">**recurrence** – označava koliko se često ovaj sastanak održava, odnosno, jedanput ili niz, kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s nizovima ponavljajućih sastanaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1731">**recurrence** - Indicates how often this meeting occurs that is, occurrence or series to help us detect issues with reoccurring meeting series</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1732">**response** – označava vrstu odgovora kao što je prihvaćanje ili odbijanje na određenim vrstama računa kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s odgovaranjem na događaje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1732">**response** - Indicates response type such as accept or decline on certain account types to help us detect issues with responding to events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1733">**response_message_length** – označava duljinu poruke kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s odgovorima na sastanak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1733">**response_message_length** - Indicates how long the message length was to help us detect issues with meeting responses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1734">**review_time_proposal_action_type** – označava odgovor korisnika za predlaganje novog vremena kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s predlaganjem novog vremena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1734">**review_time_proposal_action_type** - Indicates a user response new time proposal to help us detect issues with proposing a new time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1735">**send_response** – označava je li odgovor poslan kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi sa slanjem odgovora na pozivnice na sastanak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1735">**send_response** - Indicates whether a response was sent to help us detect issues sending meeting invite responses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1736">**txp** – označava iz koje je vrste sastanka stvoren, npr. rezervacije letova i isporuke, kako bi nam mogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s ovom vrstom sastanka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1736">**txp** - Indicates what type of meeting it was generated from flight reservations and deliveries to help us detect issues with this type of meeting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1737">**with_message_enabled** – označava može li korisnik odgovoriti porukom kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s odgovaranjem na pozivnice na sastanak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1737">**with_message_enabled** - Indicates whether a user can respond with a message to help us detect issues with responding to meeting invites</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroiddocsuifileoperationsopendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1738">Office.Android.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1738">Office.Android.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1739">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje se pokreću na platformi Android i evidentira kada se provodi radnja otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1739">This event is collected for Office applications running under Android platform and records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1740">Događaj pomaže jamčiti da je radnja otvaranja datoteke sigurna, ažurna i da se pravilno provodi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1740">The event helps in keeping the file open operation secure, up- to- date and performing properly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1741">Cilj prikupljanja ovih podataka jest kontinuirano poboljšanje funkcije otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1741">The goal of collecting this data is to continuously improve the file open performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1742">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1742">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1743">**Data_AppDocsOperationDuration** – trajanje podsloja tijekom radnje otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1743">**Data_AppDocsOperationDuration** - The duration spent in sub- layer during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1744">**Data_AppDuration** – trajanje obrade aplikacije tijekom radnje otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1744">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1745">**Data_AppWarmUpGain** – dobitak ostvaren u trajanju pokretanja aplikacije zbog prethodnog pokretanja dijela aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1745">**Data_AppWarmUpGain** - The gain in application boot duration we get because of pre-booting a part of the application beforehand.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1746">**Data_BootDuration** – trajanje pokretanja aplikacije tijekom radnje otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1746">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of application boot in process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1747">**Data_BootMarkers** – vrijednost niza koja evidentira trajanje vremena između nekih poziva funkcije tijekom pokretanja aplikacije, u obliku s ID-om i trajanjem funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1747">**Data_BootMarkers** – A string value logging the time duration between some function calls when booting the application, in a format with function ID and duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1748">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – u nekim se scenarijima otvaranja datoteka zatvaranje prethodno otvorenog dokumenta odvija prije otvaranja trenutačnog dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1748">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – In some file open scenarios, closing of a previously opened document takes place before the opening of the current document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1749">Trajanje razdoblja između nekih operacija koje se odvijaju u tom slučaju bilježe se u vrijednosti niza koja ima oblik \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1749">This time duration between some of the operations that take place in this case is captured in a string value that has the format \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1750">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – enumeracija koja upućuje na način pristupa datoteke, na primjer, samo za čitanje, za čitanje i pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1750">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, for example, read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1751">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu asinkronog toka koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1751">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1752">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu algoritma dijeljenja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1752">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1753">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – enumeracija koja upućuje na stanje korporacijske zaštite podataka datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1753">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1754">**Data_Doc_Ext** – Datotečni nastavak datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1754">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1755">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1755">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1756">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – globalno jedinstveni identifikator (GUID) koji jedinstveno identificira naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1756">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1757">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira identitet koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1757">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1758">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – enumeracija koja upućuje na detaljnu vrstu scenarija otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1758">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1759">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – enumeracija koja označava zastavice UI operacije otvaranja datoteke, na primjer, ako je datoteka predmemorirana ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1759">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, for example, if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1760">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled**– bez obzira na to je li za datoteku omogućena suradnja u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1760">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1761">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka otvorena inkrementalno ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1761">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1762">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – bez obzira na to podržava li datoteka uslugu suradnje u sustavu Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1762">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1763">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka otvorena iz izvanmrežne predmemorirane kopije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1763">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1764">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka unaprijed dohvaćena prije operacije otvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1764">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1765">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – bez obzira na to postoji li datoteka oblaka lokalno i je li sinkronizirana s poslužiteljem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1765">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1766">**Data_Doc_Location** – enumeracija koja upućuje gdje se datoteka nalazi, na primjer, lokalno ili u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1766">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, for example, locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1767">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – enumeracija koja označava razlog zbog kog je datoteka samo za čitanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1767">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1768">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira ID resursa poslužitelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1768">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource ID of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1769">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – enumeracija koja označava vrstu kanala u stvarnom vremenu (RTC) koji se koristi u datoteci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1769">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1770">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira ID dokumenta poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1770">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1771">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – enumeracija koja označava poslužiteljski protokol datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1771">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1772">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – enumeracija koja označava vrstu poslužitelja datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1772">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1773">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – enumeracija koja označava verziju poslužitelja datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1773">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1774">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – cijeli broj koji se povećava za 1 za svaku operaciju otvaranja datoteke u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1774">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer that is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1775">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – niz koji se koristi za povezivanje klijentskih i poslužiteljskih zapisnika, obično je vrsta ID-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1775">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client- side and server- side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1776">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – veličina datoteke u bajtovima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1776">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1777">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – enumeracija koja označava kakav poseban znak ima URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1777">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1778">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1778">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1779">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka otvorena inkrementalno pomoću predmemoriranih WRS podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1779">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre- cached WRS data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1817">Omogućujemo ekspanzijske datoteke za komplet paketa za Android (APK) za mobilnu aplikaciju Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1817">We are enabling Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1818">Ekspanzijske datoteke APK-a jesu dopunske datoteke resursa koje razvojni programeri aplikacija na sustavu Android mogu objaviti zajedno sa svojom aplikacijom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1818">APK Expansion files are supplementary resource files that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1819">Da bi se razumjela pouzdanost ekspanzijskih datoteka, bilježimo zastavicu koja pri svakom pokretanju označava jesu li dostupne ekspanzijske datoteke ili nisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1819">To understand the reliability of the expansion files, we log a flag indicating whether expansion files are available or not at every boot.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1823">Omogućujemo ekspanzijske datoteke za komplet paketa za Android (APK) za mobilnu aplikaciju Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1823">We are enabling Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1824">Ekspanzijske datoteke APK-a jesu dopunske datoteke resursa koje razvojni programeri aplikacija na sustavu Android mogu objaviti zajedno sa svojom aplikacijom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1824">APK Expansion files are supplementary resource files, that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1825">Da bi se razumjela pouzdanost našeg mehanizma preuzimanja ekspanzijskih datoteka, zapisujemo zastavicu koja označava možemo li uspješno preuzeti ekspanzijske datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1825">To understand the reliability of our expansion file download mechanism, we are logging a flag indicating whether we are successfully able to download expansion files.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1835">**NoteLocalId** – prepoznatljiv jedinstveni identifikator dodijeljen bilješci u vrijeme kada korisnik stvori bilješku unutar aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1835">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1836">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** – broj verzije koji označava verziju aplikacije Sticky Notes koju korisnik koristi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1836">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1837">Omogućuje prepoznavanje verzija proizvoda s kojima se pojavljuje problem kako bismo mogli ispravno odrediti njegov prioritet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1837">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1847">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** – broj verzije koji označava verziju aplikacije Sticky Notes koju korisnik koristi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1847">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1848">Omogućuje prepoznavanje verzija proizvoda s kojima se pojavljuje problem kako bismo mogli ispravno odrediti njegov prioritet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1848">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunecompliancerequest"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1849">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1849">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1850">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office na platformi Android, uključujući Office Mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint i OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1850">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, including Office mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and OneNote.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1851">Događaj označava pokušaj prijave na račun ustanove ili tvrtke s licencom za Intune za koji je administrator tvrtke ili ustanove konfigurirao pravilnike za uvjetni pristup aplikacijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1851">The event indicates an attempt to sign in to an Intune licensed organization account where the organization administrator has configured policy to enforce app conditional access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1852">Koristi se za razumijevanje broja krajnjih korisnika koji pokušavaju koristiti aplikacije u okviru ove konfiguracije pravilnika i kombinira s drugim događajem, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus, radi osiguravanja provedbe konfiguriranog pravilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1852">It is used to understand the number of end users who are attempting to use apps under this policy configuration, and is combined with another event, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus, to ensure the configured policy is enforced.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1853">Ne prikupljaju se nikakva polja podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1853">No data fields are collected.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunecompliancestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1854">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1854">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1855">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office na platformi Android, uključujući Office Mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint i OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1855">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, including Office mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and OneNote.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1856">Događaj označava pokušaj prijave na račun ustanove ili tvrtke s licencom za Intune za koji je administrator tvrtke ili ustanove konfigurirao pravilnike za uvjetni pristup aplikacijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1856">The event indicates an attempt to sign in to an Intune licensed organization account where the organization administrator has configured policy to enforce app conditional access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1857">Ovaj događaj označava status usklađivanja aplikacije u koju se korisnik prijavio i koristi se za istraživanje kvarova.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1857">This event indicates the compliance status of the application to which the user has signed-in and is used to investigate failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1858">Kombinira se s drugim događajem, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest, radi osiguravanja provedbe konfiguriranog pravilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1858">It is combined with another event, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest, to ensure the configured policy is enforced.</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1859">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1859">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1860">**Data_ComplianceStatus** – označava status usklađenosti aplikacije tijekom prijave s kodom pogreške za uspjeh ili neuspjeh.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1860">**Data_ComplianceStatus** - Indicates the compliance status of the application during sign-in with a success or failure error code.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1861">-1 – Nepoznata pogreška</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1861">-1 – Unknown error</span></span>
  -    <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1862">0 – Aplikacija je u skladu s pravilnicima ustanove ili tvrtke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1862">0 – The application is compliant with the organization policies</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1863">1 – Aplikacija nije u skladu s pravilnicima ustanove ili tvrtke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1863">1 – The application is not compliant with the organization policies</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1864">2 – Kvarovi u vezi sa servisom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1864">2 – Service-related failures</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1865">3 – Kvarovi u vezi s mrežom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1865">3 – Network-related failures</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1866">4 – Aplikacija nije uspjela dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1866">4 – Application failed to retrieve authentication token</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1867">5 – Odgovor usluge još nije primljen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1867">5 – The response has not been yet received from the service</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1868">6 – Potrebno je instalirati aplikaciju portala tvrtke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1868">6 – The company portal application needs to be installed</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidodwxpssotelemetry"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1869">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1869">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1870">Ovaj događaj pomaže u razumijevanju s kojom drugom Microsoftovom aplikacijom na uređaju, naša aplikacija se tiho jedinstveno prijavila, s koje ulazne točke i tako dalje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1870">This event helps in understanding with which other Microsoft app in the device, our app got silent single sign on, from which entry point and so on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1871">Također pomaže u razumijevanju razloga neuspjeha zbog kojeg nije došlo do tihe jedinstvene prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1871">Also helps in understanding the failure reason for not getting silent single sign on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1872">Dobivamo bolje uvide, primjerice, iz koje Microsoftove aplikacije na uređaju, dobivamo iskustvo jedinstvene prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1872">We get better insights like from which Microsoft app in the device, we are getting single sign on experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1873">Djelujte prema neuspjesima, gdje jedinstvena prijava ne funkcionira prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1873">Act upon failures, where single sign on is not working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1874">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1874">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1875">**AccountType** – označava vrstu računa koji se odnosi na jedinstvenu prijavu, poput osobnog Microsoftovog računa ili poslovnog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1875">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which single sign on is happening, like personal Microsoft account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1876">**EntryPoint** – označava ulaznu točku u aplikaciji, odakle je pokrenuta jedinstvena prijava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1876">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where single sign on attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1877">**ErrorCode** – označava kôd pogreške pri pokušaju jedinstvene prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1877">**ErrorCode** - Indicates the error code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1878">**ErrorDescription** – označava poruku o pogrešci pri pokušaju jedinstvene prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1878">**ErrorDescription** - Indicates the error message of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1879">**HResult** – označava kôd statusa rezultata pri pokušaju jedinstvene prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1879">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1880">**ProviderPackageId** – druga Microsoftova aplikacija na uređaju na kojoj se odvija jedinstvena prijava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1880">**ProviderPackageId** - Other Microsoft app in the device from which single sign on is happening.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidphonenumbersignins"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1881">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1881">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1882">Ovaj događaj pomaže u razumijevanju ako je korisnik prijavljen ili se registrirao s računom koji se temelji na telefonskom broju ili na temelju osobnog Microsoftova računa e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1882">This event helps in understanding if user signed in or signed up with phone number-based account or email based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1883">Ovaj događaj pomaže u saznanju broja korisnika koji se prijavljuju ili registriraju pomoću osobnog Microsoftovog računa temeljenog na telefonskom broju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1883">This event helps in knowing count of users signing in or signing up with phone number based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1884">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1884">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1885">**EntryPoint** – označava ulaznu točku u aplikaciji, odakle je pokrenut pokušaj prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1885">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1886">**IsEmailMissing** – nedostaje li e-pošta u podacima profila računa?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1886">**IsEmailMissing** - Is email missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1887">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** – nedostaje li telefonski broj u podacima profila računa?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1887">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** - Is phone number missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1888">**UserDecision** – označava izbor koji je odabrao korisnik, poput prijave ili registracije ili kasnije prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1888">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidusersignindecision"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1889">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1889">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1890">Ovaj događaj pomaže u razumijevanju u kojoj se fazi korisnik odbacuje u tijeku prijave, zašto prijava ne uspijeva, koliko se korisnika uspješno prijavilo, s koje ulazne točke u aplikaciji i tako dalje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1890">This event helps in understanding at which stage user is dropping in sign in flow, why sign in is failing, how many users are getting signed in successfully from which entry point in the app and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1891">Ovaj događaj pomaže s podacima o kanalima za prijavu, što pomaže u razumijevanju u kojoj se fazi korisnici više odbacuju i slično.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1891">This event helps with sign-in funnel data, which helps in understand at which stage users are getting dropped more and so on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1892">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1892">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1893">**AccountType** – označava vrstu računa s kojim je pokušana prijava, poput osobnog ili radnog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1893">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which sign-in is attempted like personal account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1894">**AfterLicensingState** – upućuje na stanje licenciranja aplikacije nakon dovršene prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1894">**AfterLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state after sign-in completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1895">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** – označava koliko je besplatnih izmjena isteklo prije pokušaja prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1895">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** - Indicates how many free edits have lapsed before sign-in was attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1896">**BeforeLicensingState** – upućuje na stanje licenciranja aplikacije prije pokušaja prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1896">**BeforeLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state before sign-in attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1897">**CompletionState** – označava fazu završetka prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1897">**CompletionState** - Indicates the stage of sign-in completion.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1898">**EntryPoint** – označava ulaznu točku u aplikaciji, odakle je pokrenut pokušaj prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1898">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1899">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** – upućuje na broj pokušaja ubrzane registracije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1899">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1900">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** – upućuje na broj otkazanih ubrzanih registracija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1900">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups canceled.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1901">**HResult** – označava kôd statusa rezultata operacije prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1901">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the sign-in operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1902">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** – je li dopuštena prijava na temelju telefonskog broja ili nije?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1902">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** - Is phone number-based sign-in allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1903">**LicenseActivationHResult** – označava kôd statusa pokušaja aktivacije licence.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1903">**LicenseActivationHResult** - Indicates the status code of license activation attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1904">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** – označava kôd poruke iz usluge licenciranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1904">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** - Indicates the message code from licensing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1905">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** – je li dopušteno besplatno uređivanje ili ne?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1905">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** - Is free edits allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1906">**SignUpAttemptCount** – upućuje na broj pokušaja prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1906">**SignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1907">**StartMode** – označava način u kojem je pokrenut pokušaj prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1907">**StartMode** - Indicates the mode in which sign-in attempt was started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1908">**UserDecision** – označava izbor koji je odabrao korisnik, poput prijave ili registracije ili kasnije prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1908">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentscanandupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1909">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1909">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1910">Prikuplja se samo kada je krajnji korisnik omogućio telemetrijsku nadzornu ploču sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1910">Only collected when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1911">Prikuplja informacije o tome kada se izvršava telemetrijski agent sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1911">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent is executed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1912">  Prikuplja se samo kada je omogućena telemetrijska nadzorna ploča sustava Office i služi za utvrđivanje stanja telemetrijskog agenta sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1912">This is only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard is enabled and is used to determine the health of Office Telemetry agent.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1913">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1913">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1914">**Data.AgentExit** – vremenska oznaka uspješnog zatvaranja telemetrijskog agenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1914">**Data.AgentExit** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent exits successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1915">**Data.AgentScan** – vremenska oznaka uspješnog dovršavanja pregleda telemetrijskog agenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1915">**Data.AgentScan** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completed a scan successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1916">**Data.AgentUpload** – vremenska oznaka uspješnog učitavanja telemetrijskog agenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1916">**Data.AgentUpload** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completes the upload successfully</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1917">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1917">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1918">Stvara se tijekom pokretanja korisnika kada je krajnji korisnik omogućio telemetrijsku nadzornu ploču sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1918">Generated on client startup when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1919">Prikuplja informacije o tome kada je telemetrijski agent sustava Office prenio podatke u mapu za zajedničko korištenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1919">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent has uploaded data to the share folder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1920">Primarno korištenje ovog događaja jest nadzirati stanje telemetrijskog agenta sustava Office, a sekundarno korištenje događaja jest procijeniti korištenje telemetrijske nadzorne ploče sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1920">The primary use of this event is to monitor the health of the Office Telemetry agent and the secondary use of the event is to estimate usage of the Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1921">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1921">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1922">**UploadTime** – vremenska oznaka posljednjeg uspješnog prijenosa koji je proveo telemetrijski agent.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1922">**UploadTime** - the timestamp of the last successful upload performed by the Telemetry Agent.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompattelemetrydashboardresiliencycrashlog"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1923">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1923">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1924">Prikuplja se samo kada je krajnji korisnik (najčešće administrator) omogućio telemetrijsku nadzornu ploču sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1924">Only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard has been enabled by end user (most likely an admin).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1925">Prikuplja pojavu rušenja dodataka i dokumenata sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1925">It collects the occurrence of Office Add-ins and documents crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1926"> Prikuplja se samo kada je korisnik omogućio telemetrijsku nadzornu ploču sustava Office i služi za utvrđivanje povećane pojave rušenja dodataka ili dokumenata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1926">This is only collected when user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard and is used to determine if there is an increased occurrence of add-in or document crashes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-1927">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1927">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1928">**Data.CollectionTime** – vremenska oznaka zapisivanja događaja rušenja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1928">**Data.CollectionTime** - Timestamp of when a crash event was logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1936">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – enumeracija koja upućuje na način pristupa datoteci, na primjer, samo za čitanje, za čitanje i pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1936">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, for example, read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-1937">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu asinkronog toka koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1937">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappleactivateperpetual"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-1992">Office.Apple.ActivatePerpetual</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-1992">Office.Apple.ActivatePerpetual</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2066">Taj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office na uređajima sa sustavom Android, iOS, Universal ili Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2066">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal, or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2067">Događaj bilježi kada se operacija otvaranja datoteke odvija pomoću puta navedenog na popisu nedavnih datoteka te se koristi za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta pogrešaka korisničkog doživljaja na temelju podataka o operaciji otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2067">The event records when a file open operation takes place from the path provided in the most recently used list and is used to understand and prioritize user-experience errors based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2068">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2068">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2069">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – ID aplikacije kada nije poznat prije okončanja izvješća za operaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2069">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – App ID when not known before report end called on the operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2070">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – stanje CanContinue prije uključivanja rukovatelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2070">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – CanContinue state, before the begin handler is invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2071">**Data_DetachedDuration** – trajanje procesa odvajanja događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2071">**Data_DetachedDuration** – The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2072">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – enumeracija koja upućuje na način pristupa datoteci, na primjer, samo za čitanje, za čitanje i pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2072">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, for example, read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2073">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu asinkronog toka koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2073">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2074">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu algoritma podjele datoteke na blokove.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2074">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2075">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – enumeracija koja upućuje na stanje korporacijske zaštite podataka datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2075">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2076">**Data_Doc_Ext** – prva četiri znaka datotečnog nastavka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2076">**Data_Doc_Ext** – First 4 characters of the extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2077">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2077">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2078">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2078">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2079">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta kojim se izvršava otvaranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2079">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open.</span></span>
