#### <a name="officedocsappdocsoperationopenfromprotocolhandler"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2239">Office.Docs.AppDocs.OperationOpenFromProtocolHandler</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2239">Office.Docs.AppDocs.OperationOpenFromProtocolHandler</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2240">Taj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office na uređajima sa sustavom Android, iOS, Universal ili Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2240">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal, or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2241">Događaj bilježi kada se operacija otvaranja datoteke odvija iz neke druge aplikacije putem sučelja rukovatelja protokolima te se koristi za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka o operaciji otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2241">The event records when a file open operation takes place from another application using the protocol handler interface and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2242">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2242">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2243">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – ID aplikacije kada nije poznat prije okončanja izvješća za operaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2243">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – App ID when not known before report end called on the operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2244">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – stanje CanContinue prije uključivanja rukovatelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2244">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – CanContinue state, before the begin handler is invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2245">**Data_DetachedDuration** – trajanje procesa odvajanja događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2245">**Data_DetachedDuration** – The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2246">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – enumeracija koja upućuje na način pristupa datoteci, na primjer, samo za čitanje, za čitanje i pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2246">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, for example, read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2247">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu asinkronog toka koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2247">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2248">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu algoritma podjele datoteke na blokove.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2248">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2249">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – enumeracija koja upućuje na stanje korporacijske zaštite podataka datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2249">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2250">**Data_Doc_Ext** – prva četiri znaka datotečnog nastavka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2250">**Data_Doc_Ext** – First 4 characters of the extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2251">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2251">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2252">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2252">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2253">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta kojim se izvršava otvaranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2253">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2259">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – je li datoteka otvorena iz izvanmrežne predmemorirane kopije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2259">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2261">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – postoji li datoteka oblaka lokalno i je li sinkronizirana s poslužiteljem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2261">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappledocsuxiossaveasthroughfilemenu"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2413">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2413">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2414">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2414">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2415">Događaj se bilježi kada se odvija operacija „Spremi kao” i koristi se za razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka o radu datoteke, poput kategorija lokacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2415">The event records when a "Save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2416">Operacija „Spremi kao” događa se kada god korisnik stvori novu datoteku i spremi je prvi put ili spremi kopiju postojeće datoteke na novu lokaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2416">A "Save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2417">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2417">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2418">**Data_OriginServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija izvorne lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2418">**Data_OriginServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the original location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2419">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija nove lokacije datoteke nakon dovršetka spremanja kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive” „Lokalno”, „WOPI”, itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2419">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the new location of a file after the save is completed like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappledocsuxmacatmentioninsertedatmention"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2420">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXMacAtMentionInsertedAtMention</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2420">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXMacAtMentionInsertedAtMention</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2421">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2421">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2422">Taj događaj bilježi kada korisnik „@” spominje drugog korisnika i koristi se za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju načina na koji korisnici surađuju s drugim korisnicima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2422">This event records when a user "@" mentions another user and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on how users collaborate with other users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2423">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2423">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2424">**Data_CharactersTyped** – numerička vrijednost koja označava ukupni broj znakova unesenih u spomenuti tekst „@”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2424">**Data_CharactersTyped** - A numerical value that indicates the total number of characters typed in the "@" mention text.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappledocsuxmacodspsharingwebviewsharingcompleted"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2425">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2425">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2426">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2426">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2427">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik izabere zajedničko korištenje dokumenta u oblaku pomoću značajke zajedničkog korištenja servisa OneDrive i koristi se za bolje razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju zajedničkog korištenja dokumenata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2427">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2428">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2428">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2429">**Data_ShareType** – niz ugrađen u kod koji označava koja vrsta operacije zajedničkog korištenja je dovršena, uključujući, ali ne ograničavajući se na „Kopiraj vezu”, „Više aplikacija”, „Teams”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2429">**Data_ShareType** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share operation was completed including but not limited to "Copy Link", "More apps", "Teams".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2430">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** – niz ugrađen u kod koji označava koji način rada za zajedničko korištenje je bio aktivan kada je zajedničko korištenje dovršeno uključujući, ali ne ograničavajući se na „Upravljanje pristupom”, „Spominjanja”, „Zajedničko korištenje”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2430">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share mode was active when the share was completed including but not limited to "ManageAccess", "AtMentions", "Share".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuicollaborationcoauthorgalleryrowtapped"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2431">Office.DocsUI.Collaboration.CoauthorGalleryRowTapped</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2431">Office.DocsUI.Collaboration.CoauthorGalleryRowTapped</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2432">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2432">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2433">Ovaj događaj bilježi kada korisnik izabere pregled popisa trenutnih suautora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2433">This event records when a user selects to look at the list of current co-authors.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2434">Ti se podaci koriste za bolje razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkih iskustava koji se odnose na istodobno suautorstvo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2434">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2435">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2435">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2436">**Data_CoauthorCount** – Numerička vrijednost koja predstavlja ukupni broj osoba koje trenutno uređuju isti dokument kao i korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2436">**Data_CoauthorCount** - A numerical value that represents the total number of people who are currently editing the same document as the user.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuicollaborationcollabcornerpeoplegallerycoauthorsupdated"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2437">Office.DocsUI.Collaboration.CollabCornerPeopleGalleryCoauthorsUpdated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2437">Office.DocsUI.Collaboration.CollabCornerPeopleGalleryCoauthorsUpdated</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2438">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2438">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2439">Događaj bilježi kada se promijeni broj aktivnih suautora u dokumentu u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2439">The event records when the number of active co-authors in a cloud document changes.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2440">Ti se podaci koriste za bolje razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkih iskustava koji se odnose na istodobno suautorstvo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2440">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2441">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2441">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2442">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** – broj suautora koji su se pridružili dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2442">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** - The number of co-authors that joined the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2443">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** – broj suautora koji su napustili dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2443">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** - The number of co-authors that left the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2444">**Data_NewCoauthorCount** – novi broj aktivnih suautora u dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2444">**Data_NewCoauthorCount** - The new count of active co-authors in the document.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2445">**Data_OldCoauthorCount** – prethodni broj aktivnih suautora prije ažuriranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2445">**Data_OldCoauthorCount** - The previous count of active co-authors before the update.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2446">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2446">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuidocstagedocstagecreatenewfromtemplate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2447">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2447">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2448">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2448">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2449">Događaj bilježi kada se stvara nova datoteka iz sučelja „Novo iz predloška” i koristi se za bolje razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka o stvaranju dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2449">The event records when a new file is created from the "New from template" experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on document creation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2450">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2450">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2451">**Data_InHomeTab** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li nova datoteka iz predloška stvorena na kartici Polazno novog sučelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2451">**Data_InHomeTab** - A Boolean value that indicates whether the new file from template was created from the Home tab of the file new experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2452">**Data_InSearch** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li datoteka stvorena kada je korisnik tražio predložak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2452">**Data_InSearch** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2453">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li kartica Polazno trenutno dostupna korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2453">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2454">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li korisniku trenutno dostupno sučelje „Preporučeno”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2454">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2455">**Data_TemplateIndex** – numerički indeks datoteke predloška dok se vizualno prikazuje korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2455">**Data_TemplateIndex** - The numerical index of the template file as it is displayed visually to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2456">**Data_TemplateType** – klasifikacija koja će vam pomoći u razlikovanju vrste predložaka poput, ali ne ograničavajući se na „Mrežne predloške”, predloške „Mrežnog pretraživanja”, „Lokalne” predloške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2456">**Data_TemplateType** - A classification to help distinguish the type of template like, but not limited to, "Online" templates, "Online search" templates, "Local" templates.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuidocstagerecommendedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2457">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.RecommendedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2457">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.RecommendedOpen</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2458">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2458">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2459">Događaj bilježi kada se operacija otvaranja datoteke odvija iz odjeljka s preporučenim datotekama galerije dokumenata i koristi se za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka operacije otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2459">The event records when a file-open operation takes place from the recommended files section of the document gallery and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2460">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2460">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2461">**Data_Success** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li operacija uspjela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2461">**Data_Success** - A Boolean value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsdocsuifileopenmacrequired"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2462">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2462">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2463">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2463">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2464">Događaj bilježi operaciju otvaranja datoteke i koristi se za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka operacije otvaranja datoteke kao što su kategorije lokacije „ServiceType” i prva četiri znaka proširenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2464">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2465">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2465">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2466">**Data_Ext** – Datotečni nastavak ograničen na prva četiri znaka proširenja ili manje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2466">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2467">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2467">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsopendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2468">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2468">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2469">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na iOS platformi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2469">This event is collected for Office applications running under iOS platform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2470">Događaj bilježi kada se operacija otvaranja datoteke odvija i koristi se za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka operacije otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2470">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information, especially performance information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2471">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2471">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2472">**Data_AppDuration** – trajanje provedeno u obradi aplikacije tijekom operacije otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2472">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2473">**Data_BootDuration** – trajanje postupka pokretanja otvorene datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2473">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of boot process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2474">**Data_ClickOrigin** – niz koji označava iz kojeg je dijela veza nastala kada je korisnik kliknuo vezu u aplikaciji iOS Outlook kako bi otvorio datoteku u aplikaciji Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2474">**Data_ClickOrigin** - A string indicating which part the link was from when user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open a file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2475">**Data_ClickTime** – vrijeme Unix epohe kada je korisnik kliknuo vezu u aplikaciji iOS Outlook kako bi otvorio datoteku u aplikaciji Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2475">**Data_ClickTime** - The Unix epoch time when the user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open the file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2476">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – vrijednost niza koja evidentira trajanje vremena između nekih poziva funkcije, u obliku s ID-om i trajanjem funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2476">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – A string value logging the time duration between some function calls, in a format with function ID and duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2477">**Data_DetachedDuration** – trajanje procesa odvajanja događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2477">**Data_DetachedDuration** - The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2478">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – enumeracija koja upućuje na način pristupa datoteke, na primjer, samo za čitanje, za čitanje i pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2478">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, for example, read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2479">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu asinkronog toka koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2479">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2480">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enumeracija koja upućuje na vrstu algoritma dijeljenja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2480">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2481">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – enumeracija koja upućuje na stanje korporacijske zaštite podataka datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2481">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2482">**Data_Doc_Ext** – Datotečni nastavak datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2482">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2483">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2483">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2484">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira naziv glavnog računala poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2484">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2485">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira identitet koji se koristi za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2485">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2486">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – enumeracija koja upućuje na detaljnu vrstu scenarija otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2486">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2487">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – enumeracija koja označava zastavice UI operacije otvaranja datoteke, na primjer, ako je datoteka predmemorirana ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2487">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, for example, if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2488">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled**– bez obzira na to je li za datoteku omogućena suradnja u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2488">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2489">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka otvorena inkrementalno ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2489">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2490">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – bez obzira na to podržava li datoteka uslugu suradnje u sustavu Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2490">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2491">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka otvorena iz izvanmrežne predmemorirane kopije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2491">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2492">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka unaprijed dohvaćena prije operacije otvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2492">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2493">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – bez obzira na to postoji li datoteka oblaka lokalno i je li sinkronizirana s poslužiteljem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2493">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2494">**Data_Doc_Location** – enumeracija koja upućuje gdje se datoteka nalazi, na primjer, lokalno ili u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2494">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, for example, locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2495">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – enumeracija koja označava razlog zbog kog je datoteka samo za čitanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2495">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2496">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira ID resursa poslužitelja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2496">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource ID of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2497">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – enumeracija koja označava vrstu kanala u stvarnom vremenu (RTC) koji se koristi u datoteci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2497">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2498">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira ID dokumenta poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2498">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2499">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – enumeracija koja označava poslužiteljski protokol datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2499">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2500">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – enumeracija koja označava vrstu poslužitelja datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2500">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2501">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – enumeracija koja označava verziju poslužitelja datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2501">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2502">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – cijeli broj koji se povećava za 1 za svaku operaciju otvaranja datoteke u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2502">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer that is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2503">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – niz koji se koristi za povezivanje klijentskih i poslužiteljskih zapisnika, obično je vrsta ID-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2503">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2504">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – veličina datoteke u bajtovima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2504">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2505">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – enumeracija koja označava kakav poseban znak ima URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2505">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2506">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID koji jedinstveno identificira URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2506">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2507">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – bez obzira na to je li datoteka otvorena inkrementalno pomoću predmemoriranih WRS podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2507">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2508">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – niz koji pokazuje iz koje usluge je datoteka WOPI (sučelje web-aplikacije s otvorenom platformom).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2508">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a WOPI (Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2509">**Data_HWModel** – vrijednost niza kojom se bilježi model uređaja iPad ili uređaja iPhone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2509">**Data_HWModel** – A string value logging the model of iPad or iPhone device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2510">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** – vrijednost niza koja evidentira trajanje vremena provedenog u nekim pozivima funkcije, u obliku s oznakom funkcije i trajanju koje uključuje trajanje poziva podfunkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2510">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2511">**Data_InitializationReason** – enumeracija koja označava kako se datoteka otvara, na primjer, iz kojeg elementa korisničkog sučelja ili je pokreće druga aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2511">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, for example, from which UI element or triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2512">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – je li datoteka već otvorena ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2512">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – Whether or not the file is already open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2513">**Data_IsInterrupted** – je li postupak otvaranja datoteke prekinut prelaskom aplikacije na pozadinu ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2513">**Data_IsInterrupted** – Whether or not the file open operation was interrupted by app transitioning to background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2514">**Data_Measurements** – vrijednost niza koja evidentira trajanje vremena provedenog u nekim pozivima funkcije, u obliku s oznakom funkcije i trajanju koje isključuje trajanje poziva podfunkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2514">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2515">**Data_OpenInPlace** – bez obzira na to treba li se datoteka kopirati u spremnik za testiranje u sustavu Office prije no što ga korisnik otvori.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2515">**Data_OpenInPlace** - Whether or not a file must be copied to the Office's sandboxed container before user can open it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2516">**Data_OpenStartTime** – vrijeme Unix epohe kada je počelo otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2516">**Data_OpenStartTime** - The Unix epoch time when the file open started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2517">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** – trajanje prikazivanja otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2517">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2518">**Data_SourceApplication** – niz koji pokazuje ID kompleta izvorišne aplikacije kada je druga aplikacija pokrenula otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2518">**Data_SourceApplication** - A string indicating the bundle ID of the source application when a file open was triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2519">**Data_StopwatchDuration** – trajanje od početka događaja do kraja događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2519">**Data_StopwatchDuration** - The duration from beginning of the event to the end of the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2520">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** – vrijednost niza koja evidentira trajanje vremena provedenog u nekim pozivima funkcije, u obliku s oznakom funkcije, početnom vremenskom oznakom i trajanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2520">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsopenfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2521">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2521">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2522">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2522">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2523">Događaj bilježi operaciju otvaranja datoteke i koristi se za razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka operacije otvaranja datoteke kao što su kategorije lokacije „ServiceType”, a odakle je u aplikaciji korisnik zatražio otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2523">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2524">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2524">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2525">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** – ovo je Booleova vrijednost koja se zapisuje ako uvidom u putanju datoteke mislimo da bi mogla biti iz mape koju sinkronizira DropBox.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2525">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is synched by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2526">**Data_IsSignedIn** – bez obzira na to je li korisnik prijavljen ili ne kada je datoteka spremljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2526">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2527">**Data_OpenReason** – otvoreni razlog numerička je vrijednost koja označava odakle je unutar aplikacije korisnik otvorio datoteku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2527">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2528">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna numerička kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2528">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationssavetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2529">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2529">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2530">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2530">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2531">Događaj se bilježi kada se odvija operacija „Spremi kao” i koristi se za razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka o radu datoteke, poput kategorija lokacije i prva četiri znaka proširenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2531">The event records when a "save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2532">Operacija „Spremi kao” događa se kada god korisnik stvori novu datoteku i spremi je prvi put ili spremi kopiju postojeće datoteke na novu lokaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2532">A "save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2533">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2533">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2534">**Data_FileExtension** – prva četiri znaka proširenja nove datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2534">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2535">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** – označava je li operacija spremanja za novu datoteku ili kopiju postojeće datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2535">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2536">**Data_IsSignedIn** – bez obzira na to je li korisnik prijavljen ili ne kada je datoteka spremljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2536">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2537">**Data_SaveErrorCode** – numerička vrijednost koja se postavlja ako postoji pogreška koja omogućuje prepoznavanje vrste pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2537">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2538">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** – određuje domenu koda SaveErrorCode kako je definirano u SaveErrorDomains tvrtke Apple „to su proizvoljni nizovi koji se koriste za razlikovanje grupe kodova”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2538">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains "are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2539">**Data_SaveLocation** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2539">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2540">**Data_SaveOperationType** – numerička vrijednost definirana u grupi vrijednosti tvrtke Apple NSSaveOperationType.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2540">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple's NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>


#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2541">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2541">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2542">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2542">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2543">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik prođe kroz nadogradnju dokumenta u protok oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2543">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2544">Ti se podaci koriste za bolje razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkih iskustava povezanih s premještanjem dokumenata na lokacije u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2544">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2545">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2545">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2546">**Data_FileStyle** – numerička vrijednost koja pokazuje iz kojeg scenarija je prikazano iskustvo nadogradnje, primjerice, pomoću prekidača za automatsko spremanje ili gumba za zajedničko korištenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2546">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2547">**Data_FileType** – prva četiri znaka proširenja trenutne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2547">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2548">**Data_InDocStage** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li iskustvo nadogradnje prikazano iz galerije dokumenta ili iz prozora dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2548">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2549">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li trenutni dokument za koji se prikazuje iskustvo nadogradnje također otvoren.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2549">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2550">**Data_IsDraft** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li trenutna datoteka ikada bila spremljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2550">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2551">**Data_IsSheetModal** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li iskustvo nadogradnje predstavljeno modalno ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2551">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2552">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2552">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2553">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2553">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2554">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik odluči prenijeti novu ili lokalnu datoteku u oblak i rezultat te operacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2554">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2555">Ti se podaci koriste za bolje razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkih iskustava povezanih s premještanjem dokumenata na lokacije u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2555">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2556">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2556">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2557">**Data_FileStyle** – numerička vrijednost koja pokazuje iz kojeg scenarija je prikazano iskustvo nadogradnje poput prekidača za automatsko spremanje ili gumba za zajedničko korištenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2557">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2558">**Data_FileType** – prva četiri znaka proširenja trenutne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2558">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2559">**Data_InDocStage** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li iskustvo nadogradnje prikazano iz galerije dokumenta ili iz prozora dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2559">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2560">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li odabrana lokacija za učitavanje dokumenta zadana lokacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2560">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2561">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li trenutni dokument za koji se prikazuje iskustvo nadogradnje također otvoren.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2561">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2562">**Data_IsDraft** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li trenutna datoteka ikada bila spremljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2562">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2563">**Data_IsSheetModal** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li iskustvo nadogradnje predstavljeno modalno ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2563">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2564">**Data_LocationServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2564">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2565">**Data_UploadAction** – niz ugrađen u kod koji označava je li prijenos bila operacija premještanja ili kopiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2565">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard-coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2566">**Data_UploadResult** – niz ugrađen u kod koji označava rezultat pokušaja prijenosa, uključujući ali ne ograničavajući se na: „Uspjeh”, „Korisnik je otkazao prijenos” i „Predautorizacija nije uspjela”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2566">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard-coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ''Success", "UserCancelledUpload", and "PreAuthFailed".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicopylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2567">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CopyLinkOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2567">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2568">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2568">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2569">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik izabere zajedničko korištenje generiranjem veze na dokument u oblaku i koristi se za bolje razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju zajedničkog korištenja dokumenata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2569">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2570">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2570">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2571">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2571">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2572">**Data_LinkType** – niz ugrađen u kod koji opisuje izvedenu vrstu poziva poput „ViewOnly” i „ViewAndEdit”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2572">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2573">**Data_ShareScenario** – opis lokacije niza ugrađenog u kod unutar korisničkog sučelja aplikacije odakle se datoteka zajednički koristi uključujući ali ne ograničavajući se na „FileMenu”, „OpenTabShareActionMenu”, „RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2573">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguidocsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2574">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2574">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2575">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2575">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2576">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik izabere zajedničko korištenje dokumenta u oblaku pomoću značajke zajedničkog korištenja servisa OneDrive i koristi se za bolje razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju zajedničkog korištenja dokumenata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2576">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2577">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2577">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2578">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** – Ako iskustvo zajedničkog korištenja doživi pogrešku, to je numerička vrijednost koja će vam pomoći da identificirate razlog neuspjeha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2578">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2579">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** – Booleova vrijednost koja kada je vrijednost „true“ ukazuje da je lagana operacija zajedničkog korištenja uspješno dovršena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2579">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2580">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** – Kada se operacija zajedničkog korištenja uspješno dovrši, to je numerička vrijednost koja se koristi za određivanje vrste završetka operacije zajedničkog korištenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2580">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2581">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** – Ako se korisničko sučelje ne učita, to je numerička vrijednost koja će vam pomoći u prepoznavanju razloga za neuspjeh.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2581">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2582">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** – Numerička vrijednost koja bilježi vrijeme potrebno za učitavanje web korisničkog sučelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2582">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguiinvitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2583">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2583">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2584">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2584">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2585">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik odluči pozvati ljude u dokument u oblaku i koristi se za bolje razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju zajedničkog korištenja dokumenata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2585">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2586">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2586">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2587">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2587">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2588">**Data_InviteeCount** – ukupni broj kontakata pozvanih u dokument u jednoj akciji poziva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2588">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2589">**Data_LinkType** – niz ugrađen u kod koji opisuje izvedenu vrstu poziva poput „ViewOnly” i „ViewAndEdit”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2589">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2590">**Data_MessageLength** – numerički broj ukupnog broja znakova poslanih u pozivnoj poruci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2590">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2591">**Data_ShareScenario** – opis lokacije niza ugrađenog u kod unutar korisničkog sučelja aplikacije odakle se datoteka zajednički koristi uključujući ali ne ograničavajući se na „FileMenu”, „OpenTabShareActionMenu”, „RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2591">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguisendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2592">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2592">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2593">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2593">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2594">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik odluči poslati kopiju dokumenta i koristi se za bolje razumijevanje i postavljanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju zajedničkog korištenja dokumenata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2594">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2595">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2595">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2596">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li kartica Polazno trenutno dostupna korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2596">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2597">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li korisniku trenutno dostupno sučelje „Preporučeno”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2597">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2598">**Data_OperationType** – numerička vrijednost koja označava koja je vrsta slanja postupka kopiranja koja se odvija kao što je slanje kopije u poruci e-pošte ili slanje kopije pomoću kontrole za zajedničko korištenje tvrtke Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2598">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple's share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2599">**Data_ServiceType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2599">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2600">**Data_ShareFileType** – Niz ugrađen u kod opisa vrste objekta koji se zajednički koristi uključujući ali ne ograničavajući se na „Dokument”, „PDF”, „Slika”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2600">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard-coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, "Document", "PDF", "Picture".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2601">**Data_ShareScenario** – opis lokacije niza ugrađenog u kod unutar korisničkog sučelja aplikacije odakle se datoteka zajednički koristi uključujući ali ne ograničavajući se na „FileMenu”, „OpenTabShareActionMenu”, „RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2601">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2602">**Data_SharingService** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li datoteka stvorena kada je korisnik tražio predložak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2602">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguiupsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2603">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2603">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2604">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2604">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2605">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada korisnik prođe kroz nadogradnju dokumenta u protok oblaka prilikom pokušaja zajedničkog korištenja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2605">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2606">Ti se podaci koriste za bolje razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkih iskustava povezanih s premještanjem dokumenata na lokacije u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2606">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2607">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2607">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2608">**Data_FileOperationResult** – numerička vrijednost koja pokazuje je li operacija uspjela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2608">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2609">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava prolazi li korisnik kroz nadogradnju na protok oblaka iz sučelja DocStage ili iz otvorenog dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2609">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2610">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li korisnik odlučio zadržati lokalnu kopiju dokumenta koji se prenosi na oblak ili premjestiti postojeći dokument u oblak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2610">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2611">**Data_NewFileType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije nove lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2611">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2612">**Data_OriginalFileType** – apstraktna kategorizacija lokacije datoteke kao što su „SharePoint”, „OneDrive”, „Lokalno”, „WOPI” itd., a izričito ne stvarna lokacija datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2612">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2613">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li korisnik odlučio prenijeti trenutni dokument u oblak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2613">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** - A Boolean to indicate if the user chose to upload the current document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2614">**Data_UploadError** – Numerička vrijednost koja pokazuje vrstu pogreške koja se dogodila ako operacija prijenosa ne uspije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2614">**Data_UploadError** - A numerical value that indicates the kind of error that occurred if an upload operation fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2615">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li prikaz prikazan iz izbornika za zajedničko korištenje. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2615">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** - A Boolean value to indicate if the view was shown from the share menu.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefeedeventsinitializing"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2640">Office.Feed.Events.Initializing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2640">Office.Feed.Events.Initializing</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2641">Taj se događaj prikuplja kada se sažetak sadržaja počne pokretati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2641">This event is collected when the feed has started initializing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2642">Taj se događaj upotrebljava da bi se pokazalo da se sažetak sadržaja pokreće te da bi se dijagnosticirali problemi s pouzdanošću prilikom pokretanja sažetka sadržaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2642">This event is used to indicate that the feed is starting and to diagnose reliability issues in launching the feed.</span></span>
