<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2777">Omogućuje da utvrdimo je li datoteka uspješno otvorena u FIO sloju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2777">Allows us to know if a file successfully opened from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2778">Koristi se za stanje i nadzor značajke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2778">Used for feature health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2779">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2779">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2780">**Activity.Group –** oznaka koja omogućuje postavljanje grupiranja događaja nadzora za upravljanje ukupnim uspjehom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2780">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2781">**Activity.IsHVA –** zastavica koja označava da je događaj ključan za uspjeh korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2781">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2782">**Data.AsyncOpen –** zastavica koja označava da se u otvorenom nalazi sadržaj koji je primljen nakon otvaranja glavnog tijela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2782">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate the open had content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2783">**Data.CacheFileId –** povezuje se s telemetrijom predmemorije dokumenta sustava Office radi omogućivanja analize utjecaja problema s predmemorijom na korisničko iskustvo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2783">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2784">**Data. CFREnabled** – ukazuje da je za sesiju omogućen CacheFileRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2784">**Data.CFREnabled** - Indicates that CacheFileRuntime is enabled for the session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2785">**Data.CFRFailure** – Ukazuje da je CacheFileRuntime naišao na pogrešku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2785">**Data.CFRFailure** - Indicated that CacheFileRuntime ran into error.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2786">**Data.CoauthStatus –** izvješćuje status suradnje dokumenta pri otvaranju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2786">**Data.CoauthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2787">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload –** broj povratnih prijenosa na poslužitelj koji se koristi za otklanjanje poteškoća s performansama i mrežom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2787">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2788">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload –** broj povratnih prijenosa na poslužitelj koji se koristi za otklanjanje poteškoća s performansama i mrežom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2788">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2789">**Data.DialogId –** postavljeno ako je otvoren dijaloški okvir korisničkog sučelja tijekom otvaranja, što upućuje da je poruka upozorenja prikazana korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2789">**Data.DialogId -** Set if a UI dialog was displayed during Open, indicating that a warning message was displayed to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2790">**Data.DidFallbackToDAV –** postavljeno ako je dokument otvoren pomoću starijeg protokola za prijenos datoteka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2790">**Data.DidFallbackToDAV -** Set if the document was opened using an older file transfer protocol</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2791">**Data.Doc.AccessMode –** dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2791">**Data.Doc.AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2792">**Data.Doc.AssistedReadingReasons –** postavljeno ako dokument ima aktiviranu zaštitu elektroničkih podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2792">**Data.Doc.AssistedReadingReasons -** Set if the document has electronic data protection in place</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2793">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2793">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2794">**Data.Doc.ChunkingType –** jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2794">**Data.Doc.ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2795">**Data.Doc.EdpState –** postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2795">**Data.Doc.EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2796">**Data.Doc.Ext –** nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2796">**Data.Doc.Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2797">**Data.Doc.Extension –** zastarjelo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2797">**Data.Doc.Extension -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2798">**Data.Doc.FileFormat –** verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2798">**Data.Doc.FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2799">**Data.Doc.Fqdn –** naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2799">**Data.Doc.Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2800">**Data.Doc.FqdnHash –** jednosmjerno raspršivanje naziva domene koji identificira korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2800">**Data.Doc.FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2801">**Data.Doc.IdentityTelemetryId –** jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta kojim se izvršava otvaranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2801">**Data.Doc.IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2802">**Data.Doc.IdentityUniqueId –** zastarjelo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2802">**Data.Doc.IdentityUniqueId -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2803">**Data.Doc.InitializationScenario –** bilježi način otvaranja dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2803">**Data.Doc.InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2804">**Data.Doc.IOFlags –** izvješćuje o predmemoriranim zastavicama za postavljanje mogućnosti zahtjeva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2804">**Data.Doc.IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set request options</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-2901">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2901">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2902">Omogućuje da utvrdimo je li datoteka uspješno spremljena u FIO sloju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2902">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2903">Koristi se za stanje i nadzor značajke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2903">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-2904">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2904">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2905">**Activity.Group –** oznaka koja omogućuje postavljanje grupiranja događaja nadzora za upravljanje ukupnim uspjehom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2905">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2906">**Activity.IsHVA –** zastavica koja označava da je događaj ključan za uspjeh korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2906">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2907">**Data.AsyncOpen –** zastavica koja označava da je dokument otvoren sa sadržajem koji je primljen nakon otvaranja glavnog tijela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2907">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate that the document was opened with content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2908">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered –** promjena dijagnostike praćenja koja označava da je zatražena osnovna verzija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2908">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered -** Change tracking diagnostic indicating that the base version of the document was requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2909">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons –** kodovi razloga za stanje blokiranog prijenosa (na primjer, isključeno automatsko spremanje, dokument je u prijelazu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2909">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons -** Reason codes for blocked upload state (for example, Autosave is turned off, the document is transitioning)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2910">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting –** prijenos je blokiran jer ne bi uspio da je ponovljen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2910">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting -** Upload is blocked as it would fail if retried</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2911">**Data.CacheFileId –** povezuje se s telemetrijom predmemorije dokumenta sustava Office radi omogućivanja analize utjecaja problema s predmemorijom na korisničko iskustvo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2911">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2912">**Data.ChartType –** zastarjelo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2912">**Data.ChartType -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2913">**Data.CoAuthStatus –** izvješćuje status suradnje dokumenta pri spremanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2913">**Data.CoAuthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2914">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext –** izvješćuje kontekst (spajanje/inkrementalno otvaranje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2914">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext -** reports context (Merge/Incremental Open)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2915">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload –** broj povratnih prijenosa na poslužitelj koji se koristi za otklanjanje poteškoća s performansama i mrežom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2915">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-2917">**Data. CFREnabled** – ukazuje da je za sesiju omogućen CacheFileRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-2917">**Data.CFREnabled** - Indicates that CacheFileRuntime is enabled for the session.</span></span>

#### <a name="officelenslenssdkcloudconnectorlaunch"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3181">Office.Lens.LensSdk.CloudConnectorLaunch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3181">Office.Lens.LensSdk.CloudConnectorLaunch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3182">Kada korisnik izreže sliku i dodirne „Potvrdi“ na posljednjem izboru slike za korištenje OCR-a, taj će se događaj prikupiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3182">When the user crops the image and taps confirm on the final image selection for using OCR, this event is collected.</span></span>     
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3183">Ovo je zapis korisnika za zahtjev za uslugu, jer na usluzi ne postoji mapiranje posla korisnika od usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3183">This is user-to-request record for the service as there is no user-to-service-job mapping on the service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3184">UserId je potreban da bi ispunio GDPR zahtjeve jer usluga nije izravno izložena korisnicima, već putem klijenata i identificira ukupan broj ljudi koji koriste uslugu, pomažući usluzi da prati količinu korisnika koji koriste proizvod, kao i identificirajući promjene u trendovima, pomoć u traženju i ispravljanju problema u proizvodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3184">UserId is required to fulfill GDPR requirements as service is not directly exposed to users, but through clients and identify the total number of people using the service, helping the service track the volume of users using the product, as well as identifying changes in trends, help look for and rectify issues in the product.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3185">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3185">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3186">**CallType** – Niz za identificiranje je li API poziv bio sinkroni ili asinkroni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3186">**CallType** - String to identify if the API call was synchronous or asynchronous.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3187">**CloudConnectorRequestId**– niz koji identificira zahtjev za servis koji je stvoren za pretvorbu slika putem servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3187">**CloudConnectorRequestId** - String that identifies the service request that was made to convert images via service.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3188">**CloudConnectorTarget** – Niz koji potvrđuje koju će vrstu pretvorbe usluga izvršiti na slikama, poput pretvaranja u PDF, Docx, tekst itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3188">**CloudConnectorTarget** - String that confirms which type of conversion the service will do on images, like converting to PDF, Docx, text, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3189">**CustomerId** – niz koji identificira korisnika koji je vlasnik slika koje se obrađuju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3189">**CustomerId** - String that identifies the user who owns the images being processed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3190">**CustomerType**-niz koji identificira klijenta kao poduzeće ili pojedinačnog korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3190">**CustomerType** - String that identifies the customer as an enterprise or individual user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3191">Ta razlika utječe na broj slika (kvota) koje klijent može pretvoriti istodobno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3191">This distinction affects the number of images (quota) the client can convert at a time.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3192">**Relid** – niz koji identificira korelacije između Leća i servisa koji se koristi za obradu datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3192">**RelationId** - String, which identifies correlation between Lens and the service used to process files.</span></span>


#### <a name="officelenslenssdkcloudconnectoruploaderror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3193">Office.Lens.LensSdk.CloudConnectorUploadError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3193">Office.Lens.LensSdk.CloudConnectorUploadError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3194">U slici u tablicu, kada korisnik dodirne ili Dijeli, Kopiraj ili Otvori, ispravci u tablici koje je napravio korisnik dijele se sa uslugom radi poboljšanja OCR-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3194">In Image to Table, when the user taps either Share, Copy or Open, the corrections in the table made by the user are shared with the service to improve the OCR.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3195">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja na temelju odgovora na pogrešku te usluge i sadrži relevantne identifikatore za rješavanje različitih problema na usluzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3195">This event is collected on the error response of that service and contains the relevant identifiers to troubleshoot various issues on the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3199">**Razlog** – niz koji sadrži kôd pogreške i opis pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3199">**Reason** - String that contains the error code and description of the error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3200">**TargetType** – niz koji identificira krajnju točku na servisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3200">**TargetType** - String that identifies the endpoint on the service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3203">U slici u tablicu, kada korisnik dodirne ili Dijeli, Kopiraj ili Otvori, ispravci u tablici koje je napravio korisnik dijele se sa uslugom radi poboljšanja OCR-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3203">In Image to Table, when the user taps either Share, Copy or Open, the corrections in the table made by the user are shared with the service to improve the OCR.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3204">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja nakon uspješnog odgovora te usluge i sadrži relevantne identifikatore za rješavanje problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3204">This event is collected on the successful response of that service and contains the relevant identifiers to troubleshoot the process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3205">Također pomaže u analizi upotrebe cjevovoda za poboljšanje usluga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3205">It also helps analyze the usage of service improvement pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3207">**CloudConnectorRequestId** – Identifikator niza za povezivanje zadatka usluge s trenutnim zahtjevom usluge za koji su podijeljeni podaci o poboljšanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3207">**CloudConnectorRequestId** - String identifier to link the service job to the current service request for which the improvement data was shared.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3209">**TargetType** – niz koji identificira krajnju točku na servisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3209">**TargetType** - String that identifies the endpoint on the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3210">**TaskType** – niz koji identificira namjeru poziva usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3210">**TaskType** - String that identifies the intent of the service call.</span></span>


#### <a name="officelenslenssdkpermission"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3211">Office.Lens.LensSdk.Permission</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3211">Office.Lens.LensSdk.Permission</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3212">Dopuštenja su osjetljiva značajka, jer bez njih korisnik ne može iskusiti nijednu značajku Objektiva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3212">Permissions are a sensitive feature, as without them user cannot experience any of Lens's features.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3213">Dozvole se prate kako bi se razumjele korisničke navike za pružanje / ukidanje dozvola.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3213">Permissions are tracked to understand user habits for providing/revoking permissions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3214">Kada korisnik stupi u interakciju s bilo kojim dijaloškim okvirom za dozvole u našoj aplikaciji, prikupljamo te događaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3214">When the user interacts with any permission dialogs in our app, we collect these events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3215">Na temelju korisničkih trendova za prihvaćanje i odbijanje dozvola, identificiramo poboljšanja značajki kako bismo korisnicima pomogli razumjeti zašto su dopuštenja kritična.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3215">Based on user trends for accepting and rejecting permissions, we identify feature enhancements to help users understand why permissions are critical.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3216">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3216">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3217">**Data_action** – Sadrži vrijednosti kao što su „CameraPermissionAllowed (ili odbijena), StoragePermissionGranted (ili odbijen), što nam omogućuje da shvaćamo je li korisnik prihvatio ili odbio dozvole za pohranu i fotoaparat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3217">**Data_action** - Contains values like “CameraPermissionAllowed (or Denied), StoragePermissionGranted (or Denied), which help us understand whether the user accepted or rejected storage and camera permissions.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3218">**Data_Action** – Ovo nam polje pomaže razumjeti koju je vrstu dopuštenja zatražio korisnik, poput Kamere ili pohrane</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3218">**Data_Action** - This field helps us understand which type of permission was asked from the user such as Camera or storage</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3219">**Data_status** – Sadrži vrijednosti kao što su dopuštene, uskraćene i DeniedForever, što nam omogućuje da shvaćamo je li korisnik prihvatio ili odbio dozvole za pohranu i fotoaparat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3219">**Data_status** - Contains values like Allowed, Denied, and DeniedForever, which help us understand whether the user accepted or rejected storage and camera permissions.</span></span>


#### <a name="officelenslenssdksavemedia"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3220">Office.Lens.LensSdk.SaveMedia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3220">Office.Lens.LensSdk.SaveMedia</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3221">Ovaj se događaj poziva kada korisnik klikne na gumb „Gotovo“ i spremi slike na Android i iOS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3221">This event is invoked when the user clicks on the done button and saves images on Android and iOS.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3222">Pomaže u mjerenju razine korisničkog angažmana kvantificirajući korisnike koji na kraju spremaju slike putem naše aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3222">It helps measure the level of user engagement by quantifying users who end up saving images through our app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3223">Sljedeća se polja prikupljaju samo za Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3223">The following fields are collected on Android:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3224">**Data_FileSizeAfterCleanUp** – Veličina datoteke nakon što je aplikacija očisti da bi se razumjelo kolika je kompresija postignuta nakon čišćenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3224">**Data_FileSizeAfterCleanUp** - Size of the file after it is cleaned by app, to understand how much compression was achieved after cleanup.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3225">**Data_FileSizeAfterSave** – Veličina datoteke nakon što je korisnik spremi kako bi razumjela kolika je kompresija postignuta nakon spremanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3225">**Data_FileSizeAfterSave** - Size of the file after it is saved by user, to understand how much compression was achieved after saving.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3226">**Data_FileSizeBeforeCleanUp** – Veličina datoteke prije nego što je aplikacija očisti kako bi shvatila kolika je veličina snimljene datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3226">**Data_FileSizeBeforeCleanUp** - Size of the file before it is cleaned by app, to understand how much captured size was</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3227">**Data_Filter** – filtar primijenjen na sliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3227">**Data_Filter** - The filter applied to the image.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3228">**Data_ImageHeightAfterCleanUp** – Visina slike nakon što ju je aplikacija očistila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3228">**Data_ImageHeightAfterCleanUp** - Height of the image after it was cleaned by app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3229">**Data_ImageWidthAfterCleanUp** – visina slike prije no što ju je očistila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3229">**Data_ImageHeightBeforeCleanUp** - Height of the image before it was cleaned by app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3230">**Data_ImageWidthAfterCleanUp** – širina slike prije no što ju je očistila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3230">**Data_ImageWidthAfterCleanUp** - Width of the image before it was cleaned by app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3231">**Data_ImageWidthAfterCleanUp** – širina slike prije no što ju je očistila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3231">**Data_ImageWidthBeforeCleanUp** - Width of the image before it was cleaned by app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3232">**Data_MediaId** – identifikator za slike da bi vam se pomoglo pri praćenju uspjeha postupka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3232">**Data_MediaId** - Identifier for images to help track operation success.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3233">**Data_ProcessMode** – Način rada korisnika u trenutku spremanja slike od strane korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3233">**Data_ProcessMode** - Mode of the user at the time of the saving the image by the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3234">**Data_Source** – određuje odakle je slika, primjerice, snimljena kamerom, uvoz iz galerije itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3234">**Data_Source** - Defines where the image was sourced from, example captured via camera, imported from gallery, etc.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3235">Sljedeća se polja prikupljaju samo za iOS:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3235">The following fields are collected on iOS:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3236">**Data_Filter** – filtar primijenjen na sliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3236">**Data_filter** - The filter applied to the image.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3237">**Data_imageDPI** – Smanjenje slike primijenjeno je na sliku spremljene datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3237">**Data_imageDPI** - Image reduction applied to the saved file image</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3238">**Data_imageSize** – veličina slike nakon što je korisnik spremio sliku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3238">**Data_imageSize** - Size of the image after user has saved the image</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3239">**Data_MediaId** – identifikator za slike da bi vam se pomoglo pri praćenju uspjeha postupka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3239">**Data_mediaId** - Identifier for images to help track operation success.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3240">**Data_mode** – Način korisnika u trenutku spremanja slike od strane korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3240">**Data_mode** - Mode of the user at the time of the saving the image by the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3241">**Data_sizeinPixel** – veličina slike u obliku piksela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3241">**Data_sizeinPixel** - Size of the image in the form of pixel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3242">**Data_Source** – određuje odakle je slika, primjerice, snimljena kamerom, uvoz iz galerije itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3242">**Data_source** - Defines where the image was sourced from, example captured via camera, imported from gallery, etc.</span></span> 


#### <a name="officelenslenssdkserviceidmapping"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3243">Office.Lens.LensSdk.ServiceIDMapping</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3243">Office.Lens.LensSdk.ServiceIDMapping</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3244">Kada se slika uspješno prenese na uslugu, taj se događaj prikuplja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3244">When an image is uploaded successfully to the service, this event is collected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3245">Označava da će usluga sada pokrenuti jedan ili više poslova za obradu slike i sadržavanje relevantnih ID-ova koji pomažu u rješavanju problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3245">It signifies that service will now run one or more jobs to process the image and contain relevant IDs to help troubleshoot the process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3246">Također pomaže u analizi upotrebe različitih značajki usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3246">It also helps analyze the usage of different service features.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3247">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3247">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3248">**CloudConnectorRequestId**– niz koji identificira zahtjev za servis koji je stvoren za pretvorbu slika putem servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3248">**CloudConnectorRequestId** - String that identifies the service request that was made to convert images via service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3249">**I2DserviceProcessID** – niz koji identificira posao usluge koji izvodi određeni podzahtjev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3249">**I2DserviceProcessID** - String that identifies the service job running a particular sub-request</span></span> 


#### <a name="officeiospaywallpaywallpresented"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3250">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Presented</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3250">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Presented</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3251">Ova se telemetrija kritične uporabe prikuplja kada se korisniku prikaže kontrola Paywall-a i upotrebljava se za razumijevanje iskustva kupnje u aplikaciji za korisnika i optimizaciju istog za buduće verzije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3251">This critical usage telemetry is collected when Paywall control is shown to the user, and is used to understand the in-app purchase experience for the user and optimize the same for future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3252">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3252">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3253">**entryPoint** – niz – gumb/tijek s kojeg je prikazan Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3253">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3254">Kao što je „Premium Upgrade Button" ili „First run flow“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3254">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3255">**isFRE** – Booleov – prikazujemo li iskustvo prvog pokretanja ili redovno korisničko sučelje?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3255">**isFRE** - Boolean – Are we showing the First Run Experience or regular UI?</span></span>

#### <a name="officeiospaywallpaywallstats"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3256">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Stats</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3256">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Stats</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3257">Ovi metapodaci temeljeni na sesiji prikupljaju se kada se korisniku prikaže korisničko sučelje Paywall, trajanje interakcije i je li kupnja pokušana i uspjela ili nije uspjela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3257">This session-based metadata is collected when the Paywall UI is shown to the user, the duration of the interaction and whether a purchase was attempted and succeeded or failed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3258">Podaci se koriste za razumijevanje korištenja i stanja cijelog iskustva plaćanja i otklanjanja pogrešaka, optimizaciju i otklanjanje poteškoća s iskustvom kupnje unutar aplikacije u budućim verzijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3258">The data is used to understand the usage and health of the entire payment experience and debug, optimize, and troubleshoot the in-app purchase experience in future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3259">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3259">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3260">**entryPoint** – niz – gumb/tijek s kojeg je prikazan Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3260">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3261">Kao što je "Premium Upgrade Button" ili „First run flow“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3261">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3262">**isFRE** – Booleov – prikazujemo li iskustvo prvog pokretanja ili redovno korisničko sučelje?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3262">**isFRE** - Boolean – Are we showing the First Run Experience or regular UI?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3263">**stanje** – niz – izlazni status Paywalla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3263">**status** - String – Exit status of Paywall.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3264">Kao što je „initiated", "paymentDone", "provisionFailed"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3264">Like “initiated”, “paymentDone”, “provisionFailed”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3265">**userDuration** – udvostručeno – trajanje u milisekundama koje je korisnik proveo na Paywall-u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3265">**userDuration** - Double – Duration in milliseconds the user spent on Paywall</span></span>


#### <a name="officeiospaywallprovisioningresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3266">Office.iOS.Paywall.Provisioning.Response</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3266">Office.iOS.Paywall.Provisioning.Response</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3267">Kritična inženjerska telemetrija s Microsoft Retail Federation Service (RFS) za prikupljanje informacija pruženih u ovom slučaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3267">Critical engineering telemetry with Microsoft Retail Federation Service (RFS) to collect the information provided in this event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3268">RFS je interni servis koji se upotrebljava unutar Microsofta za unakrsnu provjeru kupnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3268">RFS is the internal service used within Microsoft for crosschecking the purchase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3269">Podaci se upotrebljavaju za dobivanje stanja API poziva upućenog RFS-u, što bi pomoglo u razumijevanju stope uspješnosti i otklanjanju pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3269">The data is used to get the health of the API call made to RFS which would help in understanding the success rate and debugging for any failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3270">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3270">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3271">**entryPoint** – niz – gumb/tijek s kojeg je prikazan Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3271">**entryPoint**- String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3272">Kao što je "Premium Upgrade Button" ili „First run flow“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3272">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3273">**failureReason** – niz – dodan samo kada je status „neuspjeh".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3273">**failureReason**- String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3274">Ukazuje na odgovor na pogrešku koji je dao RFS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3274">Indicating the error response given by the RFS Provisioning response.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3275">**productId** – niz – ID proizvoda trgovine App Store za koji je izrađen zahtjev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3275">**productId**- String – App Store ID of the product the request was made for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3276">**stanje** – niz – uspjeh ili neuspjeh, što upućuje na to je li zahtjev uspio ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3276">**status**- String – Success or Failure, indicating if the request succeeded or failed</span></span>


#### <a name="officeiospaywallskuchooserbuybuttontap"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3277">Office.iOS.Paywall.SKUChooser.BuyButtonTap</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3277">Office.iOS.Paywall.SKUChooser.BuyButtonTap</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3278">Kritična telemetrija upotrebe koja pokazuje kada korisnik dodiruje gumb Kupnja//Kupi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3278">Critical usage telemetry that indicates when a user taps the Purchase/Buy Button.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3279">Upotrebljava se za zaključivanje o načinu korištenja i mjernim podacima konverzije za korisnike koji pokušaju kupiti pretplatu u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3279">Used to infer the usage pattern and conversion metric for users who attempt to buy a subscription in the app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3280">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3280">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3281">**entryPoint** – niz – gumb/tijek s kojeg je prikazan Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3281">**entryPoint**- String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3282">Kao što je "Premium Upgrade Button" ili „First run flow“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3282">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3283">**isdefaultSKU** – Booleova vrijednost – ako korisnik kupuje proizvod, preporučili smo mu, prikazujući ga prema zadanim postavkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3283">**isDefaultSKU**- Bool – If the user is purchasing the product, we recommended for them, by displaying it by default.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3284">**productId** – niz – ID proizvoda trgovine App-store za koji je dodirnut gumb Kupi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3284">**productId** - String – App-store product-id of the product for which the Buy Button was tapped</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3285">**toggleCount** – Int – koliko je puta korisnik prelazio s jednog prikaza proizvoda na drugi prije nego što je dodirnuo gumb Kupi u trenutačnoj sesiji Paywall-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3285">**toggleCount**- Int – Number of times the user switched between viewing various products, before they tapped the Buy Button, in the current session of Paywall.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3287">Ovaj događaj prikuplja značajke i aplikacije koje korisnik proširuje iz odjeljka „Pogledajte više pogodnostii" i trajanje provedenog vremena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3287">This event collects the features and apps the user expands from “See More Benefits”, and the duration of time spent.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3288">Podaci se upotrebljavaju za razumijevanje upotrebe značajke „Pogledajte sve pogodnosti" te daljnju optimizaciju iskustva u budućim verzijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3288">The data is used to understand usage of the “See all benefits” feature and further optimize the experience in future versions.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3291">**productId** – niz – ID proizvoda trgovine App Store za koji korisnik pregledava dodatne ponuđene pogodnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3291">**productId** - String - App Store ID of the product for which user is viewing more benefits offered</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3292">**userDuration** – udvostručeno – trajanje u milisekundama koje je korisnik proveo na Zaslonu s pogodnostima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3292">**userDuration** - Double - Duration in milliseconds the user spent on the Benefits Screen.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3298">Ta se uporaba telemetrije prikuplja da bi vam se prikazao način na koji je korisnik unio birač SKU-a, koliko vremena korisnik provodi na zaslonu birača SKU-a i zašto je izašao iz istog.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3298">This usage telemetry is collected to see how the user entered the SKU Chooser, how much time the user spends on the SKU Chooser screen and why they exited the SKU Chooser.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3299">Podaci se upotrebljavaju za razumijevanje upotrebe birača SKU-a i optimizaciju iskustva kupnje aplikacija u budućim verzijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3299">The data is used to understand usage of the SKU chooser and optimize the in-app purchase experience in future versions.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3303">**exitReason** – niz – razlog izlaza iz birača SKU-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3303">**exitReason** - String – Exit reason of SKU Chooser.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3304">Kao što je „BuyButton”, „CloseButton</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3304">Like “BuyButton”, “CloseButton</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3305">**isFRE** – Booleov – prikazujemo li iskustvo prvog pokretanja ili redovno korisničko sučelje?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3305">**isFRE** - Boolean – Are we showing the First Run Experience or regular UI?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3306">**userDuration** – udvostručeno – trajanje u milisekundama koje je korisnik proveo na biraču SKU-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3306">**userDuration** - Double – Duration in milliseconds the user spent on the SKU chooser</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3336">**cardPersonaCorrelationId** – duplikat za gornji Data.cardCorrelationId</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3336">**cardPersonaCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.cardCorrelationId above</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3337">**ClientTimeStamp** – vrijeme na aplikaciji prilikom zapisivanja događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3337">**ClientTimeStamp** - Time on the application when the event was logged</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3338">**consumerCorrelationId** – duplikat za gornji Data.clientCorrelationId</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3338">**consumerCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.clientCorrelationId above</span></span>

#### <a name="officeofficemobilepdfviewerpdffileopenmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3541">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOpenMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3541">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOpenMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3542">Taj se događaj prikuplja za aplikaciju Office za iOS, a bilježi kada dolazi do operacije otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3542">This event is collected for the Office app for iOS, it records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3543">Prikupljamo te podatke da bi se osigurala dobra izvedba za sva otvaranja datoteka u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3543">We collect this data to ensure good performance for all file opens on the app.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3544">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3544">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3545">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** – naziv domene aplikacije Davatelj usluge za scenarij aktivacije datoteke (bilježe se samo informacije o prvim stranama)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3545">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** - Domain name of the Provider app for a file activation scenario (only first party app info is being logged).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3546">**Data_Doc_CreateTelemetryReason** – telemetrijski razlog stvaranja PDF-a. (Na primjer: stvaranje iz skena, upotreba radnje „slika u PDF”, upotreba radnje „dokument u PDF” itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3546">**Data_Doc_CreateTelemetryReason** – Telemetry reason for PDF creation.(for example: Create from scan, using “picture to pdf” action, using “document to pdf” action, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3547">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** – vrijeme za preuzimanje PDF datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3547">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** - Time to download a PDF cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3548">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** – vremenska oznaka za kraj preuzimanja datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3548">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** - Timestamp for end of download of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3549">**Data_Doc_DownloadStartTime** – vremenska oznaka za početak preuzimanja datoteke u oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3549">**Data_Doc_DownloadStartTime** – Timestamp for start of download of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3550">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** – jedinstveni ID za sesiju dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3550">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique ID for a Document Session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3551">**Data_Doc_Location** – mjesto na kojem se nalazi datoteka (lokalno, ODSP, iCloud, datotečna aplikacija drugih proizvođača, wopi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3551">**Data_Doc_Location** - Location where the file sits (Local, ODSP, iCloud, third-party files app, wopi</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3552">**Data_Doc_OpenCompletionTime** – vremenska oznaka za kraj otvorene operacije PDF datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3552">**Data_Doc_OpenCompletionTime** - Timestamp for end of open operation of a PDF file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3553">**Data_Doc_OpenDurationms** – vrijeme za otvaranje PDF datoteke u milisekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3553">**Data_Doc_OpenDurationms** - Time to open a PDF file in milliseconds.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3554">**Data_Doc_OpenStartTime** – vremenska oznaka za početak otvorene operacije PDF datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3554">**Data_Doc_OpenStartTime** - Timestamp for start of open operation of a PDF file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3555">**Data_Doc_TelemetryReason** – telemetrijski razlog za otvoren događaj (na primjer: otvaranje iz MRU-a ili pregledavanje, aktivacija datoteka, aktivacija protokola itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3555">**Data_Doc_TelemetryReason** - Telemetry reason for the open event (for example: open from MRU or browse, File Activation, Protocol Activation, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3556">**Doc_RenderDurationms** – vrijeme za renderiranje PDF datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3556">**Doc_RenderDurationms** - Time to render a pdf file</span></span>


#### <a name="officeofficemobilepdfviewerpdffileoperations-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3557">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOperations (on Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3557">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOperations (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3558">Događaj se prikuplja za aplikaciju Office za sustav Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3558">The event is collected for the Office app for Android.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3559">On se bilježi kada se provede operacija otvaranja, zatvaranja ili spremanja datoteke .pdf i upotrebljava se za razumijevanje i određivanje prioriteta korisničkog iskustva na temelju podataka o radu datoteke .pdf.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3559">It records when a .pdf open, close, or save operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize the user experience based on .pdf file operation information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3560">Događaj nam omogućuje da osiguramo da operacije otvaranja, zatvaranja i spremanja datoteke .pdf funkcioniraju na očekivani način te da poboljšamo učinkovitost operacija datoteke .pdf.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3560">The event enables us to keep the .pdf open, close, and save operations performing as expected, and to improve .pdf file operation performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3561">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3561">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3562">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** – jedinstveni ID za sesiju dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3562">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique ID for a Document Session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3563">**Data_ErrorCode** – pogreška u slučaju neuspjelih otvaranja datoteka / neuspjelih preuzimanja / otkazanih preuzimanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3563">**Data_ErrorCode** - error in case of file open failures/download failures / download canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3564">**Data_ErrorMessage** – odgovarajući kôd na poruku o pogrešci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3564">**Data_ErrorMessage** - relevant message-to-error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3565">**Data_FailureReason** – u slučaju neuspjelog otvaranja, ovi identifikatori definiraju razlog neuspjeha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3565">**Data_FailureReason** - In case of open failure, these enums define the reason for failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3566">**Data_FileGUID** – globalni identifikator za datoteku koja se nasumično generira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3566">**Data_FileGUID** – Global identifier for the file, which is randomly generated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3567">**Data_FileLocation** – lokacija na kojoj se datoteka nalazi, npr.: Lokalno, ODSP, iCloud itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3567">**Data_FileLocation** - Location where the file sits, ex: Local, ODSP, iCloud, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3568">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** – ulazno mjesto za otvaranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3568">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3569">**Data_FileSize** – veličina datoteke na kojoj se operacija provodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3569">**Data_FileSize** - Size of the file on which the operation is happening</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3570">**Data_NetworkRequestErrorResponse** – odgovor pogreške mreže koji odgovara kôdu pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3570">**Data_NetworkRequestErrorResponse** – Network Error response corresponding to error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3571">**Data_NetworkRequestStage** – faza pogreške u slučaju preuzimanja PDF datoteke iz oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3571">**Data_NetworkRequestStage** – Error stage in case of cloud pdf file download.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3572">**Data_OpenMode** – u kojem se načinu rada PDF otvorio, npr.: 0: način rada Prikaz, 2: način rada Potpis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3572">**Data_OpenMode** - In which mode the PDF was opened, ex: 0: View mode, 2: Sign mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3573">**Data_PageCount** – broj stranica u PDF datoteci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3573">**Data_PageCount** - Count of page in the PDF File.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3574">**Data_PasswordProtected** – oznaka koja označava je li datoteka zaštićena lozinkom ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3574">**Data_PasswordProtected** - Marker that tells whether the file is password protected or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3575">**Data_ProviderApp** – aplikacija pružatelja usluga koji trenutno pruža usluge u slučaju isključive aktivacije datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3575">**Data_ProviderApp** - currently providing provider app in case of file activation only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3576">**Data_ReadOnly** – oznaka koja označava je li datoteka samo za čitanje ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3576">**Data_ReadOnly** - Marker that tells whether the file is read only or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3577">**Data_Result** – status operacije koja se izvršava, npr.: istinito:uspjeh, neistinito:neuspjeh</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3577">**Data_Result** - The status of the operation being performed, ex: true:success, false:failure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3660">Ovaj se događaj koristi za otkrivanje i dijagnosticiranje pogreške visoke frekvencije s kojom se korisnik susreće dok koristi značajku Rukopis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3660">This event is used to detect and diagnose a high frequency bug that a user encounters while using Ink feature.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3661">To će se koristiti za određivanje najprikladnijeg načina otklanjanja ovog problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3661">This will be used to determine the most appropriate mode of fixing this issue.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3662">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3662">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3663">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** – trenutni faktor zumiranja područja crtanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3663">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** - Current Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3664">**CurrentNotebook** – identifikator trenutne aktivne bilježnice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3664">**CurrentNotebook** - Identifier of the current active notebook.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3665">**CurrentPage** – identifikator trenutne aktivne stranice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3665">**CurrentPage** - Identifier of the current active page</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3666">**CurrentSection** – identifikator trenutno aktivnog odjeljka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3666">**CurrentSection** - Identifier of the current active section.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3667">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** – zadani faktor zumiranja područja crtanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3667">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** - Default Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3668">**InkStrokeCount** – ukupan broj rukopisnih poteza od posljednje evidencije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3668">**InkStrokeCount** - Total count of ink strokes since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3669">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** – broj rukopisnih poteza s efektom sloja rukopisa od posljednje evidencije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3669">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with layer ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3670">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** – broj rukopisnih poteza bez pritiska od posljednje evidencije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3670">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** - Count of Ink Strokes without Pressure since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3671">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** – broj rukopisnih poteza s efektom rukopisa olovkom od posljednje evidencije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3671">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with pencil ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3672">**InkStrokeWithTilt** – broj rukopisnih poteza s naginjanjem od posljednje evidencije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3672">**InkStrokeWithTilt** - Count of ink strokes with tilt since the last log.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotenavigationcreatepage"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3673">Office.OneNote.Navigation.CreatePage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3673">Office.OneNote.Navigation.CreatePage</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3679">**IsBlank** – označava je li nova stranica prazna stranica ili je stvorena s predloškom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3679">**IsBlank** - Indicates whether a new page is blanked page or created with a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3680">**IsRecentsView** – označava je li stranica stvorena iz nedavnih stavki ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3680">**IsRecentsView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a recents or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3681">**NavView** – označava je li stranica stvorena iz navigacijskog prikaza ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3681">**NavView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a navigation view or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3682">**NoteType** – označava vrstu (brza bilješka, popis ili fotografija) stranice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3682">**NoteType** - Indicates the type (quick note, list, or photo) of a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3683">**QuickNoteType** – označava vrstu (brza bilješka, popis ili fotografija) stranice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3683">**QuickNoteType** - Indicates the type (quick note, list, or photo) of a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3684">**RailState** – označava stanje navigacijske trake aplikacije OneNote tijekom stvaranja stranice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3684">**RailState** - Indicates the state of OneNote's navigation rail when creating a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3685">**Trigger** – označava ulaznu točku na kojoj je radnja stvaranja stranice započeta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3685">**Trigger** - Indicates an entry point where the create page action is started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3686">**TriggerInfo** – označava dodatne informacije povezane s okidačem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3686">**TriggerInfo** - Indicates additional information related to the trigger.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotesearchsearch"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3724">Office.OneNote.Search.Search</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3724">Office.OneNote.Search.Search</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3725">Ključni ID signala korišten za nadzor mogućnosti korisnika aplikacije OneNote za pronalazak informacija na diljem tisuća stranica i bilježnica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3725">Critical signal ID used to monitor the ability of OneNote users to find information across thousands of pages and notebooks.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3726">Telemetrija korištena za osiguravanje prepoznavanja ključne regresije za aplikaciju OneNote i stanje usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3726">Telemetry used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3727">Ako korisnici ne mogu pronaći informacije diljem bilježnica, time bi se izazvao incident visoke ozbiljnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3727">If users can't find information across notebooks this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3728">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3728">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3729">**PageSearchResultCount** – označava broj rezultata pretraživanja pronađenih u načinu rada pretraživanja stranice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3729">**PageSearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3730">**PageTimeToFirstResultInMs** – označava vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak prvog podudaranja u načinu rada za pretraživanje stranica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3730">**PageTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a page search mode.</span></span>
    
-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3731">**PageTimeToLastResultInMs** – označava vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak posljednjeg podudaranja u načinu rada za pretraživanje stranica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3731">**PageTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3732">**PageTimeToMedianResultInMs** – označava srednje vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak svih podudaranja u načinu rada za pretraživanje stranica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3732">**PageTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3733">**SearchResultCount** – označava broj pronađenih rezultata pretraživanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3733">**SearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3734">**TagSearchResultCount** – označava broj pronađenih rezultata pretraživanja u načinu rada za pretraživanje oznaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3734">**TagSearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3735">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** – označava vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak prvog podudaranja u načinu rada za pretraživanje oznaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3735">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3736">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** – označava vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak posljednjeg podudaranja u načinu rada za pretraživanje oznaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3736">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3737">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** – označava srednje vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak svih podudaranja u načinu rada za pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3737">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3738">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** – označava vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak prvog podudaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3738">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3739">**TimeToLastResultInMs** – označava vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak zadnjeg podudaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3739">**TimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3740">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** – označava srednje vrijeme koje je aplikaciji OneNote potrebno za pronalazak svih podudaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3740">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches.</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotesigscriticalerrorencountered"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3741">Office.OneNote.SIGS.CriticalErrorEncountered</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3741">Office.OneNote.SIGS.CriticalErrorEncountered</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3742">Ovim se događajem bilježi ključan signal koji se koristi za nadziranje stanja servisa Signal Ingestion Service (SIG) evidentiranjem svake kritične pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3742">This event captures a critical signal that is used to monitor the health of Signal Ingestion Service (SIGS), by logging whenever a critical error is encountered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3743">Kritične pogreške mogu blokirati cijeli SIGS, a to će nam pomoći da vidimo svaki takav problem čim korisnici na njih naiđu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3743">Critical errors can block the whole of SIGS, and this will help us catch any such issues as soon as they are encountered by users.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3744">Bez toga ćemo ovisiti o korisnicima koji prijavljuju probleme s kojima se suočavaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3744">Without this, we will be dependent on users to report the problems they are facing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3745">Odsutnost takve telemetrije mogla bi znatno povećati vrijeme rješavanja takvih problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3745">Absence of such telemetry would make the turnaround time for such issues much higher.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3746">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3746">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3747">**ErrorCode** – kôd problema na koji je naišao korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3747">**ErrorCode** - The code of the issue that was hit by the user.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3748">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (u sustavu iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (u sustavu Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3748">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3749">Ovo je ključan signal koji se koristi za nadzor mogućnosti da korisnici aplikacije Sticky Notes mogu stvarati bilješke u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3749">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3750">Telemetrija se koristi za osiguravanje prepoznavanja ključne regresije za aplikaciju OneNote i stanje usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3750">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3751">Ako korisnici ne mogu stvoriti bilješku, time bi se izazvao incident visoke ozbiljnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3751">If users can't create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3752">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3752">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3753">**NoteLocalId** – prepoznatljiv jedinstveni identifikator dodijeljen bilješci u vrijeme kada korisnik stvori bilješku unutar aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3753">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3754">**IsExportable** – zastavica koja označava je li ovaj događaj bio rezultat radnje korisnika ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3754">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3755">Treba se postaviti na Istinito jer je NoteCreated radnja koju aktivira korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3755">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3756">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** – broj verzije koji označava verziju aplikacije Sticky Notes koju korisnik koristi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3756">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3757">Omogućuje prepoznavanje verzija proizvoda s kojima se pojavljuje problem kako bismo mogli ispravno odrediti njegov prioritet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3757">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3762">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3762">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3764">**IsExportable** – zastavica koja označava je li ovaj događaj bio rezultat radnje korisnika ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3764">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3765">Treba se postaviti na Istinito jer je NoteViewed radnja koju aktivira korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3765">Should be set to True as NoteViewed is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3766">**NoteLocalId** – prepoznatljiv jedinstveni identifikator dodijeljen bilješci u vrijeme kada korisnik stvori bilješku unutar aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3766">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3767">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** – broj verzije koji označava verziju aplikacije Sticky Notes koju korisnik koristi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3767">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3768">Omogućuje prepoznavanje verzija proizvoda s kojima se pojavljuje problem kako bismo mogli ispravno odrediti njegov prioritet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3768">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3776">**CachedError_Type** – vrsta predmemorirane pogreške, na primjer, Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3776">**CachedError_Type** -the type of the cached error, for example, Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3777">**ExecutionTime** – vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za repliciranje bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3777">**ExecutionTime** -time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3778">**Gosid** – globalni ID prostora objekta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3778">**Gosid** -global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3783">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – označava je li predmemorirana pogrešna neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3783">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** -is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3784">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3784">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** -is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3785">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3785">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** -is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3786">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3786">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** -is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3790">**LastBackgroundSync** – vremenska oznaka za trenutak kada se proveo posljednji pokušaj sinkronizacije u pozadini</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3790">**LastBackgroundSync** -timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3791">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – datum kada je bilježnica zadnji put prikazana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3791">**LastNotebookViewedDate** -the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>
