- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3794">**NotebookErrorCode** – kod pogreške sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice spremljen je na prostoru grafikona bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3794">**NotebookErrorCode** -notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3795">**NotebookId** – ID bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3795">**NotebookId** -notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3796">**NotebookType** – vrsta bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3796">**NotebookType** -notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3797">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – pokreće li se sinkronizacija ponovno zbog nedosljednosti ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3797">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** -does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3798">**SectionError_Code** – numerirani ili alfanumerički kod koji se koristi za određivanje prirode pogreške sinkronizacije odjeljka i/ili razloga pojave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3798">**SectionError_Code** -a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3799">**SectionError_Description** – opis pogreške sinkronizacije odjeljka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3799">**SectionError_Description** -a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3800">**SectionError_Tag** – označava mjesto na kojem se pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka prikazuje u kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3800">**SectionError_Tag** -indicate where in the code throws the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3801">**SectionError_Type** – vrsta pogreške sinkronizacije odjeljka, na primjer, Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3801">**SectionError_Type** -the type of the section sync error, for example, Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3802">**Success** – je li bilježnica uspješno sinkronizirana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3802">**Success** -is the notebook sync successful or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3803">**SyncDestinationType** – vrsta odredišta sinkronizacije, npr. OneDrive ili SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3803">**SyncDestinationType** -sync destination type, that is, OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationclose"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3895">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3895">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3896">Prikuplja se kada su zatvorene prezentacije programa PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3896">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3897">Sadrži informacije potrebne za pravilno istraživanje i dijagnosticiranje problema do kojih dolazi u postupku zatvaranja koji obuhvaćaju održavanje i sinkroniziranje korisničkih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3897">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3898">Microsoft koristi te podatke da bi osigurao da zatvaranje funkcionira prema očekivanjima i da se korisnički sadržaj uspješno održava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3898">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3899">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3899">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3900">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long –** ima li ova stavka zapisnika svu potrebnu telemetriju dokumenta (polja Data\_Doc\_\*)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3900">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3901">Ako ne, zašto?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3901">If not, why?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3966">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3966">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3967">Prikuplja se kada PowerPoint stvori novu prezentaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3967">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3968"> Obuhvaća metriku uspjeha, neuspjeha i performansi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3968">Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3969">Te se informacije upotrebljavaju da bismo uspješno stvorili datoteke bez smanjenih performansi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3969">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3970">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3970">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3971">**NewDocumentType** – je li novi dokument stvoren iz predloška ili je stvoren kao prazan?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3971">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3972">**FLifeguarded** – je li zaštićen životni vijek dokumenta (značajka koja vraća stanje oštećenog dokumenta bez slanja upita korisniku)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3972">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-3973">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3973">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3974">Prikuplja se kada PowerPoint otvara prezentacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3974">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3975">Sadrži informacije potrebne za pravilno istraživanje i dijagnosticiranje problema do kojih dolazi u završnim fazama postupka otvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3975">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3976">Microsoft koristi te podatke da bi značajka funkcionirala prema očekivanjima i kako ne bi bilo smanjenih performansi prilikom otvaranja prezentacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3976">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-3977">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3977">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3978">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti vrste antivirusnog pregleda (IOAV, AMSI, Nema itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3978">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3979">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti antivirusnog pregleda za svaki otvoreni dokument (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3979">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long -** Predefined set of values of anti-virus scan that happens for every document opened (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3980">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool –** je li ovaj dokument zatvoren i ponovno otvoren?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3980">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3981">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long –** vrijeme tijekom kojeg je aktivnost isključena/nije pokrenuta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3981">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3982">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long –** kako je dokument otvoren (samo za čitanje | samo za pisanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3982">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3983">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3983">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3984">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3984">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3985">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long –** kako je dokument pohranjen u sustavu SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3985">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3986">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long –** stanje dokumenta s obzirom na zaštitu korporativnih podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3986">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3987">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string –** nastavak dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3987">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3988">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string –** nastavak dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3988">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3989">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti oblika datoteke (precizniji od nastavka)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3989">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3990">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string –** mjesto pohrane dokumenta (SharePoint.com, live.net), dostupno samo za domene sustava Office 365</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3990">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3991">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string –** raspršivanje mjesta pohrane dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3991">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3992">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string –** jedinstveni GUID korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3992">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3993">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string –** jedinstveni identifikator identiteta korištenog za akciju zajedničkih dokumenata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3993">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3994">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long –** bit-maska za razne zastavice vezane uz ulaz i izlaz za određeni dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3994">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO-related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3995">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti za vrstu informacija koju upravljanje pravima na informacije primjenjuje na ovom dokumentu (proslijedi, odgovori, SecureReader, uređivanje itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3995">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3996">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool –** istinito ako je HTTP zaglavlje „IsCloudCollabEnabled“ već prihvaćeno iz zahtjeva MOGUĆNOSTI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3996">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3997">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool –** je li dokument otvoren inkrementalno (nova značajka koja otvara dokument bez potrebe za preuzimanjem cijelog dokumenta)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3997">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3998">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool –** podržava li dokument suautorstvo pomoću novog servisa OCS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3998">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports co-authoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-3999">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool –** otvara li se dokument iz lokalne predmemorije?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-3999">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** Is document being opened from local cache?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4000">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool –** otvara li se dokument iz mape koja koristi aplikaciju OneDrive za povratnu sinkronizaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4000">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4001">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti mjesta na kojima se dokument pohranjuje (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, mreža itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4001">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4002">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti detaljnijih lokacija (mapa Temp, mapa preuzimanja, dokumenti servisa One Drive, slike servisa One Drive itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4002">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4003">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long –** broj suautora prilikom otvaranja dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4003">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of co-authors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4004">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti načina na koji je dokument šifriran pomoću lozinke (nema, lozinka za čitanje, lozinka za uređivanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4004">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4005">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti koji naznačuje zašto je dokument označen samo za čitanje (zaključan na poslužitelju, konačni dokument, zaštićen lozinkom za uređivanje itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4005">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4006">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string –** raspršivanje identifikatora resursa za dokumente pohranjene u oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4006">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4007">**Data_Doc_RtcType –** označava kako je kanal u stvarnom vremenu (RTC) postavljen za trenutnu datoteku (onemogućen, nepodržan, na zahtjev, uvijek uključen itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4007">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was set up for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4008">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string –** nepromjenjivi identifikator za dokumente pohranjene u oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4008">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string -** immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4009">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti o protokolu koji se koristi za komuniciranje s poslužiteljem (Http, Cobalt, WOPI itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4009">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4010">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti za vrstu poslužitelja (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4010">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4011">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long –** provjerava temelji li se poslužitelj na sustavu Office14, Office15 ili Office 16</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4011">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long -** verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15, or Office 16</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4012">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long –** generirani GUID koji identificira instancu dokumenta u sklopu iste sesije procesa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4012">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4015">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long –** veličina dokumenta u bajtovima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4015">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4016">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long –** bit-maska koja pokazuje posebne znakove u URL-u ili putu dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4016">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4017">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string –** niz koji određuje davatelja pohrane dokumenta, primjerice „DropBox“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4017">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string -** A string that identifies the document's storage provider, like "DropBox"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4018">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti statusa toka dokumenta (dostupno, trajno onemogućeno, nije dostupno)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4018">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long -** Predefined set of values of status of document Stream(available, permanently disabled, not available)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4019">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string –** raspršivanje punog URL-a dokumenata pohranjenih u oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4019">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string -** hash of full URL of documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4020">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool –** istinito ako je datoteka otvorena inkrementalno pomoću predmemoriranih WRS podataka na glavnom računalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4020">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool -** true if the file was opened incrementally using pre cached WRS data on the host</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4021">**Data\_Doc\_WopiServiceId:string –** identifikator WOPI servisa, na primjer, „Dropbox“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4021">**Data\_Doc\_WopiServiceId:string -** WOPI Service identifier, for example "Dropbox"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4022">**Data\_ExecutionCount:long –** koliko smo puta izvršili protokol IncOpen prije izvršavanja ovog protokola (OpenComplete)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4022">**Data\_ExecutionCount:long -** How many times we executed IncOpen protocol before executing this (OpenComplete) protocol</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4027">**Data_IsProtocolRunInIncOpenMode:bool –** bio je protokol za inkrementalno preuzimanje, što je preuzimanje kod kojeg su dijelovi dokumenta preuzeti nakon što se prethodno prikazao korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4027">**Data_IsProtocolRunInIncOpenMode:bool -** Was the protocol run for an incremental download, which is a download where parts of the document were downloaded after initially showing it to the user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4028">**Data\_MethodId:long –** koji je redak koda interno zadnji izvršen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4028">**Data\_MethodId:long -** Internally which line of code was last one to be executed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4029">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long –** ukupno vrijeme za aktivnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4029">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long -** Total time for Activity</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsave"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4033">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4033">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4034">Prikuplja se svaki put kada PowerPoint izvodi spremanje pomoću modernog puta koda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4034">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4035">Obuhvaća vrstu rezultata uspješno ili neuspješno metrike performansi spremanja i relevantnih metapodataka dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4035">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4036">Problemi sa spremanjem mogu uzrokovati gubitak podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4036">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4037">Microsoft koristi te podatke da bi osigurao da značajka funkcionira prema očekivanjima i da se korisnički sadržaj uspješno održava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4037">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4038">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4038">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4039">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long –** ima li ova stavka zapisnika svu potrebnu telemetriju dokumenta (polja Data\_Doc\_\*)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4039">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4040">Ako ne, zašto?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4040">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4041">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long –** vrijeme potrebno za podizanje dokumenta prije događaja spremanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4041">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4042">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long –** vrijeme potrebno za provjeru revizije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4042">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to check revision</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4112">**Data\_SaveReason:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti koji označava zašto je izvršeno spremanje?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4112">**Data\_SaveReason:long -** Predefined set of values of why this save was performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4113">(AutoSave, ToOCSTransitionSave, ToCSITransitionSave itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4113">(AutoSave, ToOCSTransitionSave, ToCSITransitionSave etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4114">**Data\_SaveType:long –** unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti o vrsti spremanja (SaveAs, Publish, Manual, OMSave itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4114">**Data\_SaveType:long -** Predefined set of values of save type (SaveAs, Publish, Manual, OMSave etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4115">**Data\_SavingWithFont:bool–** spremamo li dokument s novim ugrađenim fontovima?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4115">**Data\_SavingWithFont:bool-** Are we saving document with new embedded fonts?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4119">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4119">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4120">Prikuplja se svaki put kada PowerPoint izvodi Spremi u obliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4120">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4121">Obuhvaća vrstu rezultata uspješno ili neuspješno metrike performansi spremanja i relevantnih metapodataka dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4121">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4122">Problemi sa spremanjem mogu uzrokovati gubitak podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4122">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4123">Microsoft koristi te podatke da bi osigurao da značajka funkcionira prema očekivanjima i da se korisnički sadržaj uspješno održava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4123">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4124">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4124">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4125">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – ima li ovaj unos u zapisnik svu potrebnu telemetriju dokumenta (polja Data_Doc_\*)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4125">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4126">Ako ne, zašto?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4126">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4127">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – neuhvaćene lokalne iznimke dok se aktivnost izvršavala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4127">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4128">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – vrijeme tijekom kojeg je aktivnost bila odvojena ili se nije izvršavala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4128">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4129">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** – kako je dokument otvoren (samo za čitanje | čitanje i pisanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4129">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4130">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4130">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4131">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u novom oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4131">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the new cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4132">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** – kako je dokument pohranjen u sustavu SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4132">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4133">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** – stanje dokumenta s obzirom na zaštitu korporativnih podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4133">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4134">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** – nastavak dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4134">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4135">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** – nastavak dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4135">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4136">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** – unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti oblika datoteke (precizniji od nastavka)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4136">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** - Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4137">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** – mjesto pohrane dokumenta (SharePoint.com, live.net), dostupno samo za domene sustava Office 365</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4137">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4140">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** – jedinstveni identifikator identiteta korišten za akciju zajedničkih dokumenata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4140">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** - Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4141">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** – bit-maska za razne zastavice vezane uz ulaz i izlaz za određeni dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4141">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** - Bitmask for various IO-related flags for a given document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4142">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** – unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti za vrstu informacija koju upravljanje pravima primjenjuje na ovom dokumentu (proslijedi, odgovori, SecureReader, uređivanje itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4142">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** - Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4143">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – istinito ako je HTTP zaglavlje „IsCloudCollabEnabled” već prihvaćeno iz zahtjeva MOGUĆNOSTI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4143">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** - True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4147">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** – otvara li se dokument iz mape koja koristi aplikaciju OneDrive za povratnu sinkronizaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4147">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** - Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4148">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti mjesta na kojima se dokument pohranjuje (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, mreža itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4148">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** - Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4151">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** – unaprijed definirani skup vrijednosti načina na koji je dokument šifriran pomoću lozinke (nema, lozinka za čitanje, lozinka za uređivanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4151">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** - Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsavelegacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4219">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4219">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4220">Prikuplja se svaki put kada PowerPoint izvodi spremanje pomoću naslijeđenog puta koda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4220">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4221">Obuhvaća vrstu rezultata uspješno ili neuspješno metrike performansi spremanja i relevantnih metapodataka dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4221">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4222">Problemi sa spremanjem mogu uzrokovati gubitak podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4222">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4223">Microsoft koristi te podatke da bi osigurao da značajka funkcionira prema očekivanjima i da se korisnički sadržaj uspješno održava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4223">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4224">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4224">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4225">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – ima li ovaj unos u zapisnik svu potrebnu telemetriju dokumenta (polja Data_Doc_\*)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4225">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4226">Ako ne, zašto?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4226">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4227">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – neuhvaćene lokalne iznimke dok se aktivnost izvršavala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4227">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4228">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – vrijeme tijekom kojeg je aktivnost bila odvojena ili se nije izvršavala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4228">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4229">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** – kako je dokument otvoren (samo za čitanje | čitanje i pisanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4229">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4230">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4230">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4231">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4231">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4232">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType:long** – kako je dokument pohranjen u sustavu SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4232">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4233">**Data_Doc_EdpState:long** – stanje dokumenta s obzirom na zaštitu korporativnih podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4233">**Data_Doc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4234">**Data_Doc_Ext:string** – nastavak dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4234">**Data_Doc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptiosrehearseview"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4357">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.IOS.RehearseView</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4357">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.IOS.RehearseView</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4358">Ovaj događaj označava da je korisnik prekinuo sesiju probe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4358">This event is denoting that user has stopped the rehearsal session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4359">Podaci se koriste u kombinaciji s Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.StartSession kao prvi indikator bilo kojeg zaustavljanja ili pogreški s kojima se korisnik suočava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4359">The data is used in combination with Office.PowerPoint.IOS.Android.RehearseView.StartSession as the first indicator of any crashes or errors that user faces.</span></span>  
 
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4360">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4360">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4361">**ConnectionCreationTime** – vrijeme potrebno za stvaranje veza na strani poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4361">**ConnectionCreationTime** - time taken to create service side connections.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4362">**CountDownAlertTime** – vrijeme za koje je prikazano upozorenje za odbrojavanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4362">**CountDownAlertTime** - Time for which countdown alert was displayed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4363">**CountdownInitTime –** vrijeme između dovršetka učitavanja dijaprojekcije i početka odbrojavanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4363">**CountdownInitTime** – Time between slideshow load completed and countdown started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4364">**CritiqueSummary** – sažetak onoga što će svi korisnici-kritičari vidjeti na svojim brojačima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4364">**CritiqueSummary** - Summary of what all critiques user saw with their counts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4365">**ExitEventCode** – kôd za prepoznavanje u kojem scenariju korisnik izlazi iz sesije vježbanja, bez obzira na to je li riječ o scenariju pogreške ili uspješnom izlazu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4365">**ExitEventCode** - Code to identify under which scenario user exit out of rehearse session, whether it was error scenario or successful exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4366">**FRETime** – Vrijeme između početka prikazivanja zaslona s početnim sučeljem i vremena dok ga korisnik nije odbacio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4366">**FRETime** - Time between FRE screen started to display until user dismissed it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4367">**MikrophonePermissionTime** – vrijeme tijekom kojeg je prikazano upozorenje o dozvolama mikrofona dok korisnik ne odabere jednu od mogućnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4367">**MicrophonePermissionTime** - Time for which microphone permission alert was displayed until user selected one of the options.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4368">**PauseRehearsingCount** – koliko je puta korisnik kliknuo na pauziranje probe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4368">**PauseRehearsingCount** - Count of how many times user clicked on pause rehearsal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4369">**RehearsalInitTime** vrijeme koje je probi bilo potrebno da se pokrene</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4369">**RehearsalInitTime** - Time taken by rehearsal to initialize</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4370">**ResumeRehearsingCount** – koliko je puta korisnik kliknuo na nastavak probe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4370">**ResumeRehearsingCount** - Count of how many times user clicked on resume rehearsal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4371">**Sessionid** – to je ID sjednice govornog ulaza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4371">**Sessionid** - This is speech front door session ID.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4372">Koristi se za ispravljanje pogrešaka u zapisnicima servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4372">This is used to debug service logs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4373">**SlideshowViewLoadTime** – vrijeme učitavanja dijaprojekcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4373">**SlideshowViewLoadTime** - Time taken by slideshow to load.</span></span>


#### <a name="officepowerpointpptiosrehearseviewrehearsalsummarypage"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4374">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.IOS.RehearseView.RehearsalSummaryPage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4374">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.IOS.RehearseView.RehearsalSummaryPage</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4375">Događaj se aktivira kada stranica sažetka dovrši učitavanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4375">Event is triggered when summary page has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4376">Taj nam događaj pomaže pri snimanju izvedbe stranice sažetka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4376">This event helps us capture the performance of the summary page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4377">Govori nam koliko je vremena potrebno da se stranica usluge sažetka probe učita na klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4377">It tells how much time it takes for the rehearsal summary service page to load on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4378">Potrebno je održavati performanse značajke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4378">It is required to keep the feature performant.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4379">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4379">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4380">**PayloadCreationTime** – vrijeme koje je potrebno u milisekundama za stvaranje opterećenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4380">**PayloadCreationTime** - This is the time taken in milliseconds to create payload.</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4381">**PostUrlCallTime** – vrijeme koje je potrebno u milisekundama za slanje naknadnog URL poziva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4381">**PostUrlCallTime** - This is the time taken in milliseconds to send the post URL call.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4382">**RehearseSessionId** – to je ID sesije ulaznih vrata govora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4382">**RehearseSessionId** - This is speech front door session ID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4383">Može se koristiti za ispravljanje pogrešaka u zapisnicima servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4383">We can use this to debug service logs.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4476">Prati broj korisnika koji primaju poruke servisa BizBar i Dynamic Canvas iz značajke TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4476">Tracks the number of users receiving BizBar and Dynamic Canvas messages from TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4477">Ti su podaci ključni da bi se razumjelo koje poruke korisnici primaju i na kojoj površini kako bismo osigurali da ne propuste nijednu poruku koja može biti ključna za njihovo daljnje korištenje proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4477">This data is critical to understand what messages users are getting and on what surface so that we can ensure they are not missing any messages that may be critical to their continued use of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4478">Također su potrebni za točno mjerenje uspjeha naših eksperimenata i kampanja pokrenutih putem TMS-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4478">Also needed to accurately measure the success of our experiments and campaigns run through TMS.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4479">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4479">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4480">**Data\_Surface** – naziv površine kojoj se isporučuje ova poruka putem servisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4480">**Data\_Surface** – Name of the surface that this service delivered message is meant for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4481">**Data\_Flight** – identifikator ECS/CT međuverzije koji je korišten za isporuku poruke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4481">**Data\_Flight** – ECS/CT Flight identifier that was used to deliver this message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4482">**Data\_CampaignId** – identifikator kampanje koje je ova poruka dio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4482">**Data\_CampaignId** – identifier of the campaign that this message is part of</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4483">**Data\_MessageId** – identifikator ove poruke koju je isporučio servis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4483">**Data\_MessageId** – identifier of this service delivered message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4484">**Data\_TransactionId** – identifikator ove transakcije sa servisom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4484">**Data\_TransactionId** – identifier of this transaction with the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4485">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – korak u kojem je ovaj događaj zapisan (poruka primljena i poruka prikazana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4485">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – The step in which this event was logged (message received vs message displayed)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxacccheckeracccheckerfinalviolationcountperrule"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4618">Office.UX.AccChecker.AccCheckerFinalViolationCountPerRule</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4618">Office.UX.AccChecker.AccCheckerFinalViolationCountPerRule</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4619">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada se prijave problemi s pristupačnošću za trenutačno otvoreni dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4619">This event is triggered when Accessibility issues are reported for the currently opened document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4620">Ovaj događaj predstavlja povrede pristupačnosti (pogreške, upozorenja i savjete) koja postoje za svako pravilo, za otvoreni dokument pri početku i kraju sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4620">This event represents the Accessibility violations (Errors, Warnings, and Tips) that exist per Rule, for the opened document at the beginning and end of the session.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4621">Ovaj događaj upotrebljava se za evidenciju broja povreda pristupačnosti (pogreške, upozorenja i savjete) za svako pravilo, za otvoreni dokument pri početku i kraju sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4621">This event is used to record the counts of Accessibility violations (Errors, Warnings, and Tips) per Rule, for the opened document at the beginning and end of the session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4622">Pojedinosti o brojevima povreda za svako pravilo pomažu Microsoftu pri prepoznavanju koji su problemi s pristupačnošću najčešći u dokumentima sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4622">Details of violation counts per rule help Microsoft to identify which Accessibility issues are most common in Office documents.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4623">To pomaže pri njihovu otklanjanju te potiče stvaranje inkluzivnog okruženja na radnom mjestu i u učionici za osobe s invaliditetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4623">This helps with work on remediating them and drives the creation of an inclusive environment in the workplace and classroom for people with disabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4624">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4624">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4625">**Data_FinalCount_RuleID_0** – broj povreda ID-a pravila = n koji ostaje od zadnjeg puta kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4625">**Data_FinalCount_RuleID_0** - Number of violations of Rule ID = n that remain the last time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxacccheckeracccheckerviolationinformation"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4667">Office.UX.AccChecker.AccCheckerViolationInformation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4667">Office.UX.AccChecker.AccCheckerViolationInformation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4668">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada se prijave problemi s pristupačnošću za trenutačno otvoreni dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4668">This event is triggered when Accessibility issues are reported for the currently opened document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4669">On predstavlja zbirni broj povreda (pogreške, upozorenja i savjete) koja postoje za svako pravilo, za otvoreni dokument pri početku i kraju sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4669">It represents the aggregate counts of violations (Errors, Warnings, and Tips) for the opened document at the beginning and end of the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4670">Ovaj događaj upotrebljava se za evidenciju zbirnog broja povreda pristupačnosti (pogreške, upozorenja i savjete) za otvoreni dokument pri početku i kraju sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4670">This event is used to record the aggregate counts of Accessibility violations (Errors, Warnings, and Tips) for the opened document at the beginning and end of the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4671">Znanje stečeno iz upotrebe Provjere pristupačnosti Microsoftu omogućuje poboljšanje kako bi doživljaji njegove aplikacije bili inkluzivniji za osobe s invaliditetom u scenarijima upotrebe sustava Office za radno mjesto i učionicu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4671">The knowledge of Accessibility checker usage allows Microsoft to improve its application experiences to be more inclusive for people with disabilities in Office usage scenarios for the workplace and classroom.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4672">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4672">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4673">**FinalDocID** – konačni ID dokumenta skeniranog dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4673">**FinalDocID** - Final DocumentID of the scanned document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4674">**FinalDocUrlHash** – konačni URL raspršivanja dokumenta skeniranog dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4674">**FinalDocUrlHash** - Final DocumentURLHash of the scanned document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4675">**FinalErrorCount** – konačan broj pogrešaka koje je Provjera pristupačnosti prijavila za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4675">**FinalErrorCount** - Final count of Errors reported by Accessibility Checker for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4676">**FinalIntelligentServiceCount** – konačan broj problema s pametnim servisima koje je Provjera pristupačnosti prijavila za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4676">**FinalIntelligentServiceCount** - Final count of Intelligent services issues reported by Accessibility Checker for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4677">**FinalTipCount** – konačan broj savjeta koje je Provjera pristupačnosti prijavila za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4677">**FinalTipCount** - Final count of tips reported by Accessibility Checker for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4678">**FinalViolationCount** – konačan broj povreda koje je Provjera pristupačnosti prijavila za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4678">**FinalViolationCount** - Final count of violations reported by Accessibility Checker for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4679">**FinalWarningCount** – konačan broj upozorenja koje je Provjera pristupačnosti prijavila za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4679">**FinalWarningCount** - Final count of warnings reported by Accessibility Checker in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4680">**InitialDocID** – početni ID dokumenta skeniranog dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4680">**InitialDocID** - Initial DocumentID of the scanned document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4681">**InitialDocUrlHash** – početni URL raspršivanja dokumenta skeniranog dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4681">**InitialDocUrlHash** - Initial DocumentURLHash of the scanned document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4682">**InitialErrorCount** – broj svih povreda vrste Pogreška koje su pronađene prvi put kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4682">**InitialErrorCount** - Number of all violations of type Error that were found the first time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4683">**InitialIntelligentServicesCount** – broj svih povreda vrste Pametna usluga koje su pronađene prvi put kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4683">**InitialIntelligentServicesCount** - Number of all violations of type Intelligent Service that were found the first time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4684">**InitialTipCount** – broj svih povreda vrste Savjet koje su pronađene prvi put kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4684">**InitialTipCount** - Number of all violations of type Tip that were found the first time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4685">**InitialUrlHash** – broj svih povreda vrste Pogreška koje su pronađene prvi put kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4685">**InitialUrlHash** - Number of all violations of type error that were found the first time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4686">**InitialViolationCount** – broj svih povreda koje su pronađene prvi put kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4686">**InitialViolationCount** - Number of all violations that were found the first time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4687">**InitialWarningCount** – broj svih povreda vrste Upozorenje koje su pronađene prvi put kada je Provjera pristupačnosti bila pokrenuta u sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4687">**InitialWarningCount** - Number of all violations of type Warning that were found the first time the acc checker ran in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4688">**PaneOpened** – Booleova vrijednost koja prati je li okno Provjere pristupačnosti dokumenta bilo otvoreno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4688">**PaneOpened** - A Boolean that tracks whether the Accessibility Checker pane was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4689">**ServerDocID** – ID dokumenta poslužitelja za dokument koji je skenirala Provjera pristupačnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4689">**ServerDocID** - Server DocumentID for the document scanned by the Accessibility checker</span></span>


#### <a name="officeuxacccheckerbackgroundacccheckerenabledstate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4690">Office.UX.AccChecker.BackgroundAccCheckerEnabledState</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4690">Office.UX.AccChecker.BackgroundAccCheckerEnabledState</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4691">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada je korisnik ili IT administrator omogućio pozadinski alat za provjeru pristupačnosti za korisnika sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4691">This event is triggered when the user or IT Admin has enabled the Background Accessibility checker for the Office user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4692">Ovaj se događaj upotrebljava za razumijevanje slučajeva kada je pozadinski alat za provjeru pristupačnosti omogućen za korisnike sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4692">This event is used to understand the instances when the Background Accessibility checker is enabled for Office users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4693">Omogućeno stanje pozadinskog alata za provjeru pristupačnosti omogućuje Microsoftu utvrditi mogu li se dokumenti automatski skenirati u pozadini.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4693">The enabled status of the Background Accessibility checker allows Microsoft to understand if documents can be scanned automatically in the background.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4694">Time se stvara inkluzivnije okruženje na radnom mjesto i u učionici za osobe s invaliditetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4694">This helps to create a more inclusive workplace and classroom environment for people with disabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4695">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4695">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4696">**BackgroundAccCheckerEnabled** – Booleova vrijednost za praćenje stanja Omogućeno/Onemogućen pozadinskog alata za provjeru pristupačnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4696">**BackgroundAccCheckerEnabled** - Boolean to track the Enabled/Disabled state of the Background Accessibility checker</span></span>


#### <a name="officeuxacccheckerbackgroundscanningcheckboxclicked"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4697">Office.UX.AccChecker.BackgroundScanningCheckboxClicked</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4697">Office.UX.AccChecker.BackgroundScanningCheckboxClicked</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4698">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada korisnik omogući pozadinski alat za provjeru pristupačnosti iz okna zadatka Provjere pristupačnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4698">This event is triggered when the user enables the Background Accessibility checker from the Accessibility checker task pane.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4699">Ovaj se događaj upotrebljava za razumijevanje slučajeva kada je pozadinski alat za provjeru pristupačnosti omogućen za dokumente sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4699">This event is used to understand the instances when the Background Accessibility checker is enabled for Office documents.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4700">Omogućeno stanje pozadinskog alata za provjeru pristupačnosti omogućuje Microsoftu utvrditi mogu li se dokumenti automatski skenirati u pozadini.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4700">The enabled status of the Background Accessibility checker allows Microsoft to understand if documents can be scanned automatically in the background.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4701">Time se stvara inkluzivnije okruženje na radnom mjesto i u učionici za osobe s invaliditetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4701">This helps to create a more inclusive workplace and classroom environment for people with disabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4702">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4702">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4703">**FinalBackgroundScanningState** – početno stanje potvrdnog okvira koji omogućuje pozadinsko skeniranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4703">**FinalBackgroundScanningState** - Initial state of the checkbox that enables background scanning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4704">**InitialBackgroundScanningState** – početno stanje potvrdnog okvira koji omogućuje pozadinsko skeniranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4704">**InitialBackgroundScanningState** - Initial state of the checkbox that enables background scanning</span></span>


#### <a name="officeuxacccheckerdisabledresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4705">Office.UX.AccChecker.DisabledResults</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4705">Office.UX.AccChecker.DisabledResults</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4706">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada se Provjera pristupačnosti onemogući za otvoreni dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4706">This event is triggered when the Accessibility Checker gets disabled for the opened document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4707">Ovaj se događaj upotrebljava za razumijevanje slučajeva kada se alat za provjeru pristupačnosti sustava Office onemogući zbog starije ili nepodržane verzije dokumenta sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4707">This event is used to understand the instances when the Office Accessibility checker gets disabled, due to a legacy or unsupported Office document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4708">Onemogućeno stanje Provjere pristupačnosti omogućuje Microsoftu utvrđivanje koliko se često dokument ne može skenirati te pomaže korisnicima pri dopuštanju skeniranja takvih dokumenata – pretvaranjem dokumenta u suvremeni oblik datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4708">The disabled status of the Accessibility checker allows Microsoft to understand how often a document cannot be scanned, and to assist users in allowing the scanning of such documents – by upconverting the document to a modern file format.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4709">Time se stvara inkluzivnije okruženje na radnom mjesto i u učionici za osobe s invaliditetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4709">This helps to create a more inclusive workplace and classroom environment for people with disabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4710">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4710">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4711">**Data_Disabled_ID** – ID onemogućene pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4711">**Data_Disabled_ID** - ID of the disabled error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4712">**Data_Disabled_Reason** – razlog za onemogućivanje Provjere pristupačnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4712">**Data_Disabled_Reason** - Reason for disabling the Accessibility Checker</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4713">**Data_IsUpConvertEnabled** – prati je li dostupna mogućnost pretvaranja dokumenta u suvremen oblik datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4713">**Data_IsUpConvertEnabled** - Tracks whether Upconvert to a modern file format is available for the document</span></span>


#### <a name="officeuxacccheckershowtaskpane"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4714">Office.UX.AccChecker.ShowTaskPane</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4714">Office.UX.AccChecker.ShowTaskPane</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4715">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada se okno zadatka Provjere pristupačnosti pokrene za trenutačno otvoreni dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4715">This event is triggered when the Accessibility Checker task pane is launched for the currently opened document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4716">Ovaj se događaj upotrebljava za razumijevanje upotrebe Provjere pristupačnosti sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4716">This event is used to understand the usage of the Office Accessibility Checker.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4717">Provjera pristupačnosti upotrebljava se za prepoznavanje i popravak problema s pristupačnošću u dokumentima sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4717">The Accessibility Checker is used to identify and remediate Accessibility issues in Office documents.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4718">Znanje stečeno iz upotrebe Provjere pristupačnosti Microsoftu omogućuje poboljšanje kako bi doživljaji njegove aplikacije bili inkluzivniji za osobe s invaliditetom u scenarijima upotrebe sustava Office za radno mjesto i učionicu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4718">The knowledge of Accessibility Checker usage allows Microsoft to improve its application experiences to be more inclusive for people with disabilities in Office usage scenarios for the workplace and classroom.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4719">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4719">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4720">**BackgroundScanCheckboxEnabled** – prati je li omogućen pozadinski alat za provjeru pristupačnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4720">**BackgroundScanCheckboxEnabled** - Tracks whether the Background Accessibility Checker is enabled</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4721">**Column** – svrha</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4721">**Column** - Purpose</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4722">**DocUrlHash** – jedinstveno raspršivanje ID-a dokumenta koji je bio skeniran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4722">**DocUrlHash** - Unique doc ID hash of the document that was scanned</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4723">**HasAccessibilityViolations** – prati sadrži li dokument ikakve povrede pristupačnosti u trenutku otvaranja okna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4723">**HasAccessibilityViolations** - Tracks if the document contains any accessibility violations at the point the pane is opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4724">**IsPaneDisabled** – prati je li okno Provjere pristupačnosti otvoreno u onemogućenom stanju (stara ili nepodržana verzija dokumenta)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4724">**IsPaneDisabled** - Tracks if the Accessibility Checker pane is opened in a disabled state (legacy or unsupported document)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4725">**PaneOpenedBefore** – prati je li okno Provjere pristupačnost već bilo otvoreno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4725">**PaneOpenedBefore** - Tracks if the Accessibility Checker pane was opened before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4726">**WAC_ServerDocId** – ID dokumenta poslužitelja za dokument koji je bio skeniran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4726">**WAC_ServerDocId** - Server Document ID for the document that was scanned</span></span>


#### <a name="officevisiosharedfeatureexperimentation"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4727">Office.Visio.Shared.FeatureExperimentation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4727">Office.Visio.Shared.FeatureExperimentation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4728">Značajka prati isporuku testnih verzija korisnicima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4728">Tracks feature flighting for users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4729">Taj nam događaj pomaže odrediti uspješnost ili neuspješnost isporuke testnih verzija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4729">This event helps us determines success or failure of feature flights.</span></span>
