  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4731">**Data\_Enable:bool**– vrijednost „istinito” označava da je značajka omogućena za trenutnog korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4731">**Data\_Enable:bool**- true indicate the feature is enabled for current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4732">**Data\_Feature:string** – naziv značajke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4732">**Data\_Feature:string** - name of the feature</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4733">**Data\_Flighted:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da je značajka omogućena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4733">**Data\_Flighted:bool** - true indicates the feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4734">**Data\_Licensed:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da je značajka u postupku provjere licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4734">**Data\_Licensed:bool** - true indicates the feature is under licensing check</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4735">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da korisnik ima licencu za pretplatu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4735">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** - true indicates the user has subscription license</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedrefreshsmartdiagram"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4736">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4736">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4737">Bilježi neuspjela osvježavanja dijagrama kada je datoteka stvorena putem DV-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4737">Captures diagram refresh failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4738">To nam olakšava ispravljanje pogrešaka i problema pri osvježavanju podataka u DV dijagramu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4738">This helps us debug the failures and issues in data refresh in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4739">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4739">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4740">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** – istinito ako je osvježeni dijagram izvorno stvoren korištenjem poveznika koji se temelji na mogućnosti „niz”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4740">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true if the refreshed diagram was originally created using connector based on sequence" option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4741">**Data\_DialogError**:**string** – pogreška tijekom osvježavanja pametnog dijagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4741">**Data\_DialogError**:**string** - error during refreshing smart diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4742">**Data\_FileError:string** – niz pogreške kada povezana datoteka programa Excel nije valjana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4742">**Data\_FileError:string** - error string when connected Excel file is invalid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4743">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** – istinito ako je korisnik odabrao mogućnost koja prebriše dijagram tijekom osvježavanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4743">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** - true if user selected overwrite diagram option during refresh</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4744">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** – istinito ako se korisniku tijekom osvježavanja podataka prikazalo bilo kakvo upozorenje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4744">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** - true if there was any warning shown to user during data refresh</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedwritebacktoexcel"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4745">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4745">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4746">Bilježi neuspjela povratna zapisivanja u Excel kada je datoteka stvorena putem DV-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4746">Captures Excel write back failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4747">To nam olakšava ispravljanje pogrešaka i problema pri povratnom zapisivanju u Excel u DV dijagramu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4747">This helps us debug the failures and issues in writing back data to Excel in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4748">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4748">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4749">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” znači da se poveznici stvaraju na temelju postavki niza</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4749">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true means connectors are created based on sequence settings</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4750">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** – to polje označava je li osnova za stvaranje dijagrama „Table” ili „CustomRange”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4750">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** - This filed indicates whether diagram is created from  "Table" or "CustomRange"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4751">**Data\_DialogError:string** – prilagođena vrsta pogreške prilikom stvaranja pametnog dijagrama putem programa Excel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4751">**Data\_DialogError:string** - Custom Error type while creating smart diagram through Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4752">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** – broj oblika dodanih tijekom funkcije povratnog zapisivanja u Excel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4752">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** - Number of shapes added during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4753">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** – broj oblika izbrisanih tijekom funkcije povratnog zapisivanja u Excel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4753">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Number of shapes deleted during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4754">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da je korisnik odabrao mogućnost koja prebriše podatke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4754">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - true indicate user selected overwrite data option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4755">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da su izvorni podaci izmijenjeni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4755">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - true indicates source data is modified</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4756">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da se korisniku prikazalo upozorenje o ažuriranju podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4756">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - true means data update warning shown to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4757">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da se korisniku prikazalo upozorenje zbog prisutnosti formule u programu Excel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4757">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user because of presence of formula in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4758">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da se korisniku prikazalo upozorenje zbog odsutnosti identifikatora sljedećeg koraka u programu Excel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4758">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - true indicates warning show to the user because next step Identifier missing in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4759">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** – vrijednost „istinito” označava da se korisniku prikazalo upozorenje da pretvori podatke programa Excel u tablični oblik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4759">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user to convert Excel data to table format</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfilenewcreatenewfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4760">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4760">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4761">Taj događaj označava da je novi dokument stvoren u programu Office Word i prati uspjeh ili neuspjeh operacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4761">This event indicates that a new document is created in Office Word and tracks success or failure of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4762">Događaj se koristi za praćenje radi li stvaranje novog dokumenta prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4762">The event is used to monitor that new document creation is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4763">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4763">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4764">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4764">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4765">**Data\_DirtyState** – je li dokument stvoren u prljavom stanju (s promjenama koje treba spremiti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4765">**Data\_DirtyState** - whether the document was created in a dirty state (with changes that need to be saved)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4766">**Data\_ErrorID** – identifikator pogreške u slučaju pogreške operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4766">**Data\_ErrorID** - error identifier in case of operation failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4767">**Data\_MainPdod –** identifikator dokumenta tijekom ove sesije postupka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4767">**Data\_MainPdod** - The document identifier during this process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4768">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** – označava je li dokument stvoren iz prilagođenog predloška</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4768">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** - indicates whether the document was created from a custom template</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenuserinitiatedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4769">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4769">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4770">Ovaj događaj označava da je aplikacija Office Word otvorila dokument na zahtjev korisnika umjesto programski putem aplikacije Office Word.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4770">This event indicates Office Word opens a document by user initiation instead of by Office Word programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4771">Sadrži i ključne podatke o performansama otvaranja datoteka, a iz perspektive korisnika predstavlja događaj pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4771">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4772">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li otvaranje datoteka prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4772">The event monitors whether file-open is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4773">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4773">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4774">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4774">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4775">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4775">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4776">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4776">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4777">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova za koje vjerujemo da možemo otvoriti datoteku bez njih ako ih dobijemo prije nego što korisnik poželi početi uređivati ili možda spremati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4777">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4778">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – broj (sažetih) bajtova bez kojih bismo možda mogli otvoriti datoteku, ali bi to zahtijevalo značajna ulaganja u kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4778">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4779">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova koje moramo imati prije nego što možemo početi otvarati datoteku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4779">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4780">**Data_BytesUnknown** – broj bajtova u dijelovima dokumenta koje ne očekujemo pronaći.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4780">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4781">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4781">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4782">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4782">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4783">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4783">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4784">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4784">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4785">**Data_Doc_Ext** – nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4785">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4786">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4786">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactcmdgosubsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4836">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4836">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4837">Taj događaj označava da korisnik sprema promjene u novom dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4837">This event indicates that a user is saving their changes to a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4838">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li spremanje u novom dokumentu prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4838">The event monitors whether saving to a new document is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4839">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4839">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4840">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4840">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4841">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4841">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4842">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4842">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4843">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko je dugo aktivnost bila odvojena od niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4843">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4844">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4844">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4845">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4845">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4846">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4846">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4847">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4847">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4848">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4848">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4849">**Data_Doc_Ext** – nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4849">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4850">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4850">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4851">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4851">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactfconfirmsavedoccorequerysave"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4886">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4886">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4887">Taj događaj označava da Office Word traži od korisnika da spremi promjene kada pokuša zatvoriti dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4887">This event indicates Office Word prompts the user to save changes when it tries to close the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4888">To omogućuje Microsoftu praćenje radi li spremanje pri zatvaranju prema očekivanjima kako bi se spriječio gubitak podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4888">It allows Microsoft to monitor whether save-at-quit works as expected to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4889">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li spremanje pri zatvaranju prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4889">The event monitors whether save-at-quit is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4890">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4890">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4891">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4891">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4892">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4892">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4893">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4893">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4894">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko je dugo aktivnost bila odvojena od niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4894">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4895">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4895">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4896">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4896">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4897">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4897">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4898">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4898">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4899">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4899">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4900">**Data_Doc_Ext** – nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4900">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4901">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4901">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4902">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4902">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4903">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje naziva domene koji identificira korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4903">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4904">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta kojim se izvršava otvaranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4904">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4905">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – bilježi način otvaranja dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4905">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4907">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – radnje koje dopuštaju pravila zaštite elektroničkih podataka koja su primijenjena na dokument/korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4907">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4908">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – zastavica koja označava da je dokument inkrementalno otvoren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4908">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4910">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – zastavica koja označava da je otvorena izvanmrežna kopija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4910">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4911">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – zastavica koja označava da na računalu postoji automatski sinkronizirana kopija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4911">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4912">**Data_Doc_Location** – označava koji je servis pružio dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4912">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesavesaveassavefile"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-4948">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4948">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4949">Taj događaj označava da Office Word sprema dokument u novi dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4949">This event indicates Office Word saves a document into a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4950">On Microsoftu omogućuje otkrivanje pogrešaka pri izvođenju naredbe Spremi kao, što je važno za izbjegavanje gubitka podataka iz dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4950">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in save-as which is important to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4951">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li naredba Spremi kao prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4951">The event monitors whether save-as is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4952">Koristi se i izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4952">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-4953">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4953">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4954">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4954">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4955">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4955">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4956">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** – izvješćuje jesmo li mogli pravilno popuniti ostale vrijednosti vezane uz telemetriju dokumenta u sklopu događaja za odredišni dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4956">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event for the destination document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4957">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4957">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4958">**Data_AddDocTelemResSrc** – izvješćuje jesmo li mogli pravilno popuniti ostale vrijednosti vezane uz telemetriju dokumenta u sklopu događaja za izvorni dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4958">**Data_AddDocTelemResSrc** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event for the source document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4959">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4959">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4960">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko je dugo aktivnost bila odvojena od niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4960">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4961">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4961">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4962">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4962">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4963">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4963">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4964">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4964">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4965">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4965">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4966">**Data_Doc_Ext** – nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4966">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4967">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4967">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4968">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4968">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4971">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – izvješćuje o predmemoriranim zastavicama za postavljanje mogućnosti zahtjeva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4971">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-4972">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – radnje koje dopuštaju pravila zaštite elektroničkih podataka koja su primijenjena na dokument/korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-4972">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordworddocumentdirtyflagchanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5073">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5073">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5074">Ovaj događaj označava da Office Word uređuje dokument koji mijenja interno stanje dokumenta u „prljavo”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5074">This event indicates Office Word edits a document that changes the document internal state into "dirty".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5075">On Microsoftu omogućuje procjenu stanja značajke uređivanja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5075">It allows Microsoft to evaluate the feature health of edit-document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5076">Taj je događaj impuls korisničkog uređivanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5076">The event is a heartbeat of user edits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5077">Koristi se i izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5077">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5078">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5078">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5079">**Data\_CollectionTime–** vremenska oznaka događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5079">**Data\_CollectionTime-** Timestamp of the event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5080">**Data\_DocumentLocation–** vrsta mjesta dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5080">**Data\_DocumentLocation-** type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5081">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails–** podvrsta mjesta dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5081">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails-** Sub-type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5082">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled–** označava je li omogućeno spremanje u bilo kojem trenutku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5082">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled-** Indicates whether always-save was enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5083">**Data\_FirstEditTime–** vremenska oznaka prvog uređivanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5083">**Data\_FirstEditTime-** Timestamp of first edit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5084">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors–** broj koautora koji uređuju dokument tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5084">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors-** Number of co-authors editing the document during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5085">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied–** broj izmjena u dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5085">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied-** Number of edits made to the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5086">**Data\_Pdod–** identifikator dokumenta u sklopu procesa Office Word</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5086">**Data\_Pdod-** Document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5087">**Data\_UrlHash–** raspršivanje puta dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5087">**Data\_UrlHash-** Hash of the document path</span></span>

#### <a name="readconversation"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5118">read.conversation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5118">read.conversation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5120">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5120">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5121">**above_40fps** – broj prikazanih okvira iznad 40 fps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5121">**above_40fps** - count of frames rendered above 40 fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5122">**above_50fps** – broj prikazanih okvira iznad 50 fps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5122">**above_50fps** - count of frames rendered above 50 fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5123">**above_55fps** – broj prikazanih okvira iznad 55 fps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5123">**above_55fps** - count of frames rendered above 55 fps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5124">**adal_id** – ID provjere autentičnosti aktivnog direktorija računa, jedinstveni identifikator u sustavu za provjere autentičnosti tvrtke Microsoft</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5124">**adal_id** - the account's active directory authentication ID, a unique identifier in the Microsoft authentication system</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5125">**component_name** – naziv komponente/prikaza koji je aktivan tijekom filtriranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5125">**component_name** - the name of the component/view that is active during the filtering</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5126">**event_mode** – mjesto u aplikaciji na kojem je korisnik ušao u razgovor (grupni ili drugi)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5126">**event_mode** - the place in the app that the user entered the conversation (groups or other)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5127">**internet_message_id** – ID praćenja za najnoviju poruku u razgovoru</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5127">**internet_message_id** - a tracking ID for the most recent message in the conversation</span></span>
      
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5128">**orientation** – orijentacija ekrana u trenutku događaja (okomito ili vodoravno)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5128">**orientation** - the screen orientation at the time of the even (portrait or landscape)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5129">**recent_message_id** – ID najnovije poruke u razgovoru</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5129">**recent_message_id** - the ID of the most recent message in the conversation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5130">**suggested_reply_state** – stanje predloženih odgovora za ovaj razgovor (nedostupno, dostupno, prikazano, korišteno ili odbačeno)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5130">**suggested_reply_state** - the state of suggested replies for this conversation (unavailable, available, shown, used, or discarded)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5131">**suggested_reply_types** – označava vrstu i broj predloženog odgovora prikazanog/korištenog za taj razgovor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5131">**suggested_reply_types** - indicates type and count of suggested reply shown/used for this conversation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5132">To je rječnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5132">It’s a dictionary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5133">Na primjer, {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5133">For example, {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5134">**total_count** – ukupan broj okvira koji komponenta prikazuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5134">**total_count** - total frames displayed by the component</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5135">**view_duration** – koliko je dugo korisnik pregledavao komponentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5135">**view_duration** - how long the component was viewed by the user</span></span>

#### <a name="saveattempt"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5136">save.attempt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5136">save.attempt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5137">Omogućuje utvrđivanje utjecaja problema uzrokovanih korisnicima koji pokušavaju spremiti datoteku procjenom broja zahvaćenih sesija te postoje li zajedničke značajke tih sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5137">Allows us to identify the impact of issues caused by users attempting to save a file by evaluating the number of sessions impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5138">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5138">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5139">**file_type** – vrsta datoteke koju je korisnik pokušao spremiti (primjerice .doc)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5139">**file_type** - The type of file the user tried to save (such as .doc)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5140">**origin** – odakle pokušaj spremanja potječe (primjerice iz poruke e-pošte) kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme u vezi sa spremanjem datoteke s određenog mjesta u aplikaciji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5140">**origin** - Where the file save attempt originated from (such as from an email) so we can detect issues associated with saving a file from a specific place in the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5141">**token_type** – vrsta tokena korištenog za provjeru autentičnosti radi spremanja datoteka koji nam pomaže prepoznati probleme s provjerom autentičnosti u vezi sa spremanjem datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5141">**token_type** - the type of token used to authenticate the account in order to save the file to help us detect authentication issues associated with saving a file</span></span>

#### <a name="searchsubtabselected"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5142">search.subtab.selected</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5142">search.subtab.selected</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5143">Događaj prikuplja točke podrijetla za razlog što je odabrana podkartica za pretraživanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5143">The event collects origin points for the reason a search sub_tab was selected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5144">Podkartice se nalaze ispod primarne trake za pretraživanje aplikacije radi filtriranja podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5144">The sub tabs sit under the primary app search bar to filter data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5145">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje praćenje pilula vrste entiteta (sve, pošta, kontakti i kalendar) koje korisnici koriste kada provode pretraživanja kako bismo mogli osigurati da mehanizmi filtara pretraživanja propisno funkcioniraju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5145">This event lets us track the entity type pills (all, mail, contacts, and calendar) that users are using when they do their searches so we can ensure the search filter mechanisms are working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5146">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5146">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5147">**properties_general** – opća svojstva koja prikupljaju svi događaji Aria</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5147">**properties_general** -The general properties that all Aria event is collecting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5148">**selected_reason** – uzrok vrste pilule koja se odabire, a koja može biti jedna od ovih vrijednost (glif je ikona)i: tap_on_header, tap_on_see_all, enter_search_mode, mail_glyph, calendar_glyph.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5148">**selected_reason** - The cause of the type pill getting selected, which could be one of the following values (glyph being an icon): tap_on_header, tap_on_see_all, enter_search_mode, mail_glyph, calendar_glyph.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5149">**subtab_type** – vrsta pilule koja je odabrana, a koja može biti jedna od ove četiri vrijednosti: sve, pošta, kontakt, događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5149">**subtab_type** - The type pill that got selected, which could be one of these four values: all, mail, contact, event.</span></span>

#### <a name="sendmessage"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5150">send.message</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5150">send.message</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5151">Koristi se za nadzor mogućeg negativnog utjecaja na funkciju i stanje slanja poruka e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5151">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on the performance and health of sending email messages.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5152">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5152">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5153">**account** – prati račun koji je proveo radnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5153">**account** - tracks the account that performed the action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5154">**compose_duration** – prati ukupno vrijeme koje je korisniku bilo potrebno za sastavljanje poruke uključujući sesiju s više skica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5154">**compose_duration** - tracks the total time user took to compose the message including multiple drafts session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5155">**draft_message_id** – prati ID sastavljanja poruke koja se šalje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5155">**draft_message_id** - tracks the compose message ID of the message being sent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5156">**event_mode** – prati način događaja ako se odnosi na poruku, („grupni” ili „ostalo”)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5156">**event_mode** - tracks the event mode if applicable to the message ("groups" or "other")</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5157">**has_attachment** – označava ima li poruka privitke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5157">**has_attachment** - indicates whether message has any attachments</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5158">**has_mip_label** – označava je li poruka označena oznakom MIP ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5158">**has_mip_label** - indicates whether a MIP label was stamped on the message or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5159">**is_group_escalation** – označava je li ovo eskalirana grupna poruka, „eskalirana poruka” jest poruka koja je poslana u ulaznu poštu korisnika zbog eskalacije (pretplata na grupu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5159">**is_group_escalation** - is this a group escalated message, "escalated message" is a message that was sent to the user's mailbox because of an escalation (subscribed to group)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5160">**is_groups** – prati je li poslana poruka grupna poruka ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5160">**is_groups** - track whether message sent is a groups message or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5161">**key_stroke_count** – prati broj pritisaka tipki za poruku koja se šalje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5161">**key_stroke_count** - tracks the keystrokes count for the message that is being sent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5162">**message_id** – prati ID poruke koja se odgovorila/proslijedila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5162">**message_id** - tracks the message ID being replied/forwarded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5163">**origin** – označava gdje je sastavljanje pokrenuto, npr. novo, odgovor, brzi odgovor itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5163">**origin** - indicates where compose was initiated, that is, new, reply, quick reply etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5164">**send_draft_origin** – označava gdje je slanje pokrenuto, tj. sastavljanje ili brzi odgovor</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5164">**send_draft_origin** - indicates where send was initiated, that is, compose or quick reply</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5165">**smart_compose_model_version** – prati koja se verzija modela pametnog sastavljanja upotrebljava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5165">**smart_compose_model_version** - tracks which version of smart compose model is being used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5166">**source_inbox** – označava vrstu izvorne ulazne pošte za referentnu poruku,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5166">**source_inbox** - indicates source inbox type for reference message,</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5167">**suggested_reply_state** – utvrđuje predloženo stanje odgovora, tj. nedostupno, dostupno, prikazano, korišteno ili odbačeno za ovu poslanu poštu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5167">**suggested_reply_state** - capturing suggested reply state that is, unavailable, available, shown, used, discarded for this sent mail</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5168">**suggested_reply_types** – označava vrstu i broj predloženog odgovora prikazanog/korištenog za tu poslanu poruku e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5168">**suggested_reply_types** - indicates type and count of suggested reply shown/used for this sent email.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5169">To je rječnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5169">It’s a dictionary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5170">Na primjer, {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5170">For example, {text: 2,  send_avail: 1}.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5171">**suggestions_requested** – označava koliko ste modela pametnog sastavljanja tražili</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5171">**suggestions_requested** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions requested</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5172">**suggestions_results** – rezultat prijedloga pametnog sastavljanja, tj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5172">**suggestions_results** - smart compose suggestions’ result, i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5173">prihvaćeno, odbijeno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5173">accepted, rejected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5174">**suggestions_returned** – označava koliko je prijedloga pametnog sastavljanja vraćeno s poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5174">**suggestions_returned** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions returned from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5175">**suggestions_shown** – označava koliko je prijedloga pametnog sastavljanja prikazano korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5175">**suggestions_shown** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5176">**thread_id** – označava ID niti razgovora na koji se odgovara/prosljeđuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5176">**thread_id** - indicates thread ID of the conversation being replied/forwarded</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5177">session</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5177">session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5178">Omogućuje nam prepoznavanje i rješavanje situacija u kojima se vaša baterija previše troši te nam pomaže utvrditi što bi mogao biti uzrok.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5178">Allows us to detect and fix situations where we are using up too much of your device's battery and helps us identify what could be the cause.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5179">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5179">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5180">**battery_level** – govori nam razinu napunjenosti baterije uređaja kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati kada naša aplikacija ima negativan utjecaj na razinu napunjenosti baterije vašeg uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5180">**battery_level** - tells us the battery level on the device to help us detect when our app is causing a negative impact on your device's battery level</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5181">**has_hx** – govori nam da račun koristi naš novi servis sinkronizacije kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme uzrokovane našim servisom sinkronizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5181">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5182">**Session.Duration** – duljina sesije u sekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5182">**Session.Duration** - the length of the session in seconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5183">**Session.DurationBucket** – vremensko razdoblje dužine trajanja *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutnih verzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojaviti u starijim verzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5183">**Session.DurationBucket** - duration length time bucket *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5184">**Session.FirstLaunchTime** – prvo snimljeno vrijeme pokretanja aplikacije *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5184">**Session.FirstLaunchTime** - first recorded launch time of the app *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5185">**Session.State** – pokazatelj je li to početak ili kraj sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5185">**Session.State** - the indicator of whether this is the start or end of the session</span></span>

#### <a name="settingsaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5186">settings.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5186">settings.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5187">Ovaj događaj prikuplja informacije o konfiguraciji u postavkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5187">This event collects the configuration information in settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5188">Podaci nam omogućuju prepoznavanje situacija u kojima može doći do negativnog utjecaja na sposobnost korisnika za konfiguriranje postavki aplikacije, primjerice postavki obavijesti, primarnog računa pošte i konfiguriranja potpisa e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5188">The data allows us to detect situations where there is possible negative impact on the users’ ability configure app settings, such as notification settings, primary mail account, and configuring the email signature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5189">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5189">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5190">**account_order_changed** – da biste provjerili jeste li promijenili redoslijed računa kako biste osigurali da ova konfiguracija pravilno funkcionira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5190">**account_order_changed** - To check if you changed the order of your accounts to make sure this configuration works properly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5191">**action** – moguće radnje provedene u postavkama, primjerice brisanje računa kako bi nam pomogao dijagnosticirati probleme i osigurati da nema negativnog utjecaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5191">**action** - possible actions taken in settings, such as deleting an account to help us diagnose issues and ensure no negative impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5192">**auth_type** – vrsta provjere autentičnosti koju račun koristi kako bismo mogli razumjeti koji sloj sinkronizacije u pozadini koristimo kako bismo mogli dijagnosticirati probleme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5192">**auth_type** - The authentication type being used by the account, so we understand which backend sync layer we are using to help us diagnose issues</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5193">**changed_folder** – utvrđuje je li mapa promijenjena kako bi nam pomogao dijagnosticirati probleme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5193">**changed_folder** - Capturing whether a folder was changed to help us diagnose issues.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5194">**delete_scope** – tijekom brisanja računa, jeste li izbrisali račun s ovog uređaja ili sa svih uređaja s programom Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5194">**delete_scope** - During an account deletion, whether you deleted the account from this device or from all devices with Outlook.</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5195">**enabled_state** – utvrđuje jesu li vaše postavke za automatski odgovor, spremanje kontakata i blokiranje vanjskih slika ispravno konfigurirane</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5195">**enabled_state** - Whether your auto reply, save contacts, and block external images settings are configured correctly</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5196">**notification_action** – služi provjeri jeste li konfigurirali ikakve radnje obavijesti za razvrstavanje poruka e-pošte kako bismo mogli provjeriti funkcionira li ova postavka ispravno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5196">**notification_action** - To check if you have configured any notification actions for triaging emails to help us make sure this setting is working successfully</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5197">**notification_action_number** – da biste provjerili jesu li radnje obavijesti (radnja jedan ili radnja dva) ispravno konfigurirane</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5197">**notification_action_number** - To check if your notification actions (action one or action two) are configured correctly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5198">**server_type** – slično događaju auth_type, govori nam koju vrstu računa imate kako bi nam pomogao u boljem dijagnosticiranju problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5198">**server_type** - Similar to auth_type, it tells us which type of account you have to help us diagnose issues better.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5199">Primjeri: Office365, Gmail, Outlook</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5199">Examples: Office365, Gmail, Outlook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5200">**setting_properties** – prati odnos svojstava prema radnji postavljanja detaljno u nastavku:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5200">**setting_properties** - Tracks properties relation to setting action detailed below:</span></span> 
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5201">**alternate_app_icon_setting** – odabrana ikona zamjenske aplikacije (svijetla, tamna)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5201">**alternate_app_icon_setting** - the selected alternate app icon (light, dark)</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5202">**auth_type** – označava vrstu provjere autentičnosti u pozadini koja nam omogućava da saznamo postoji li problem s određenom vrstom računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5202">**auth_type** - indicates the back-end authentication type allowing us to know if there is an issue with a particular account type</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5203">**badge_count_state** – označava koju vrstu broja znački je korisnik tražio, odnosno nema znački, samo fokusirana poštanska pošta itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5203">**badge_count_state** - indicates what type of badge count the user has asked for that is, no badges, focused inbox only, etc.</span></span> 
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5204">**changed_folder** – utvrđuje je li ova radnja bila arhivirana, zakazana ili je postojala druga radnja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5204">**changed_folder** - determines whether this action was archived, scheduled, or another action.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5205">**delete_scope** – prati je li ova radnja bila povezana s brisanjem nekoga samo na ovom uređaju ili na svim uređajima, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5205">**delete_scope** - tracks whether this action was related to deleting someone just on this device or on all devices, if applicable.</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5206">**enabled_state** – utvrđuje je li stanje povezano s radnjom omogućeno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5206">**enabled_state** - whether state related to the action is enabled</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5207">**in_app_language** – odabrani jezik u aplikaciji, vrsta niza (zadano, en-US, fa, ru itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5207">**in_app_language** - the selected in-app language, string type (default, en-US, fa, ru etc.)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5208">**notification_action_setting** – označava pojedinosti o, ako je primjenjivo, postavkama radnje obavijesti povezanim s ovom radnjom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5208">**notification_action_setting** - indicates the details of, if applicable, notification action settings related to this action</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5209">**notification_action** – označava što je korisnik pokušavao učiniti, odnosno, označiti zastavicom, izbrisati, arhivirati, omogućuje nam utvrditi koju radnju poruke je korisnik želio izvršiti na obavijesti te je li radnja bila neuspješna ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5209">**notification_action** - indicates what the user was trying to do, that is, flag, delete, archive, it allows us to determine what message action the user wanted to perform on the notification and if the action failed or not.</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5210">**notification_action_number** – označava kojem je broju radnji (dvije od tri radnje su prilagodljive) dodijeljena radnja obavijesti, odnosno, radnja jedan, radnja dva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5210">**notification_action_number** - indicates which action number (two of three actions are customizable) was assigned a notification action, that is, action one, action two.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5211">To nam omogućuje utvrditi postoji li problem s određenom radnjom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5211">This allows us to determine if there is a problem with a particular action.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5212">**notification_state** – označava koju je vrstu značke korisnik zatražio, tj. nema značke, samo za fokusiranu ulaznu poštu itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5212">**notification_state** - indicates what type of badge count the user has asked for that is, no badges, focused inbox only, etc.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5213">**server_type** – označava vrstu poslužitelja u pozadini koja nam omogućava da saznamo postoji li problem s određenom vrstom poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5213">**server_type** - indicates the back-end server type allowing us to know if there is an issue with a particular server type</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5214">**source** – označava koji je izvor obavijesti, ako je primjenjivo, iz postavki ili postavke ne ometaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5214">**source** - indicates what is the source of notifications, if applicable, from settings or do not disturb setting</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5215">**swipe_setting** – označava pojedinosti o, ako je primjenjivo, postavkama prelaska prstom povezanim s ovom radnjom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5215">**swipe_setting** - indicates the details of, if applicable, swipe settings related to this action</span></span>
     - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5216">**swipe_action** – označava što je korisnik pokušavao učiniti, odnosno, označiti zastavicom, izbrisati, arhivirati, omogućuje nam utvrditi koju je radnju korisnik želio provesti te je li radnja bila neuspješna ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5216">**swipe_action** - indicates what the user was trying to do, that is, flag, delete, archive, it allows us to determine what action the user wanted and if the action failed or not.</span></span> 
     - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5217">**swipe_direction** – označava za koji je smjer korisnik postavio prelazak prstom, tj. slijeva udesno ili zdesna ulijevo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5217">**swipe_direction** - indicates which way the user set up the swipe to be, that is, left to right or right to left.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5218">To nam omogućuje utvrditi postoji li problem s određenim smjerom prelaska prstom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5218">This allows us to determine if there is a problem with a particular swipe direction.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5219">**temperature_unit_setting** – odabrana jedinica temperature koja će se upotrebljavati za vrijeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5219">**temperature_unit_setting** -  the selected temperature unit to be used for weather</span></span> 
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5220">**theme_color_setting** – prilagođena tematska boja aplikacije koju je odabrao korisnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5220">**theme_color_setting** - the custom app theme color selected by the user</span></span> 
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5221">**ui_mode_setting** – odabrani način korisničkog sučelja (tamno, svijetlo, zadane postavke sustava, niska razina baterije, itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5221">**ui_mode_setting** - the selected UI mode (dark, light, system default, low battery etc.)</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5222">**signature_setting** – označava je li postavka bila primijenjena na sve račune ili na pojedini račun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5222">**signature_setting** - indicates if the setting was applied to all account or an individual account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5223">**state_changed_to** – služi provjeri je li vaša postavka uključivanja/isključivanja fokusirane ulazne pošte pravilno konfigurirana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5223">**state_changed_to** - To check if your focused inbox On/Off setting is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5224">**swipe_action** – služi provjeri jeste li konfigurirali ikakve radnje prelaska prstom za razvrstavanje poruka e-pošte kako bismo mogli provjeriti funkcionira li ova postavka ispravno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5224">**swipe_action** - To check if you have configured any swipe actions for triaging emails to help us make sure this setting is working successfully</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5225">**swipe_direction** – služi provjeri jesu li vaši smjerovi prelaska prstom (ulijevo ili udesno) ispravno konfigurirani</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5225">**swipe_direction** - To check if your swipe directions (left or right) are configured correctly</span></span>


#### <a name="sidebaraction"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5226">sidebar.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5226">sidebar.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5227">Omogućuje nam prepoznavanje situacija u kojima može doći do negativnog utjecaja na vašu mogućnost konfiguriranja postavki aplikacije, primjerice vaših postavki obavijesti, vašeg primarnog računa pošte i konfiguriranja vašeg potpisa e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5227">Allows us to detect situations where there is possible negative impact on your ability configure your app settings, such as your notification settings, your primary mail account, and configuring your mail signature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5228">Polja podataka koja su uobičajena za Outlook Mobile za ovaj događaj na operacijskim sustavima iOS i Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5228">Data fields that are common for Outlook Mobile for this event on iOS and Android:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5229">**Account** – prati račun i njegove podatke povezane s događajem, vrijednosti praćene u okviru ovih podataka nalaze se u polju zajedničke dokumentacije *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5229">**Account** - tracks the account and its data associated with the event, values tracked in this data are in the common om field documentation *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5230">**action** – prati vrstu provedene radnje bočne trake, tj. odbačeno, odabir gumba za pomoć, bočna traka pošte itd.,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5230">**action** - tracks the type of side bar action occurred, that is, dismissed, help button selected, mail side bar, etc.,</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5231">**from_favorites** – prati potječe li radnja iz stavke ili iz favorita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5231">**from_favorites** - tracks if the action is coming from an item in favorites</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5232">**mail_folder_type** – vrsta mape koja je odabrana tijekom radnje bočne trake, ako postoji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5232">**mail_folder_type** - what type of folder was selected during the side bar action, if any.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5233">**sidebar_type** – prati vrstu bočne trake povezane s ovim događajem, odnosno, pošta ili kalendar, kako bi nam pomogao osigurati da navigacija iz postavke favorita pravilno funkcionira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5233">**sidebar_type** - tracks the type of side bar associated with this event, that is, mail or calendar to help us ensure the navigation from the favorites setting works properly</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5234">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5234">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5235">**account_type** – označava koju vrstu provjere autentičnosti račun ima, tj. Gmail, Outlook itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5235">**account_type** - indicates what authentication type the account is that is, Gmail, outlook, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5236">**account_has_groups** – pomaže nam provjeriti ima li račun grupe te jesu li one ispravno konfigurirane</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5236">**account_has_groups** - Helps us make sure if the account has groups, they are configured correctly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5237">**calendar_accounts_count** – broj računa kalendara koje imate kako bismo mogli osigurati da su računi kalendara ispravno konfigurirani</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5237">**calendar_accounts_count** - Number of calendar accounts you have to help us make sure your calendar accounts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5238">**calendar_apps_count** – broj aplikacija kalendara koje imate kako bismo mogli osigurati da su vaše aplikacije zanimljivih kalendara ispravno konfigurirani</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5238">**calendar_apps_count** - Number of calendar apps you have to help us make sure your interesting calendar apps are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5239">**calendar_type** – vrsta kalendara koji imate (primarni kalendar, grupni kalendar itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5239">**calendar_type** - The type of calendar you have (Primary calendar, Group calendar, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5240">**has_favorite_folders** – pomaže nam osigurati pravilan način konfiguriranja omiljenih mapa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5240">**has_favorite_folders** - Helps us make sure favorite folders are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5241">**has_favorite_people** – pomaže nam osigurati pravilan način konfiguriranja omiljenih osoba/kontakata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5241">**has_favorite_people** - Helps us make sure favorite people/contacts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5242">**has_group_calendar** – pomaže nam osigurati pravilan način konfiguriranja grupnih kalendara ako ih imate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5242">**has_group_calendar** - Helps us make sure if you have group calendars, they are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5243">**has_group_calendar_account** – pomaže nam osigurati pravilan način konfiguriranja grupnih kalendara ako ih imate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5243">**has_group_calendar_account** - Helps us make sure if you have group calendars, they are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5244">**has_group_toggled** – pomaže nam osigurati pravilan način konfiguriranja postavki uključenih/isključenih grupnih kalendara</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5244">**has_group_toggled** - Helps us make sure if you have toggled group calendars, this setting is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5245">**interesting_calendars_accounts_count** – broj računa zanimljivih kalendara koje imate kako bismo mogli osigurati da su računi zanimljivih kalendara ispravno konfigurirani</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5245">**interesting_calendars_accounts_count** - Number of interesting calendar accounts you have to help us make sure your interesting calendar accounts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5246">**mail_accounts_count** – ukupan broj računa pošte na bočnoj traci kako bismo osigurali da je to ispravno konfigurirano</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5246">**mail_accounts_count** - The total number of mail accounts in the sidebar to make sure this is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5247">**mail_folder_type** – vrsta mape koju je korisnik dodirnuo kako bismo osigurali da je ispravno konfigurirana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5247">**mail_folder_type** - The type of folder the user tapped on to make sure it's configured correctly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5248">To može uključivati Izbrisanu mapu, Neželjenu poštu ili vašu mapu Poslana pošta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5248">This could include Deleted folder, Spam, or your Sent folder.</span></span>
