#### <a name="storeop"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5251">StoreOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5251">StoreOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5252">Prikuplja se kada korisnik pokuša otvoriti dokument zaštićen IRM-om ili primijeniti zaštite IRM-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5252">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5253">Sadrži informacije potrebne za pravilno istraživanje i dijagnosticiranje problema do kojih dolazi kada se provodi operacija pohranjivanja licence usluge upravljanja pravima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5253">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when Rights Management Service license store operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5254">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5254">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5255">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hijerarhija klijenata koja označava da aplikacija radi u proizvodnom okruženju ili okruženju za razvojne inženjere</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5255">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy, which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5256">**AppInfo.Name** – naziv aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5256">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5257">**AppInfo.Version** – verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5257">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5258">**iKey** – identifikacijski broj poslužitelja pružatelja usluge zapisivanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5258">**iKey** - Logging service server ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5259">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** – identifikacijski broj scenarija koji pruža aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5259">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario ID provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5260">**RMS.ContentId** – identifikacijski broj sadržaja u licenci krajnjeg korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5260">**RMS.ContentId** - Content ID in End User License</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5261">**RMS.Duration** – ukupno vrijeme potrebno za dovršavanje poziva API-ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5261">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5262">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – ukupno vrijeme umanjeno za potrošene vanjske operacije poput latencije mreže.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5262">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5263">**RMS.ErrorCode** – kod pogreške koji, ako postoji, vraća operacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5263">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5264">**RMS.HttpCall** – označava postoji li operacija HTTP-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5264">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5265">**RMS.LicenseFormat** – format licence: Xrml ili Json</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5265">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5266">**RMS.OperationName** – naziv operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5266">**RMS.OperationName** - Operation name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5267">**RMS.Result** – uspjeh ili neuspjeh operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5267">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5268">**RMS.ScenarioId** – identifikacijski broj scenarija koji definira klijent usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5268">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario ID defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5269">**RMS.SDKVersion** – verzija klijenta usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5269">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5270">**RMS.ServerType** – vrsta poslužitelja usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5270">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5271">**RMS.StatusCode** – kod statusa rezultata operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5271">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the operation result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5272">**RMS.Url** – URL poslužitelja usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5272">**RMS.Url** - The URL of Rights Management Service Server</span></span>

#### <a name="watchappv2"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5273">watchAppV2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5273">watchAppV2</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5274">Ovaj nam događa omogućuje otkrivanje i rješavanje mogućih problema s mogućnostima na uređaju Apple Watch kao što su primanje obavijesti i odgovaranje na poruke e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5274">This event allows us to detect and fix possible issues with capabilities on your Apple Watch such as receiving notifications and responding to emails.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5275">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5275">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5276">**app_action** – govori nam vrste radnji koje je korisnik proveo na uređaju Apple Watch, primjerice „archive_message”, kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenom radnjom, primjerice nemogućnost uspješnog arhiviranja poruka na uređaju Apple Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5276">**app_action** - Tells us the types of action the user took on the Apple watch, such as "archive_message" to help us detect issues related to a specific action such as being unable to successfully archive messages on the Apple Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5277">**is_watch_app_installed** – govori nam je li korisnik instalirao našu aplikaciju Apple Watch na svom uređaju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5277">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user has installed our Apple Watch app on their device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5278">**is_complication_enabled** – govori nam je li korisnik dodao program Outlook na ekran uređaja Apple Watch kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme u vezi s ekranima uređaja Apple Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5278">**is_complication_enabled** - Tells us if the user has added Outlook to their Apple Watch screen to help us detect issues related to Apple Watch screens</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5279">**watch_os** – govori nam verziju operacijskog sustava uređaja Apple Watch koja je instalirana kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim verzijama operacijskog sustava uređaja Apple Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5279">**watch_os** - Tells us the OS version of the Apple Watch they have installed to help us detect issues related to specific OS versions of the Apple Watch</span></span>


### <a name="application-status-and-boot-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5280">*Podvrsta stanja i pokretanja aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5280">*Application status and boot subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5281">Utvrđivanje je li došlo do određenih događaja povezanih sa značajkama, poput pokretanja ili zaustavljanja, te je li značajka pokrenuta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5281">Determination if specific feature events have occurred, such as start or stop, and if feature is running.</span></span>

#### <a name="appstartup"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5282">app.startup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5282">app.startup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5283">Ovaj nam događaj omogućava prepoznavanje i popravljanje problema kada se Outlook pokreće sporo ili nepotpuno, zbog čega korisnici imaju probleme s korištenjem naše aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5283">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook is starting slowly or incompletely, making it difficult for users to use our app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5284">To uključuje informacije o konkretnim značajkama koje su bile omogućene i koliko su dugo dijelovi pokretanja trajali.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5284">This includes information on the specific features that were enabled and how long parts of the startup took.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5285">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5285">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5286">**attach_base_context_millis** – vrijeme između početka osnovnog konteksta i stavke onCreate()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5286">**attach_base_context_millis** - time between the base Context starting and onCreate() starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5287">**device_ram_in_mb** – količina RAM-a dostupna na uređaju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5287">**device_ram_in_mb** - the RAM available on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5288">**has_company_portal** – je li instalirana aplikacija portala tvrtke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5288">**has_company_portal** - whether the company portal app is installed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5289">**hx_okhttp_mode** – koristi li nova komponenta servisa sinkronizacije poruka e-pošte OKHttp za slanje i primanje mrežnih zahtjeva koji se temelje na HTTP-u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5289">**hx_okhttp_mode** - whether the new email syncing service component is using OKHttp for sending and receiving HTTP-based network requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5290">**initial_activity_name** – aktivnost sustava Android koja je pokrenula aplikaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5290">**initial_activity_name** - the Android Activity that launched the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5291">**manufacturer** – proizvođač uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5291">**manufacturer** - the device manufacturer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5292">**model** – model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5292">**model** - the device model</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5293">**on_create_millis** – vrijeme koje je proteklo za metodu onCreate()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5293">**on_create_millis** - time taken in the onCreate() method</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5294">**on_resume_millis** – vrijeme koje je proteklo za metodu onResume()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5294">**on_resume_millis** - time taken in the onResume() method</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5295">**time_until_attach** – vrijeme koje je proteklo između učitavanja razreda i pokretanja osnovnog konteksta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5295">**time_until_attach** - time between the class loading and the base Context starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5296">**total_millis** – ukupno vrijeme od početka učitavanja razreda do dovršavanja nastavka aktivnosti sustava Android</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5296">**total_millis** - total time from class loading start to Android Activity resume completion</span></span>

#### <a name="boottime"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5297">boot.time</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5297">boot.time</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5298">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje otkrivanje kada su nastupile kritične pogreške aplikacije koje bi uzrokovale rušenje vaše aplikacije ili iskustvo ozbiljnih problema, primjerice prikaz praznih redaka u vašoj ulaznoj pošti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5298">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred that would cause your app to crash or experience serious issues like causing you to see empty rows in your inbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5299">Ovaj događaj prikuplja informacije koje nam omogućuju kategorizaciju i razvrstavanje problema kako bismo mogli odrediti prioritet utjecaja problema na korisnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5299">This event collects information that allows us to categorize and classify issues to help prioritize the impact of issues on customers.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5300">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5300">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5301">**black_list_reason** – govori nam postoji li razlog zašto bismo trebali zanemariti ove podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5301">**black_list_reason** - Tells us if there is a reason why we should disregard this data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5302">Pojedini primjeri uključuju pokretanje zbog udaljene obavijesti i pokretanje zbog pozadinskog dohvaćanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5302">Some examples include launching due to a remote notification and launching due to a background fetch.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5303">**step_premain** – govori nam koliko je vremena bilo potrebno da Outlook nakon korisnikovog dodirivanja ikone prijeđe na step0_main, "glavni" korak definiran u ovom dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5303">**step_premain** – Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the user tapping the icon to step0_main the “main” step defined in this document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5304">**step0_main** – govori nam koliko je vremena bilo potrebno da Outlook dospije do koraka „main”, što je korak koji je odredila tvrtka Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5304">**step0_main** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to get to the "main" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5305">**step1_appWillFinishLaunching** – govori nam koliko je vremena bilo potrebno da Outlook dospije od koraka „main” do koraka „appWillFinishLaunching”, što je korak koji je odredila tvrtka Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5305">**step1_appWillFinishLaunching** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "main" step to the "appWillFinishLaunching" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5306">**step2_appDidFinishLaunching** – govori nam koliko je vremena bilo potrebno da Outlook dospije od koraka „appWillFinishLaunching” do koraka „appDidFinishLaunching”, što je korak koji je odredila tvrtka Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5306">**step2_appDidFinishLaunching** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "appWillFinishLaunching" step to the "appDidFinishLaunching" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5307">**step3_engineStarted** – govori nam koliko je vremena potrebno da Outlook dospije od koraka „appDidFinishLaunching” do pokretanja modula aplikacije, koji upravlja spremanjem i sinkronizacijom podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5307">**step3_engineStarted** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "appDidFinishLaunching" step to starting the engine of the app, which handles storing and syncing data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5308">**step4_runLoopFirstIdle** – govori nam koliko je vremena bilo potrebno da Outlook dospije od koraka „engineStarted” do faze bez potrebe za dovršavanjem dodatnih zadataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5308">**step4_runLoopFirstIdle** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "engineStarted" step to having no additional work to complete.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5309">**total_time** – govori nam koliko je vremena bilo potrebno da Outlook dovrši proces pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5309">**total_time** - Tells us the total amount of time it has taken for Outlook to complete the boot process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5395">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hijerarhija klijenata koja označava da aplikacija radi u proizvodnom okruženju ili okruženju za razvojne inženjere</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5395">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy, which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5396">**AppInfo.Name** – naziv aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5396">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5397">**AppInfo.Version** – verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5397">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5398">**iKey** – identifikacijski broj poslužitelja pružatelja usluge zapisivanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5398">**iKey** - Logging service server ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5399">**RMS.Duration** – ukupno vrijeme potrebno za dovršavanje poziva API-ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5399">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5400">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – ukupno vrijeme umanjeno za potrošene vanjske operacije poput latencije mreže.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5400">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5401">**RMS.ErrorCode** – kod pogreške koji, ako postoji, vraća poziv API-ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5401">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5402">**RMS.HttpCall** – označava postoji li operacija HTTP-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5402">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5403">**RMS.Result** – uspjeh ili neuspjeh poziva API-ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5403">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5404">**RMS.ScenarioId** – identifikacijski broj scenarija definiran API-jem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5404">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario ID defined by the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5405">**RMS.SDKVersion** – verzija klijenta usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5405">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5406">**RMS.StatusCode** – kod statusa vraćenog rezultata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5406">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the returned result</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidaccountstorageinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5407">Office.Android.AccountStorageInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5407">Office.Android.AccountStorageInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5408">Tim se događajem određuje broj računa MSA i ADAL u registru i zajedničkim postavkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5408">This event determines the number of MSA and ADAL accounts in the registry and shared preferences.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5409">Omogućuje analizu nedosljednosti među spremištima podataka i omogućuje stabiliziranje performansi aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5409">It enables the analysis of inconsistencies between data stores and helps us to stabilize app performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5410">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5410">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5411">**RegistryADALCount** – upućuje na broj računa ADAL u registru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5411">**RegistryADALCount**- Indicates number of ADAL accounts in registry.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5412">**RegistryLiveIdCount** – upućuje na broj računa MSA u registru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5412">**RegistryLiveIdCount**- Indicates number of MSA accounts in registry.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5413">**SharedPrefADALCount** – upućuje na broj računa ADAL u zajedničkim postavkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5413">**SharedPrefADALCount**- Indicates number of ADAL accounts in shared preferences.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5414">**SharedPrefLiveIdCount** – upućuje na broj računa MSA u zajedničkim postavkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5414">**SharedPrefLiveIdCount**- Indicates number of MSA accounts in shared preferences.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidandroidoffice16bootlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5415">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5415">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5416">Ključno je za snimanje metrike performansi aplikacije s obzirom na vrijeme odaziva aplikacije prilikom pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5416">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5417">Microsoft to upotrebljava za prikupljanje vremena potrebnog za reagiranje aplikacije i otkrivanje scenarija koji mogu utjecati na vrijeme pokretanja u aplikacijama Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5417">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5418">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5418">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5419">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** – vrijeme pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5419">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** - App launch responsive time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5420">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li aplikacija obustavljena tijekom pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5420">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5421">**CollectionTime** – vrijeme događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5421">**CollectionTime** - Time of event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5422">**FileActivationAttempted** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li pokušana aktivacije datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5422">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if file activation as attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5423">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** – vrijeme neaktivnosti niti aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5423">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** - App thread idle time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5424">**IsThisFirstLaunch** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li ovo prvo pokretanje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5424">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is first time app launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5425">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li blokiralo korisničko sučelje tijekom pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5425">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if there was a blocking UI during boot</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityofficejsappactivated"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5426">Office.Extensibility.OfficeJS.Appactivated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5426">Office.Extensibility.OfficeJS.Appactivated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5429">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5429">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5430">**Data\_AirspaceInitTime:integer–** trajanje inicijalizacije komponente Airspace za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5430">**Data\_AirspaceInitTime:integer-** time taken to initialize Airspace Office component</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5431">**Data\_AllShapes:integer –** broj oblika u dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5431">**Data\_AllShapes:integer -** number of shapes in the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5432">**Data\_APIInitTime:integer –** trajanje inicijalizacije API modula za Visio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5432">**Data\_APIInitTime:integer -** time taken to initialize Visio API module</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5433">**Data\_AppSizeHeight –** visina prozora dodatka **-**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5433">**Data\_AppSizeHeight –** Add **-** in window size's height</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5434">**Data\_AppSizeWidth –** širina prozora dodatka **-**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5434">**Data\_AppSizeWidth –** Add **-** in window size's width</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5435">**Data\_AppURL –** URL dodatka; bilježi puni URL za dodatke iz trgovine i domenu URL-a za dodatke koji nisu iz trgovine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5435">**Data\_AppURL -** URL of the Add-in; Logs full URL for Store Add-ins and URL domain for non-store Add-ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5436">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5436">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5437">**Data\_AuthorsCount:integer –** broj autora koji su uređivali dokument u toj sesiji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5437">**Data\_AuthorsCount:integer -** number of authors who edited the document in this session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5438">**Data\_BackgroundPages:integer –** broj pozadinskih stranica u dijagramu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5438">**Data\_BackgroundPages:integer -** number of background pages in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5439">**Data\_BootTime:integer –** trajanje pokretanja programa Visio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5439">**Data\_BootTime:integer -** The amount of time it took to boot Visio</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5440">**Data\_Browser –** niz preglednika s informacijama o pregledniku kao što su vrsta i verzija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5440">**Data\_Browser -** Browser string with information about the browser such as type, version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5441">**Data\_ChildWindowMixedModeTime:integer –** trajanje omogućavanja mješovitog načina rada u programu Visio (podređeni prozor može imati drukčije svojstvo DpiAwareness od nadređenog)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5441">**Data\_ChildWindowMixedModeTime:integer -** time taken to enable mixed mode in Visio (Child window can have different DpiAwareness from parent window)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5442">**Data\_CommentsCount:integer –** broj komentara u dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5442">**Data\_CommentsCount:integer -** number of comments in document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5443">**Data\_ConnectionCount:integer –** broj podatkovnih veza u dijagramu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5443">**Data\_ConnectionCount:integer -** number of data connections in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5444">**Data\_ContentMgrInitTim:integer –** trajanje inicijalizacije upravitelja sadržaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5444">**Data\_ContentMgrInitTim:integer -** time taken to initialize content manager</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5445">**Data\_CreateMainFrameTime:integer –** vrijeme stvaranja glavnog okvira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5445">**Data\_CreateMainFrameTime:integer -** Create mainframe time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5446">**Data\_CreatePaletteTime:integer –** trajanje stvaranja globalne palete boja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5446">**Data\_CreatePaletteTime:integer -** Time taken to create the global color palette</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5447">**Data\_DispFormatCount:integer –** broj podatkovnih grafika u dijagramu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5447">**Data\_DispFormatCount:integer -** number of data graphics in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5448">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string –** nastavak dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5448">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5449">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string –** mjesto pohrane dokumenta (SharePoint.com, live.net), dostupno samo za domene sustava Office 365</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5449">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5450">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string –** raspršivanje mjesta pohrane dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5450">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5451">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool–** : je li dokument otvoren inkrementalno (nova značajka koja otvara dokument bez potrebe za preuzimanjem cijelog dokumenta)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5451">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool-** : Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5452">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool –** otvara li se dokument iz lokalne predmemorije?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5452">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** Is document being opened from local cache?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5453">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool–** istinito kad je riječ o poslužiteljskom dokumentu koji postoji lokalno te se sinkronizira s poslužiteljem (na primjer, putem servisa OneDrive ili ODB klijentskih aplikacija)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5453">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool-** true when this is a server document that exists locally, and is synchronized with the server (for example, through OneDrive or ODB client apps)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5454">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long–** : unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti mjesta na kojima se dokument pohranjuje (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, mreža itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5454">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long-** : Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5455">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti detaljnijih lokacija (mapa Temp, mapa preuzimanja, dokumenti servisa One Drive, slike servisa One Drive)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5455">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5456">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string –** raspršivanje identifikatora resursa za dokumente pohranjene u oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5456">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource Identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5457">**Data_Doc_RtcType –** označava kako je kanal u stvarnom vremenu (RTC) postavljen za trenutnu datoteku (onemogućen, nepodržan, na zahtjev, uvijek uključen itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5457">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5458">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string –** nepromjenjivi identifikator za dokumente pohranjene u oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5458">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string -** immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5459">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long –** generirani GUID koji identificira instancu dokumenta u sklopu iste sesije procesa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5459">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5460">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long –** veličina dokumenta u bajtovima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5460">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5461">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long –** dugačka bit-maska koja pokazuje posebne znakove u URL-u ili putu dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5461">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** long Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5462">**Data\_Doc\_SyncBackedType –** pokazatelj vrste dokumenta (lokalni ili na servisu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5462">**Data\_Doc\_SyncBackedType -** Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5463">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string –** raspršivanje punog URL-a dokumenata pohranjenih u oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5463">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string -** hash of full URL of documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5464">**Data\_DpiAwarenessTime:integer –** trajanje omogućivanja svjesnosti o razlučivosti po monitoru</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5464">**Data\_DpiAwarenessTime:integer -** Time taken to enable Per Monitor DPI Awareness</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5465">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds:double–** trajanje spremanja u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5465">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds:double-** Duration to complete save as in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5466">**Data\_ErrorCode:int –** 0 za uspjelo, a cijeli broj za neuspjelo spremanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5466">**Data\_ErrorCode:int -**  0 for success, integer for failure in save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5467">**Data\_FailureReason:integer –** razlog neuspjeha za asinkrono spremanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5467">**Data\_FailureReason:integer -** failure reason for asynchronous save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5468">**Data\_FileExtension –** datotečni nastavak otvorenog dijagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5468">**Data\_FileExtension -** File extension of diagram opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5469">**Data\_FileHasDGMaster:bool –** istinito kada datoteka sadrži podatkovne grafike</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5469">**Data\_FileHasDGMaster:bool -** true when file has Data Graphics</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5549">**Data\_SDX\_OfficeJsVersion –** to je verzija sustava Office.js koja će se preusmjeriti na verziju specifičnu za određenu platformu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5549">**Data\_SDX\_OfficeJsVersion -** This is the version of Office.js that will redirect to the platform-specific version.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5550">**Data\_SDX\_Version –** verzija dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5550">**Data\_SDX\_Version -** Version of the Add-in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5551">**Data\_ShellCmdLineTime:integer –** trajanje raščlambe i izvođenja naredbi ljuske u naredbenom retku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5551">**Data\_ShellCmdLineTime:integer -** time taken to Parse and execute any shell commands on the command line</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5552">**Data\_Size:long** – veličina datoteke u bajtovima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5552">**Data\_Size:long** - File size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5553">**Data\_StartEndTransactionTime:integer –** trajanje inicijalizacije komponenti programa Visio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5553">**Data\_StartEndTransactionTime:integer -** time taken to initialize Visio components</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5554">**Data\_STNInitTime:integer –** trajanje inicijalizacije konfiguracije prozora šablone</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5554">**Data\_STNInitTime:integer -** time taken to initialize stencil window configuration</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5555">**Data\_Tag:string –** jedinstveni identifikator za prepoznavanje događaja „Spremi kao”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5555">**Data\_Tag:string -** unique identifier to identify Save As event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5556">**Data\_ThemeCount:integer –** broj tema u dijagramu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5556">**Data\_ThemeCount:integer -** number of themes in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5557">**Data\_TimeStamp –** vremenska oznaka u trenutku zatvaranja dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5557">**Data\_TimeStamp -** Time stamp when document was closed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5558">**Data\_UIInitTime:integer –** trajanje inicijalizacije korisničkog sučelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5558">**Data\_UIInitTime:integer -** UI initialization time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5559">**Data\_WasSuccessful:bool –** istinito ako je spremanje bilo uspješno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5559">**Data\_WasSuccessful:bool -** true if save as was successful</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5560">**Data\_WinLaunchTime:integer –** trajanje pokretanja početnog okna programa Visio itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5560">**Data\_WinLaunchTime:integer -** time taken to launch the Visio startup pane, etc.)</span></span>

  
#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5561">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5561">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5562">Prikuplja se kada je dodatku sustava Office potrebno neočekivano puno vremena za pokretanje (>5 sek).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5562">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5563">Koristi se za otkrivanje i rješavanje problema u vezi s pokretanjem dodataka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5563">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5564">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5564">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5565">**AppId** – ID aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5565">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5566">**AppInfo** – podaci koji se odnose na vrstu dodatka (okno zadatka ili UILess ili u sadržaju itd.) i vrstu pružatelja (omen, SharePoint, filesystem itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5566">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5567">**AppInstanceId** – ID instance aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5567">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5568">**AssetId** – ID sadržaja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5568">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5569">**IsPreload** – upućuje na to je li dodatak unaprijed učitan u pozadini radi poboljšanja performansi aktivacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5569">**IsPreload** – indicates if the add-in is being preloaded in background for improving activation performance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5570">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – brojač aktiviranih dodataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5570">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5571">**RemoterType** – određuje vrstu daljinskog elementa (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF itd.) koji se koristi za aktivaciju dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5571">**RemoterType** - specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5572">**StoreType** – porijeklo aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5572">**StoreType** - origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5573">**TimeForAuth** – vrijeme utrošeno na autorizaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5573">**TimeForAuth** - time spent on auth</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5574">**TimeForSandbox** – vrijeme utrošeno na testno okruženje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5574">**TimeForSandbox** - time spent on the sandbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5575">**TimeForServerCall** – vrijeme utrošeno na poziv poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5575">**TimeForServerCall** - time spent on the server call</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5576">**TotalTime** – ukupno utrošeno vrijeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5576">**TotalTime** - total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5577">**UsesSharedRuntime** – upućuje na to da koristi li aplikacija sharedRuntime ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5577">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates if the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officelenslenssdklaunchlens"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5578">Office.Lens.LensSdk.LaunchLens</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5578">Office.Lens.LensSdk.LaunchLens</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5579">Kada korisnik pokrene Lens da bi snimio/la ili uvezao/la slike u bilo kojoj aplikaciji, pokrenut će se Lens SDK, a taj će se događaj prikupiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5579">When user launches Lens to capture or import images in any app, Lens SDK is launched, and this event is collected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5580">Podaci o pokretanju pomažu nam utvrditi broj korisnika / uređaja koji pokreću aplikaciju i dalje razumjeti upotrebu značajki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5580">Launch data helps us determine the number of users/devices launching the app and further understand feature usage.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5581">Pomaže nam u praćenju broja korisnika koji koriste proizvod, kao i prepoznavanju promjena u trendovima, pomaže u traženju i ispravljanju problema u proizvodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5581">It helps us track the volume of users using the product, as well as identifying changes in trends, help look for and rectify issues in the product.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5582">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5582">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5583">**Data_isResumeSession** – Je li aplikacija pokrenuta u nastavku ili je korisnik započeo novi postupak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5583">**Data_isResumeSession** - Whether the app was launched in resume or user did a fresh start.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5584">(Booleova polja)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5584">(Boolean field)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5585">**Data_launchPerf** – Cijeli broj koji označava vrijeme koje je potrebno za pokretanje aplikacije (na sustavu Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5585">**Data_launchPerf** - Integer indicating time taken to launch the app (on Android)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5586">**Data_LaunchWorkFlowItem** – polje određuje je li aplikacija pokrenuta sa zaslona fotoaparata ili na zaslonu uređivanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5586">**Data_LaunchWorkFlowItem** - Field specifies if the app is launched from camera screen or edit screen.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5587">**Data_mediaCompressionFactor** – faktor pomoću kojeg aplikacija komprimira slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5587">**Data_mediaCompressionFactor** - The factor by which images are compressed by app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5588">**Data_RecoveryMode** -Boolean polje koje upućuje na to je li ta sesija vraćena kada je aplikacija ubijena (na sustavu Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5588">**Data_RecoveryMode** - Boolean field indicating if this session was recovered after app was killed (on Android)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5589">**IsDexModeEnabled** -Booleov izraz označava ako uređaj podržava Samsung Dex značajke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5589">**IsDexModeEnabled** - Boolean indicating if device supports Samsung Dex features.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5590">**IsEmbeddedLaunch** -Boolean polje koje upućuje na to je li korisnik pokrenuo kontrolu u načinu slike u slici.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5590">**IsEmbeddedLaunch** - Boolean field indicating if user launched the control in picture-in-picture mode.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5591">**IsInterimCropEnabled** –Boolean polje koje upućuje na to je li korisnik odabrao ručno obrezivanje svake slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5591">**IsInterimCropEnabled** - Boolean field indicating if user has chosen to manually crop each image.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5592">**IsMultiWindowEnabled** – Boolean polje koje pokazuje da li je moguće pokrenuti aplikaciju na podijeljenom zaslonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5592">**IsMultiWindowEnabled** - Boolean field indicating if it's possible to run app in split screen.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5593">**LaunchPerf** – Cijeli broj koji označava vrijeme koje je potrebno za pokretanje aplikacije (na sustavu iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5593">**LaunchPerf** - Integer indicating time taken to launch the app (on iOS)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5594">**Ponovno ponavljanje** -Boolean polje koje upućuje na to je li ta sesija vraćena nakon ubojstva aplikacije (na sustavu iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5594">**RecoveryMode** - Boolean field indicating if this session was recovered after app was killed (on iOS)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5595">**SDKMode** – Način na koji su snimljene slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5595">**SDKMode** - The mode in which images were captured.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeofficemobileappactivationlaunch"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5596">Office.OfficeMobile.AppActivation.Launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5596">Office.OfficeMobile.AppActivation.Launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5597">Ovaj događaj identificira prvu i daljnje aktivacije putem vanjskih okidača koji aktiviraju aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5597">This event identifies first time and subsequent activations through external triggers that activate the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5598">Aktivacija aplikacije učitava određene ovisnosti koje su odgovorne za rad aplikacije bez poteškoća i taj će događaj zabilježiti jesu li se uspješno učitale.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5598">App activation loads certain dependencies that are responsible for making the app run smoothly and this event will record if it loaded successfully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5599">Također će zabilježiti izvor aktivacije i namjeru aplikacije koja je bila odgovorna za aktivaciju aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5599">It will also record the source of activation and app intent that was responsible for activating the app</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5600">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5600">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5601">**ActionName** – mapiranje vrijednosti cijelog broja na ime radnje/značajke koja je pozvana iz točke aktivacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5601">**ActionName** - Integer value mapping to the name of the action/feature which is invoked from the activation point.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5602">**ActivationType** – mapiranje vrijednosti cijelog broja na izvor aktivacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5602">**ActivationType** - Integer value mapping to the source of activation</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5603">**IsActionTriggered** – Booleova vrijednost koja određuje je li radnja pokrenuta nakon uspješne aktivacija aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5603">**IsActionTriggered** - Boolean value determining whether the action got triggered after the successful activation of the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5604">**IsFirstRun** – Booleova vrijednost koja određuje radi li se o prvom ili daljnjem izvršavanju aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5604">**IsFirstRun** - Boolean value determining whether it was the first run of the app or a subsequent run.</span></span>
 

#### <a name="officeofficemobilefrefirstrunsetup"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5605">Office.OfficeMobile.FRE.FirstRunSetup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5605">Office.OfficeMobile.FRE.FirstRunSetup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5606">Prvo pokretanje aplikacije nakon instalacije aktivirat će taj događaj otkucaja srca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5606">The first run of the app after installation will trigger this heartbeat event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5607">To će pomoći pri prepoznavanju instalacija i automatskih nadogradnji sa starijih verzija aplikacije te nam omogućiti prepoznavanje pogrešaka u automatskim nadogradnjama, uključujući neuspjela učitavanja biblioteka i preuzimanja paketa proširenja ili jezičnih paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5607">It will help identify installs and auto upgrades from older versions of the app and enable us to identify errors in auto-upgrades, including library loads and expansion/language package download failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5608">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5608">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5609">**IsFlightAssigned** – Booleova vrijednost koja određuje je li korisnik dio bilo koje unaprijed dodijeljene grupe za testne verzije koja može uzrokovati izlaganje određenim doživljajima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5609">**IsFlightAssigned** - Boolean value determining if the user was part of any preassigned flight group which can trigger exposure to certain experiences.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5610">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** – cijeli broj koji navodi rezultantno stanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5610">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** - integer mentioning the result state</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidappappbootcomplete-officeandroidearlytelemetryappbootcomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5611">Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5611">Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5612">*[Ovaj je događaj prethodno imenovan OneNote.AppLaunch.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5612">*[This event was previously named OneNote.App.AppBootComplete.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5613">Ključni signal korišten za osiguravanje da novi privatni korisnici (Microsoftov račun) uspješno mogu prvi put koristiti aplikaciju OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5613">The critical signal used to ensure new consumer users (Microsoft Account) can successfully launch and use OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5614">To se koristi za osiguravanje prepoznavanja ključne regresije za aplikaciju OneNote i stanje usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5614">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5615">Ako korisnici ne mogu prvi put pokrenuti aplikaciju, time bi se izazvao incident visoke ozbiljnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5615">If users can't launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5616">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5616">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5617">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** – vrijeme potrebno za dovršetak stvaranja aktivnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5617">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** - Time taken to complete Activity creation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5618">**ACTIVITY_NAME** – naziv otvorene aktivnosti prilikom pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5618">**ACTIVITY_NAME** - Name of the Activity opened when booted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5619">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** – označava pokazuje li se tijekom pokretanja neki dijaloški okvir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5619">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** - Indicates if any dialog is shown during boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5620">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** – označava je li pokretanje sustava spriječeno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5620">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** - Indicates if the boot was preempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5621">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** – vrijeme potrebno za stvaranje niti aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5621">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** - Time taken to create Application threads</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5622">**AVAILABLE_MEMORY_IN_MB** – ukupna memorija dostupna na uređaju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5622">**AVAILABLE_MEMORY_IN_MB** - Total memory available in device</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5623">**AVG_SNAPSHOT_POPULATION_TIME** – prosječno vrijeme potrebno za dohvaćanje struktura bilježnica tijekom korištenja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5623">**AVG_SNAPSHOT_POPULATION_TIME** - Avg. time taken to fetch notebook structures while using the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5624">**BOOT_END_AT_VIEW** – potkategorija naziva aktivnosti (naziv prikaza)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5624">**BOOT_END_AT_VIEW** - Sub-category of Activity name (Name of the View)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5697">Prikuplja se svaki put kada PowerPoint otvori datoteku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5697">Collected whenever PowerPoint opens a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5698">Sadrži informacije o uspješnosti, pojedinosti neuspjeha, metriku performansi i osnovne detalje o datoteci, uključujući vrstu oblika datoteke i metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5698">Contains success information, failure details, performance metrics, and basic details about the file including file format type and document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5699">Te su informacije nužne da bi se osiguralo da PowerPoint može uspješno otvarati datoteke bez smanjenja performansi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5699">This information is necessary to ensure PowerPoint can open files successfully with no degradation in performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5700">To omogućuje dijagnosticiranje bilo kakvih problema koje otkrijemo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5700">It allows us to diagnose any problems we discover.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptdesktopbootime"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5873">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5873">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5874">Prikupljanje načina na koji je PowerPoint pokrenut.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5874">Collecting how PowerPoint is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5875">Obuhvaća pokretanje u zaštićenom prikazu, u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju, iz makronaredbe, ispisa, novog i praznog dokumenta, oporavka dokumenta, automatizacije ili klikom do cilja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5875">It includes boot PowerPoint in protected view, in assisted reading mode, from Macro, print, new and blank document, document recovery, from automation and if it is click- to-run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5876">Prikuplja i trajanje pokretanja programa PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5876">It also collects how long it takes PowerPoint to boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5877">Ti su podaci ključni da bi se moglo jamčiti da su performanse programa PowerPoint zadovoljavajuće pri pokretanju u različitim načinima rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5877">This data is critical to guarantee PowerPoint performs well when booted from different modes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5878">Microsoft te podatke koristi da bi opazio dugo trajanje pokretanja prilikom otvaranja programa PowerPoint u različitim načinima rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5878">Microsoft uses this data to catch long booting time when opening PowerPoint from different modes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5879">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5879">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5880">**AssistedReading –** u načinu rada za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5880">**AssistedReading -** in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5881">**Automation –** putem automatizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5881">**Automation -** from automation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5882">**Benchmark –** pokretanje standardiziranog testa performansi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5882">**Benchmark -** run performance benchmark</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5883">**Blank –** prazan dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5883">**Blank -** blank document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5884">**BootTime –** trajanje pokretanja sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5884">**BootTime -** session boot time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5885">**Embedding –** ugrađivanje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5885">**Embedding -** embedding document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5886">**IsC2R –** jest klikom do cilja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5886">**IsC2R -** is click-to-run</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5887">**IsNew –** novi dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5887">**IsNew -** new document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5888">**IsOpen –** otvoren je</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5888">**IsOpen -** is open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5889">**Macro1 –** izvođenje makronaredbe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5889">**Macro1 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5890">**Macro2 –** izvođenje makronaredbe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5890">**Macro2 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5891">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – nema nestandardnog razmaka u naredbenom retku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5891">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – there is non-standard space in command line</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5892">**Print –** ispis dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5892">**Print -** print document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5893">**PrintDialog –** ispis dokumenta putem dijaloškog okvira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5893">**PrintDialog -** print document with dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5894">**PrintPrinter –** ispis dokumenta putem pisača</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5894">**PrintPrinter -** print document with printer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5895">**ProtectedView –** u zaštićenom prikazu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5895">**ProtectedView -** in protected view</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5896">**Regserver –** registriranje programa PowerPoint kao COM poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5896">**Regserver -** Register PowerPoint as a COM server</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5897">**Restore –** vraćanje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5897">**Restore -** restore document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5898">**Show –** prikaz dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5898">**Show -** show document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5899">**Time –** vrijeme sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5899">**Time -** session time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5900">**UnprotectedView –** u nezaštićenom prikazu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5900">**UnprotectedView -** in unprotected view</span></span>

#### <a name="officeprojectbootandopenproject"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5906">Office.Project.BootAndOpenProject</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5906">Office.Project.BootAndOpenProject</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5907">Project je pokrenut otvaranjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5907">Project is booted by opening a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5908">Taj događaj označava da je korisnik otvorio Office Project putem pridružene datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5908">This event indicates that a user has opened Office Project with an associated file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5909">Sadrži podatke ključne za uspješnu potvrdu da se Project može pokrenuti i da može učitati datoteku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5909">It contains critical success data of making sure Project can start and load a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5910">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5910">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5911">**Data\_AlertTime –** trajanje aktivnosti dijaloškog okvira pri pokretanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5911">**Data\_AlertTime -** The amount of time the boot dialog was active.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5912">**Data\_BootTime –** trajanje pokretanja programa Project</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5912">**Data\_BootTime -** The amount of time it took to boot Project</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5913">**Data\_CacheFileSize –** ako je datoteka predmemorirana, veličina datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5913">**Data\_CacheFileSize -** If the file was cached, the size of the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5914">**Data\_EntDocType –** vrsta otvorene datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5914">**Data\_EntDocType -** The type of file that was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5915">**Data\_IsInCache –** je li otvorena datoteka predmemorirana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5915">**Data\_IsInCache -** Whether the file opened was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5916">**Data\_LoadSRAs –** želi li korisnik učitati SRA-ove</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5916">**Data\_LoadSRAs -** If the user wants to load SRAs or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5917">**Data\_Outcome –** ukupno trajanje pokretanja i otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5917">**Data\_Outcome -** Total boot and file open time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5918">**Data\_OpenFromDocLib –** ako je otvorena datoteka programa Project bila iz biblioteke dokumenata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5918">**Data\_OpenFromDocLib -** If the Project file opened was from the document library</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5919">**Data\_ProjectServerVersion –** trenutna verzija i međuverzija programa Project</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5919">**Data\_ProjectServerVersion -** The version and build that Project is currently on</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5924">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5924">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5925">**Data\_BootTime –** trajanje pokretanja programa Project</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5925">**Data\_BootTime -** The amount of time it took to boot Project</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5926">**Data\_FileLoaded –** neistinito ako se otvara izvana ili s novim praznim projektom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5926">**Data\_FileLoaded -** False if opening from out-space or new blank project</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5927">**Data\_IsEntOfflineWithProfile –** jesu li korisnici u profesionalnom SKU-u pa nisu povezani s poslužiteljem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5927">**Data\_IsEntOfflineWithProfile -** If the users are in the professional SKU and not connected to the server</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5930">**Data\_ProjectServerVersion –** trenutna verzija i međuverzija programa Project</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5930">**Data\_ProjectServerVersion -** The version and build that Project is currently on</span></span>


#### <a name="officeprojectopenproject"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5931">Office.Project.OpenProject</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5931">Office.Project.OpenProject</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5935">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5935">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5939">**Data\_EntDocType –** vrsta otvorene datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5939">**Data\_EntDocType -** the type of file that was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5940">**Data\_IsInCache –** je li otvorena datoteka predmemorirana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5940">**Data\_IsInCache -** whether the file opened was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5941">**Data\_LoadSRAs –** želi li korisnik učitati SRA-ove</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5941">**Data\_LoadSRAs -** If the user wants to load SRAs or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5942">**Data\_OpenFromDocLib –** ako je otvorena datoteka programa Project bila iz biblioteke dokumenata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5942">**Data\_OpenFromDocLib -** If the Project file opened was from the document library</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5943">**Data\_Outcome –** ukupno trajanje pokretanja i otvaranja datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5943">**Data\_Outcome -** Total boot and file open time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5944">**Data\_Outcome –** ukupno trajanje pokretanja i otvaranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5944">**Data\_Outcome -** Total boot and file open time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5945">**Data\_ProjectServerVersion –** trenutna verzija i međuverzija programa Project</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5945">**Data\_ProjectServerVersion -** The version and build that Project is currently on</span></span>

#### <a name="officesessionidproviderofficeprocesssessionstart"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5946">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5946">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5947">Primjenjuje se na sve aplikacije sustava Office za Windows: win32 i UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5947">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5948">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5948">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5949">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** šalje osnovne informacije nakon što započne nova sesija sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5949">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5950">Koristi se za brojanje jedinstvenih sesija na određenom uređaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5950">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5951">To se koristi kao impulsni događaj da bi se pouzdano utvrdilo je li aplikacija pokrenuta na uređaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5951">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5952">Osim toga, služi i kao ključni signal za općenitu pouzdanost aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5952">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5953">**AppSessionGuid** – identifikator određene sesije aplikacije, koja započinje u trenutku stvaranja procesa i traje do njegovog okončanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5953">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5954">Oblikovan je kao standardni 128-bitni GUID, ali se sastoji od četiri dijela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5954">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of four parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5955">Ta su četiri dijela redom: (1) 32-bitni ID procesa (2) 16-bitni ID sesije (3) 16-bitni ID pokretanja (4) 64-bitno UTC vrijeme stvaranja procesa, izraženo u koracima od 100 ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5955">Those four parts in order are (1) 32-bit Process ID (2) 16-bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64-bit Process creation time in UTC 100 ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5956">**processSessionId** – nasumično generirani guid za identifikaciju sesije aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5956">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5957">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** – konstantna Booleova vrijednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5957">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5958">Uvijek istinito.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5958">Always true.</span></span>

#### <a name="officesystemsessionhandoff"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5959">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5959">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5960">Označava da je trenutna sesija sustava Office ručno premještanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5960">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5961">To znači da se rukovanje korisnikovim zahtjevom za otvaranje dokumenta predaje već pokrenutoj instanci iste aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5961">This means that handling of a user's request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5962">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5962">The following fields are collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5963">**ParentSessionId** – ID sesije koja će preuzeti rukovanje korisnikovim zahtjevom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5963">**ParentSessionId** - The ID of the session that will be taking over handling of the users' request.</span></span>
