<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5965">Primjenjuje se na aplikacije sustava Office za UWP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5965">Applicable for Office UWP applications.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5966">Taj se događaj pokreće kada se aplikacija sustava Office prvi put pokrene nakon nadogradnje/instalacije iz trgovine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5966">This event is fired when an Office application is initiated for the first-time post upgrade/install from the store.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5967">Dio je osnovnih dijagnostičkih podataka, a koristi se za praćenje je li riječ o sesiji prvog pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5967">This is part of basic diagnostic data, used to track whether a session is launch session or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5968">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5968">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5969">**appVersionBuild** – broj međuverzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5969">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5970">**appVersionMajor** – broj glavne verzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5970">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5971">**appVersionMinor** – broj sporedne verzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5971">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5972">**appVersionRev** – broj verzije revizije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5972">**appVersionRev** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5973">**sessionID** – nasumično generirani GUID za identifikaciju sesije aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5973">**SessionID** - Randomly generated GUID to identify the app session</span></span>

#### <a name="officetelemetryenginesessionhandoff"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5974">Office.TelemetryEngine.SessionHandOff</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5974">Office.TelemetryEngine.SessionHandOff</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5975">Primjenjuje se na aplikacije sustava Office za Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5975">Applicable to Win32 Office applications.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5976">Taj nam događaj pomaže razumjeti je li stvorena nova sesija za obradu događaja otvaranja datoteke koje je pokrenuo korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5976">This event helps us understand whether there was a new session created to handle a user-initiated file open event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5977">To je ključna dijagnostička informacija koja se koristi za izvođenje signala pouzdanosti i provjeru radi li aplikacija prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5977">It is a critical diagnostic information that is used to derive reliability signal and ensure that the application is working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5978">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5978">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5979">**appVersionBuild** – broj međuverzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5979">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5980">**appVersionMajor** – broj glavne verzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5980">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5981">**appVersionMinor** – broj sporedne verzije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5981">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5982">**appVersionRev** – broj verzije revizije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5982">**appVersionRev** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5983">**childSessionID** – nasumično generirani guid za identifikaciju sesije aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5983">**childSessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5984">**parentSessionId** – nasumično generirani guid za identifikaciju sesije aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5984">**parentSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisioiosappboottime"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5985">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppBootTime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5985">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppBootTime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5989">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5989">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5990">**Data_AppBootTime** – trajanje potrebno za pokretanje aplikacije u milisekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5990">**Data_AppBootTime** - Duration taken for app to boot, in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisioiosappresumetime"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5991">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppResumeTime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5991">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppResumeTime</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5992">Ovaj se događaj pokreće svaki put kada se aplikacija Visio iOS nastavi izvoditi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5992">This event is triggered every time the Visio iOS app resumes focus.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5993">Neophodno je izmjeriti performanse nastavka izvođenja aplikacije i riješiti probleme s performansama aplikacije Visio iOS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5993">It is essential to measure app resume performance and troubleshoot performance issues of Visio iOS app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5995">**Data_AppResumeTime** – Trajanje nastavka izvođenja aplikacije u milisekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5995">**Data_AppResumeTime** - Duration for app to resume in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-5996">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5996">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-5997">Taj događaj označava da Office Word otvara dokument s popisa nedavno korištenih dokumenata (MRU).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5997">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5998">Sadrži i ključne podatke o performansama otvaranja datoteka, a iz perspektive korisnika predstavlja događaj pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5998">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-5999">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li otvaranje datoteka s MRU-a prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-5999">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6000">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6000">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6001">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6001">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6002">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6002">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6003">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6003">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6004">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova za koje vjerujemo da možemo otvoriti datoteku bez njih ako ih dobijemo prije nego što korisnik poželi početi uređivati ili možda spremati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6004">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6005">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – broj (sažetih) bajtova bez kojih bismo možda mogli otvoriti datoteku, ali bi to zahtijevalo značajna ulaganja u kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6005">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6006">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova koje moramo imati prije nego što možemo početi otvarati datoteku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6006">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6007">**Data_BytesUnknown** – broj bajtova u dijelovima dokumenta koje ne očekujemo pronaći</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6007">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6008">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko je dugo aktivnost bila odvojena od niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6008">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6009">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6009">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6010">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6010">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6011">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6011">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6012">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6012">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6062">**PathData_Doc_StreamAvailability** – pokazatelj je li niz dokumenata dostupan/onemogućen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6062">**PathData_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6063">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6063">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6064">Taj događaj označava da Office Word otvara dokument koji je korisnik dvaput kliknuo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6064">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double-clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6065">Sadrži i ključne podatke o performansama otvaranja datoteka, a iz perspektive korisnika predstavlja događaj pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6065">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6066">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li otvaranje datoteke dvostrukim klikom prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6066">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6067">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6067">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6068">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6068">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6069">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6069">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6070">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6070">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6071">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova za koje vjerujemo da možemo otvoriti datoteku bez njih ako ih dobijemo prije nego što korisnik poželi početi uređivati ili možda spremati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6071">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6072">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – broj (sažetih) bajtova bez kojih bismo možda mogli otvoriti datoteku, ali bi to zahtijevalo značajna ulaganja u kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6072">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6073">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova koje moramo imati prije nego što možemo početi otvarati datoteku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6073">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6074">**Data_BytesUnknown** – broj bajtova u dijelovima dokumenta koje ne očekujemo pronaći</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6074">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6075">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko je dugo aktivnost bila odvojena od niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6075">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6076">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6076">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6077">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6077">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6078">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6078">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6079">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6079">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6080">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6080">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6081">**Data_Doc_Ext** – nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6081">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6082">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6082">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6083">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6083">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6084">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje naziva domene koji identificira korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6084">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6085">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – izvješćuje o predmemoriranim zastavicama za postavljanje mogućnosti zahtjeva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6085">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6086">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta kojim se izvršava otvaranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6086">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6130">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6130">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6131">Taj događaj označava da Office Word otvara dokument putem COM aktivacije ili naredbenog retka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6131">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6132">Sadrži i ključne podatke o performansama otvaranja datoteka, a iz perspektive korisnika predstavlja događaj pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6132">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6133">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li otvaranje datoteka iz naredbenog retka prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6133">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6134">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6134">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6135">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6135">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6136">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes –** izvješćuje jesmo li mogli pravilno popuniti ostale vrijednosti vezane uz telemetriju dokumenta u sklopu događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6136">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6137">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6137">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6138">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous –** broj (sažetih) bajtova za koje vjerujemo da možemo otvoriti datoteku bez njih ako ih dobijemo prije nego što korisnik poželi početi uređivati ili možda spremati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6138">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6139">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork –** broj (sažetih) bajtova bez kojih bismo možda mogli otvoriti datoteku, ali bi to zahtijevalo značajna ulaganja u kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6139">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6140">**Data\_BytesSynchronous –** broj (sažetih) bajtova koje moramo imati prije nego što možemo početi otvarati datoteku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6140">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6141">**Data\_BytesUnknown –** broj bajtova u dijelovima dokumenta koje ne očekujemo pronaći.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6141">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6142">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode –** dokument je samo za čitanje ili za uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6142">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6143">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons –** unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6143">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6144">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6144">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6145">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType –** jedinice korištene za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6145">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6146">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState –** postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6146">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6147">**Data\_Doc\_Ext –** nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6147">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6148">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat –** verzija protokola za oblik datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6148">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6149">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn –** naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6149">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6150">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash –** jednosmjerno raspršivanje naziva domene koji identificira korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6150">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6151">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags –** izvješćuje o predmemoriranim zastavicama korištenima za postavljanje mogućnosti otvorenog zahtjeva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6151">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6152">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId –** jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta koji se koristio za otvaranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6152">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6153">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario –** bilježi način otvaranja dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6153">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6154">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights –** radnje dopuštene pravilima zaštite elektroničkih podataka primijenjenima na dokument/korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6154">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights -** Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6155">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen –** zastavica koja označava da je dokument inkrementalno otvoren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6155">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen -** Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6156">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported –** zastavica koja označava da je dokument podržan u servisu za suradnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6156">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported -** Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6157">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy –** zastavica koja označava da je otvorena izvanmrežna kopija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6157">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy -** Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6158">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked –** zastavica koja označava da na računalu postoji automatski sinkronizirana kopija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6158">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked -** Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6159">**Data\_Doc\_Location –** označava koji je servis dobavio dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6159">**Data\_Doc\_Location -** Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6182">**Data\_LastLoggedTag –** jedinstvena oznaka mjesta pozivanja koda, koja se koristi za identifikaciju dvokratnog neuspjelog pokušaja otvaranja (koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6182">**Data\_LastLoggedTag -** Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6187">**Data\_MoveDisabledReason –** pogreška koja onemogućuje premještanje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6187">**Data\_MoveDisabledReason -** Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6188">**Data\_MoveFlightEnabled –** je li omogućena testna verzija za značajku premještanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6188">**Data\_MoveFlightEnabled -** Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6189">**Data\_PartsUnknown –** broj dijelova dokumenta za koje nismo mogli pribaviti podatke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6189">**Data\_PartsUnknown -** the number of document parts that we couldn't get data for</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6196">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6196">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6197">Taj događaj označava da Office Word otvara dokument putem dijaloškog okvira Otvaranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6197">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6198">Sadrži i ključne podatke o performansama otvaranja datoteka, a iz perspektive korisnika predstavlja događaj pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6198">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6199">Događaj nadzire funkcionira li otvaranje datoteke putem dijaloškog okvira Otvaranje prema očekivanjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6199">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6200">Koristi se i za izračunavanje broja mjesečnih aktivnih korisnika/uređaja i metriku pouzdanosti oblaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6200">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6201">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6201">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6202">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – Izvještava jesmo li u slučaju uspjeli pravilno popuniti druge vrijednosti povezane s telemetrijom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6202">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry-related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6203">Koristi se za dijagnostiku kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6203">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6204">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova za koje vjerujemo da možemo otvoriti datoteku bez njih ako ih dobijemo prije nego što korisnik poželi početi uređivati ili možda spremati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6204">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6205">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – broj (sažetih) bajtova bez kojih bismo možda mogli otvoriti datoteku, ali bi to zahtijevalo značajna ulaganja u kod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6205">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6206">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – broj (sažetih) bajtova koje moramo imati prije nego što možemo početi otvarati datoteku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6206">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6207">**Data_BytesUnknown** – broj bajtova u dijelovima dokumenta koje ne očekujemo pronaći</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6207">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6208">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko je dugo aktivnost bila odvojena od niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6208">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6209">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za čitanje/uređivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6209">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6210">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – unaprijed definiran skup vrijednosti razloga zbog kojih se dokument otvorio u načinu za pomoć pri čitanju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6210">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6211">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** označava je li otvorena predmemorirana verzija dokumenta u oblaku i koja je logika za asinkrono osvježavanje korištena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6211">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6212">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – jedinice koje se koriste za inkrementalno otvaranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6212">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6213">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – postavka zaštite elektroničkih podataka za dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6213">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6214">**Data_Doc_Ext** – nastavak dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6214">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6215">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – verzija protokola oblika datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6215">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6216">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – naziv domene servisa OneDrive ili sustava SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6216">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6217">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje naziva domene koji identificira korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6217">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6218">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – jednosmjerno raspršivanje korisničkog identiteta kojim se izvršava otvaranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6218">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6219">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – bilježi način otvaranja dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6219">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6220">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – izvješćuje o predmemoriranim zastavicama za postavljanje mogućnosti zahtjeva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6220">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6221">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – radnje koje dopuštaju pravila zaštite elektroničkih podataka koja su primijenjena na dokument/korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6221">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6222">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – zastavica koja označava da je dokument inkrementalno otvoren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6222">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6223">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – zastavica koja označava da je dokument podržan u servisu za suradnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6223">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6224">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – zastavica koja označava da je otvorena izvanmrežna kopija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6224">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6225">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – zastavica koja označava da na računalu postoji automatski sinkronizirana kopija dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6225">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6226">**Data_Doc_Location** – označava koji je servis pružio dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6226">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6227">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – označava koja je poznata mapa pružila lokalno pohranjeni dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6227">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6228">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – broj drugih korisnika u sesiji zajedničkog uređivanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6228">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6229">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – označava postavljene zastavice za čitanje/pisanje lozinke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6229">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6230">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – razlozi zbog kojih je dokument otvoren samo za čitanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6230">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6231">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – anonimizirani identifikator dokumenta za dijagnosticiranje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6231">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6232">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – označava kako je postavljen kanal u stvarnom vremenu (RTC) za trenutnu datoteku (Onemogućeno, nepodržano, na zahtjev, uvijek uključeno itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6232">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was set up for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

### <a name="office-accessibility-configuration-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6302">*Podvrsta konfiguracije pristupačnosti za Office*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6302">*Office accessibility configuration subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6303">Značajke pristupačnosti u sustavu Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6303">Office accessibility features</span></span>

#### <a name="officeaccessibilityaccessibilitytoolsessionpresencewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6304">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6304">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6305">Omogućuje otkrivanje ima li korisnik alat za pomoćne tehnologije i kako se taj alat zove.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6305">Allows us to detect that the user has an Assistive technology tool and its name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6306">To nam omogućuje razumjeti ima li korisnik sustava Office problema s određenim alatom za pomoćne tehnologije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6306">This allows us to understand if an Office user is experiencing issues with a specific Assistive Technology tool.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6307">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6307">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6308">**Data\_Data\_Jaws –** označava je li Jaws bio pokrenut tijekom sesije **Data\_Data\_Magic –** označava je li Magic bio pokrenut tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6308">**Data\_Data\_Jaws -** indicates if Jaws was running during the session **Data\_Data\_Magic -** indicates if Magic was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6309">**Data\_Data\_Magnify –** označava je li Povećavanje bilo pokrenuto tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6309">**Data\_Data\_Magnify -** indicates if Magnify was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6310">**Data\_Data\_Narrator –** označava je li Pripovjedač bio pokrenut tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6310">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** indicates if Narrator was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6311">**Data\_Data\_NVDA –** označava je li NVDA bila pokrenuta tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6311">**Data\_Data\_NVDA -** indicates if NVDA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6312">**Data\_Data\_SA –** označava je li SA bila pokrenuta tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6312">**Data\_Data\_SA -** indicates if SA was running during the session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6372">Ovaj događaj predstavlja radnju pokrenutu od strane korisnika ili sustava koja je dio korisničkog iskustva zaštite privatnosti za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6372">This event represents a user or system initiated action that is part of the privacy User experience for Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6373">Pokreće se u dijaloškim okvirima zaštite privatnosti Prvog pokretanja, dijaloškom okviru za zaštitu privatnosti računa i obavijestima o zaštiti privatnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6373">It is triggered on the privacy First Run dialogs, Account Privacy dialog, and privacy notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6374">Događaj se koristi za razumijevanje sljedećeg: korisnici pristaju na postavke zaštite privatnosti sustava Office, korisnici mijenjaju postavke zaštite privatnosti sustava Office i postavke zaštite privatnosti sustava Office ažuriraju se u korisničkim sesijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6374">The event is used to understand the following: users consenting to Office privacy settings, users changing Office privacy settings, and Office privacy settings getting updated in user sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6375">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6376">**Data_ActionId –** korisnička akcija u dijaloškom okviru za zaštitu privatnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6376">**Data_ActionId -** User action in a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6377">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState –** postavka korisničkih pravila za dodatna neobavezna povezana iskustva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6377">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState -** User policy setting for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6378">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState –** korisnička postavka za preuzeti sadržaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6378">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6379">**Data_ForwardLinkId –** veza za dokumentaciju o privatnosti za korisnički scenarij</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6379">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6380">**Data_HRESULT –** zapis o pogreškama tijekom interakcije s dijalogom zaštite privatnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6380">**Data_HRESULT -** Record of errors during interaction with a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6381">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser –** kategorija korisničke licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6381">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser -** User license category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6382">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState –** korisnička postavka za povezane usluge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6382">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState -** User setting for connected services</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6383">**Data_RecordRegistry –** zapis o prikazivanje dijaloškog okvira privatnosti za veliku tvrtku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6383">**Data_RecordRegistry -** Record of showing the enterprise privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6384">**Data_Scenario –** scenarij prvog pokretanja na temelju korisničke licence i kategorije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6384">**Data_Scenario -** First run scenario based on the user license and category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6385">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog –** zapis o prikazivanje dijaloškog okvira privatnosti za program Insiders</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6385">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog -** Record of showing the Insiders privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6386">**Data_SendTelemetryOption –** korisnička postavka za telemetriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6386">**Data_SendTelemetryOption -** User setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6387">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy –** korisnička postavka pravilnika za telemetriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6387">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy -** User policy setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6388">**Data_UserCategory –** vrsta korisničkog računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6388">**Data_UserCategory -** User account type</span></span>  

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6389">**Data_UserCCSDisabled –** korisničko nadjačavanje za neobavezna povezana iskustva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6389">**Data_UserCCSDisabled -** User override for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6390">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState –** korisnička postavka za analizu sadržaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6390">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for analyzing content</span></span>
