- [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6396">Pogreška aktivnosti aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6396">Application activity error</span></span>](#application-activity-error-subtype)

### <a name="unexpected-application-exit-crash-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6397">*Podvrsta neočekivanog zatvaranja (rušenja) aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6397">*Unexpected application exit (crash) subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6398">Neočekivana zatvaranja aplikacija i stanje aplikacije kada se to dogodi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6398">Unexpected application exits and the state of the application when that happens.</span></span>

#### <a name="appstartupreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6399">app.startup.reason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6399">app.startup.reason</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6400">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje prepoznavanje i rješavanje problema zbog kojih se program Outlook srušio tijekom pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6400">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook crashed during app startup.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6401">Ovaj događaj uključuje informacije o tome zašto je došlo do rušenja kako bismo brzo mogli riješiti ovaj problem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6401">This event includes information on why the crash happened so we can fix the issue quickly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6402">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6402">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6403">**app_background_time** – vrijeme tijekom kojeg je aplikacija u posljednjoj sesiji bila u pozadini</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6403">**app_background_time** - duration of how long app was in background last session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6404">**startup_reason_type** – označava razlog zašto se aplikacija pokreće, a to će označiti je li je bilo potrebno prisilno zaustaviti ili je bio posrijedi drugi razlog.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6404">**startup_reason_type** - indicates why the app is starting up, this will indicate if it was due to force quit, or other reason.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6405">**watch_status_info** – prati sljedeće informacije, ako je primjenjivo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6405">**watch_status_info** - keeps track of the following information, if applicable.</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6406">**is_watch_app_installed** – utvrđuje je li korisnik instalirao aplikaciju Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6406">**is_watch_app_installed** - determines if the user has the Watch app installed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6407">**is_watch_paired** – utvrđuje je li uređaj iOS uparen sa satom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6407">**is_watch_paired** - determines if iOS device is paired to a watch</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6408">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – označava ima li sat mogućnost podrške te je li aktivan tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6408">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - indicates whether a watch is supportive and active during the session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6409">Sljedeća se polja prikupljaju samo za Outlook Mobile za iOS:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6409">The following fields are collected for only Outlook Mobile for iOS:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6410">**clean_exit_reason** – niz riječi koji označava je li postojao razlog za zaustavljanje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6410">**clean_exit_reason** - A string of words indicating why if there was a reason for the app stop</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6411">**is_agenda_user** – označava je li korisnik nedavno otvorio raspored, što upućuje na to zapisuje li se na disk tijekom pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6411">**is_agenda_user** - Indicates if the user has opened the agenda recently, which indicates if we are writing disk on the startup</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6412">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – označava ima li sat mogućnost podrške te je li aktivan tijekom sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6412">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - indicates whether a watch is supportive and active during the session</span></span>


#### <a name="applicationcrash"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6413">application.crash</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6413">application.crash</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6414">Koristi se za nadzor kritičnih rušenja aplikacije i pomaže nam prikupiti informacije o razlogu zašto se aplikacija srušila te kako to možemo spriječiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6414">Used for monitoring critical app crashes and helps us collect information on why the app has crashed and how to prevent it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6415">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6415">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6416">**android.hardware.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6416">**android.hardware.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6417">– (na primjer, android.hardware.bluetooth) Vrijednosti konfiguracije hardvera koje pruža platforma Android</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6417">- (for example, android.hardware.bluetooth) Hardware configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6418">**android.software.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6418">**android.software.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6419">– (npr. android.software.device_admin) Vrijednosti konfiguracije softvera koje pruža platforma Android</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6419">- (for example, android.software.device_admin) Software configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6420">**android_version** – naziv verzije sustava Android kao što označava android.os.Build.VERSION#RELEASE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6420">**android_version** - Device android version name as indicated by android.os.Build.VERSION#RELEASE</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6421">**application_package_name** – naziv paketa aplikacija kao što označava android.content.Context#getPackageName()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6421">**application_package_name** - Application package name as indicated by android.content.Context#getPackageName()</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6422">**application_stack_trace** – snop praćenja rušenja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6422">**application_stack_trace** - the stack trace of the crash</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6423">**application_version_code** – kod verzije aplikacije koji je definirala aplikacija Outlook</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6423">**application_version_code** - Application version code defined by the Outlook app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6424">**application_version_name** – naziv verzije aplikacije koji je definirala aplikacija Outlook</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6424">**application_version_name** - Application version name defined by the Outlook app</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6425">**com.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6425">**com.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6426">(na primjer, com.google.android.feature.FASTPASS_BUILD, com.amazon.feature.PRELOAD, com.samsung.android.bio.face) Vrijednosti konfiguracije specifične za proizvođača koje je pružila platforma Android</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6426">(for example, com.google.android.feature.FASTPASS_BUILD, com.amazon.feature.PRELOAD, com.samsung.android.bio.face) Manufacturer-specific configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6427">**crash_report_sdk** – SDK za slanje zapisnika o zatvaranju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6427">**crash_report_sdk** - SDK to send crash logs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6428">Ili Hockey ili AppCenter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6428">Either Hockey or AppCenter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6429">**crash_type** – crash_type može biti: java, izvorni i koji nisu fatalni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6429">**crash_type** - crash_type will have java, native, non-fatal as types.</span></span>

     - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6430">java – ako se zatvaranje zabilježi u aplikacijskom sloju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6430">java - if crash recorded on application Layer.</span></span>

     - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6431">izvorni – ako se zatvaranje zabilježi u okviru aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6431">native - if crash recorded on native layer within the app.</span></span> 

     - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6432">nije fatalni – zatvaranje se bilježi da bi se ispravila pogreška bilo koje značajke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6432">non-fatal - crashes being recorded to debug any feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6433">Aplikacija se neće zatvoriti, ali će prenositi zapisnike o zatvaranju koji nisu fatalni da biste lakše mogu ispravljati pogreške na značajci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6433">Application won’t crash but it will upload non-fatal crash logs to help in debugging a feature.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6434">**device_brand** – marka uređaja (proizvođač ili nosač) kao što označava android.os.Build#BRAND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6434">**device_brand** - Device brand (manufacturer or carrier) as indicated by android.os.Build#BRAND</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6435">**device_ID** – jedinstveni ID uređaja (IMEI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6435">**device_ID** - Device unique ID (IMEI)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6436">**device_manufacturer** – proizvođač uređaja kao što označava android.os.Build#MANUFACTURER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6436">**device_manufacturer** - Device manufacturer as indicated by android.os.Build#MANUFACTURER</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6437">**device_model** – model uređaja kao što označava android.os.Build#MODEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6437">**device_model** - Device model as indicated by android.os.Build#MODEL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6438">**device_name** – naziv uređaja kao što označava android.os.Build#DEVICE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6438">**device_name** - Device name as indicated by android.os.Build#DEVICE</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6439">**device_total_memory** – procjena ukupne veličine memorije uređaja na temelju statistika datotečnog sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6439">**device_total_memory** - Estimation of the total device memory size based on filesystem stats.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6440">**glEsVersion** – ključ verzije ugrađenih sustava OpenGL Embedded</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6440">**glEsVersion** - OpenGL Embedded Systems version key</span></span>


#### <a name="crashevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6441">crash.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6441">crash.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6442">Omogućuje nam prepoznavanje i ispravak situacija tijekom kojih je došlo do kritičnih rušenja aplikacije i pomaže nam prikupiti informacije o razlogu zašto se aplikacija srušila te kako to možemo spriječiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6442">Allows us to detect and fix situations where critical app crashes have occurred and helps us collect information on why the app has crashed and how to prevent it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6443">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6443">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6444">**crashTime** – datum i vrijeme u koje se rušenje dogodilo kao pomoć tijekom istrage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6444">**crashTime** - Date and time the crash occurred to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6445">**crash_time_from_start** – proteklo vrijeme od pokretanja aplikacije do rušenja, kao pomoć tijekom istrage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6445">**crash_time_from_start** – The elapsed time from app start to the crash occurred, to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6446">**exceptionName** – naziv iznimke koja je izazvala rušenje kao pomoć tijekom istrage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6446">**exceptionName** - The name of the exception that triggered the crash to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6447">**exception_reason** – naziv razloga koji je izazvao rušenje kao pomoć tijekom istrage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6447">**exception_reason** – The reason of the exception that triggered the crash to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6448">**hasHx** – govori nam da račun koristi naš novi servis sinkronizacije kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme uzrokovane našim servisom sinkronizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6448">**hasHx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6449">**incidentIdentifier** – jedinstveni ID za izvješće o rušenju kako bismo mogli pronaći odgovarajući problem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6449">**incidentIdentifier** - A unique ID for the crash report so we can find the corresponding issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6450">**isAppKill** – pomaže nam razumjeti je li ta aplikacija bila zaustavljena ili zatvorena na uređaju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6450">**isAppKill** - Helps us understand if that app was killed or close on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6451">**is_crashloop** – pomaže nam razumjeti je li vjerojatno da je uzrok rušenja nastanak petlje rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6451">**is_crashloop** – Helps us understand if the crash could likely be a crash loop.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6452">**reportKey** – jedinstveni ID za instalaciju aplikacije na uređaju za buduću istragu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6452">**reportKey** - A unique ID for the application installation om the device for issue investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6453">**signal** – signal koji je uzrokovao rušenje kako bi nam mogao pružiti više pojedinosti za istraživanje rušenja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6453">**signal** - A signal that caused the crash to give us more details to investigate this crash</span></span>


#### <a name="error"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6454">Error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6454">Error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6455">Omogućuje nam razumijevanje problema s kojima se mobilne aplikacije suočavaju tijekom pokušavanja dohvaćanja postavki zaštite privatnosti s poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6455">Allows us to understand the issues that mobile apps are facing when attempting to fetch privacy settings from the server.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6456">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6456">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6457">**correlationId** – jedinstveni identifikator za servisnu vezu koja je rezultirala pogreškom, što nam omogućuje što nije bilo u redu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6457">**correlationId** - a unique identifier for a service connection that resulted in an error, allowing us to diagnose what might have gone wrong</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6458">**errorCode** – prepoznaje relevantni kod pogreške primljen iz usluge koji se može koristiti za dijagnosticiranje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6458">**errorCode** - identifies the relevant error code received from the service that could be used to diagnose the problem</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6459">**exceptionType** – vrsta pogreške koju je biblioteka prepoznala tijekom dohvaćanja postavke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6459">**exceptionType** - type of error that the library encountered when fetching the setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6460">**message** – prepoznaje poruku o pogrešci primljenu od servisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6460">**message** - identifies the error message received from the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6461">**roamingSettingType** – označava mjesto s kojeg smo pokušali čitati postavke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6461">**roamingSettingType** - identifies the location from which we attempt to read settings</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6462">**settingId** – postavka koju se pokušalo dohvatiti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6462">**settingId** - the setting that was attempted to be fetched</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdomainunhandledexceptionhandlerfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6463">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6463">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6464">Prikuplja informacije za sve neobrađene iznimke pomoću aplikacije Data Streamer.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6464">Collects information for any unhandled exceptions using the Data Streamer App.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6465">Ti se podaci koriste za praćenje stanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6465">This data is used to monitor the health of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6466">Taj događaj generira dodatak Microsoft Data Streamer za Excel.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6466">This event is generated by Microsoft Data Streamer for Excel Add-in.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6467">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6467">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6468">**Iznimka** – poziv stogu zbog iznimke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6468">**Exception** - Call stack for the Exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6469">**Naziv događaja** – naziv događaja je kategorija i oznaka događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6469">**Event Name** - Event Name is the Event Category and Event Label.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappleidentitydomainname"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6470">Office.Apple.IdentityDomainName</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6470">Office.Apple.IdentityDomainName</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6471">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6471">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6472">Događaj se koristi za nadziranje stanja našeg sustava kao i za ispitivanje uzroka pogrešaka određenih korisnika domene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6472">The event is used to monitor the health of our system as well as investigating causes of failures by certain domain users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6473">Prikupljamo domenu koju koriste naši korisnici prilikom provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6473">We collect the domain used by our users when they authenticate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6474">Te podatke koristimo za identificiranje i rješavanje onih problema koji se na širokoj razini možda ne čine previše utjecajni, ali koji ispadaju vrlo utjecajni za određenu domenu korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6474">We use this data to help identify and fix those issues that might not seem too impactful at a broader level, but that turn out to be very impactful to a certain domain of users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6475">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6475">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6476">**Data_Domain** – domena koja se koristi za provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6476">**Data_Domain** - the domain used for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6477">**Data_IdentityProvider** – naziv davatelja identiteta provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6477">**Data_IdentityProvider** - The authentication identity provider name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6478">(odnosno LiveId ili ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6478">(that is, LiveId or ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6479">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** – kôd davatelja identiteta provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6479">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** - The authentication identity provider code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6480">(Broj)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6480">(A number)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeapplesystemhealthappexitmacandios"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6481">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6481">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6482">Ovaj se događaj prikuplja za aplikacije sustava Office koje rade na Apple platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6482">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6483">Događaj se koristi za nadziranje stanja aplikacija sustava Office kao i za ispitivanje uzroka pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6483">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications and for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6484">Prikupljamo podatke pri svakom izlazu iz aplikacije kako bismo utvrdili je li aplikacija zatvorena bez poteškoća.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6484">We collect data on each application exit to determine whether an application exited gracefully.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6485">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6485">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6486">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** – identifikator za sesiju koja ima izlaz iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6486">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** - The identifier for the session that experience the application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6487">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** – sporedna verzija aplikacije u kojoj je uočen izlaz iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6487">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6488">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** – duljina sesije od početka do kraja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6488">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** - The length of the session from start to exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6489">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** – pokazatelj stanja telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6489">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6490">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** – pokazatelj stanja telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6490">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6491">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** – regionalna shema OS-a na kojoj je uočen izlaz iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6491">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** - The Locale of the OS under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6492">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** – verzija OS-a u okviru koje je uočen izlaz iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6492">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** - The OS version under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6493">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** – količina ugrađene memorije koja je potrošena kada je došlo do izlaza iz aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6493">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of resident memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6494">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** – pokazatelj koji će označavati da je određena pogreška pogođena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6494">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** - An identifier that will denote the specific error being hit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6495">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** – vrijeme početka sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6495">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** - The time at which the session started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6496">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** – vrsta uočenog izlaza iz aplikacije (ako je bio izlaz bez poteškoća, taj će kôd označiti vrstu opažene pogreške)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6496">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** - The type of application exit observed (if it was an ungraceful exit, this code will denote the type of error observed)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6497">**Data_AffectedSessionVersion** – glavna verzija aplikacije u kojoj je uočen izlaz iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6497">**Data_AffectedSessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6498">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** – količina virtualne memorije koja je potrošena kada je došlo do izlaza iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6498">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of virtual memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6499">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** – je li izlaz iz aplikacije bio bez poteškoća ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6499">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** - Whether the application Exit was graceful or ungraceful.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitycomaddinunhandledexception"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6500">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6500">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6501">Događaj koji se generira kad se COM dodatak sruši na potrošačkoj verziji aplikacija sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6501">Event generated when COM Add-in crashes on a consumer version of Office applications.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6502">Ovo se upotrebljava se za izračun globalne „primjene” programa Microsoft 365 Apps za velike tvrtke za dodatak koji se zatim upotrebljava u drugim alatima, kao što je Readiness Toolkit.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6502">This is used to compute a global, non-enterprise-specific Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise "adoption" for an add-in, which is then used by tools like the Readiness Toolkit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6503">To korisnicima omogućuje da provjere valjanost dodataka koji su razmješteni u njihovim organizacijama u odnosu na kompatibilnost s najnovijim verzijama okruženja Microsoft 365 Apps za velike tvrtke te u skladu s tim planiraju njihove nadogradnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6503">This allows enterprise customers to validate if the add-ins they have deployed in their organizations are compatible with the latest versions of Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise and plan their upgrades accordingly.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6504">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6504">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6505">**ScopeId** – doseg trenutne niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6505">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6506">**Method** – metoda sustava Office u kojoj je došlo do iznimke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6506">**Method** – Office method where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6507">**Interface** – sučelje sustava Office u kojem je došlo do iznimke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6507">**Interface** – Office interface where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6508">**AddinId** – ID klase dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6508">**AddinId** – the add-in Class ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6509">**AddinProgId** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6509">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6510">**AddinFriendlyName** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6510">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6511">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – vremenska oznaka dodatka iz metapodataka DLL-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6511">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6512">**AddinVersion** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6512">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6513">**AddinFileName** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6513">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6514">**VSTOAddIn** – je li dodatak VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6514">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6515">**AddinConnectFlag** – trenutno ponašanje učitavanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6515">**AddinConnectFlag** – current load behavior</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6516">**LoadAttempts** – broj pokušaja učitavanja dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6516">**LoadAttempts** – number of attempts to load add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6521">**ScopeId** – doseg trenutne niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6521">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6522">**Method** – metoda sustava Office u kojoj je došlo do iznimke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6522">**Method** – Office method where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6524">**AddinId** – ID klase dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6524">**AddinId** – the add-in Class ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6525">**AddinProgId** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6525">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6526">**AddinFriendlyName** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6526">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6527">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – vremenska oznaka dodatka iz metapodataka DLL-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6527">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6528">**AddinVersion** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6528">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6529">**AddinFileName** – ukinut</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6529">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6530">**VSTOAddIn** – je li dodatak VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6530">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6531">**AddinConnectFlag** – trenutno ponašanje učitavanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6531">**AddinConnectFlag** – current load behavior</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6533">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6533">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6534">Dodaci za Office pokreću se u testnom okruženju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6534">Office Add-ins run in a sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6535">Ovaj događaj prikuplja impulsne informacije o aktivacijama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6535">This event collects heartbeat information on activations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6536">Kada se dodatak sruši, taj događaj prikuplja razlog zašto se srušio u slučaju da je povezan s našim testnim okruženjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6536">When an add-in crashes, this event collects why it crashed in the case it's related to our sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6537">Koristi se za istraživanje kada korisnici eskaliraju probleme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6537">Used to investigate when customers escalate issues.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6538">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6538">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6539">**AppId** – ID aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6539">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6540">**AppInfo** – podaci koji se odnose na vrstu dodatka (okno zadatka ili UILess ili u sadržaju itd.) i vrstu pružatelja (omen, SharePoint, filesystem itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6540">**AppInfo** - Data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6541">**AppInstanceId** – ID instance aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6541">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6542">**AssetId** – ID sadržaja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6542">**AssetId** - Asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6543">**ErrorCode** – ukupno utrošeno vrijeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6543">**ErrorCode** - Total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6544">**IsAugmentationScenario** – upućuje na to je li augmentacijska petlja odgovorna za pokretanje kontrole Okvir s rješenjima sustava Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6544">**IsAugmentationScenario** – indicates if the augmentation loop is responsible for initializing the Office Solutions Framework control</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6545">**IsDebug** – označava je li u pitanju sesija uklanjanje pogrešaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6545">**IsDebug** - indicates if session is a debug session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6546">**IsPreload** – upućuje na to je li dodatak unaprijed učitan u pozadini radi poboljšanja performansi aktivacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6546">**IsPreload** – indicates if the add-in is being preloaded in background for improving activation perf.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6547">**IsWdagContainer** – upućuje na to odvija li se aktivacija dodatka u Application Guard spremniku programa Windows Defender.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6547">**IsWdagContainer** – indicates if the add-in activation is being taken place in a Windows Defender Application Guard container.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6548">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – brojač aktiviranih dodataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6548">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - Counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6549">**RemoterType** – određuje vrstu daljinskog elementa (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF itd.) koji se koristi za aktivaciju dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6549">**RemoterType** - Specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF, etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6550">**StoreType** – porijeklo aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6550">**StoreType** - Origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6551">**Tag**– određuje gdje točno kôd nije uspio pomoću jedinstvene oznake povezane s njim.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6551">**Tag**- Specifies where exactly the code has failed using the unique tag associated with it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6552">**UsesSharedRuntime** – upućuje na to da koristi li aplikacija sharedRuntime ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6552">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeextensibilityvbatelemetrybreak"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6553">Office.Extensibility.VbaTelemetryBreak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6553">Office.Extensibility.VbaTelemetryBreak</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6554">Događaj koji se stvara kada datoteka s omogućenim makronaredbama naiđe na pogrešku pri kompiliranju ili izvođenju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6554">Event generated when a macro-enabled file runs into a compile or runtime error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6555">Analitika za stolna računala: koristi se kao brojnik za izračun stanja vrsta makronaredbi (na primjer, makronaredbe za Word, Excel itd.) koje je specifično za velike tvrtke i koje se tijekom pilot-programa koristi da bi se zaključilo je li dodatak „spreman za nadogradnju” u produkcijskom okruženju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6555">Desktop Analytics: This is used as numerator in the computation of enterprise-specific health status for macro types (for example, Word macros, Excel macros, etc.) which is used to infer during pilot if the add-in is "ready to upgrade" in the production ring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6556">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6556">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6557">**TagId** – ID telemetrijske oznake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6557">**TagId** – the ID of the telemetry tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6558">**BreakReason** – razlog zastoja (izvođenje, kompiliranje, druga pogreška)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6558">**BreakReason** – the reason for the break (runtime, compile, other error)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6559">**SolutionType** – vrsta rješenja (dokument, predložak, dodatak za aplikaciju, COM dodatak)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6559">**SolutionType** – type of solution (document, template, app add-in, COM add-in)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6560">**Data.ErrorCode** – kod pogreške koji je prijavio VBA modul</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6560">**Data.ErrorCode** – error code reported by VBA engine</span></span>


#### <a name="officefindtimeappfailedtostart"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-6561">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6561">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-6687">Događaj koji se stvara prilikom učitavanja COM dodatka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6687">Event generated when a COM Add-in is loaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6688">Taj je podatak ključan da bi se utvrdilo je li neki dodatak uzrokovao rušenje aplikacije sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6688">This information is critical to determine whether an add-in caused an Office application crash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-6689">Koristi se za procjenu globalne kompatibilnosti dodataka s aplikacijama sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-6689">It is used to assess global add-in compatibility with Office applications.</span></span>
