  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7183">**Data.Cid** – dinamički generiran korelacijski identifikator koji se šalje servisu prilikom pozivanja servisa radi dohvaćanja pravilnika za oblak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7183">**Data.Cid** - dynamically generated correlation identifier sent to the service when the service call was made to fetch the cloud policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7184">Koristi se za utvrđivanje korelacije s pozivom koji uzrokuje problem tijekom primjene pravilnika na oblak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7184">Used to correlate which call caused an issue while applying the policies on the cloud.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7185">**Data.Last Error** – jedna od pet vrijednosti niza (enumeratora) koja se koristi da bi se zabilježilo koja se faza primjene pravilnika izvršavala u trenutku kada je došlo do iznimke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7185">**Data.Last Error** - One of five string values (enumerators) to log which stage of policy application was being executed when the exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7195">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** – vraća vrijeme koje je potrebno za dovršavanje dodjele resursa u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7195">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** - Returns time taken to complete provisioning in millisecond</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7214">Ključni znak koji se upotrebljava za praćenje kada odlučimo prikazati korisniku dijaloški okvir za sigurno pokretanje pri sljedećem pokretanju jer smo se neprekidno rušili više puta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7214">The critical signal used to track when we decide to show user a safe boot dialog on next boot because we have been crashing on boot multiple times continuously.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7215">To se upotrebljava za osiguravanje prepoznavanja ključne regresije za aplikaciju OneNote i stanje usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7215">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7216">Ako korisnici vide dijaloški okvir za sigurno pokretanje, imamo kritičnu pogrešku rušenja sigurnog pokretanja i ta će nam informacija pomoći da znamo koliko se korisnika suočava s tim problemom i koliko će korisnika ponovno pokrenuti aplikaciju da bi zapravo vidjeli dijaloški okvir za sigurnu pokretanje naspram broja korisnika koji se neće vratiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7216">If users are seeing the safe boot dialog, then we have a critical boot crash bug and this info will help us know how many users are facing this issue and how many users boot the app again to actually see the safe boot dialog vs how many don’t return.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7217">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7217">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7218">Nijedno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7218">None</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopbootperfmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7219">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7219">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7220">Prikuplja podatke o trajanju pokretanja programa Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7220">Collects time taken to boot Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7221">Trajanje pokretanja programa Outlook aktivno se nadzire radi otkrivanja i dijagnostike nazadovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7221">The boot time of Outlook is actively monitored to detect and diagnose regressions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7222">Koristi se i za dijagnosticiranje eskalacija od strane korisnika, i za poboljšavanje performansi pokretanja s vremenom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7222">It is also used to diagnose customer escalations and improve boot performance over time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7223">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7223">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7224">**AddinElapsedTotal** – ukupno vrijeme utrošeno na učitavanje dodataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7224">**AddinElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for loading add-ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7225">**CredPromptCount** – broj prikazanih upita za vjerodajnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7225">**CredPromptCount** – Number of credential prompts shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7226">**ElapsedTotal** – ukupno vrijeme utrošeno na pokretanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7226">**ElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for boot</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7227">**IsLoggingEnabled** – je li omogućeno bilježenje u zapisnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7227">**IsLoggingEnabled** - Is logging enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7228">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – je li se prikazao dijaloški okvir Odabir profila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7228">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Whether the Choose Profile Dialog was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7231">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** – neuspjelo pokretanje potaknulo je otvaranje dijaloškog okvira za podršku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7231">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** - Boot failure triggered support dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7232">**ShowSafeModeDlg** – je li se sesija otvorila u sigurnom načinu rada</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7232">**ShowSafeModeDlg** - is the session opened in safe mode</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookmacbootperf"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7234">Office.Outlook.Mac.BootPerf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7234">Office.Outlook.Mac.BootPerf</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7235">Prikuplja podatke o trajanju pokretanja programa Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7235">Collects time taken to boot Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7236">Trajanje pokretanja programa Outlook aktivno se nadzire radi otkrivanja i dijagnostike nazadovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7236">The boot time of Outlook is actively monitored to detect and diagnose regressions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7237">Koristi se i za dijagnosticiranje eskalacija od strane korisnika, i za poboljšavanje performansi pokretanja s vremenom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7237">It is also used to diagnose customer escalations and improve boot performance over time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7238">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7238">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7239">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** – ukupno vrijeme utrošeno na pokretanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7239">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** - total time spent booting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7240">**MacOLKBootPerfID** – identifikator za vrijeme utrošeno na pokretanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7240">**MacOLKBootPerfID** - identifier for the time spent booting</span></span>


#### <a name="officeoutlookmacperformanceunresponsive"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7241">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7241">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7242">Koristi se za identificiranje problema u programu Outlook koje utječu na korisnike i koje se mogu manifestirati kao smanjena kvaliteta performansi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7242">Used to identify user impacting issues in Outlook that may manifest as degraded performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7243">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7243">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7244">**Duration** – vrijeme proteklo od smanjene kvalitete performansi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7244">**Duration** - time elapsed of degraded performance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7245">**EventType** – vrsta događaja koji bilježi smanjenu kvalitetu performansi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7245">**EventType** - type of event experiencing degraded performance</span></span>


#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7246">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7246">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7247">Prikuplja se tijekom pokretanja aplikacije sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7247">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7248">Obuhvaća utvrđivanje je li pokretanje pokrenuto otvaranjem datoteke ili pokretanjem putem izbornika Start, je li to bilo prvo pokretanje aplikacije, koliko memorije aplikacija koristi te je li korisniku prikazano blokirajuće korisničko sučelje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7248">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7249">Koristi se za mjerenje brzine pokretanja aplikacija sustava Office i koliko memorije one koriste tijekom pokretanja kako bi se osigurao prihvatljiv korisnički doživljaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7249">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7250">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7250">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7251">**ActivationKind** – je li aplikacija pokrenuta pokretanjem putem izbornika Start, otvaranjem datoteke ili putem OLE automatizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7251">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7252">**BootTostart** – je li korisnik odabrao prikazivanje početnog zaslona kada se aplikacija pokrene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7252">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7253">**ColdBoot** – je li aplikacija sustava Office pokrenuta prvi put nakon ponovnog pokretanja sustava ili se binarni podaci aplikacije moraju učitati s diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7253">**ColdBoot** - Whether is first time Office application runs after a system restart or application binary had to be loaded from disk.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7254">**DeviceModel** – model uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7254">**DeviceModel** - The model of the device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7255">**DocLocation** – kod otvaranja dokumenta označava koji je servis dobavio dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7255">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7256">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** – trajanje u mikrosekundama između pokretanja procesa sustava Office i učitavanja mso20win32client.dll-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7256">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** - The duration in microseconds it took between when the Office process was initialized and mso20win32client.dll was loaded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7257">**Embedding** – je li aplikacija otvorena za OLE ulaganje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7257">**Embedding** – Whether the app was opened for OLE embedding.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7258">**FirstBoot** – je li ovo bilo prvo pokretanje aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7258">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7259">**InitializationDuration** – trajanje u mikrosekundama koje je bilo potrebno za prvo pokretanje procesa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7259">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7260">**InterruptionMessageId** – je li pokretanje prekinuo dijaloški okvir koji je tražio korisnički unos, ID dijaloškog okvira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7260">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7261">**LegacyDuration** – koliko je dugo trebalo da se aktivnost izvrši, izmjereno koristeći različite početne i završne točke u odnosu na Activity.Duration.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7261">**LegacyDuration** - The length of time the activity took to execute, measured using different starting and ending points than Activity.Duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7262">**OpenAsNew** – je li aplikacija pokrenuta otvaranjem postojećeg dokumenta kao predloška za novi dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7262">**OpenAsNew** – Whether the app was started by opening an existing document as the template for a new one.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7263">**TotalWorkingSetMB** – količina memorije u megabajtima u radnom skupu procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7263">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's working set.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7264">**VirtualSetMB** – količina memorije u megabajtima u virtualnom skupu procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7264">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7265">(samo za MacOS / iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7265">(macOS / iOS only)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7266">**WorkingSetPeakMB** – najveća količina memorije u megabajtima koja se ikad dosad nalazila u radnom skupu procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7266">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process's working set so far.</span></span>


#### <a name="officepowerpointpptandroidrehearseview"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7267">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7267">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7281">**Sessionid** – Ovo je ID sjednice govornog ulaza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7281">**Sessionid** - This is speech frontdoor session ID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7282">Koristi se za ispravljanje pogrešaka u zapisnicima servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7282">This is used to debug service logs.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptandroidrehearseviewstartsession"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7302">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.StartSession</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7302">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.StartSession</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7303">Događaj se aktivira kada korisnik klikne na sesiju početka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7303">Event triggered when user clicks on start session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7304">Taj nam događaj pomaže pri snimanju broja korisnika koji upotrebljavaju značajku trenera za prezentacije na uređaju sa sustavom Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7304">This event helps us in capturing how many users are using the feature of Presenter coach on Android.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7305">U kombinaciji s Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView reći će nam koliko je korisnika uspješno dovršilo sesiju probe i koliko ih nije moglo to napraviti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7305">When combined with Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView it will tell us how many users successfully completed the rehearsal session and how many couldn’t.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7306">To je naš prvi indikator rušenja ili pogrešaka u značajci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7306">This is our first indicator of crashes or errors in the feature.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7307">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7307">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7308">Nijedno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7308">None</span></span>


#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharedrehearseviewerrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7309">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.RehearseView.Errors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7309">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.RehearseView.Errors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7310">*[Ovaj je događaj prethodno imenovan Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.Errors]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7310">*[This event was previously named Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.Errors]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7311">Događaj koji se aktivira kada se pojavi bilo koja pogreška.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7311">Event triggered when any error occurs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7312">Taj će nam događaj pomoći da znamo pogreške s kojima se korisnik suočio i pomoći će performansama trenera za prezentacije na mobilnom uređaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7312">This event will help us know what errors that user has faced and will help keep the Presenter Coach performant on mobile.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7313">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7313">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7314">**Session ID** – ID sesije probe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7314">**Session ID** – rehearsal session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7315">**RehearsalEventCode** – kod pogreške probe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7315">**RehearsalEventCode** – rehearsal error code</span></span>


#### <a name="officepowerpointrehearsalsessionmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7316">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7316">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7317">Događaj koji se aktivira prilikom zaustavljanja sesije govora trenera za prezentacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7317">Event triggered when the speech session is stopped for Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7318">Taj nam događaj pomaže pri hvatanju nekih metričkih podataka za sesiju vježbe u treneru za prezentacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7318">This event helps us in capturing some metrics for a rehearsal session in Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7319">To će pripomoći održavanje visoke kvalitete usluge za tu značajku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7319">It will help in maintaining a high quality of service for this feature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7320">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7320">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7321">**ActualRehearseBootTimeInMs** – to je stvarno utrošeno vrijeme za stvaranje veza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7321">**ActualRehearseBootTimeInMs** – This is the actual time taken for the connections to be created.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7322">**AdaptationTextSize** – to je veličina teksta koji se šalje u servis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7322">**AdaptationTextSize** – This is the size of the text that is sent to service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7323">**AuthDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za provjeru autentičnosti (osvježavanje tokena za provjeru autentičnosti).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7323">**AuthDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for authentication (refresh the auth token).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7324">**AuthError** – opisuje pogrešku provjere autentičnosti koja se dogodila (ako se dogodila).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7324">**AuthError** – This describes the authentication error that occurred (if at all).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7325">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – to je prosječno vrijeme povratnog putovanja mrežne govorne poruke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7325">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – This is the average round-trip time for network speech messages.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7326">**ConnectDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno da sesija dovrši povezivanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7326">**ConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the session to complete the connection.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7327">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za primanje prvih audiopodataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7327">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the first audio data to be received.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7328">**FRetriedOnOpenConnection** – to je Booleova vrijednost koja pokazuje je li došlo do ponovnog pokušaja za openconnection ili nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7328">**FRetriedOnOpenConnection** – This is a Boolean that indicates whether retry happens for openconnection or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7329">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za inicijalizaciju sloja za snimanje medijskih sadržaja / audiozapisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7329">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to initialize the media/audio capture layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7330">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – to je ukupan broj lokalno ispuštenih poruka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7330">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped locally.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7331">**NumReconnectAttemptsDuringSession** – to pokazuje koliko je puta pokušano ponovno povezivanje na speechservice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7331">**NumReconnectAttemptsDuringSession** – This indicates how many times the attempt was made to reconnect to speechservice.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7332">**NumTriesDuringEachReconnectAttempt** – to je polje koje pokazuje broj izvršenih pokušaja tijekom svakog pokušaja ponovnog povezivanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7332">**NumTriesDuringEachReconnectAttempt** – This is an array that indicates number of tries that were done during each reconnect attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7333">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za otvaranje veze sa servisom FrontDoor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7333">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – This is the time in milliseconds taken to open the connection to the FrontDoor service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7334">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za slanje adaptacijskog teksta servisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7334">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to send the adaptation text to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7335">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – to je ukupan broj poruka koje je servis ispustio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7335">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped by the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7336">**SessionDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme trajanja cijele sesije od kada je korisnik kliknuo za početak do kada je kliknuo za kraj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7336">**SessionDurationInMs** – This is the time duration of entire session from when user clicked start to when user clicked stop.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7337">**Sessionid** – to je ID sjednice govornog ulaza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7337">**SessionId** – This is the speech frontdoor session ID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7338">Može se koristiti za ispravljanje pogrešaka u zapisnicima servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7338">We can use this to debug service logs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7339">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – to je polje kodova pogrešaka primljenih zajedno s vremenskim oznakama, koji vam mogu pomoći pri otklanjanju pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7339">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps, which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7340">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – to je polje kodova pogrešaka primljenih zajedno s vremenskim oznakama, koji vam mogu pomoći pri otklanjanju pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7340">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps, which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7341">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za početak snimanja govora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7341">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to start speech capture.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7342">**StartSpeechServiceDurationInMs** – to je polje vremena koliko je potrebno da sesija govora započne svaki put kada dođe do ponovnog povezivanja, uključujući trajanje prve pokrenute sesije govora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7342">**StartSpeechServiceDurationInMs** – This is an array of time taken to start speech session every time there is a reconnect, including first start speech session duration also.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7343">**TotalMessageCount** – to je ukupan broj audioporuka poslanih servisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7343">**TotalMessageCount** – This is the total number of audio messages sent to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7344">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – to je vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za dovršenje povezivanja s web-utičnicom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7344">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to complete the web socket connection.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsiderregistercurrentinsider"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7352">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.RegisterCurrentInsider</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7352">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.RegisterCurrentInsider</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsidershowofficeinsiderdlg"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7360">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7360">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7361">Ključni signal koji prati interakciju korisnika s dijaloškim okvirom Join Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7361">Critical signal tracking user interaction with Join Office Insider dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7362">Koristi se za prepoznavanje svih problema u provedbi promjena koje je pokrenuo korisnik kao što su pridruživanje ili napuštanje programa Office Insider i promjena razine programa Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7362">It is used for identifying any issues in performing user-initiated changes such as joining or leaving Office Insider program and changing Office Insider level.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7363">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7363">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7366">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** – razina programa Insider tijekom zatvaranja dijaloškog okvira „Pridruživanje programu Office Insider”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7366">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** - Insider level on closing of "Join Office Insider" dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7367">**Data_IsInternalUser** – označava pokreće li se aplikacija putem vjerodajnica Microsoftova poslovnog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7367">**Data_IsInternalUser** - Indicates whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7368">**Data_IsInternalUser** – označava može li kod utvrditi pokreće li se aplikacija putem vjerodajnica Microsoftova poslovnog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7368">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** - Indicates whether the code could determine whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7369">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** – označava je li poveznica za pretplatu na bilten programa Office Insider aktivirana pod uvjetom da se korisnik pridružio programu Office Insider, da je značajka pretplate na bilten omogućena i da korisnik nije otkazao otvaranje web-mjesta pretplate na bilten programa Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7369">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** - Indicates whether Office Insider Newsletter Subscription link was triggered under condition that user has joined Office Insider program, Newsletter Subscription feature is enabled, and the user have not canceled opening of Office Insider Newsletter Subscription webpage.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7370">**Data_RegisterInsider** – stanje registracije programa Office Insider</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7370">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7371">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – kod rezultata za registraciju programa Office Insider</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7371">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7372">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – trenutno stanje registracije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7372">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7373">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** – zatraženo stanje registracije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7373">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>


#### <a name="officevisiosharedvisiofilerender"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7374">Office.Visio.Shared.VisioFileRender</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7374">Office.Visio.Shared.VisioFileRender</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7375">Taj događaj bilježi trajanje vizualizacije datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7375">This event captures file render time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7376">Taj nam događaj pomaže paziti na performanse vizualizacije datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7376">This event helps us keep file render performance in check.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7377">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7377">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7378">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** – prosječno trajanje vizualizacije crteža programa Visio u sesiji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7378">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** - Average time it took to render Visio drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7379">**Data\_CompositeSurfEnabled: bool** – istinito znači da je omogućen kombinirani način vizualizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7379">**Data\_CompositeSurfEnabled: bool** - true is composite rendering mode is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7380">**Data\_Count: integer** – broj vizualizacija crteža u sesiji programa Visio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7380">**Data\_Count: integer** - Number of times Visio renders the drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7381">**Data\_FirstRenderTime: long** – trajanje vizualizacije datoteke prilikom prvog pokretanja, u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7381">**Data\_FirstRenderTime: long** - duration to render file on first launch in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7382">**Data\_MaxTime: integer** – maksimalno trajanje vizualizacije crteža programa Visio u sesiji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7382">**Data\_MaxTime: integer** - Max time it took to render Visio drawing in a session</span></span>


#### <a name="officevisiovisiofileopenreliability"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7383">Office.Visio.VisioFileOpenReliability</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7383">Office.Visio.VisioFileOpenReliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7384">Taj događaj prikuplja podatke o performansama otvaranja datoteka za Visio Dev16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7384">This event collects File open perf data for Visio Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7385">Taj se događaj koristi za praćenje performansi otvaranja datoteka u programu Visio Dev16 i njihovo povezivanje sa svojstvima datoteke kao što je njezina veličina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7385">This event is used to monitor performance of File open and associates it with file properties like file size for Visio Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7386">Svojstva datoteke omogućuju nam brže ispravljanje pogrešaka i otkrivanje korijenskih uzroka problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7386">File properties enable us to debug and root cause issues faster.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7387">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7387">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7390">**Data\_DocumentId: string –** GUID puta datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7390">**Data\_DocumentId: string -** GUID of file path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7391">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds:double –** trajanje spremanja u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7391">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds: double -** Duration to complete save as in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7392">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double –** kvadrat vrijednosti DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7392">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double -** squared value for DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7393">**Data\_ErrorCode: integer –** interni kod pogreške pri neuspjelom otvaranju datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7393">**Data\_ErrorCode: integer -** Internal error code for file open failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7394">**Data\_Extension\_Docs: string –** datotečni nastavak otvorenog dijagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7394">**Data\_Extension\_Docs: string -** File extension of diagram opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7397">**Data\_FileIOBytesWritten: int –** ukupan broj bajtova zapisanih prilikom spremanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7397">**Data\_FileIOBytesWritten: int -** total bytes written while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7399">**Data\_FileName:binary** – binarno raspršivanje naziva datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7399">**Data\_FileName: binary -** Binary Hash of file name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7400">**Data\_FileOpenDownloadDurationInMs: long –** trajanje preuzimanja datoteke u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7400">**Data\_FileOpenDownloadDurationInMs: long -** duration to download file in milliseconds</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7401">**Data\_FileOpenEndDurationInMs: long: –** trajanje otvaranja datoteke u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7401">**Data\_FileOpenEndDurationInMs: long: -** duration to open file in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7402">**Data\_FileOpenTimeStamp: time: –** vremenska oznaka u trenutku početka otvaranja datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7402">**Data\_FileOpenTimeStamp: time: -** Time stamp when file started opening</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7408">**Data\_IsIRM:bool –** istinito ako je datoteka zaštićena pravima na informacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7408">**Data\_IsIRM: bool -** true if file is Information Right Protected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7409">**Data\_IsReadOnly: bool –** istinito ako je datoteka samo za čitanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7409">**Data\_IsReadOnly: bool -** true if the file is read only</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7410">**Data\_IsSuccess: bool –** istinito kada je otvaranje datoteke uspješno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7410">**Data\_IsSuccess: bool -** true when file open was successful</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7411">**Data\_Location: string –** lokacija datoteke, kao što je lokalno, SharePoint, OneDrive, WopiConsumer, WopiBusiness, GenericThirdPartyConsumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7411">**Data\_Location: string -** location of the file like Local, SharePoint, OneDrive, WopiConsumer, WopiBusiness, GenericThirdPartyConsumer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7412">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesRead: int –** ukupan broj mrežnih bajtova pročitanih prilikom spremanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7412">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesRead: int -** total network bytes read while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7413">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesReadSquared: int –** kvadrat vrijednosti Data\_NetworkIOBytesRead</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7413">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesReadSquared: int -** squared value of Data\_NetworkIOBytesRead</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7414">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesWritten: int –** ukupan broj mrežnih bajtova zapisanih prilikom spremanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7414">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesWritten: int -** total network bytes written while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7415">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesWrittenSquared: int –** kvadrat vrijednosti NetworkIOBytesWritten</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7415">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesWrittenSquared: int -** squared value of NetworkIOBytesWritten</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7416">**Data\_OpenLocation: integer –** lokacija s koje je datoteka otvorena: 0, lokalno, 1, mreža, 2, SharePoint, 3 – web</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7416">**Data\_OpenLocation: integer -** Location of the file from which it was opened 0, Local, 1, Network, 2, SharePoint, 3 – Web</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7417">**Data\_Size\_Docs: integer –** veličina dokumenta u bajtovima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7417">**Data\_Size\_Docs: integer -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7418">**Data\_Tag: string –** jedinstveni identifikator za prepoznavanje događaja „Spremi kao”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7418">**Data\_Tag: string -** unique identifier to identify Save AS event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7419">**Data\_WasSuccessful: bool –** istinito ako je otvaranje bilo uspješno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7419">**Data\_WasSuccessful: bool -** true if open as was successful</span></span>


#### <a name="onenoteappsafebootdialogactiontaken-officeonenoteandroidsafebootdialogactiontaken-officeandroidearlytelemetrysafebootdialogactiontaken"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7420">OneNote.App.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.OneNote.Android.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SafeBootDialogActionTaken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7420">OneNote.App.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.OneNote.Android.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SafeBootDialogActionTaken</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7421">Ključni znak koji se koristi za praćenje korisnikovog odgovora kada korisnik vidi dijalog sigurnog pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7421">The critical signal used to track user response when the user sees a safe boot dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7422">Dijaloški se okvir sigurnog pokretanja prikazuje kada uzastopno pokretanje nije moguće.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7422">Safe boot dialog is shown when we were unable to launch repeatedly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7423">Odabir se korisnika za sigurno pokretanje upotrebljava u obliku dozvole za brisanje podataka u aplikaciji radi uspješnog pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7423">User choice to safe boot is used as permission to clear app data to launch successfully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7424">To se upotrebljava za osiguravanje prepoznavanja ključne regresije za aplikaciju OneNote i stanje usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7424">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7425">Korisnik vidi kada će naići na kritičnu pogrešku rušenja sigurnog pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7425">User sees when they encounter critical boot crash bug.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7426">S pomoću te informacije ćemo moći pratiti je li uzrok zatvaranja riješen i može li korisnik uspješno pokrenuti aplikaciju ili ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7426">This info will help track if they crash cause has been resolved and user can launch the app successfully or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7427">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7427">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7428">**DIALOG_ACTION** – na koji je gumb dijaloškog okvira korisnik kliknuo – pozitivni gumb ili negativni gumb</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7428">**DIALOG_ACTION** - Which dialog button did the user click on – Positive button or negative button</span></span>


#### <a name="perfevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7429">perf.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7429">perf.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7430">Koristi se za praćenje mogućih negativnih utjecaja na funkciju učitavanja različitih dijelova aplikacije, primjerice za osiguravanje da se vaša ulazna pošta što brže učitava tijekom prvog otvaranja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7430">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on performance of loading different parts of the app, for example to ensure when you first open the app, your inbox loads as quickly as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7431">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7431">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7432">**app_start_show_message_list** – to znači da je došlo do problema s funkcijom u okviru pokretanja aplikacije, što je dovelo do dugačkog učitavanja popisa poruka vaše ulazne pošte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7432">**app_start_show_message_list** - that means there was a performance issue with the app start-up causing your inbox message list to take a long time to load</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7433">**Prosječna** – sakuplja iznos ponovnih učitavanja koji se događaju u razgovoru podijeljen s količinom poruka u tom razgovoru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7433">**average** - collects the number of reloads that happen on a conversation divided by the number of messages in that conversation.</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7434">**event_type** – govori nam vrstu događaja funkcije koji je doveo do problema s funkcijom kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenom vrstom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7434">**event_type** - tells us the type of performance event that caused a performance issue to help us detect issues related to a specific type.</span></span>   

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7435">**extra_params** – razvojni inženjer ovdje može dodati dodatne parametre kako bi nam pomogao pružiti više pojedinosti o tome što bi moglo uzrokovati ovaj problem s funkcijom, odnosno, kada je ova radnja započela i završila itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7435">**extra_params** - A developer can add additional parameters here to help give us more details about what could be causing this performance issue, that is, when did this action start and end, etc.</span></span> 

-   <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7436">**has_work_profile** – označava radi li aplikacija pod Android Work Profile ili sličnom konfiguracijom kako bi se analiza izvedbe povezala s tim okruženjima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7436">**has_work_profile** - indicates whether the app is running under Android Work Profile or similar configuration, in order to correlate performance analysis to these environments.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7437">**profiling_summary** – omogućuje informacije o grupi zadataka, broju zadataka i prosječnom vremenu za te grupe da biste bolje razumjeli potencijalne regresije u pojedinim područjima prilikom učitavanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7437">**profiling_summary** - provides information about the group of tasks, the number of tasks and the average time for those groups to help understand potential regressions in specific areas when loading the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7438">**runtime_performance_monitoring_data** – pruža podatke o izvedbi (vrijeme učitavanja, brojanje zapisa) prilikom učitavanja podataka u različitim dijelovima aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7438">**runtime_performance_monitoring_data** - provides the performance data (loading time, record count) when loading data in different parts of the app.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7439">**average_cost_time_ns** –prosječno vrijeme troška mjereno u nanosekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7439">**average_cost_time_ns** - The average cost time measured in nanoseconds.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7440">**cost_type** – govori nam je li taj događaj namijenjen za mjerenje izvršenja sloja prostora za pohranu ili cjelokupno trajanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7440">**cost_type** - Tells us whether this event is for measuring storage layer execution or total duration.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7441">**hx_object_type** – pruža detaljni tip objekta mjerenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7441">**hx_object_type** - Provides the detail programming object type of the measuring.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7442">**is_main_thread** – govori nam mjeri li ovaj događaj samo vrijeme izvršenja glavne niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7442">**is_main_thread** - Tells us whether this event only measures main thread execution time.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7443">**record_count** – broj zapisa koje vraća pozadinski sloj za pohranu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7443">**record_count** - The number of records the underlying storage layer returns.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7444">**scope_name** – predstavlja naziv stranice/komponenti korisničkog sučelja kojoj taj događaj pripada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7444">**scope_name** - Provides the name of UI page/components this event belongs to.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7445">**average_cost_time_ns** – ukupno vrijeme troška mjereno u nanosekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7445">**total_cost_time_ns** - The total execution time measured in nanoseconds.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7446">**total_time_elapsed** – govori nam koliko je događaj funkcije trajao kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti ozbiljnost problema s funkcijom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7446">**total_time_elapsed** - Tells us how long the performance event took to help us understand the severity of the performance issue</span></span>

#### <a name="performancerecord"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7447">performance.record</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7447">performance.record</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7448">Ovim se događajem prikuplja metrika performansi aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7448">This event collects performance metrics of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7449">Omogućuje nam otkrivanje i rješavanje situacija kada iskorištenost memorije aplikacije i CPU postanu kritično visoki ili postoje neki drugi problemi s performansama, što može dovesti do usporavanja vašeg uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7449">This allows us to detect and fix situations where the app memory usage and CPU usage becomes critically high or has other performance issues, which could cause your device to slow down.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7450">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7450">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7451">**app_exit_metric** – javlja nam metriku o broju različitih vrsti performansi za prednji i pozadinski izlaz iz aplikacije, kao pomoć u razumijevanju neočekivanog izlaska iz aplikacije s razlozima negativnih performansi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7451">**app_exit_metric** - Tell us the metrics about counts of different performance types of foreground and background app exits, to help us understand app exits unexpectedly with negative performance reasons.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7452">**average_suspended_memory** – javlja nam prosječnu količinu memorije koju aplikacija upotrebljava kada je obustavljena kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan učinak na funkciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7452">**average_suspended_memory** - Tells us the average amount of memory in use by the app when it’s suspended so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7453">**category** – govori nam je li aplikacija u određenom trenutku u prvom planu ili pozadini.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7453">**category** - Tells us if the app is in the foreground or background at the time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7454">Moguće vrijednosti uključuju prvi plan ili pozadinu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7454">Possible values include foreground and background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7455">**cpu_usage** – govori nam koliko je CPU-a aplikacija koristila kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan učinak na funkciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7455">**cpu_usage** - Tells us how much CPU was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7456">**cumulative_CPU_time** – govori nam koliko ukupno CPU-a aplikacija koristi s mjerenjem trajanja kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan učinak na funkciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7456">**cumulative_CPU_time** - Tells us the total amount of CPU the app used with the measurement of duration of time, so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7457">**cumulative_GPU_time** – govori nam koliko ukupno GPU vremena aplikacija koristi kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan utjecaj vijeka trajanja baterije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7457">**cumulative_GPU_time** - Tells us the total amount of GPU time used by the app, so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative battery life impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7458">**is_watch_app_installed** – govori nam koristi li korisnik trenutno uređaj Apple Watch te je li on instaliran kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti negativan utjecaj na funkciju zbog uređaja Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7458">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is installed to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7459">**is_watch_paired** – govori nam koristi li korisnik trenutno uređaj Apple Watch te je li on uparen s uređajem kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti negativan utjecaj na funkciju zbog uređaja Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7459">**is_watch_paired** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is paired with the device to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7460">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – govori nam koristi li korisnik trenutno uređaj Apple Watch te je li on aktivan kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti negativan utjecaj na funkciju zbog uređaja Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7460">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is active to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7461">**memoAry_used_percentage** – govori nam koji je postotak memorije aplikacija koristila kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan učinak na funkciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7461">**memoAry_used_percentage** - Tells us what percentage of memory was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7462">**memory_used** – govori nam koliko je memorije aplikacija koristila kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan učinak na funkciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7462">**memory_used** - Tells us how much memory was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7463">**peak_memory_usage** – govori nam koliko je najviše memorije aplikacija koristila kako bismo imali vrijednost za usporedbu i kako bismo razumjeli negativan učinak na funkciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7463">**peak_memory_usage** - Tells us the largest amount of memory used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7464">**scroll_hitch_time_ratio** – govori nam koji je omjer vremena proveden u zastoju tijekom kretanja kroz korisničko sučelje kako bismo razumjeli negativan utjecaj na učinak korisničkog sučelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7464">**scroll_hitch_time_ratio** - Tells us the ratio of the time spent hitching while scrolling on UI, to help us understand the negative UI performance impact.</span></span>


### <a name="application-activity-error-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7465">*Podvrsta pogreške aktivnosti aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7465">*Application activity error subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7466">Pogreške u funkcioniranju značajke ili korisničkog okruženja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7466">Errors in functionality of a feature or user experience.</span></span>

#### <a name="assertion"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7467">assertion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7467">assertion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7468">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje otkrivanje kada su nastupile kritične pogreške aplikacije koje bi uzrokovale rušenje vaše aplikacije ili iskustvo ozbiljnih problema, primjerice prikaz praznih redaka u vašoj ulaznoj pošti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7468">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred that would cause your app to crash or experience serious issues like causing you to see empty rows in your inbox.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7469">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7469">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7470">**count** – ukupan broj stavki povezanih s pogreškom; primjerice, broj kalendara koji imaju pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7470">**count** - Total number of items associated with the error; for example, number of calendars that have errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7471">**has_hx** – govori nam da račun koristi naš novi servis sinkronizacije kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme uzrokovane našim servisom sinkronizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7471">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7472">**host_name** – naziv glavnog računala servisa koji je bio uključen u grešku kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim glavnim računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7472">**host_name** - the name of the service host that was involved in the error to help us detect issues related to a specific host</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7473">**host_type** – vrsta glavnog računala koje je bilo uključeno u pogrešku kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s vrstom određenog glavnog računala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7473">**host_type** - the type of host that was involved in the error to help us detect issues related to a specific host type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7474">**message** – prilagođena poruka za označavanje da se koristi za dijagnozu problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7474">**message** - custom message for the assertion that is used to diagnose the issue</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7475">**origin** – podrijetlo pogreške u kodu koji nam pomaže prepoznavanje problema u vezi s određenim dijelom koda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7475">**origin** - the origin of the error in the code to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7476">**stacktrace** – snop praćenja u kojem je označavanje nastupilo kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim dijelom koda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7476">**stacktrace** - the stack trace where the assertion occurred to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7477">**type** – vrsta pogreške označavanja koja je nastupila, na primjer, null_folder_name, compose_selected_null_account, kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme u vezi s određenim dijelom koda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7477">**type** - the type of assertion error that occurred, for example, null_folder_name, compose_selected_null_account, to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

#### <a name="editcontacterror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7478">edit.contact.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7478">edit.contact.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7479">Omogućuje nam otkrivanje i rješavanje situacija u okviru kojih su pogreške uzrokovane kada pokušavate vidjeti ili uređivati kontakte putem aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7479">Allows us to detect and fix situations where errors were caused when you're trying to view or edit contacts through our app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7480">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7480">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7481">**errorType** – vrsta pogreške koja je nastupila kako bi nam pomogao dijagnosticirati problem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7481">**errorType** - the type of error that occurred to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7482">**field** – polje kontakta koje je korisnik pokušao uređivati kako bi nam pomogao dijagnosticirati problem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7482">**field** - The contact field that the user was trying to edit to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7483">**version** – verzija servisa kartice kontakta koji koristimo kako bi nam pomogao dijagnosticirati problem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7483">**version** - The version of the contact card service we are using to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

#### <a name="errorreport"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7484">error.report</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7484">error.report</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7485">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje prepoznati kada su nastupile kritične pogreške korištene aplikacije da bismo mogli spriječiti probleme koji mogu prouzročiti rušenje aplikacije ili vam onemogućiti čitanje e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7485">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app to crash or prevent you from reading email.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7486">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7486">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7487">**client-request-id** – identifikator zahtjeva klijenta za zahtjev koji je uzrokovao pogrešku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7487">**client-request-id** - the client request identifier for the request that caused the error</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7488">**date** – datumska oznaka zahtjeva koji je uzrokovao pogrešku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7488">**date** - the datestamp of the request that caused the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7489">**error** – vrsta pogreške, npr. get_mailbox_location_failed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7489">**error** - the type of error, for example, get_mailbox_location_failed</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7490">**error_body** – tijelo poruke o pogrešci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7490">**error_body** - the body of the error message</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7491">**is_x_mailbox_anchor_set** – je li na zahtjevu bilo postavljeno svojstvo X-AnchorMailbox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7491">**is_x_mailbox_anchor_set** - whether the X-AnchorMailbox property was set on the request</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7492">**reason** – razlog za pogrešku, odnosno, poruka o pogrešci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7492">**reason** - the reason for the error, that is, an error message</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7493">**request-id** – identifikator zahtjeva poslužitelja za zahtjev koji je uzrokovao pogrešku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7493">**request-id** - the server request identifier for the request that caused the error</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7494">**source** – izvor pogreške unutar infrastrukture modela objekta, u pravilu „BE” ili „FE”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7494">**source** - the source of the error within the OM infrastructure, typically one of 'BE' or 'FE'</span></span>


#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriversofthang"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7495">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7495">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7496">Pomaže Microsoftu razdvojiti duge blokade upravljačkog programa grafičke kartice od onih kratkih, što pak olakšava donošenje odluka o tome s kojim upravljačkim programima grafičkih kartica možda ima problema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7496">Helps Microsoft separate long video card driver hangs from short ones, which in turn helps make decisions about which video card drivers may be having problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7497">Upravljački program grafičke kartice uzrokovao je blokadu sustava Office, ali utjecaj te blokade još nije poznat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7497">The user's video card driver has caused Office to hang, but the impact of the hang is not known yet</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7498">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7498">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7499">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – metoda primijenjena na grafičkoj kartici koja je uzrokovala blokadu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7499">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - The method called on the video card that produced the hang</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7500">**Data\_Timeout** – trajanje blokade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7500">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted</span></span>

  #### <a name="officeandroidadalsigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7501">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7501">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7502">Tim se događajem označava da je upit za prijavu stigao korisniku, za školski ili poslovni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7502">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for school or work account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7503">Ovaj događaj pomaže u razumijevanju stanja prijava u našim aplikacijama i poduzima odgovarajuće radnje kada uočimo neočekivane ponovne upite za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7503">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7504">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7504">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7505">**LastLoginDelta** – delta vremena od posljednje uspješne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7505">**LastLoginDelta** - The time delta from last successful login.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7506">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** – označava stanje računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7506">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** - Indicates the state of the account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7507">**PreviousIdentityState** – označava stanje računa, poput isteka sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7507">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7508">**SignInResultCode** – označava kôd rezultata za kraj upita za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7508">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7509">**UseCache** – označava smo li prisilno zatražili korisniku da ponovno unese lozinku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7509">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7510">**UserType** – upućuje na to je li riječ o postojećem računu ili novom računu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7510">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidappdocsfileoperationends"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7511">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7511">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7512">Ključna dokumenta samo za Android (AppDocs) podaci telemetrije za kraj operacija Datoteka/Novo/Spremi kao.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7512">Critical Docs Android Only (AppDocs) telemetry data for File New/Open/SaveAs end operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7513">Ovo bilježi kodove pogrešaka za neuspjehe tih AppDocs operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7513">This captures error codes for failures of these AppDocsOperations.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7514">Microsoft to koristi za identificiranje kvarova u različitim operacijama datoteka i točnog sloja na kojem se kvar dogodio u programu Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7514">Microsoft uses this to identify failures in various file operations and the exact layer at which the failure has occurred in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7515">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7515">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7516">**AccessMode** – vrijednost enumeracije za način pristupa datoteci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7516">**AccessMode** - enumeration value for the access mode for the file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7517">Vrijednost – nema, samo za čitanje, samo za čitanje koja se može nadograditi, za čitanje i pisanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7517">Values- None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7518">**BlockingUIShown** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li blokiranje korisničkog sučelja bilo prikazano bilo gdje u protoku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7518">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7519">**ContentUriAuthority** – autoritet URL-a za sadržaj iz SAF-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7519">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7520">**Correlation** – GUID za ID korelacije koji se odnosi na operaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7520">**Correlation** - GUID for the correlation ID related to the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7521">**DocId** – ID dokumenta koji je generirao AppDocs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7521">**DocId** - the document ID generated by AppDocs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7522">**DocInstanceId** – DocInstanceId ID instance dokumenta koji generira AppDocs koji je obuhvaćen instancom operacije u dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7522">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7523">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li dokument zaštićen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7523">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7524">**DocUserId** – korisnički ID iz MS sloja za autorizaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7524">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7525">**DocUserIdProvider** – enumeracija koja predstavlja davatelja korisničkog ID-a, 0 = Nepoznato, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7525">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user ID provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7526">**DurationInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama do završetka operacije datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7526">**DurationInMs** - time in millisecond for the file operation to end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7527">**EndReason** – vrijednost enumeracije za krajnji razlog.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7527">**EndReason** - enumeration value for the end reason.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7528">Vrijednosti – nema, uspjeh, neuspjeh, odustani</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7528">Values - None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7529">**ErrorCode** – kôd pogreške za operaciju datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7529">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7530">**Extension** – proširenje datoteke koja se otvara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7530">**Extension** - extension of the file being opened.</span></span>
