#### <a name="officeandroidandroidautherror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7553">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7553">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7554">Ovaj događaj označava osnovne pogreške u provjeri autentičnosti za vrijeme tihog osvježavanja tokena, učitavanje stranice za prijavu iz usluge i tako dalje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7554">This event denotes core authentication failures during silent token refresh, loading sign in page from service and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7555">Ovaj događaj pomaže u razumijevanju stanja prijava u našim aplikacijama, pokušajima prijave i poduzima odgovarajuće radnje kada uočimo neočekivane ponovne upite za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7555">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps, sign in attempts that are made, and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected failures.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7556">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7556">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7557">**ADALErrorCode** – označava kôd pogreške prilikom prikazivanja upita za prijavu ili pokušaja dohvaćanja tihog tokena za poslovni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7557">**ADALErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7558">**ADALRawErrorCode** – označava kôd neobrađene pogreške prilikom prikazivanja upita za prijavu ili pokušaja dohvaćanja tihog tokena za poslovni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7558">**ADALRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7559">**ErrorGroup** – označava vrstu računa kao što je osobni račun ili poslovni račun ili lokalni poslovni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7559">**ErrorGroup** - Indicates the type of account like personal account or work account or on-premise work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7560">**IDCRLErrorCode** – označava kôd pogreške prilikom prikazivanja upita za prijavu za osobni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7560">**IDCRLErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7561">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** – označava kôd neobrađene pogreške prilikom prikazivanja upita za prijavu za osobni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7561">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7562">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** – označava kôd pogreške prilikom pokušaja osvježavanja tihog tokena za osobni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7562">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** - Indicates error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7563">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** – označava kôd neobrađene pogreške prilikom pokušaja osvježavanja tihog tokena za osobni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7563">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7564">**NTLMErrorCode** – označava kôd pogreške prilikom prikazivanja upita za prijavu za lokalni poslovni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7564">**NTLMErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for on-premise work account.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidfileasyncsavestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7565">Office.Android.AndroidFileAsyncSaveStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7565">Office.Android.AndroidFileAsyncSaveStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7566">Snima asinkronu datoteku, sprema podatke o statusu i razne kodove pogrešaka iz različitih komponenti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7566">Captures File async save status data and various error codes from different components.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7567">Microsoft koristi ove podatke kako bi analizirao postoji li gubitak korisničkih podataka u aplikaciji tijekom spremanja datoteka u aplikacijama Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7567">Microsoft uses this data to analyze if there is any user data loss in the app during saving of files in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7572">**FileSize** – veličina datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7572">**FileSize** - size of file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7573">**FileSourceLocation** – enumeracija lokacije izvora datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7573">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration for file source location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7574">Vrijednosti: Nema, Lokalno, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, Nepoznati poslužitelj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7574">Values: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7588">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** – posljednja pogreška BSC (usluga binarne pretvorbe) klijenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7588">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7590">**InitializationReason** – enumeracija za ulaznu točku za otvaranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7590">**InitializationReason** - enumeration for the entry point for file open</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidfilesavestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7608">Office.Android.AndroidFileSaveStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7608">Office.Android.AndroidFileSaveStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7609">Ključno za snimanje podataka o statusu spremanja datoteke i razne kodove pogrešaka iz različitih komponenti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7609">Critical to capture File save status data and various error codes from different components.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7610">Microsoft koristi ove podatke kako bi analizirao postoji li gubitak korisničkih podataka u aplikaciji tijekom spremanja datoteka u aplikacijama Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7610">Microsoft uses this data to analyze if there is any user data loss in the app during saving of files in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficeactivationlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7637">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7637">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7638">Ključni podaci za prikupljanje sveobuhvatnog vremena otvaranja datoteka za sva otvaranja datoteka u aplikacijama sustava Windows, Excel i PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7638">Critical data to collect end-to-end file open time for all file opens in Windows, Excel, PowerPoint apps.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7639">To koristi Microsoft da bi saznao metriku performansi otvaranja datoteke naših aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7639">This is used by Microsoft to find out the metric for file open performance of our apps</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7640">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7640">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7641">**Appbootingocod** – Booleova vrijednost da biste provjerili je li dovršeno pokretanje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7641">**AppBootingOccured** - Boolean to check if app boot is complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7642">**ApplicationBootTime** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7642">**ApplicationBootTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7643">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Booleova vrijednost koja provjerava je li aplikacija obustavljena tijekom pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7643">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to check if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7644">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li postojao bilo koji dijaloški okvir blokiranja tijekom operacije otvaranja datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7644">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7645">**CachedInfoAvailable** – Booleova vrijednost za traženje predmemoriranih informacija koje su specifične za otvaranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7645">**CachedInfoAvailable** - Boolean to look for cached info specific to file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7646">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li dokument na čekanju za oporavak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7646">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if there was a document pending for recovery</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7647">**EndToEndActivationTime** – vrijeme potrebno za prikazivanje datoteke za datoteke otvorene izvan aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7647">**EndToEndActivationTime** - time taken to render the file for files opened from outside the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7648">**EndToEndFileOpenTime** – vrijeme potrebno za prikazivanje datoteke za datoteke otvorene unutar aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7648">**EndToEndFileOpenTime** - time taken to render the file for files opened from inside the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7649">**FileOpenPhaseDurationInMs** – vrijeme operacije otvaranja datoteke koje koriste specifične faze</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7649">**FileOpenPhaseDurationInMs** - file open operation time consumed by specific phase</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7650">**FileSourceLocation** – vrijednost enumeracije za lokaciju datoteke kao što su Nema, Lokalno, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7650">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for File location such as None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7651">**InitalizationReason** – ulazna točka za otvaranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7651">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7652">**InitialBootPhaseTime** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7652">**InitialBootPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7653">**IsThisFirstLaunch** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li ovo prvo pokretanje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7653">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is the first launch of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7654">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7654">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7655">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7655">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7656">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7656">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7657">**PostAppInitTimeInMs** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7657">**PostAppInitTimeInMs** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7658">**PPTRenderPhase** – vrijeme povezano s određenom fazom u PPT renderiranju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7658">**PPTRenderPhase** - time related to specific phase in PPT rendering</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7659">**PreAppInitTimeInMs** – vrijeme potrebno tijekom određene faze pokretanja aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7659">**PreAppInitTimeInMs** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7660">**ProviderApp** – naziv paketa aplikacije iz koje se datoteka otvara</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7660">**ProviderApp** - the package name of the app from which file is opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7661">**TelemetryReason** – slično je vrijednosti InitialisationReason, no to je vrijednost enumeracije s više detalja koje se odnose na ulaznu točku za otvaranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7661">**TelemetryReason** - similar to InitialisationReason, but more detailed enumeration value regarding the entry point for File open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7662">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li postojao bilo koji dijaloški okvir za blokiranje tijekom pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7662">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7663">**XLRenderPhase** – vrijeme koje se odnosi na specifičnu fazu prikazivanja u programu Excel.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7663">**XLRenderPhase** - time related to specific phase in Excel rendering</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidappdocsfileoperationends"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7664">Office.Android.AppDocsFileOperationEnds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7664">Office.Android.AppDocsFileOperationEnds</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7665">Ključna dokumenta samo za Android (AppDocs) podaci telemetrije za kraj operacija Datoteka/Novo/Spremi kao.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7665">Critical Docs Android Only (AppDocs) telemetry data for File New/Open/SaveAs end operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7666">Ovo bilježi kodove pogrešaka za neuspjehe tih AppDocs operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7666">This captures error codes for failures of these AppDocsOperations.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7667">Microsoft to koristi za identificiranje kvarova u različitim operacijama datoteka i točnog sloja na kojem se kvar dogodio u programu Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7667">Microsoft uses this to identify failures in various file operations and the exact layer at which the failure has occurred in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7668">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7668">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7669">**AccessMode** – vrijednost enumeracije za način pristupa datoteci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7669">**AccessMode** - enumeration value for the access mode for the file.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7670">Vrijednost: nema, samo za čitanje, samo za čitanje koja se može nadograditi, za čitanje i pisanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7670">Values: None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7671">**BlockingUIShown** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li blokiranje korisničkog sučelja bilo prikazano bilo gdje u protoku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7671">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7672">**ContentUriAuthority** – autoritet URL-a za sadržaj iz SAF-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7672">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7673">**Correlation** – GUID za ID korelacije koji se odnosi na operaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7673">**Correlation** - GUID for the correlation ID related to the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7674">**DocId** – ID dokumenta koji je generirao AppDocs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7674">**DocId** - the document ID generated by AppDocs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7675">**DocInstanceId** – DocInstanceId ID instance dokumenta koji generira AppDocs koji je obuhvaćen instancom operacije u dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7675">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7676">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li dokument zaštićen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7676">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7677">**DocUserId** – korisnički ID iz MS sloja za autorizaciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7677">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7678">**DocUserIdProvider** – enumeracija koja predstavlja davatelja korisničkog ID-a, 0 = Nepoznato, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7678">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user ID provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7679">**DurationInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama do završetka operacije datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7679">**DurationInMs** - time in milliseconds for the file operation to end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7680">**EndReason** – vrijednost enumeracije za krajnji razlog.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7680">**EndReason** - enumeration value for the end reason.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7681">Vrijednosti: nema, uspjeh, neuspjeh, odustani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7681">Values: None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7682">**ErrorCode** – kôd pogreške za operaciju datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7682">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7683">**Extension** – prva četiri znaka proširenja datoteke koja se otvara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7683">**Extension** - first four characters of the extension of the file being opened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7684">**FileSourceLocation** – vrijednost enumeracije lokacije datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7684">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for file location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7685">Moguće vrijednosti: Nema, Lokalno, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, Nepoznati poslužitelj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7685">Possible values: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7686">**FILETIME** – vrijeme događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7686">**FILETIME** - Time of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7687">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** – informacije o kodu pogreške povezane s pretvorbama datoteka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7687">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** - Error code information related to file conversions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7688">**HttpStatusCode** – HTTP kôd odgovora za zahtjev web usluge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7688">**HttpStatusCode** - HTTP response code for web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7689">**InitalizationReason** – ulazna točka za otvaranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7689">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7690">**K2FileIOHresult** – Hresult kôd za kraj operacije otvaranja datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7690">**K2FileIOHresult** - Hresult code for File open operation end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7691">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** – posljednja pogreška BSC (usluga binarne pretvorbe) klijenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7691">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidauthaceerrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7706">Office. Android. AuthACEErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7706">Office.Android.AuthACEErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7707">Taj događaj koristi Microsoftov račun (MSA) za određivanje korisnika koji se pokušava prijaviti u aplikaciju te tijekom čega se telemetrija u raspravi pokreće kao dio neuspješnog pokušaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7707">This event uses the Microsoft Account (MSA) to determine which user is attempting to sign in to the app and during that which telemetry in discussion is getting triggered as part of an unsuccessful attempt.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7708">Ovaj događaj omogućuje analizu raspodjele pogrešaka kod prijave na MSA, što pomaže u razumijevanju razloga neuspješne prijave na MSA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7708">This event helps with MSA sign-in error distribution analysis, which helps in understanding reasons behind unsuccessful MSA sign-in flow end.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7709">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7709">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7710">**ExceptionsName** – označava klase iznimki koje se javljaju za vrijeme tijeka prijave na Microsoftov račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7710">**ExceptionsName** - indicates exception classes with regard to exception tags that occur during Microsoft account sign-in flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7711">**ExceptionsTag** – upućuje na to koje se iznimke prisutne u uniji pojavljuju za tijek prijave na MSA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7711">**ExceptionsTag** - indicates which inflow exceptions present in union are occurring for MSA-sign in flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7712">**IDCRLACEEErrorCode** – prikazuje kôd pogreške koji se pojavljuje za vrijeme tijeka prijave na MSA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7712">**IDCRLACEErrorCode** - Gives error code occurring during MSA sign-in flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7713">Različiti kodovi pogrešaka navedeni na %SRCROOT%\identity\coreapi\public\IdentityData.h</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7713">Different error codes mentioned at %SRCROOT%\identity\coreapi\public\IdentityData.h</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7714">**IDCRLAuthenticationStatusErrorCode** – označava kôdove pogrešaka za nevaljani status rezultata provjere autentičnosti koji dolazi sa Microsoftova računa (MSA).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7714">**IDCRLAuthenticationStatusErrorCode** - Indicates error codes for invalid status of Authentication result coming from Microsoft Account (MSA).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7715">**IDCRLUserInteractionMissingError** – upućuje na to je li tijek prijave na Microsoftov račun (MSA) pozvan sa zastavicom showUI kao lažan koji uzrokuje pozitivni rezultat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7715">**IDCRLUserInteractionMissingError** - Indicates if Microsoft Account (MSA) sign-in flow invoked with showUI flag as false causing the hit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7721">**FileExtension** – prva četiri znaka proširenja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7721">**FileExtension** - First four characters of the extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7722">**IsFileDirty** – Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li u datoteci bilo nespremljenih promjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7722">**IsFileDirty** - Boolean to indicate if there were unsaved changes in the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7723">**Location** – enumeracija lokacije datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7723">**Location** - File location enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7724">Vrijednosti: OneDrive, SharePoint, Dropbox, itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7724">Values: OneDrive, SharePoint, Dropbox, Others</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7725">**PDFConversionError** – Oznaka pri kojoj dolazi do pogreške za pretvorbu PDF-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7725">**PDFConversionError** - Tag at which error occurs for PDF conversion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7726">**PdfConversionErrorCode** – kôd pogreške za pretvorbu PDF dokumenata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7726">**PdfConversionErrorCode** - PDF conversion error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7727">**PdfConversionHRStatus** – kôd statusa pretvorbe PDF-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7727">**PdfConversionHRStatus** - PDF conversion status code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7728">**PdfConversionResult** – enumeracija rezultata PDF pretvorbe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7728">**PdfConversionResult** - PDF Conversion result enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7729">Vrijednosti: „Success"; „Failed" i „Canceled"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7729">Values: "Success", "Failed" and "Canceled"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7730">**PdfFileSize** – veličina PDF-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7730">**PdfFileSize** - Size of the PDF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7747">**PurchaseOrderId** – identifikator narudžbenice iz Google/Samsung trgovine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7747">**PurchaseOrderId** - Purchase order identifier from Google/Samsung store</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7748">**RedemptionTaskHR** – HResult za zadatak aktivacije pretplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7748">**RedemptionTaskHR** - HResult for redemption task of subscription</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7749">**SubscriptionProvisioningSucceeded** – Booleova vrijednost za uspješan rezultat dodjele pretplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7749">**SubscriptionProvisioningSucceeded** - Boolean for subscription provisioning result success</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroiddbfailurecause"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7753">Office.Android.DBFailureCause</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7753">Office.Android.DBFailureCause</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7754">Telemetrija ključne pogreške za pogreške u bazi podataka tijekom pregledavanja datoteka i dodavanje mjesta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7754">Critical Error telemetry for Database Failure while file browsing and adds places.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7755">Microsoft to upotrebljava za prepoznavanje problema s oštećenjem DB-a u aplikacijama koje mogu ometati korisnika da dodaje mjesta ili ih pregledava unutar aplikacije u aplikacijama Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7755">Microsoft uses this to identify DB corruption issues in the apps which might hinder user to add places or browse through them from within the app in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7756">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7756">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7757">**ErrorAt** – Vrijednost oznake: informacije o mjestu na kojem je došlo do pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7757">**ErrorAt** - Tag Value: Information about the place where the Failure happened</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfileserrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7759">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7759">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7760">Ekspanzijske datoteke za komplet datoteka sustava Android (APK) za mobilnu aplikaciju Office jesu dopunske datoteke resursa koje razvojni programeri aplikacija na sustavu Android mogu objaviti zajedno sa svojom aplikacijom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7760">Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app are supplementary resource files that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7761">Da bismo svoj mehanizam preuzimanja ekspanzijskih datoteka učinili pouzdanijim, bilježimo razlog pogrešaka koje nastupe bilo tijekom preuzimanja ekspanzijskih datoteka ili čitanja preuzetih ekspanzijskih datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7761">To make our Expansion files download mechanism more reliable, we are logging the cause of errors that occur either in downloading the expansion files or while reading the downloaded expansion files.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7762">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7762">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7763">**Data_ClassName** – tekst koji predstavlja naziv datoteke izvornog koda u kojem je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7763">**Data_ClassName** - Text representing the source code file name where there is an error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7764">**Data_ErrorMessage** – tekst koji predstavlja operaciju koja nije uspjela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7764">**Data_ErrorMessage** - Text representing the operation that has failed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7765">**Data_ExceptionMessage** – neobavezno tekstno polje koje predstavlja razlog iznimke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7765">**Data_ExceptionMessage** - An optional text field representing the cause of the exception.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7766">**Data_ExceptionType** – neobavezno tekstno polje koje predstavlja naziv iznimke izbačene iz izvornog koda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7766">**Data_ExceptionType** - An optional text field representing the name of the exception thrown from source code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7767">**Data_MethodName** – tekst koji predstavlja naziv metode u izvornom kodu u kojem je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7767">**Data_MethodName** - Text representing the method name in source code where there is an error.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryextractionerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7768">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExtractionError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7768">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExtractionError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7769">Da biste smanjili veličinu aplikacija sustava Office i Android, primjenjujemo kompresiju na resurse u konačnom paketu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7769">To reduce the size of Office Android apps, we apply compression to the resources in the final package.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7770">Za vrijeme izvođenja te resurse prvo izdvojimo prije nego što ih upotrijebimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7770">At run time, we first extract these resources before using them.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7771">Ponekad ima neočekivanih pogrešaka tijekom izdvajanja, što dovodi do rušenja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7771">Sometimes there are unexpected errors while performing extractions, which leads to app crashes.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7772">Kroz ovaj događaj prikupljamo neke dijagnostičke informacije vezane uz izdvajanje, kao što je naziv resursa koji se izdvaja, put gdje je izdvojen, itd., besplatni raspoloživi prostor na disku itd. Ti se podaci prikupljaju samo kada se pojave pogreške u izdvajanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7772">Through this event we are collecting some diagnostic information related to extraction, like name of the resource being extracted, path where its extracted etc., free disk space available etc. This data is collected only when there are extraction errors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7773">Ove podatke upotrebljavamo kako bismo shvatili uzrok neuspjelih izdvajanja te unaprijedili korisnički doživljaj naših aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7773">We use this data to understand the cause of extraction failures, and to improve the user experience of our apps.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7777">**Data_ArchiveSizeKB** – naziv resursa koji se izdvaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7777">**Data_ArchiveSizeKB** - Size of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7778">**Data_ClassName** – naziv datoteke u izvornom kodu gdje je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7778">**Data_ClassName** - File name in source code where the error is encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7782">**Data_FreeDiskSpaceMB** – količina slobodnog diskovnog prostora dostupnog na uređaju mjerenog u mega bajtovima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7782">**Data_FreeDiskSpaceMB** - The amount of free disk space available on the device measured in Mega Bytes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7896">Telemetrija kritične pogreške za praćenje neuspjeha u aktiviranju licenci za račune sustava Office 365 u aplikacijama Word, Excel ili PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7896">Critical Error telemetry to track failures to activate licenses for Office 365 accounts in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7897">Microsoft to upotrebljava za analiziranje neuspjeha pri aktiviranju kupljene licence Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7897">Microsoft uses this to analyze failures to activate a purchased Office 365 license.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7900">**HResult** – kôd pogreške za neuspjeh</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7900">**HResult** - error code for the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7901">**IsGallatin** – Booleova vrijednost da provjerite je li to Gallatin račun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7901">**IsGallatin** - Boolean to check if it is a Gallatin account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7902">**MessageCode** – enumeracija za označavanje mjesta neuspjeha za aktiviranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7902">**MessageCode** - enumeration to indicate the point of failure for activation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7903">**PreviousEntryPoint** – enumeracija ulazne točke za pokretanje tijeka aktivacije licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7903">**PreviousEntryPoint** - Entrypoint enumeration for triggering the license activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7904">**StateAfterActivation** – enumeracija koja upućuje na stanje licenciranja aplikacije prije nego što je započeo tijek aktivacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7904">**StateAfterActivation** - enumeration to indicate licensing state of the app before the activation flow started</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidmsasigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7907">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7907">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7908">Tim se događajem označava da je upit za prijavu stigao korisniku, za osobni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7908">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for personal account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7909">Ovaj događaj pomaže u razumijevanju stanja prijava u našim aplikacijama i poduzima odgovarajuće radnje kada uočimo neočekivane ponovne upite za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7909">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7910">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7910">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7911">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** – kôd pogreške pokušaja osvježavanja tokena prije prikazivanja upita za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7911">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** - Error code of token refresh attempt, before showing sign-in prompt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7912">**LastLoginDelta** – delta vremena od posljednje uspješne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7912">**LastLoginDelta** - The time delta from last successful login.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7913">**MSAserverUAID** – ID korelacije s telemetrijskim podacima usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7913">**MSAserverUAID** - Correlation ID with service telemetry data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7914">**PreviousIdentityState** – označava stanje računa, poput isteka sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7914">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7915">**SignInResultCode** – označava kôd rezultata za kraj upita za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7915">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7916">**UseCache** – označava smo li prisilno zatražili korisniku da ponovno unese lozinku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7916">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7917">**UserType** – upućuje na to je li riječ o postojećem računu ili novom računu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7917">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7918">**WasIdentitySignedOut** – upućuje na to je li račun bio u odjavljenom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7918">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - Indicates if account was in signed out state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7948">Ta informacija za izvješćivanje o iznimkama važna je za procjenu ukupnog stanja grafičkog stoga i identifikaciju dijelova koda u kojima često dolazi do neuspjeha kako bi se odredili prioriteti istrage.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7948">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency, in order to prioritize investigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7949">Ta informacija za izvješćivanje o iznimkama važna je za procjenu ukupnog stanja grafičkog stoga i identifikaciju dijelova koda u kojima često dolazi do neuspjeha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7949">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, and identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7950">To inženjeru pomaže utvrditi koji neuspjesi pri vizualizaciji zahvaćaju najveći broj korisnika te nam omogućuje odrediti prioritete istrage da bismo riješili one probleme od kojih će korisnici imati najviše koristi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7950">This helps an engineer to determine which rendering failures are impacting the most users, enabling us to prioritize our investigations toward fixing issues that will have the greatest user benefit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7951">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7951">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7952">**Data\_HResult** – kod pogreške koji je neuspjeh vratio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7952">**Data\_HResult** - The error code returned from failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7953">**Data\_TagCount** – broj svih neuspjeha do kojih je došlo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7953">**Data\_TagCount** - The count of each failure that occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7954">**Data\_TagID** – identifikator neuspjeha do kojeg je došlo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7954">**Data\_TagID** - The identifier of the failure that occurred</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7968">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult i Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning prikupljaju se kada otkrijemo oštećenje u korisnikovoj PST/OST datoteci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7968">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult and Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning are collected when we detect corruption in a user's PST/OST.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7969">Kada prepoznamo oštećenje, Microsoft prikuplja oblik baze podataka, mjesto na kojem ga je otkrio i malu količinu konteksta oštećenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7969">When we detect corruption, Microsoft collects the format of the database, the place where detected it, and a small amount of context about the corruption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7970">Oštećenje OST-a/PST-a korisnicima onemogućuje pristup njihovoj e-pošti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7970">OST/PST corruption prevents users from accessing their emails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7971">Aktivno nadziremo ima li u tim podacima neuobičajenih aktivnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7971">We actively monitor this data for anomalous activity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7972">Nastojimo istražiti i dijagnosticirati probleme da bismo ograničili gubitak korisničkih podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7972">We aim to investigate and diagnose issues to limit loss of customer data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7973">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7973">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7974">**0 –** naziv procesa koji je prijavio oštećenje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7974">**0 -** The Process name that reported corruption</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7975">**1 –** Booleova vrijednost koja označava je li korisnik odabrao novu datoteku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7975">**1 -** Bool indicating if the user chooses new file or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7976">**2 –** broj drugih procesa koji su otvorili bazu podataka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7976">**2 -** the number of other processes that have the database open</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopndbcorruptstorewarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-7977">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7977">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-7983">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7983">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7985">**Context** – kontekst oštećenog spremišta, gdje je oštećenje otkriveno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7985">**Context** - Corrupt Store Context, where corruption was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7987">**Details** – pojedinosti o rušenju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7987">**Details** – Details about the crash</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7988">**NdbType** – vrsta spremišta, može biti 0 = NdbUndefined, 1 = NdbSmall, 2 = NdbLarge, 3 = NdbTardis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7988">**NdbType** - Store Type, can be 0 = NdbUndefined, 1 = NdbSmall, 2 = NdbLarge, 3 = NdbTardis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7989">**ProcessName** – naziv procesa koji je uzrokovao oštećenje spremišta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7989">**ProcessName** - Process Name causing the store to get corrupted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7990">**PstVersion** – verzija datoteke MSPST32.DLL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7990">**PstVersion** - Version of the MSPST32.DLL</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-7991">**Version** – verzija oblika datoteke spremišta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-7991">**Version** - Version of store file format</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8094">**FirstTimeStamp** – prvi put kada je došlo do pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8094">**FirstTimeStamp** - The first time at which the error occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8095">**Trackback** – jedinstveni identifikator određene pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8095">**Trackback** - A unique identifier for a specific error</span></span>

#### <a name="officesystemsystemhealtherrorswithtag"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8096">Office.System.SystemHealthErrorsWithTag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8096">Office.System.SystemHealthErrorsWithTag</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8097">Koristi se za identifikaciju problema u pokrenutoj aplikaciji koji utječu na korisnike te se mogu manifestirati u obliku rušenja ili smanjene funkcionalnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8097">Used to identify customer impacting issues within the running app that may manifest as crashes or degraded functionality.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8098">Bilježi pogreške do kojih je došlo tijekom izvođenja procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8098">Records errors that occur during process runtime.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8099">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8099">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8100">**Count** – broj pojavljivanja svake od pogrešaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8100">**Count** - The count of each error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8102">**ErrorCode** – identifikator pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8102">**ErrorCode** – An identifier for the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8103">**ErrorGroup** – identifikator grupiranja za svaku pogrešku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8103">**ErrorGroup** - A bucketing identifier for each error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8104">**ErrorId** – identifikator pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8104">**ErrorId** – An identifier for the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8105">**FirstTimeStamp** – prvi put kada je došlo do pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8105">**FirstTimeStamp** - The first time at which the error occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8106">**Trackback** – jedinstveni identifikator određene pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8106">**Trackback** - A unique identifier for a specific error</span></span>

#### <a name="renewidentityfailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8107">RenewIdentityFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8107">RenewIdentityFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8108">Prikuplja se kada korisnik pokuša otvoriti dokument zaštićen IRM-om ili primijeniti zaštite IRM-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8108">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8109">Sadrži informacije potrebne za pravilno istraživanje i dijagnosticiranje problema do kojih dolazi kada obnavljanje korisničkih certifikata nije bilo uspješno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8109">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when failed to renew user certificates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8110">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8110">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8111">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hijerarhija klijenata koja označava da aplikacija radi u proizvodnom okruženju ili okruženju za razvojne inženjere</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8111">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy, which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8112">**AppInfo.Name** – naziv aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8112">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8113">**AppInfo.Version** – verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8113">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8114">**Failure.Category** – kategorija pogreške „UnhandledError”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8114">**Failure.Category** - The category of the failure "UnhandledError"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8115">**Failure.Detail** – detaljne informacije o pogrešci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8115">**Failure.Detail** - The detailed info of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8116">**Failure.Id** – identifikacijski broj pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8116">**Failure.Id** - Failure ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8117">**Failure.Signature** – potpis pogreške koji je jednak nazivu događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8117">**Failure.Signature** - The signature of the failure, which is same as the event name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8118">**iKey** – identifikacijski broj poslužitelja pružatelja usluge zapisivanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8118">**iKey** - Logging service server ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8119">**RMS.HRESULT** – rezultat obnavljanja korisničkog certifikata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8119">**RMS.HRESULT** - The result of renewing user certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8120">**RMS.ScenarioId** – identifikacijski broj scenarija koji definira klijent usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8120">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario ID defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8121">**RMS.SDKVersion** – verzija klijenta usluge upravljanja pravima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8121">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

#### <a name="saveerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8122">save.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8122">save.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8123">Omogućuje nam otkrivanje i rješavanje situacija u kojima je došlo do pogreške kada ste pokušali spremiti datoteku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8123">Allows us to detect and fix situations where there was an error when you attempted to save a file.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8124">On prati pogreške uzrokovane neuspješnim spremanjem datoteke, uključujući opisnu poruku o pogrešci kako bi nam pomogao riješiti problem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8124">It tracks errors caused by failures to save a file, including a descriptive error message to help us resolve the issue.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8125">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8125">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8126">**error** – vrsta pogreške koja je nastupila kako bi nam pomogao otkriti i riješiti probleme u vezi s određenom vrstom pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8126">**error** - The type of error that happened to help us detect and resolve issues related to a specific error type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8127">**file_type** – vrsta datoteke koju je korisnik pokušao spremiti (primjerice .doc)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8127">**file_type** - The type of file the user tried to save (such as .doc)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8128">**origin** – odakle pokušaj spremanja potječe (primjerice iz poruke e-pošte) kako bismo mogli prepoznati probleme u vezi sa spremanjem datoteke s određenog mjesta u aplikaciji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8128">**origin** - Where the file save attempt originated from (such as from an email) so we can detect issues associated with saving a file from a specific place in the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8129">**token_type** – vrsta tokena korištenog za provjeru autentičnosti radi spremanja datoteka koji nam pomaže prepoznati probleme s provjerom autentičnosti u vezi sa spremanjem datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8129">**token_type** - the type of token used to authenticate the account in order to save the file to help us detect authentication issues associated with saving a file</span></span>

#### <a name="wkwebviewerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8130">wkwebview.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8130">wkwebview.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8131">Ovaj nam događaj omogućuje utvrđivanje kada su se pogreške s web-prikazom pojavile pri sastavljanju ili čitanju poruke e-pošte kako bismo mogli izbjeći probleme koji bi mogli uzrokovati nemogućnost sastavljanja ili čitanja poruke e-pošte aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8131">This event lets us detect when web view errors occurred when composing or reading email so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app can’t compose email or read email.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8132">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8132">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8133">**description** – opis pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8133">**description** - description for the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8134">**error_code** – kôd pogreške za WKError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8134">**error_code** - error code for WKError</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8135">**function_name** – naziv JavaScript funkcije kada dođe do pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8135">**function_name** - JavaScript function name when error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8136">**js_exception_column_number** – broj stupca u kojemu se pojavila iznimka JavaScripta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8136">**js_exception_column_number** - The column number where JavaScript exception occurred</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8137">**js_exception_line_number** – broj retka u kojemu se pojavila iznimka JavaScripta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8137">**js_exception_line_number** - The line number where JavaScript exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8138">**js_exception_message** – poruka o iznimci kada se iznimka JavaScripta pojavila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8138">**js_exception_message** - The exception message when JavaScript exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8139">**js_exception_source_url** – izvorišni URL u kojemu se iznimka JavaScripta pojavila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8139">**js_exception_source_url** - The source URL where JavaScript exception occurred</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8140">**scenario** – gdje se pogreška pojavila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8140">**scenario** - where the error occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8141">To je numeracija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8141">It’s an enum.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8142">Possible values are old_renderer, react_renderer, and composing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8142">Possible values are old_renderer, react_renderer, and composing.</span></span>

#### <a name="wkwebviewterminate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8143">wkwebview.terminate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8143">wkwebview.terminate</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8144">Taj nam događaj omogućuje prepoznavanje kada je sustav prekinuo web-prikaz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8144">This event allows us to detect when web view is terminated by the system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8145">Ti nam podaci omogućuju praćenje pogreške koje je korisnik naišao prilikom sastavljanja ili čitanja poruke e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8145">This data allows us to monitor the error user encountered when composing or reading an email.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8146">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8146">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8147">**is_foreground** – bez obzira na to je li aplikacija u prvom planu kada se događaj dogodi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8147">**is_foreground** - whether app is in foreground when this event happens.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8148">**Scenario** – gdje se pogreška pojavila, prilikom prikazivanja ili sastavljanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8148">**Scenario** - where the error occurred, when rendering or composing.</span></span>


## <a name="device-connectivity-and-configuration-data-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8149">Događaji koji se odnose na povezivost i konfiguracijske podatke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8149">Device connectivity and configuration data events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8150">Ovo su podvrste podataka u toj kategoriji:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8150">The following are the data subtypes in this category:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8151">Povezivost i konfiguracija uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8151">Device connectivity and configuration</span></span>](#device-connectivity-and-configuration-subtype)


### <a name="device-connectivity-and-configuration-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8152">*Podvrsta događaja koji se odnose na povezivost i konfiguraciju uređaja*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8152">*Device connectivity and configuration subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8153">Stanje mrežne veze i postavke uređaja, kao što je memorija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8153">Network connection state and device settings, such as memory.</span></span>

#### <a name="applicationdidreceivememorywarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8154">application.did.receive.memory.warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8154">application.did.receive.memory.warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8155">Ovaj se događaj šalje kada nam Apple kaže da aplikaciji ponestaje memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8155">This event is sent when Apple tells us that the application is running out of memory.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8156">On nam govori da smo uveli problem s upravljanjem memorijom na vašem uređaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8156">It tells us that we have introduced an issue with memory management on your device.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8157">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8157">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8158">**current_memory_used** – govori nam količinu memorije koju je aplikacija koristila u trenutku kad je aplikaciji ponestalo memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8158">**current_memory_used** - Tells us the amount of memory used by the application at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8159">**current_memory_used_percentage** – govori nam postotak memorije koju je aplikacija koristila među ukupnom dostupnom memorijom u trenutku kad je aplikaciji ponestalo memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8159">**current_memory_used_percentage** - Tell us the percentage of memory used by the application out of the total memory available at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8160">**currentVC** – govori nam prikaz koji se trenutno prikazuje kad aplikaciji ponestane memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8160">**currentVC** - Tells us the view that is currently showing when the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8161">**has_hx** – govori nam da račun koristi naš novi servis sinkronizacije kako bi nam pomogao prepoznati probleme uzrokovane našim servisom sinkronizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8161">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8162">**is_watch_app_installed** – govori nam koristi li korisnik trenutno uređaj Apple Watch te je li on instaliran kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti negativan utjecaj na funkciju zbog uređaja Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8162">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is installed to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8163">**is_watch_paired** – govori nam koristi li korisnik trenutno uređaj Apple Watch te je li on uparen s uređajem kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti negativan utjecaj na funkciju zbog uređaja Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8163">**is_watch_paired** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is paired with the device to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8164">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – govori nam koristi li korisnik trenutno uređaj Apple Watch te je li on aktivan kako bi nam pomogao razumjeti negativan utjecaj na funkciju zbog uređaja Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8164">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is active to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8165">**rn_initialized** – govori nam je li stavka React Native bila pokrenuta u trenutku kad je aplikaciji ponestalo memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8165">**rn_initialized** - Tell us if React Native has been initialized at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8166">**running_time** – govori nam količinu vremena koju je aplikacija provela na pokretanje u trenutku kad je aplikaciji ponestalo memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8166">**running_time** - Tell us the amount of time that app has spent running at the time the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

#### <a name="conversationmemoryleak"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8167">conversation.memory.leak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8167">conversation.memory.leak</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8168">Omogućuje nam otkrivanje situacija u kojima naš razgovor poruka e-pošte uzrokuje korištenje više memorije na vašem uređaju od očekivanog.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8168">Allows us to detect situations where our email conversation view is causing us to use up more memory on your device that expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8169">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8169">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8170">Ne prikupljaju se nikakva polja ni dodatni podaci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8170">No fields or added data are collected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8171">Prikupljaju se samo zapisnici ako postoji curenje memorije u vezi s niti razgovora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8171">Only logs are collected if there is a memory leak related to a conversation thread.</span></span>

#### <a name="coredatacorruption"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8172">core.data.corruption</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8172">core.data.corruption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8173">Omogućuje nam otkrivanje situacija u kojima vam ne možemo prikazati vaše poruke e-pošte ili kalendar jer je mjesto na kojem spremamo e-poštu na vašem uređaju postalo oštećeno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8173">Allows us to detect situations where we cannot show you your email or calendar because where we store your email on your device has become corrupted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8174">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8174">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8175">**errorSource** – označava je li došlo iz radnje spremanja ili kreiranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8175">**errorSource** - indicates whether it came from a save or create action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8176">**sqlError** – numerički kod pogreške naveden u https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/c_abort.html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8176">**sqlError** - numerical error code listed at https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/c_abort.html</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8178">Omogućuje nam prepoznavanje situacija u kojima ste izbrisali ili vratili izvorne postavke svog računa u našoj aplikaciji i kada je to bilo uzrokovano oštećenjem podataka e-pošte koje smo pohranili na vašem uređaju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8178">Allows us to detect situations where you have deleted or reset your account in our app and it was caused by a corruption in email data we've stored on your device.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistdriverupdated"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8220">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8220">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8221">Korisnik je ažurirao upravljački program grafičke kartice koji je prije uzrokovao rušenje sustava Office te se zbog toga više ne koristi za vizualizaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8221">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8222">Obavještava Microsoft da su korisnici koji su jednom bili u neoptimalnom stanju prikazivanja ponovno u preporučenom stanju prikazivanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8222">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a suboptimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8223">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8223">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8224">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** – verzija upravljačkog programa koja je na popisu za blokiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8224">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8225">**Data\_DeviceId** – identifikator uređaja grafičke kartice koji je na popisu za blokiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8225">**Data\_DeviceId** -identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8226">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** – verzija ažuriranog upravljačkog programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8226">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8227">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8227">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8228">Pojedinosti o upravljačkom programu korisnikove grafičke kartice koji je uzrokovao veći broj nedavnih rušenja aplikacija sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8228">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8229">Office neće koristiti tu grafičku karticu u ovoj sesiji sustava Office (umjesto nje koristit će softversku vizualizaciju) dok se upravljački program ne ažurira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8229">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8230">Obavještava Microsoft o upravljačkim programima grafičke kartice koji uzrokuju probleme u sustavu Office radi prepoznavanja trendova i analize utjecaja takvih upravljačkih programa na korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8230">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8231">Microsoftu govori koliko je korisnika u tom suboptimalnom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8231">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this suboptimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8232">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8232">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8233">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** – jesu li sve aplikacije sustava Office na popisu za blokiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8233">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8234">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** – identifikator uređaja grafičke kartice koji je na popisu za blokiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8234">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8235">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** – verzija upravljačkog programa koja je na popisu za blokiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8235">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8236">**Data\_CrashHistory** – niz koji predstavlja povijest upravljačkog programa grafičke kartice koji je uzrokovao rušenje, za potrebe analize</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8236">**Data\_CrashHistory** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8237">**Data\_SecsBetweenCrashes** – koliko često dolazi do rušenja upravljačkog programa kartice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8237">**Data\_SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacewincompisenabled"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8238">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceWinCompIsEnabled</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8238">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceWinCompIsEnabled</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8239">Koristi li se najnovija platforma niske razine za vizualizaciju u sustavu Office, koja se temelji na platformi Windows Composition.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8239">Whether the latest Office low-level rendering platform based on Windows Composition is being used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8240">Dok se najnovija platforma niske razine za vizualizaciju u sustavu Office razvija i počinje distribuirati korisnicima, to Microsoftu omogućuje uvid u broj korisnika koji koriste pojedinu verziju kako se na platformi ne bi pojavile programske pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8240">As the latest Office low-level rendering platform is developed and begins to be released to customers, this allows Microsoft to see how many users are on each version to ensure the platform remains bug-free.</span></span>
