  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8242">**Data\_WinCompEnabled** – koristi li se pozadinski sustav utemeljen na platformi Windows Composition</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8242">**Data\_WinCompEnabled** -Whether the Windows Composition-based backend is in use</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorblocklistapp"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8243">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8243">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8244">Otkriveno je da korisnikova grafička kartica uzrokuje dugačke ili nepopravljive blokade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8244">User's video card has been detected as causing long or unrecoverable hangs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8245">Office neće koristiti tu grafičku karticu u ovoj sesiji sustava Office (umjesto nje koristit će softversku vizualizaciju) dok se upravljački program ne ažurira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8245">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8246">Obavještava Microsoft o upravljačkim programima grafičke kartice koji uzrokuju probleme u sustavu Office radi prepoznavanja trendova i analize utjecaja takvih upravljačkih programa na korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8246">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8247">Također, pridonosi informiranju o broju korisnika u tom suboptimalnom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8247">Also helps in informing how many users are in this suboptimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8248">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8248">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8249">**Data\_AppName** – u kojoj je aplikaciji došlo do blokade upravljačkog programa grafičke kartice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8249">**Data\_AppName** - Which app has encountered video card driver hangs</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorregistrywrite"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8250">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8250">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8251">Office je utvrdio da je korisnikov upravljački program grafičke kartice uzrokovao blokadu koju treba analizirati prilikom sljedećeg pokretanja aplikacije sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8251">Office has identified that the user's video card driver has caused a hang that should be analyzed at the next Office application boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8252">Koristi se da bi se utvrdilo bi li korištenje drugog upravljačkog programa ili prilagodnika grafičke kartice nudilo bolji korisnički doživljaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8252">Used to determine whether using a different video card driver or adapter would offer a better user experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8253">Kada opazi uzorke, Microsoft će možda provesti određene prilagodbe da bi doživljaj korištenja sustava Office ostao što je moguće ugodniji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8253">As patterns occur, Microsoft may make adjustments to keep the Office experience as smooth as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8254">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8254">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8255">**Data\_HangDetected** – je li otkrivena blokada</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8255">**Data\_HangDetected** - Whether a hang was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8256">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – koji je vizualizacijski poziv Office uputio grafičkoj kartici kada je došlo do blokade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8256">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Which video card rendering call Office was in when the hang occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8257">**Data\_Timeout** – trajanje blokade ako je došlo do oporavka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8257">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted, if it recovered</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8258">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** – je li obično moguće oporaviti se od blokade u ovoj vizualizacijskoj naredbi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8258">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Whether the hang in this video card rendering command is typically recoverable.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32localblocklistactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8259">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8259">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistActivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8260">Pojedinosti o upravljačkom programu korisnikove grafičke kartice koji je uzrokovao veći broj nedavnih rušenja aplikacija sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8260">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8261">Office neće koristiti tu grafičku karticu u ovoj sesiji sustava Office (umjesto nje koristit će softversku vizualizaciju) dok se upravljački program ne ažurira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8261">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8262">Obavještava Microsoft o upravljačkim programima grafičke kartice koji uzrokuju probleme u sustavu Office radi prepoznavanja trendova i analize utjecaja takvih upravljačkih programa na korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8262">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8263">Microsoftu govori koliko je korisnika u tom suboptimalnom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8263">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this suboptimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8264">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8264">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8265">**Data.AllAppsBlocked** – jesu li sve aplikacije sustava Office na popisu za blokiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8265">**Data.AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8266">**Data.BlockedDeviceId** – identifikator uređaja grafičke kartice koji je blokiran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8266">**Data.BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8267">**Data.BlockedDriverVersion** – verzija upravljačkog programa koja je na popisu za blokiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8267">**Data.BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8268">**Data.CrashHistory System.String** – niz koji predstavlja povijest upravljačkog programa grafičke kartice koji je uzrokovao rušenje, za potrebe analize</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8268">**Data.CrashHistory System.String** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8269">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** – koliko često dolazi do rušenja upravljačkog programa kartice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8269">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32localblocklistdriverupdatedactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8270">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistDriverUpdatedActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8270">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistDriverUpdatedActivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8271">Korisnik je ažurirao upravljački program grafičke kartice koji je prije uzrokovao rušenje sustava Office te se zbog toga više ne koristi za vizualizaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8271">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8272">Obavještava Microsoft da su korisnici koji su jednom bili u neoptimalnom stanju prikazivanja ponovno u preporučenom stanju prikazivanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8272">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a suboptimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8273">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8273">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8274">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** – identifikator uređaja grafičke kartice koji je na popisu za blokiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8274">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8275">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** – verzija upravljačkog programa koja je na popisu za blokiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8275">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8276">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** – verzija ažuriranog upravljačkog programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8276">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officegraphicsspritememcorrupt"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8277">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8277">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8278">Izvješćuje o svim otkrivenim pogreškama u telemetriji obračuna memorije sprajtova.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8278">Reports any errors detected in the sprite memory accounting telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8279">Ključno za procjenu stanja telemetrije korištenja grafičke memorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8279">Critical for assessing health of the graphics memory usage telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8280">Taj je podatak potreban za provjeru ispravnosti naše telemetrije za SpriteMem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8280">This information is needed to validate the correctness of our SpriteMem telemetry.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8281">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8281">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8282">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** – ukupna količina memorije aktivno dodijeljene čuvanju sprajtova (slika) iz kojih nastaje sadržaj zaslona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8282">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** - Total amount of memory that is actively allocated to hold sprites (images) that result in screen content.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8283">**Data\_Function** – naziv funkcije koja pokušava osloboditi memoriju za sprajtove.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8283">**Data\_Function** - The name of the function that is attempting to release sprite memory.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8284">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** – količina memorije koja više neće biti dodijeljena sprajtovima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8284">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** - Amount of memory to be removed from sprite allocation.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharednointernetconnectivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8285">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8285">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8286">Prikuplja se kad god PowerPoint otkrije da nema internetske veze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8286">Collected whenever PowerPoint detects there is no internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8287">Microsoft koristi te podatke da bi prikupio dijagnostičke podatke o korisnikovoj internetskoj vezi i razumio kako to utječe na povezivanje sa servisima sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8287">Microsoft uses this data to get diagnostic information about the user's internet connection to be able to understand how that impacts connectivity to Office services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8288">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8288">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8289">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** – pokazuje jesmo li stanje internetske veze dobili prilikom pozivanja servisa Nexus (vrijednost „istinito”) ili API poziva generičkom web-servisu (vrijednost „neistinito”)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8289">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** - shows whether we got the Internet connectivity status when calling Nexus service (value true) or when calling generic web service API call (value false)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerofficesvcmgrprofile"></a><span data-ttu-id="8046f-8290">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8290">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8291">Taj se događaj aktivira kada se pokrene upravitelj uslužnosti sustava Office i presudan je za pružanje točnih uvida u vezi sa statusom implementacije i rušenjem aplikacija i dodataka unutar sustava kupca omogućujući nam generiranje uvida u to da IT administrator može pouzdano uvoditi ažuriranja za njihove poslovne strojeve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8291">This event is triggered when Office Serviceability Manager starts, and is critical for providing accurate insights related to Deployment Status and Application and Add-in crashes within customer's tenant by allowing us to generate insights for the IT Admin to be able to confidently roll out updates for their enterprise machines.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="8046f-8292">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8292">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8293">**DeviceIdJoinToken** – koristi se za spajanje podataka telemetrije iz stanja sustava i stanja implementacije s drugim funkcionalnim podacima koji se prikupljaju putem cjevovoda za usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8293">**DeviceIdJoinToken** - used to join Telemetry data from Health and Deployment Status with other Functional Data, which is collected via the Services pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8046f-8294">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** – Booleova zastavica koja se koristi za određivanje broja upravljanih uređaja u sustavu Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8046f-8294">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** - a Boolean flag used to determine the number of Managed devices in the Office eco-system.</span></span>
